  line `26. Property owned by co-owners.`
  line `27. “Owner of house property”, “annual charge”, etc., defined.`
  line `D. — Profits and gains of business or profession`
  line `28. Profits and gains of business or profession.`
  line `29. Income from profits and gains of business or profession, how computed.`
