  line `79. Carry forward and set off of losses in case of certain companies.`
  line `80. Submission of return for losses.`
  line `CHAPTER VI-A`
  line `D EDUCTIONS TO BE MADE IN COMPUTING`
  line `TOTAL INCOME`
  line `A. — General`
  line `80A. Deductions to be made in computing total income.`
  line `80AA. [ Omitted. ].`
