  line `273AA. Power of Principal Commissioner or Commissioner to grant immunity from penalty.`
  line `273B. Penalty not to be imposed in certain cases.`
  line `274. Procedure.`
  line `275. Bar of limitation for imposing penalties.`
  line `CHAPTER XXII`
  line `O FFENCES AND PROSECUTIONS`
  line `275A. Contravention of order made under sub-section ( 3 ) of section 132.`
  line `275B. Failure to comply with the provisions of clause ( iib ) of sub-section ( 1 ) of section 132.`
