obj_root_law_sections_31_content:
  string
  line 31
  line `( A ) in any area which is comprised within the jurisdiction of a municipality`
  line `(whether known as a municipality, municipal corporation, notified area committee,`
  line `town area committee, town committee or by any other name) or a cantonment board`
  line `and which has a population of not less than ten thousand 1 ***; or`
  line `2 [( B ) in any area within the distance, measured aerially, —`
  line `( I ) not being more than two kilometres, from the local limits of any`
  line `municipality or cantonment board referred to in item (A) and which has a`
  line `population of more than ten thousand but not exceeding one lakh; or`
  line `( II ) not being more than six kilometres, from the local limits of any`
  line `municipality or cantonment board referred to in item (A) and which has a`
  line `population of more than one lakh but not exceeding ten lakh; or`
  line `( III ) not being more than eight kilometres, from the local limits of any`
  line `municipality or cantonment board referred to in item (A) and which has a`
  line `population of more than ten lakh.]`
  line `3 [ Explanation 4 [1.] — For the removal of doubts, it is hereby declared that revenue derived`
  line `from land shall not include and shall be deemed never to have included any income arising from`
  line `the transfer of any land referred to in item (a) or item (b) of sub-clause ( iii ) of clause ( 14 ) of this`
  line section.]
  line `5 [ Explanation 2. — For the removal of doubts, it is hereby declared that income derived from`
  line `any building or land referred to in sub-clause ( c ) arising from the use of such building or land for`
  line `any purpose (including letting for residential purpose or for the purpose of any business or`
  line `profession) other than agriculture falling under sub-clause ( a ) or sub-clause ( b ) shall not be`
  line `agricultural income.]`
  line `6 [ Explanation 3. — For the purposes of this clause, any income derived from saplings or`
  line `seedlings grown in a nursery shall be deemed to be agricultural income.]`
  line `7 [ Explanation 4. — For the purposes of clause ( ii ) of the proviso to sub-clause ( c ),`
  line `“ population ” means the population according to the last preceding census of which the relevant`
  line `figures have been published before the first day of the previous year;]`
  line `8 [ 9 [( 1B )] “ amalgamation ”, in relation to companies, means the merger of one or more companies`
  line `with another company or the merger of two or more companies to form one company (the company`
  line `or companies which so merge being referred to as the amalgamating company or companies and the`
  line `company with which they merge or which is formed as a result of the merger, as the amalgamated`
  line `company) in such a manner that —`
  line `( i ) all the property of the amalgamating company or companies immediately before the`
  line `amalgamation becomes the property of the amalgamated company by virtue of the amalgamation;`
  line `( ii ) all the liabilities of the amalgamating company or companies immediately before the`
  line `amalgamation become the liabilities of the amalgamated company by virtue of the amalgamation;`
  line `1. Certain words omitted by Act 17 of 2013, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-2014).`
  line `2. Subs. by s. 3, ibid., for item ( B ) (w.e.f. 1-4-2014).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 13 of 1989, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-1970).`
  line `4. Explanation renumbered as Explanation 1 thereof by Act 10 of 2000, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-2001).`
  line `5. Ins. by s. 3, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-2001).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 18 of 2008, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-2009).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 17 of 2013, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-2014).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 20 of 1967, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-4-1967).`
  line `9. Clause ( 1A ) renumbered as clause ( 1B ) thereof by Act 4 of 1988, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
