obj_root_law_sections_34_content:
  string
  line 34
  line `( 14 ) 1 [ “ capital asset ” means —`
  line `( a ) property of any kind held by an assessee, whether or not connected with his business or`
  line profession;
  line `( b ) any securities held by a Foreign Institutional Investor which has invested in such`
  line `securities in accordance with the regulations made under the Securities and Exchange Board of`
  line `India Act, 1992 (15 of 1992),`
  line `but does not include —`
  line `( i ) any stock-in-trade [other than the securities referred to in sub-clause ( b )]], consumable`
  line `stores or raw materials held for the purposes of his business or profession;`
  line `2 [( ii ) personal effects, that is to say, movable property (including wearing apparel and`
  line `furniture) held for personal use by the assessee or any member of his family dependant on him,`
  line `but excludes —`
  line `( a ) jewellery;`
  line `( b ) archaeological collections;`
  line `( c ) drawings;`
  line `( d ) paintings;`
  line `( e ) sculptures; or`
  line `( f ) any work of art.`
  line `Explanation 3 [1]. — For the purposes of this sub-clause, “ jewellery ” includes —`
  line `( a ) ornaments made of gold, silver, platinum or any other precious metal or any alloy`
  line `containing one or more of such precious metals, whether or not containing any precious`
  line `or semi-precious stone, and whether or not worked or sewn into any wearing apparel;`
  line `( b ) precious or semi-precious stones, whether or not set in any furniture, utensil or`
  line `other article or worked or sewn into any wearing apparel.]`
  line `4 [ Explanation 2. — For the purposes of this clause —`
  line `( a ) the expression “ Foreign Institutional Investor ” shall have the meaning assigned to`
  line `it in clause ( a ) of the Explanation to section 115AD;`
  line `( b ) the expression “ securities ” shall have the meaning assigned to it in clause ( h ) of`
  line `section 2 of the Securities Contracts (Regulation) Act, 1956 (42 of 1956);]`
  line `5 [( iii ) agricultural land in India, not being land situate —`
  line `( a ) in any area which is comprised within the jurisdiction of a municipality (whether`
  line `known as a municipality, municipal corporation, notified area committee, town area`
  line `committee, town committee, or by any other name) or a cantonment board and which has a`
  line `population of not less than ten thousand 6 ***; or`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 25 of 2014, s. 3, for certain words (w.e.f. 1-4-2015).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 22 of 2007, s. 3, for clause ( ii ) (w.e.f. 1-4-2008).`
  line `3. Explanation renumbered as Explanation 1 thereof by Act 25 of 2014, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-2015).`
  line `4. Ins. by s. 3, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-2015).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 19 of 1970, s. 3, for sub-clause ( iii ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1970).`
  line `6. The words “acco rding to the last preceding census of which the relevant figures have been published before the first day`
  line `of the previous year” omitted by Act 17 of 2013, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1 -4-2014).`
