obj_root_law_sections_36_content:
  string
  line 36
  line `1 [( 15A ) “ Chief Commissioner ” means a person appointed to be a Chief Commissioner of Income-`
  line `tax or a Principal Chief Commissioner of Income-tax under sub-section ( 1 ) of section 117;]`
  line `2 [ 3 [( 15B )] “ child ”, in relation to an individual, includes a step-child and an adopted child of that`
  line individual;]
  line `4 [( 16 ) “ Commissioner ” means a person appointed to be a Commissioner of Income-tax or a`
  line `Director of Income-tax or a Principal Commissioner of Income-tax or a Principal Director of`
  line `Income-tax under sub-section ( 1 ) of section 117;]`
  line `5 [( 16A ) “ Commissioner (Appeals) ” means a person appointed to be a Commissioner of Income-`
  line `tax (Appeals) under sub-section ( 1 ) of section 117;]`
  line `6 [( 17 ) “ company ” means —`
  line `( i ) any Indian company, or`
  line `( ii ) any body corporate incorporated by or under the laws of a country outside India, or`
  line `( iii ) any institution, association or body which is or was assessable or was assessed as a`
  line `company for any assessment year under the Indian Income-tax Act, 1922 (11 of 1922), or which`
  line `is or was assessable or was assessed under this Act as a company for any assessment year`
  line `commencing on or before the 1st day of April, 1970, or`
  line `( iv ) any institution, association or body, whether incorporated or not and whether Indian or`
  line `non-Indian, which is declared by general or special order of the Board to be a company:`
  line `Provided that such institution, association or body shall be deemed to be a company only for such`
  line `assessment year or assessment years (whether commencing before the 1st day of April, 1971, or on or`
  line `after that date) as may be specified in the declaration;]`
  line `( 18 ) “ company in which the public are substantially interested ”— a company is said to be a`
  line `company in which the public are substantially interested —`
  line `7 [( a ) if it is a company owned by the Government or the Reserve Bank of India or in which`
  line `not less than forty per cent.. of the shares are held (whether singly or taken together) by the`
  line `Government or the Reserve Bank of India or a corporation owned by that bank; or]`
  line `8 [( aa ) if it is a company which is registered under section 25 of the Companies`
  line `Act, 1956 (1 of 1956); or]`
  line `( ab ) if it is a company having no share capital and if, having regard to its objects, the nature`
  line `and composition of its membership and other relevant considerations, it is declared by order of`
  line `the Board to be a company in which the public are substantially interested:`
  line `Provided that such company shall be deemed to be a company in which the public are`
  line `substantially interested only for such assessment year or assessment years (whether commencing`
  line `before the 1st day of April, 1971, or on or after that date) as may be specified in the declaration;`
  line or]
  line `1. Subs. by Act 25 of 2014, s. 3, for clause ( 15A ) (w.e.f. 1-6-2013).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 41 of 1975, s. 2 (w.e.f. 1-4-1976).`
  line `3. Clause ( 15A ) renumbered as clause ( 15B ) thereof by Act 4 of 1988, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-1988).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 25 of 2014, s. 3, for clause ( 16 ) (w.e.f. 1-6-2013).`
  line `5. Ins. by the Act 29 of 1977, s. 39 and the Fifth Schedule (w.e.f. 10-7-1978).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 32 of 1971, s. 3, for clause ( 17 ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1971).`
  line `7. Subs. by Act 5 of 1964, s. 4, for sub-clause ( a ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1964).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 32 of 1971, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-1971).`
