  content obj_root_law_sections_38_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_38_footnotes
  sourcePage 38
obj_root_law_sections_38_content:
  string
  line 38
  line `( ii ) all the liabilities relatable to the undertaking, being transferred by the demerged company,`
  line `immediately before the demerger, become the liabilities of the resulting company by virtue of the`
  line demerger;
  line `( iii ) the property and the liabilities of the undertaking or undertakings being transferred by the`
  line `demerged company are transferred at values appearing in its books of account immediately before`
  line `the demerger;`
  line `( iv ) the resulting company issues, in consideration of the demerger, its shares to the`
  line `shareholders of the demerged company on a 1 [proportionate basis except where the resulting`
  line `company itself is a shareholder of the demerged company];`
  line `( v ) the shareholders holding not less than three-fourths in value of the shares in the demerged`
  line `company (other than shares already held therein immediately before the demerger, or by a`
  line `nominee for, the resulting company or, its subsidiary) become share-holders of the resulting`
  line `company or companies by virtue of the demerger,`
  line `otherwise than as a result of the acquisition of the property or assets of the demerged company or any`
  line `undertaking thereof by the resulting company;`
  line `( vi ) the transfer of the undertaking is on a going concern basis;`
  line `( vii ) the demerger is in accordance with the conditions, if any, notified under sub-section ( 5 )`
  line `of section 72A by the Central Government in this behalf.`
  line `Explanation 1. — For the purposes of this clause, “ undertaking ” shall include any part of an`
  line `undertaking, or a unit or division of an undertaking or a business activity taken as a whole, but does`
  line `not include individual assets or liabilities or any combination thereof not constituting a business`
  line activity.
  line `Explanation 2. — For the purposes of this clause, the liabilities referred to in sub-clause ( ii ), shall`
  line `include —`
  line `( a ) the liabilities which arise out of the activities or operations of the undertaking;`
  line `( b ) the specific loans or borrowings (including debentures) raised, incurred and utilised solely`
  line `for the activities or operations of the undertaking; and`
  line `( c ) in cases, other than those referred to in clause ( a ) or clause ( b ), so much of the amounts of`
  line `general or multipurpose borrowings, if any, of the demerged company as stand in the same`
  line `proportion which the value of the assets transferred in a demerger bears to the total value of the`
  line `assets of such demerged company immediately before the demerger.`
  line `Explanation 3. — For determining the value of the property referred to in sub-clause ( iii ), any`
  line `change in the value of assets consequent to their revaluation shall be ignored.`
  line `Explanation 4. — For the purposes of this clause, the splitting up or the reconstruction of any`
  line `authority or a body constituted or established under a Central, State or Provincial Act, or a local`
  line `authority or a public sector company, into separate authorities or bodies or local authorities or`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 3, for “proportionate basis” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2013).`
obj_root_law_sections_38_footnotes:
  string
