  line `sub-section ( 1 ) of section 80F” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1989).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 21 of 2006, s. 3, for certain words, brackets, figures and letters (w.e.f. 1-4-2007). Earlier certain words`
  line `inserted by s. 3, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-1999).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 33 of 2009, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-2010).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 3 of 1989, s. 2 (w.e.f. 1-4-1962).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 44 of 1980, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-1980).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 12 of 1990, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4- 1962).`
