  line 43
  line `1 [( vb ) any sum chargeable to income-tax under clause ( iiib ) of section 28;]`
  line `2 [( vc ) any sum chargeable to income-tax under clause ( iiic ) of section 28;]`
  line `3 [( vd )] the value of any benefit or perquisite taxable under clause ( iv ) of section 28;`
  line `4 [( ve ) any sum chargeable to income-tax under clause ( v ) of section 28;]`
  line `( vi ) any capital gains chargeable under section 45;`
  line `( vii ) the profits and gains of any business of insurance carried on by a mutual insurance`
  line `company or by a co-operative society, computed in accordance with section 44 or any surplus`
  line `taken to be such profits and gains by virtue of provisions contained in the First Schedule;`
  line `5 [( viia ) the profits and gains of any business of banking (including providing credit facilities)`
  line `carried on by a co-operative society with its members;]`
  line `6 * * * * *`
  line `7 [( ix ) any winnings from lotteries, crossword puzzles, races including horse races, card games`
  line `and other games of any sort or from gambling or betting of any form or nature whatsoever.]`
  line `8 [ Explanation. — For the purposes of this sub-clause, —`
  line `( i ) “lottery” includes winnings from prizes awarded to any person by draw of lots or by`
  line `chance or in any other manner whatsoever, under any scheme or arrangement by whatever`
  line `name called;`
  line `( ii ) “card game and other game of any sort” includes any game show, an entertainment`
  line `programme on television or electronic mode, in which people compete to win prizes or any`
  line `other similar game;]`
  line `9 [( x ) any sum received by the assessee from his employees as contributions to any provident`
  line `fund or superannuation fund or any fund set up under the provisions of the Employees’ State`
  line `Insurance Act, 1948 (34 of 1948), or any other fund for the welfare of such employees;]`
  line `10 [( xi ) any sum received under a Keyman insurance policy including the sum allocated by`
  line `way of bonus on such policy.`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this clause, the express ion “Keyman insurance policy”`
  line `shall have the meaning assigned to it in the Explanation to clause ( 10D ) ofsection 10;]`
  line `11 [( xii ) any sum referred to in 12 [clause ( va ) of section 28;]`
  line `13 [( xiia ) the fair market value of inventory referred to in clause ( via ) of section 28;]`
  line `14 [( xiii ) any sum referred to in clause ( v ) of sub-section ( 2 ) of section 56;]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 12 of 1990, s. 3 (w.r.e.f. 1-4-1967).`
