  line `4. Ins. by Act 18 of 1992, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-1993).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 21 of 2006, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-2007).`
  line `6. Clause ( viii ) omitted by Act 26 of 1988, s. 54 (w.e.f. 1-4-1988).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 16 of 1972, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-1972).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 14 of 2001, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-2002).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 11 of 1987, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-1988).`
  line `10. Ins. by Act 33 of 1996, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-10-1996).`
