  line `5 [( xvii ) any sum of money referred to in clause ( ix ) of sub-section ( 2 ) of section 56;]`
  line `6 [( xviia ) any sum of money or value of property referred to in clause ( x ) of sub-section ( 2 )`
  line `section 56;]`
  line `7 [( xviib ) any compensation or other payment referred to in clause ( xi ) of sub-section ( 2 ) of`
  line `section 56;]`
  line `8 [( xviii ) assistance in the form of a subsidy or grant or cash incentive or duty drawback or`
  line `waiver or concession or reimbursement (by whatever name called) by the Central Government or`
  line `a State Government or any authority or body or agency in cash or kind to the assessee 9 [other`
  line `than, —`
  line `( a ) the subsidy or grant or reimbursement which is taken into account for determination`
  line `of the actual cost of the asset in accordance with the provisions of Explanation 10 to`
  line `clause ( 1 ) of section 43; or`
  line `( b ) the subsidy or grant by the Central Government for the purpose of the corpus of a`
  line `trust or institution established by the Central Government or a State Government, as the`
  line `case may be];]`
  line `( 25 ) “Income - tax Officer” means a person appointed to be an Income -tax Officer under`
  line `10 *** section 117;`
  line `11 [( 25A ) “India” means the territory of India as referred to in article 1 of the Constitution, its`
  line `territorial waters, seabed and subsoil underlying such waters, continental shelf, exclusive economic`
  line `zone or any other maritime zone as referred to in the Territorial Waters, Continental Shelf, Exclusive`
  line `Economic Zone and other Maritime Zones Act, 1976 (80 of 1976), and the air space above its`
  line `territory and territorial waters;]`
  line `( 26 ) “Indian company” means a company formed and registered under the Companies Act, 1956`
  line `(1 of 1956), and includes —`
  line `( i ) a company formed and registered under any law relating to companies formerly in force`
  line `in any part of India 12 [other than the State of Jammu and Kashmir and the Union territories`
  line `specified in sub-clause ( iii ) of this clause];`
  line `13 [( ia ) a corporation established by or under a Central, State or Provincial Act;`
  line `( ib ) any institution, association or body which is declared by the Board to be a company`
  line `under clause ( 17 );]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 22 of 2007, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-2007).`
