  line `determination of the actual cost of the asset in accordance with the provisions of Explanation 10 to clause ( 1 ) of`
  line `section 43” by s. 3 (w.e.f. 1 -4-2017).`
  line `10. The words, brackets a nd figures “sub -section ( 1 ) of” omitted by Act 3 of 1989, s. 2 (w.e.f. 1 -4-1988).`
  line `11. Subs. by Act 22 of 2007, s. 3, for clause ( 25A ) (w.e.f. 25-8-1976).`
