  line `( ii ) in the case of the State of Jammu and Kashmir, a company formed and registered under`
  line `any law for the time being in force in that State;`
  line `1 [( iii ) in the case of any of the Union territories of Dadra and Nagar Haveli, Goa, Daman and`
  line `Diu, and Pondicherry, a company formed and registered under any law for the time being in force`
  line `in that Union territory:]`
  line `Provided that the 2 [registered or, as the case may be, principal office of the company,`
  line `corporation, institution, association or body] in all cases is in India;`
  line `3 [( 26A ) “infrastructure capital company” means such company which makes investments by way`
  line `of acquiring shares or providing long-term finance to any enterprise or undertaking wholly engaged in`
  line `the business referred to in sub-section ( 4 ) of section 80-IA or sub-section ( 1 ) of section 80-IAB or an`
  line `undertaking developing and building a housing project referred to in sub-section ( 10 ) of`
  line `section 80-IB or a project for constructing a hotel of not less than three-star category as classified by`
  line `the Central Government or a project for constructing a hospital with at least one hundred beds for`
  line patients;
  line `( 26B ) “infrastructure capital fund” means such fund operating under a trust deed registered under`
  line `the provisions of the Registration Act, 1908 (16 of 1908) established to raise monies by the trustees`
  line `for investment by way of acquiring shares or providing long-term finance to any enterprise or`
  line `undertaking wholly engaged in the business referred to in sub-section ( 4 ) of section 80-IA or`
  line `sub-section ( 1 ) of section 80-IAB or an undertaking developing and building a housing project`
  line `referred to in sub-section ( 10 ) of section 80-IB or a project for constructing a hotel of not less than`
  line `three-star category as classified by the Central Government or a project for constructing a hospital`
  line `with at least one hundred beds for patients;]`
  line `4 * * * * *`
  line `( 28 ) “Inspector of Income - tax” means a person appointed to be an Inspector of Income -tax under`
  line `5 [sub-section ( 1 )] of section 117;`
  line `6 [( 28A ) “interest” means interest payable in any manner in respect of any moneys borrowed or`
  line `debt incurred (including a deposit, claim or other similar right or obligation) and includes any service`
  line `fee or other charge in respect of the moneys borrowed or debt incurred or in respect of any credit`
  line `facility which has not been utilised;`
  line `7 [( 28B ) “interest on securities” means,—`
  line `( i ) interest on any security of the Central Government or a State Government;`
  line `( ii ) interest on debentures or other securities for money issued by or on behalf of a local`
  line `authority or a company or a corporation established by a Central, State or Provincial Act;]`
  line `1. Ins. by the Taxation Laws (Extension to Union Territories) Regulation, 1963 (Reg. 3 of 1963), s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-1963).`
  line `2. Subs. b y Act 32 of 1971, s. 3, for “registered office of the company” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1971).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 21 of 2006, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-2006).`
  line `4. Clause ( 27 ) omitted by Act 4 of 1988, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-1988).`
  line `5. Subs. by s. 3, ibid., for “sub - section (2)” (w.e.f. 1-4-1988).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 66 of 1976, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-6-1976).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 26 of 1988, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
