  line `of registration under section 3 of that Act;]`
  line `2 [( 28C ) “Joint Commissioner” means a person appointed to be a Joint Commissioner of`
  line `Income-tax or an Additional Commissioner of Income-tax under sub-section ( 1 ) of section 117;`
  line `( 28D ) “Joint Director” means a person appointed to be a Joint Director of Income -tax or an`
  line `Additional Director of Income-tax under sub-section ( 1 ) of section 117;]`
  line `( 29 ) “legal representative” has the meaning ass igned to it in clause ( 11 ) of section 2 of the Code`
  line `of Civil Procedure, 1908 (5 of 1908);`
  line `3 [( 29A ) “long - term capital asset” means a capital asset which is not a short -term capital asset;`
  line `( 29B ) “long - term capital gain” means capital gain arising from the tr ansfer of a long-term capital`
  line asset;]
  line `4 [( 29BA ) “manufacture”, with its grammatical variations, means a change in a non -living physical`
  line `object or article or thing, —`
  line `( a ) resulting in transformation of the object or article or thing into a new and distinct object`
  line `or article or thing having a different name, character and use; or`
  line `( b ) bringing into existence of a new and distinct object or article or thing with a different`
  line `chemical composition or integral structure;]`
  line `5 [( 29C ) “maximum marginal rate” means the rate of income -tax (including surcharge on`
  line `income-tax, if any) applicable in relation to the highest slab of income in the case of an individual`
  line `6 [, association of persons or, as the case may be, body of individuals] as specified in the Finance`
  line `Act of the relevant year;]`
  line `7 [( 29D ) “National Tax Tribunal” means the National Tax Tribunal established under section 3`
  line `of the National Tax Tribunal Act, 2005;]`
  line `( 30 ) “non - resident” means a person who is not a “resident” 8 [, and for the purposes of`
  line `sections 92, 93 9 *** and 168, includes a person who is not ordinarily resident within the meaning of`
  line `clause ( 6 ) of section 6;`
  line `( 31 ) “person” includes—`
  line `( i ) an individual,`
  line `( ii ) a Hindu undivided family,`
