  line 48
  line `( 37 ) “ public servant” has the same meaning as in section 21 of the Indian Penal Code (45 of`
  line `1860);`
  line `1 [( 37A ) “rate or rates in force” or “rates in force”, in relation to an assessment year or f inancial`
  line `year, means —`
  line `( i ) for the purposes of calculating income-tax under the first proviso to sub-section ( 5 )`
  line `of section 132, or computing the income-tax chargeable under sub-section ( 4 ) of section 172 or`
  line `sub-section ( 2 ) of section 174 or section 175 or sub-section ( 2 ) of section 176 or deducting`
  line `income-tax under section 192 from income chargeable under the head “Salaries” 2 *** or`
  line `3 [computation of the “advance tax” payable under Chapter XVIIC 4 [in a case not`
  line `falling under section 115A or 5 [section 115B 6 [or section 115BB or section 115BBB or section`
  line `115E] or section 164 or section 164A 7 *** 8 [or section 167B]]], the rate or rates of income-tax`
  line `specified in this behalf in the Finance Act of the relevant year, and for the purposes of`
  line `computation of the “advance tax” payable under Chapter XVII -C 9 [in a case falling under section`
  line `115A or 10 [section 115B 6 [or section 115BB or section 115BBB or section 115E] or`
  line `section 164 or section 164A 7 *** 8 [or section 167B]], the rate or rates specified in section`
  line `115A or 5 [section 115B 6 [or section 115BB or section 115BBB or section 115E] or section 164`
  line `or section 164A 7 *** 8 [or section 167B ], as the case may be,]] or the rate or rates of income-tax`
  line `specified in this behalf in the Finance Act of the relevant year, whichever is applicable;]`
  line `( ii ) for the purposes of deduction of tax under sections`
  line `193, 194, 11 [194A, 12 [194B, 194BB] 13 [and 194D], the rate or rates of income-tax specified in this`
  line `behalf in the Finance Act of the relevant year;]`
  line `( iii ) for the purposes of deduction of tax under 14 [section 194LBA or] 15 [section`
  line `194LBB or section 194LBC or] section 195, the rate or rates of income-tax specified in this`
  line `behalf in the Finance Act of the relevant year or the rate or rates of income-tax specified in 16 [an`
  line `agreement entered into by the Central Government under section 90, or an agreement notified by`
  line `the Central Government under section 90A, whichever is applicable by virtue of the provisions`
  line `of section 90, or section 90A, as the case may be];]`
  line `( 38 ) “recognised provident fund” means a provident fund which has been and continues to be`
  line `recognised by the 17 [ 18 [Principal Chief Commissioner or Chief Commissioner] or 18 [Principal`
  line `Commissioner or Commissioner]] in accordance with the rules contained in Part A of the Fourth`
  line `Schedule, and includes a provident fund established under a scheme framed under the Employees ’`
  line `Provident Funds Act, 1952 (19 of 1952);`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 20 of 1967, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-4-1967).`
  line `2. The words, brackets, figures and letters “or sub -section ( 9 ) of section 80E from any payment referred to therein” omitted`
  line `by Act 4 of 1988, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989). Earlier the quoted words were inserted by Act 19 of 1968, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-4-1968).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 19 of 1970, s. 3, for “computation of the “advance tax” payable under Chapter XVII -C, the rate or rates of`
  line `income- tax specified in this behalf in the Finance Act of the relevant year” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1971).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 66 of 1976, s. 3, for “in a case not falling under section 164” (w.e.f. 1 -6-1976).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 4 of 1988, s. 3, for “section 115B or section 164” (w.e.f 1 -4-1988).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 3, for “or section 115BB or section 115E” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2003).`
  line `7. The words, figures and letters “or section 167A” omitted by Act 3 of 1989, s. 2 (w.e.f. 1 -4-1989).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 4 of 1988, s. 2 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `9. Subs.by Act 66 of 1976, s. 3, for “in a case falling under section 164, the rate specified in that section” (w.e.f. 1 -6-1976).`
  line `10. Subs. by Act 4 of 1988, s. 3, for “section 115B or, as the case may be, section 164” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1988).`
  line `11. Subs. by Act 16 of 1972, s. 3, for “194A” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1972).`
  line `12. Subs. by Act 19 of 1978, s. 32, for “194B,” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1978).`
  line `13. Subs. by Act 49 of 1991, s. 3, for “, 194D and 195” (w.e.f. 1 -10-1991).`
  line `14. Ins. by Act 20 of 2015, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-2016).`
  line `15. Ins. by Act 28 of 2016, s.3 (w.ef. 1-6-2016).`
  line `16. Subs. by Act 21 of 2006, s. 3, for “an agreement entered into by the Central Government under section 90, whichever is`
  line `applicable by virtue of the provisions of section 90” (w.e.f. 1 -6-2006).`
  line `17. Subs. by Act 4 of 1988, s. 2, for “Commissioner” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1988).`
  line `18. Subs. by Act 25 of 2014, s. 4, for “Commissioner” (w. e.f. 1-6-2013).`
