  line 49
  line `1 * * * * *`
  line `( 40 ) “regular assessment” means the assessment m ade under 2 [sub-section ( 3 ) of`
  line `section 143] or section 144;`
  line `( 41 ) “relative”, in relation to an individual, means the husband, wife, brother or sister or any`
  line `lineal ascendant or descendant of that individual;`
  line `3 [( 41A ) “resulting company” means one or more companies (including a wholly owned subsidiary`
  line `thereof) to which the undertaking of the demerged company is transferred in a demerger and, the`
  line `resulting company in consideration of such transfer of undertaking, issues shares to the shareholders`
  line `of the demerged company and includes any authority or body or local authority or public sector`
  line `company or a company established, constituted or formed as a result of demerger;]`
  line `( 42 ) “resident” means a person who is resident in India within the meaning of section 6;`
  line `4 [( 42A ) 5 [“short - term capital asset” means a capital asset held by an assessee for not more than`
  line `6 [thirty-sixmonths] immediately preceding the date of its transfer:]]`
  line `7 [Provided that in the case of 8 [a security (other than a unit) listed in a recognised stock exchange`
  line `in India] 9 [or a unit of the Unit Trust of India established under the Unit Trust of India Act, 1963 (52`
  line `of 1963) or 10 [a unit of an equity oriented fund]] 11 [or a zero coupon bond], the provisions of this`
  line `clause shall have effect as if for the words “thirty - six months”, the words “twelve months” had been`
  line `substituted:]`
  line `12 [Provided further that in case of a share of a company (not being a share listed in a recognised`
  line `stock exchange) or a unit of a Mutual Fund specified under clause ( 23D ) of section 10, which is`
  line `transferred during the period beginning on the 1st day of April, 2014 and ending on the 10th day of`
  line `July, 2014, the provisions of this clause shall have effect as if for the words “thirty - six months”, the`
  line `words “twelve months” had been substituted:]`
  line `13 [Provided also that in the case of a share of a company (not being a share listed in a recognised`
  line `stock exchange in India), 14 [or an immovable property, being land or building or both] the provisions`
  line `of this clause shall have effect as if for the words “thirty - six months”, the words “twenty -four`
  line `months” had been substituted.]`
  line `15 [ Explanation 1 ]. — ( i ) In determining the period for which any capital asset is held by the`
  line `assessee —`
  line `( a ) in the case of a share held in a company in liquidation, there shall be excluded the period`
  line `subsequent to the date on which the company goes into liquidation;`
  line `1. Clause ( 39 ) omitted by Act 18 of 1992, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-1993). Earlier clause ( 39 ) substituted by Act 36 of 1989, s. 2`
  line `(w.e.f. 1-4-1989) which was later omitted by Act 4 of 1988, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989) and again restored by Act 3 of 1989, s.`
  line `95 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 12 of 1990, s. 3, for “section 143” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1989).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 27 of 1999, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-2000).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 20 of 1962, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-1962).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 21 of 1973, s. 3, for certain words (w.e.f. 1-4-1974).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 29 of 1977, s. 3, for “sixty months” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1978).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 11 of 1987, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-1988).`
  line `8. Subs. by Act 25 of 2014, s. 3, for “a share held in a company or any other security listed in a recognized stock exchange`
  line `in India” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2015).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 32 of 1994, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-1995).`
  line `10. Subs. by Act 25 of 2014, s. 3, for “a unit of a Mutual Fund specified under clause ( 23D ) of section 10” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2015)`
  line `11. Ins. by Act 18 of 2005, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-2006).`
  line `12. Ins. by Act 25 of 2014, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-2015).`
  line `13. Ins. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
  line `14. Ins. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 3 (we.f. 1-4-2018).`
  line `15. Existing Explanation renumbered as Explanation 1 by Act 32 of 1994, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-1995).`
