  line 50
  line `( b ) in the case of a capital asset which becomes the property of the assessee in the`
  line `circumstances mentioned in 1 [sub-section ( 1 )] of section 49, there shall be included the period for`
  line `which the asset was held by the previous owner referred to in the said section;`
  line `2 [( ba ) in the case of a capital asset referred to in clause ( via ) of section 28, the period shall be`
  line `reckoned from the date of its conversion or treatment;]`
  line `3 [( c ) in the case of a capital asset being a share or shares in an Indian company, which`
  line `becomes the property of the assessee in consideration of a transfer referred to in clause ( vii )`
  line `of section 47, there shall be included the period for which the share or shares in the amalgamating`
  line `company were held by the assessee;]`
  line `4 [( d ) in the case of a capital asset, being a share or any other security (hereafter in this clause`
  line `referred to as the financial asset) subscribed to by the assessee on the basis of his right to`
  line `subscribe to such financial asset or subscribed to by the person in whose favour the assessee has`
  line `renounced his right to subscribe to such financial asset, the period shall be reckoned from the date`
  line `of allotment of such financial asset;`
  line `( e ) in the case of a capital asset, being the right to subscribe to any financial asset, which is`
  line `renounced in favour of any other person, the period shall be reckoned from the date of the offer of`
  line `such right by the company or institution, as the case may be, making such offer;]`
  line `5 [( f ) in the case of a capital asset, being a financial asset, allotted without any payment and on`
  line `the basis of holding of any other financial asset, the period shall be reckoned from the date of the`
  line `allotment of such financial asset;]`
  line `6 [( g ) in the case of a capital asset, being a share or shares in an Indian company, which`
  line `becomes the property of the assessee in consideration of a demerger, there shall be included the`
  line `period for which the share or shares held in the demerged company were held by the assessee;]`
  line `7 [( h ) in the case of a capital asset, being trading or clearing rights of a recognised stock`
  line `exchange in India acquired by a person pursuant to demutualisation or corporatisation of the`
  line `recognised stock exchange in India as referred to in clause ( xiii ) of section 47, there shall be`
  line `included the period for which the person was a member of the recognised stock exchange in India`
  line `immediately prior to such demutualisation or corporatisation;`
  line `( ha ) in the case of a capital asset, being equity share or shares in a company allotted pursuant`
  line `to demutualisation or corporatisation of a recognised stock exchange in India as referred to in`
  line `clause (x iii ) of section 47, there shall be included the period for which the person was a member`
  line `of the recognised stock exchange in India immediately prior to such demutualisation or`
  line corporatisation;]
  line `1. Subs. by Act 20 of 1967, s. 4, for “clauses ( i ) to ( iii )” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1967).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 13 of 2018, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-2019).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 20 of 1967, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-4-1967).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 32 of 1994, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-1995).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 22 of 1995, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-1996).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 27 of 1999, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-2000).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-2004).`
