  line 51
  line `1 [( hb ) in the case of a capital asset, being any specified security or sweat equity shares`
  line `allotted or transferred, directly or indirectly, by the employer free of cost or at concessional rate`
  line `to his employees (including former employee or employees), the period shall be reckoned from`
  line `the date of allotment or transfer of such specified security or sweat equity shares;]`
  line `2 [( hc ) in the case of a capital asset, being a unit of a business trust, allotted pursuant to`
  line `transfer of share or shares as referred to in clause ( xvii ) of section 47, there shall be included the`
  line `period for which the share or shares were held by the assessee;]`
  line `3 [( hd ) in the case of a capital asset, being a unit or units, which becomes the property of the`
  line `assessee in consideration of a transfer referred to in clause ( xviii ) of section 47, there shall be`
  line `included the period for which the unit or units in the consolidating scheme of the mutual fund`
  line `were held by the assessee;`
  line `( he ) in the case of a capital asset, being share or shares of a company, which is acquired by`
  line `the non-resident assessee on redemption of Global Depository Receipts referred to in clause ( b )`
  line `of sub-section ( 1 ) of section 115AC held by such assessee, the period shall be reckoned from the`
  line `date on which a request for such redemption was made;]`
  line `4 [( hf ) in the case of a capital asset, being equity shares in a company, which becomes the`
  line `property of the assessee in consideration of a transfer referred to in clause ( xb ) of section 47, there`
  line `shall be included the period for which the preference shares were held by the assessee;]`
  line `5 [( hg ) in the case of a capital asset, being a unit or units, which becomes the property of the`
  line `assessee in consideration of a transfer referred to in clause ( xix ) of section 47, there shall be included`
  line `the period for which the unit or units in the consolidating plan of a mutual fund scheme were held by`
  line `the assessee;]`
  line `( ii ) In respect of capital assets other than those mentioned in clause ( i ), the period for which any`
  line `capital asset is held by the assessee shall be determined subject to any ruleswhich the Board may`
  line `make in this behalf.`
  line `6 [ Explanation 2. —For the purposes of this clause, the expression “security” shall have the`
  line `meaning assigned to it in clause ( h ) of section 2 of the Securities Contracts (Regulation) Act, 1956`
  line `(42 of 1956).]`
  line `1 [ Explanation 3. —For the purposes of this clause, the expressions “specified security” and “sweat`
  line `equity shares” shall have the meanings respectively assigned to them in the Explanation to clause ( d )`
  line `of sub-section ( 1 ) of section 115WB.]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 22 of 2007, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-2008).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 25 of 2014, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-10-2014).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 20 of 2015, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-2016).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-2018).`
  line `5. Ins. by s. 3, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 32 of 1994, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-1995).`
