  content obj_root_law_sections_57_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_57_footnotes
  sourcePage 57
obj_root_law_sections_57_content:
  string
  line 57
  line `9. Income deemed to accrue or arise in India. — ( 1 ) The following incomes shall be deemed to`
  line `accrue or arise in India: —`
  line `( i ) all income accruing or arising, whether directly or indirectly, through or from any business`
  line `connection in India, or through or from any property in India, or through or from any asset or source`
  line `of income in India, 1 *** or through the transfer of a capital asset situate in India.`
  line `Explanation 2 [1]. — For the purposes of this clause —`
  line `( a ) in the case of a business of which all the operations are not carried out in India, the`
  line `income of the business deemed under this clause to accrue or arise in India shall be only such part`
  line `of the income as is reasonably attributable to the operations carried out in India;`
  line `( b ) in the case of a non-resident, no income shall be deemed to accrue or arise in India to him`
  line `through or from operations which are confined to the purchase of goods in India for the purpose`
  line `of export;`
  line `3 * * * * *`
  line `4 [( c ) in the case of a non-resident, being a person engaged in the business of running a news`
  line `agency or of publishing newspapers, magazines or journals, no income shall be deemed to accrue`
  line `or arise in India to him through or from activities which are confined to the collection of news`
  line `and views in India for transmission out of India;]`
  line `5 [( d ) in the case of a non-resident, being —`
  line `( 1 ) an individual who is not a citizen of India; or`
  line `( 2 ) a firm which does not have any partner who is a citizen of India or who is resident in`
  line `India; or`
  line `( 3 ) a company which does not have any shareholder who is a citizen of India or who is`
  line `resident in India,`
  line `no income shall be deemed to accrue or arise in India to such individual, firm or company`
  line `through or from operations which are confined to the shooting of any cinematograph film in`
  line India;]
  line `6 [( e ) in the case of a foreign company engaged in the business of mining of diamonds, no`
  line `income shall be deemed to accrue or arise in India to it through or from the activities which are`
  line `confined to the display of uncut and unassorted diamond in any special zone notified by the`
  line `Central Government in the Official Gazette in this behalf.]`
  line `7 [ Explanation 2. — For the removal of doubts, it is hereby declared that “ business connection ”`
  line `shall include any business activity carried out through a person who, acting on behalf of the non-`
  line `resident, —`
  line `1. The words “or through or from any money lent at interest and brought into India in cash or in kind” omitted by`
  line `Act 66 of 1976, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-6-1976).`
  line `2. Explanation renumbered as Explanation 1 thereof by Act 32 of 2003, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-2004).`
  line `3. The proviso omitted by Act 5 of 1964, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-1964).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 11 of 1983, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-4-1962).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 67 of 1984, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-1982).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-2016).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-2004).`
obj_root_law_sections_57_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_58:
  kind page
  sectionId pdf-page-58
