obj_root_law_sections_60_content:
  string
  line 60
  line `( ii ) reporting to persons holding the share or interest,`
  line `then, the period of twelve months ending with the other day shall be the accounting period of the`
  line `company or, as the case may be, the entity:`
  line `Provided further that the first accounting period of the company or, as the case may be, the`
  line `entity shall begin from the date of its registration or incorporation and end with the 31st day of`
  line `March or such other day, as the case may be, following the date of such registration or`
  line `incorporation, and the later accounting period shall be the successive periods of twelve months:`
  line `Provided also that if the company or the entity ceases to exist before the end of accounting`
  line `period, as aforesaid, then, the accounting period shall end immediately before the company or, as`
  line `the case may be, the entity, ceases to exist;`
  line `( d ) “specified date” means the—`
  line `( i ) date on which the accounting period of the company or, as the case may be, the entity`
  line `ends preceding the date of transfer of a share or an interest; or`
  line `( ii ) date of transfer, if the book value of the assets of the company or, as the case may be,`
  line `the entity on the date of transfer exceeds the book value of the assets as on the date referred to`
  line `in sub-clause ( i ), by fifteen per cent.`
  line `Explanation 7. — For the purposes of this clause, —`
  line `( a ) no income shall be deemed to accrue or arise to a non-resident from transfer, outside`
  line `India, of any share of, or interest in, a company or an entity, registered or incorporated outside`
  line `India, referred to in the Explanation 5, —`
  line `( i ) if such company or entity directly owns the assets situated in India and the transferor`
  line `(whether individually or along with its associated enterprises), at any time in the twelve`
  line `months preceding the date of transfer, neither holds the right of management or control in`
  line `relation to such company or entity, nor holds voting power or share capital or interest`
  line `exceeding five per cent. of the total voting power or total share capital or total interest, as the`
  line `case may be, of such company or entity; or`
  line `( ii ) if such company or entity indirectly owns the assets situated in India and the`
  line `transferor (whether individually or along with its associated enterprises), at any time in the`
  line `twelve months preceding the date of transfer, neither holds the right of management or`
  line `control in relation to such company or entity, nor holds any right in, or in relation to, such`
  line `company or entity which would entitle him to the right of management or control in the`
  line `company or entity that directly owns the assets situated in India, nor holds such percentage of`
  line `voting power or share capital or interest in such company or entity which results in holding of`
  line `(either individually or along with associated enterprises) a voting power or share capital or`
  line `interest exceeding five per cent. of the total voting power or total share capital or total`
  line `interest, as the case may be, of the company or entity that directly owns the assets situated in`
  line India;
  line `( b ) in a case where all the assets owned, directly or indirectly, by a company or, as the case`
  line `may be, an entity referred to in the Explanation 5, are not located in India, the income of the`
  line `non-resident transferor, from transfer outside India of a share of, or interest in, such company or`
  line `entity, deemed to accrue or arise in India under this clause, shall be only such part of the income`
  line `as is reasonably attributable to assets located in India and determined in such manner as may be`
  line prescribed;
  line `( c ) “associated enterprise” shall have the meaning assigned to it in section 92A;]`
  line `( ii ) income which fa lls under the head “Salaries”, if it is earned in India.`
  line `1 [ Explanation. — For the removal of doubts, it is hereby declared that the income of the nature`
  line `referred to in this clause payable for —`
  line `( a ) service rendered in India; and`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 27 of 1999, s. 5, for the Explanation (w.e.f. 1-4-2000).`
