  line
obj_root_law_sections_64:
  kind page
  sectionId pdf-page-64
  sectionNo (64)
  orderNo 64
  title `Page 64`
  content obj_root_law_sections_64_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_64_footnotes
  sourcePage 64
obj_root_law_sections_64_content:
  string
  line 64
  line `1 [ 9A. Certain activities not to constitute business connection in India. — ( 1 ) Notwithstanding`
  line `anything contained in sub-section ( 1 ) of section 9 and subject to the provisions of this section, in the case`
  line `of an eligible investment fund, the fund management activity carried out through an eligible fund`
  line `manager acting on behalf of such fund shall not constitute business connection in India of the said fund.`
  line `( 2 ) Notwithstanding anything contained insection 6, an eligible investment fund shall not be said to`
  line `be resident in India for the purpose of that section merely because the eligible fund manager, undertaking`
  line `fund management activities on its behalf, is situated in India.`
  line `( 3 ) The eligible investment fund referred to in sub-section ( 1 ), means a fund established or`
  line `incorporated or registered outside India, which collects funds from its members for investing it for their`
  line `benefit and fulfils the following conditions, namely: —`
  line `( a ) the fund is not a person resident in India;`
  line `( b ) the fund is a resident of a country or a specified territory with which an agreement referred to`
  line `in sub-section ( 1 ) of section 90 or sub-section ( 1 ) ofsection 90A has been entered into 2 [or is`
  line `established or incorporated or registered in a country or a specified territory notified by the Central`
  line `Government in this behalf];`
  line `( c ) the aggregate participation or investment in the fund, directly or indirectly, by persons`
  line `resident in India does not exceed five per cent. of the corpus of the fund;`
  line `( d ) the fund and its activities are subject to applicable investor protection regulations in the`
  line `country or specified territory where it is established or incorporated or is a resident;`
  line `( e ) the fund has a minimum of twenty-five members who are, directly or indirectly, not connected`
  line persons;
  line `( f ) any member of the fund along with connected persons shall not have any participation interest,`
  line `directly or indirectly, in the fund exceeding ten per cent.;`
  line `( g ) the aggregate participation interest, directly or indirectly, of ten or less members along with`
  line `their connected persons in the fund, shall be less than fifty per cent.;`
  line `( h ) the fund shall not invest more than twenty per cent. of its corpus in any entity;`
  line `( i ) the fund shall not make any investment in its associate entity;`
  line `( j ) the monthly average of the corpus of the fund shall not be less than one hundred crore rupees:`
  line `Provided that if the fund has been established or incorporated in the previous year, the corpus of`
  line `fund shall not be less than one hundred crore rupees at the end of such previous year:`
  line `3 [Provided further that nothing contained in this clause shall apply to a fund which has been`
  line `wound up in the previous year;]`
  line `( k ) the fund shall not carry on or control and manage, directly or indirectly, any business in`
  line `India 4 ***;`
  line `( l ) the fund is neither engaged in any activity which constitutes a business connection in India nor`
  line `has any person acting on its behalf whose activities constitute a business connection in India other`
  line `than the activities undertaken by the eligible fund manager on its behalf;`
  line `( m ) the remuneration paid by the fund to an eligible fund manager in respect of fund management`
  line `activity undertaken by him on its behalf is not less than the arm ’ s length price of the said activity:`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 20 of 2015, s. 6 (w.e.f. 1-4-2016).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 6 (w.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
  line `3. The proviso inserted by Act 7 of 2017, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-2016).`
  line `4. The words “or from India” omitted by Act 28 of 2016, s. 6 (w.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
obj_root_law_sections_64_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_65:
  kind page
  sectionId pdf-page-65
  sectionNo (65)
  orderNo 65
  title `Page 65`
  content obj_root_law_sections_65_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_65_footnotes
  sourcePage 65
obj_root_law_sections_65_content:
  string
  line 65
  line `Provided that the conditions specified in clauses ( e ), ( f ) and ( g ) shall not apply in case of an`
  line `investment fund set up by the Government or the Central Bank of a foreign State or a sovereign fund, or`
  line `such other fund as the Central Government may subject to conditions, if any, by notification in the`
  line `Official Gazette, specify in this behalf.`
  line `( 4 ) The eligible fund manager, in respect of an eligible investment fund, means any person who is`
  line `engaged in the activity of fund management and fulfils the following conditions, namely: —`
  line `( a ) the person is not an employee of the eligible investment fund or a connected person of the`
  line fund;
  line `( b ) the person is registered as a fund manager or an investment advisor in accordance with the`
  line `specified regulations;`
  line `( c ) the person is acting in the ordinary course of his business as a fund manager;`
  line `( d ) the person along with his connected persons shall not be entitled, directly or indirectly, to`
  line `more than twenty per cent. of the profits accruing or arising to the eligible investment fund from the`
  line `transactions carried out by the fund through the fund manager.`
  line `( 5 ) Every eligible investment fund shall, in respect of its activities in a financial year, furnish within`
  line `ninety days from the end of the financial year, a statement in the prescribed form, to the prescribed`
  line `income-tax authority containing information relating to the fulfilment of the conditions specified in this`
  line `section and also provide such other relevant information or documents as may be prescribed.`
  line `( 6 ) Nothing contained in this section shall apply to exclude any income from the total income of the`
  line `eligible investment fund, which would have been so included irrespective of whether the activity of the`
  line `eligible fund manager constituted the business connection in India of such fund or not.`
  line `( 7 ) Nothing contained in this section shall have any effect on the scope of total income or`
  line `determination of total income in the case of the eligible fund manager.`
  line `( 8 ) The provisions of this section shall be applied in accordance with such guidelines and in such`
  line `manner as the Board may prescribe in this behalf.`
  line `( 9 ) For the purposes of this section, —`
  line `( a ) “associate” means an entity in which a director or a trustee or a partner or a memb er or a fund`
  line `manager of the investment fund or a director or a trustee or a partner or a member of the fund`
  line `manager of such fund, holds, either individually or collectively, share or interest, being more than`
  line `fifteen per cent. of its share capital or interest, as the case may be;`
  line `( b ) “connected person” shall have the meaning assigned to it in clause ( 4 ) of section 102;`
  line `( c ) “corpus” means the total amount of funds raised for the purpose of investment by the eligible`
  line `investment fund as on a particular date;`
  line `( d ) “entity” means any entity in which an eligible investment fund makes an investment;`
  line `( e ) “specified regulations” means the Securities and Exchange Board of India (Portfolio`
  line `Managers) Regulations, 1993 or the Securities and Exchange Board of India (Investment Advisers)`
  line `Regulations, 2013, or such other regulations made under the Securities and Exchange Board of India`
  line `Act, 1992 (15 of 1992), which may be notified by the Central Government under this clause.]`
  line `CHAPTER III`
  line `I NCOMES WHICH DO NOT FORM PART OF TOTAL INCOME`
  line `10. Incomes not included in total income. — In computing the total income of a previous year of any`
  line `person, any income falling within any of the following clauses shall not be included —`
  line `( 1 ) agricultural income;`
