  line 69
  line `made by the foreign company with Government or the Indian concern after the 31st day of March,`
  line `1976 1 [but before the 1st day of June, 2002] 2 [and, —`
  line `( a ) where the agreement relates to a matter included in the industrial policy, for the time`
  line `being in force, of the Government of India, such agreement is in accordance with that policy; and`
  line `( b ) in any other case, the agreement is approved by the Central Government,`
  line `the tax on such income is payable, under the terms of the agreement, by Government or the Indian`
  line `concern to the Central Government, the tax so paid].`
  line `Explanation. — 3 [For the purposes of this clause and clause ( 6B )], —`
  line `( a ) “fees for technical services” shall have the same meaning as in Explanation 2 to clause`
  line `( vii ) of sub-section ( 1 ) of section 9;`
  line `( b ) “foreign company” shall have the same meaning as in section 80B;`
  line `( c ) “royalty” shall have the same meaning as in Explanation 2 to clause ( vi ) of sub-section ( 1 )`
  line `of section 9;]`
  line `4 [( 6B ) where in the case of a non-resident (not being a company) or of a foreign company`
  line `deriving income (not being salary, royalty or fees for technical services) from Government or an`
  line `Indian concern in pursuance of an 5 [agreement entered into before the 1st day of June, 2002by the`
  line `Central Government] with the Government of a foreign State or an international organisation, the tax`
  line `on such income is payable by Government or the Indian concern to the Central Government under the`
  line `terms of that agreement or any other 6 [related agreement approved before that date] by the Central`
  line `Government, the tax so paid;]`
  line `7 [( 6BB ) where in the case of the Government of a foreign State or a foreign enterprise deriving`
  line `income from an Indian company engaged in the business of operation of aircraft, as a consideration of`
  line `acquiring an aircraft or an aircraft engine (other than payment for providing spares, facilities or`
  line `services in connection with the operation of leased aircraft) on lease under 8 [an agreement entered`
  line `into after the 31st day of March, 1997 but before the 1st day of April, 1999, 9 [or entered into after the`
  line `31st day of March, 2007and approved by the Central Government in this behalf]] and the tax on such`
  line `income is payable by such Indian company under the terms of that agreement to the Central`
  line `Government, the tax so paid.`
  line `Explanation. —For the purposes of this clause, the expression “foreign enterprise” means a person`
  line `who is a non-resident;]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-4-2003).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 18 of 1992, s. 4, for certain words (w.e.f. 1-6-1992).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 26 of 1988, s. 4, for “For the purposes of this clause” (w.e.f. 1-4-1988).`
  line `4. Ins. by s. 4, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-1988).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 4, for “agreement entered into by the Central Government” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2003).`
  line `6. Subs. by s. 4, ibid. for “related agreement approved” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2003).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 26 of 1997, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-1998).`
  line `8. Subs. by Act 23 of 2004, s. 5, for certain words, figures and letters (w.e.f. 1-4-2006).`
  line `9. Subs. by Act 21 of 2006, s. 4, for “or entered into after the 31st day of September, 2006 and approved by the Central`
  line `Go vernment in this behalf” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2007).`
