obj_root_law_sections_73_content:
  string
  line 73
  line `the period of ten months immediately preceding his retirement 1 [whether on superannuation] or`
  line `otherwise, 2 [subject to such limit as the Central Government may, by notification in the Official`
  line `Gazette, specify in this behalf having regard to the limit applicable in this behalf to the employees of`
  line `that Government]:`
  line `Provided that where any such payments are received by an employee from more than one`
  line `employer in the same previous year, the aggregate amount exempt from income-tax under this sub-`
  line `clause 3 [shall not exceed the limit so specified]:`
  line `Provided further that where any such payment or payments was or were received in any one or`
  line `more earlier previous years also and the whole or any part of the amount of such payment or`
  line `payments was or were not included in the total income of the assessee of such previous year or years,`
  line `the amount exempt from income-tax under this sub-clause 3 [shall not exceed the limit so specified],`
  line `as reduced by the amount or, as the case may be, the aggregate amount not included in the total`
  line `income of any such previous year or years.`
  line `4 * * * * *`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of sub-clause ( ii ), —`
  line `5 *** the entitlement to earned leave of an employee shall not exceed thirty days for every year of`
  line `actual service rendered by him as an employee of the employer from whose service he has retired;`
  line `6 * * * * *`
  line `7 [( 10B ) any compensation received by a workman under the Industrial Disputes Act, 1947 (14 of`
  line `1947), or under any other Act or Rules, orders or notifications issued thereunder or under any`
  line `standing orders or under any award, contract of service or otherwise, 8 [at the time of his`
  line `retrenchment:`
  line `Provided that the amount exempt under this clause shall not exceed —`
  line `( i ) an amount calculated in accordance with the provisions of clause ( b ) of section 25F of the`
  line `Industrial Disputes Act, 1947 (14 of 1947); or`
  line `9 [( ii ) such amount, not being less than fifty thousand rupees, as the Central Government may,`
  line `by notification in the Official Gazette, specify in this behalf,]`
  line `whichever is less:`
  line `Provided further that the preceding proviso shall not apply in respect of any compensation`
  line `received by a workman in accordance with any scheme which the Central Government may, having`
  line `regard to the need for extending special protection to the workmen in the undertaking to which such`
  line `scheme applies and other relevant circumstances, approve in this behalf.]`
  line `1. S ubs. by Act 67 of 1984, s. 4 for “on superannuation”(w.e.f. 1 -4-1978).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 4 of 1988, s. 6, for “thirty thousand rupees, whichever is less” (w.e.f. 1 -7-1986).`
  line `3. Subs. by s. 6, ibid., for “shall not exceed thirty thousand rupees” (w.e.f. 1 -7-1986).`
  line `4. The third and fourth provisos omitted by s. 6 ibid. (w.e.f. 1-7-1986).`
  line `5. The brackets and figure “( i )” omitted by s. 6 ibid. (w.e.f. 1-7-1986).`
  line `6. Clause ( ii ) omitted by s. 6, ibid., (w.e.f. 1-7-1986).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 25 of 1975, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-1976).`
  line `8. Subs. by Act 32 of 1985, s. 4, for certain words (w.e.f. 1-4-1986).`
  line `9. Subs. by Act 4 of 1988, s. 6, for sub-clause ( ii ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
