  line 76
  line `1 [( 10D ) any sum received under a life insurance policy, including the sum allocated by way of`
  line `bonus on such policy, other than —`
  line `( a ) any sum received under sub-section ( 3 ) of section 80DD or sub-section ( 3 ) of`
  line `section 80DDA; or`
  line `( b ) any sum received under a Keyman insurance policy; or`
  line `( c ) any sum received under an insurance policy issued on or after the 1st day of April, 2003`
  line `2 [but on or before the 31st day of March, 2012] in respect of which the premium payable for any`
  line `of the years during the term of the policy exceeds twenty per cent. of the actual capital sum`
  line `3 [assured; or]`
  line `4 [( d ) any sum received under an insurance policy issued on or after the 1st day of April, 2012`
  line `in respect of which the premium payable for any of the years during the term of the policy`
  line `exceeds ten per cent. of the actual capital sum assured:]`
  line `Provided that the provisions of 5 [sub-clauses ( c ) and ( d )] shall not apply to any sum received`
  line `on the death of a person:`
  line `Provided further that for the purpose of calculating the actual capital sum assured under`
  line `5 [sub-clause( c )], effect shall be given to the 6 [ Explanation to sub-section ( 3 ) of section 80C or`
  line `the Explanation to sub-section ( 2A ) of section 88, as the case may be:]`
  line `7 [Provided also that where the policy, issued on or after the 1st day of April, 2013, is for`
  line `insurance on life of any person, who is —`
  line `( i ) a person with disability or a person with severe disability as referred to in section 80U;`
  line or
  line `( ii ) suffering from disease or ailment as specified in the rules made under`
  line `section 80DDB,`
  line `the provisions of this sub- clause shall have effect as if for the words “ten per cent. ”, the words`
  line `“fif teen per cent. ” had been substituted.]`
  line `8 [ Explanation 1 ]. —For the purposes of this clause, “Keyman insurance policy” means a life`
  line `insurance policy taken by a person on the life of another person who is or was the employee of the`
  line `first-mentioned person or is or was connected in any manner whatsoever with the business of the`
  line `first-mentioned person] 7 [and includes such policy which has been assigned to a person, at any time`
  line `during the term of the policy, with or without any consideration;]`
  line `9 [ Explanation 2. — For the purposes of sub-clause ( d ), the expression “actual capital sum assured”`
  line `shall have the meaning assigned to it in the Explanation to sub-section ( 3A ) of section 80C;]`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 6, for clause ( 10D ) (w.e.f. 1-4-2004).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-2013).`
  line `3. Subs. by s. 5, ibid., for “assured” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2013).`
  line `4. Ins. by s. 5, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-2013).`
  line `5. Subs. by s. 5, ibid., for “this sub - clause” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2013).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 18 of 2005, s. 4 for “ Explanation to sub-section ( 2A ) of section 88” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2006).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 17 of 2013, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-2014).`
  line `8. Explanation renumbered as Explanation 1 thereof by Act 23 of 2012, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-2013).`
  line `9. Ins. by s. 5, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-2013).`
