  line 78
  line `exclusively incurred in the performance of the duties of an office or employment of profit, 1 [as may`
  line `be prescribed], to the extent to which such expenses are actually incurred for that purpose;`
  line `( ii ) any such allowance granted to the assessee either to meet his personal expenses at the place`
  line `where the duties of his office or employment of profit are ordinarily performed by him or at the place`
  line `where he ordinarily resides, or to compensate him for the increased cost of living, 2 [as may be`
  line `prescribed and to the extent as may be prescribed]:]`
  line `3 [Provided that nothing in sub-clause ( ii ) shall apply to any allowance in the nature of personal`
  line `allowance granted to the assessee to remunerate or compensate him for performing duties of a special`
  line `nature relating to his office or employment unless such allowance is related to the place of his posting`
  line `or residence;]`
  line `4 * * * * *`
  line `( 15 ) 5 [( i ) income by way of interest, premium on redemption or other payment on such securities,`
  line `bonds, annuity certificates, savings certificates, other certificates issued by the Central Government`
  line `and deposits as the Central Government may, by notification in the Official Gazette, specify in this`
  line `behalf, subject to such conditions and limits as may be specified in the said notification;`
  line `6 [( iib ) 7 [in the case of an individual or a Hindu undivided family,] interest on such Capital`
  line `Investment Bonds as the Central Government may, by notification in the Official Gazette, specify in`
  line `this behalf:]`
  line `8 [Provided that the Central Government shall not specify, for the purposes of this sub-clause, such`
  line `Capital Investment Bonds on or after the 1st day of June, 2002;]`
  line `9 [( iic ) in the case of an individual or a Hindu undivided family, interest on such Relief Bonds as`
  line `the Central Government may, by notification in the Official Gazette, specify in this behalf;]`
  line `10 [( iid ) interest on such bonds, as the Central Government may, by notification in the Official`
  line `Gazette, specify, arising to —`
  line `( a ) a non-resident Indian, being an individual owning the bonds; or`
  line `( b ) any individual owning the bonds by virtue of being a nominee or survivor of the non-`
  line `resident Indian; or`
  line `( c ) any individual to whom the bonds have been gifted by the non-resident Indian:`
  line `Provided that the aforesaid bonds are purchased by a non-resident Indian in foreign exchange and`
  line `the interest and principal received in respect of such bonds, whether on their maturity or otherwise, is`
  line `not allowable to be taken out of India:`
  line `Provided further that where an individual, who is a non-resident Indian in any previous year in`
  line `which the bonds are acquired, becomes a resident in India in any subsequent year, the provisions of`
  line `this sub-clause shall continue to apply in relation to such individual:`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 22 of 1995, s. 4, for “as the Central Government may, by notification in the Official Gazette, specify” (w.e.f.`
  line `1-7-1995).`
  line `2. Subs. by s. 4, ibid., for “as the Central Government may, by notification in the Official Gazette, specify, to the extent`
  line `specified in the notification” (w.e.f. 1 -7-1995).`
  line `3. Added by Act 36 of 1989, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `4. Clause ( 14A ) omitted by Act 20 of 2002, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-4-2003).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 4 of 1988, s. 6, for clause ( i ), ( ia ), ( ib ), ( ii ) and ( iia ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 14 of 1982, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-4-1983).`
  line `7. Subs. by Act 11 of 1983, s. 5, for “interest or such capital interest” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1983).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-4-2003).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 26 of 1988, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `10. Ins. by Act 3 of 1989, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
