obj_root_law_sections_79_content:
  string
  line 79
  line `Provided also that in a case where the bonds are encashed in a previous year prior to their`
  line `maturity by an individual who is so entitled, the provisions of this sub-clause shall not apply to such`
  line `individual in relation to the assessment year relevant to such previous year:`
  line `1 [Provided also that the Central Government shall not specify, for the purposes of this sub-clause,`
  line `such bonds on or after the 1st day of June, 2002.]`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this sub- clause, the expression “non - resident Indian” shall`
  line `have the meaning assigned to it in clause ( e ) of section 115C;]`
  line `( iii ) interest on securities held by the Issue Department of the Central Bank of Ceylon constituted`
  line `under the Ceylon Monetary Law Act, 1949;`
  line `2 [( iiia ) interest payable to any bank incorporated in a country outside India and authorised to`
  line `perform central banking functions in that country on any deposits made by it, with the approval of the`
  line `Reserve Bank of India, with any scheduled bank.`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this sub- clause, “scheduled bank” shall have the meaning`
  line `assigned to it in 3 [clause ( ii ) of the Explanation to clause ( viia ) of sub-section ( 1 ) of section 36];]`
  line `4 [( iiib ) interest payable to the Nordic Investment Bank, being a multilateral financial institution`
  line `constituted by the Governments of Denmark, Finland, Iceland, Norway and Sweden, on a loan`
  line `advanced by it to a project approved by the Central Government in terms of the Memorandum of`
  line `Understanding entered into by the Central Government with that Bank on the 25th day of November,`
  line 1986;]
  line `5 [( iiic ) interest payable to the European Investment Bank, on a loan granted by it in pursuance of`
  line `the framework-agreement for financial co-operation entered into on the 25th day of November, 1993`
  line `by the Central Government with that Bank;]`
  line `( iv ) interest payable —`
  line `6 [( a ) by Government or a local authority on moneys borrowed by it before the 1st day of`
  line `June, 2001 from, or debts owed by it before the 1st day of June, 2001 to, sources outside India;]`
  line `( b ) by an industrial undertaking in India on moneys borrowed by it under 7 [a loan agreement`
  line `entered into before the 1st day of June, 2001 with any such financial institution] in a foreign`
  line `country as may be approved in this behalf by the Central Government by general or special`
  line order;
  line `( c ) by an industrial undertaking in India on any moneys borrowed or debt incurred by it`
  line `8 [before the 1st day of June, 2001] in a foreign country in respect of the purchase outside India of`
  line `raw materials 9 [or components] or capital plant and machinery, 10 [to the extent to which such`
  line `interest does not exceed the amount of interest calculated at the rate approved by the Central`
  line `Government in this behalf, having regard to the terms of the loan or debt and its repayment.]`
  line `9 [ 11 [ Explanation 1.] —For the purposes of this item, “purchase of capital plant and machinery”`
  line `includes the purchase of such capital plant and machinery under a hire-purchase agreement or a lease`
  line `agreement with an option to purchase such plant and machinery.]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-4-2003).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 32 of 1985, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-4-1985).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 4 of 1988, s. 126, for “the Explanation to clause ( iii ) of sub-section ( 6 ) of section 11” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1989).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 54 of 2003, s. 2 (w.e.f. 1-4-2001).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 23 of 2004, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-2005).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 14 of 2001, s. 5, for item ( a ) (w.e.f. 1-4-2002).`
  line `7. Subs. by s. 5, ibid., for “a loan agreement entered into with any such financial institution” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2002).`
  line `8. Subs. by s. 5, ibid., for “moneys borrowed or debt incurred by it” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2002).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 11 of 1983, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-1983).`
  line `10. Subs. by Act 5 of 1964, s. 6, for “in any case where the loan or debt is approved by the Central Government, having`
  line `regard to its terms generally and in particular to the terms of its repayment” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1964).`
  line `11. Explanation renumbered as Explanation 1 thereof by Act 54 of 2003, s. 2 (w.e.f. 1-4-1962).`
