  line `6. Subs. by Act 14 of 2001, s. 5, for “any moneys borrowed by it from sources outside India” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2002).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 66 of 1976, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-6-1976).`
  line `8. Subs. by, Act 14 of 2001 s. 5, for “a loan agreement approved by the Central Government” (w. e.f. 1-4-2001).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 49 of 1991, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-1991).`
