  line `2. Ins. by Act 27 of 1999, s. 6 (w.e.f. 1-4-2000).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 7 (w.e.f. 1-4-2016).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 22 of 2007, s. 6, for sub-clause ( vii ) (w.e.f. 1-4-2008).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 28 o 2005, s. 27 and the second Schedule (w.e.f. 10-2-2006).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 22 of 1995, s. 4, for clause ( 15A ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1996).`
  line `7. Ins. by 26 of 1997, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-1998).`
  line `8. Subs. by Act 27 of 1999, s. 6“entered before the 1 st day of April, 1997” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2000).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 23 of 2004, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-2006).`
  line `10. Subs. by Act 21 of 2006, s. 4, for “the 1st day of April, 2006” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2007).`
  line `11. Subs. by Act 46 of 1986, s. 3, for clause ( 17 ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1986).`
  line `12. The word “and” omitted by Act 11 of 1987, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1 -4-1986).`
  line `13. Subs. by s. 4, ibid., for sub-clause ( ii ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1986).`
  line `14. Subs. by Act 21 of 2006, s. 4, for sub-clause ( iii ) (w.e.f. 1-4-2007).`
