  line `legally entitled to, or entrusted by the Government with, the control or management of a`
  line `Municipal or local fund; or`
  line `( iv ) Cantonment Board as defined in section 3 of the Cantonments Act, 1924 (2 of 1924);]`
  line `1 * * * * *`
  line `2 [( 21 ) any income of a 3 [research association] for the time being approved for the purpose of`
  line `clause ( ii ) 4 [or clause ( iii )] of sub-section ( 1 ) of section 35:`
  line `Provided that the 3 [research association] —`
  line `( a ) applies its income, or accumulates it for application, wholly and exclusively to the objects`
  line `for which it is established, and the provisions of sub-section ( 2 ) and sub-section ( 3 ) of section`
  line `11 shall apply in relation to such accumulation subject to the following modifications, namely: —`
  line `( i ) in sub-section ( 2 ), —`
  line `( 1 ) the words, brackets, letters and figure “referred to in clause ( a ) or clause ( b ) of`
  line `sub-section ( 1 ) read with the Explanation to that sub- section” shall be omitted;`
  line `( 2 ) for the words “to charitable or religious purposes”, the words “for the purposes o f`
  line `5 [scientific research or research in social science or statistical research]” shall be`
  line substituted;
  line `( 3 ) the reference to “Assessing Officer” in clause ( a ) thereof shall be construed as a`
  line `reference to the “prescribed authority” referred to in clause ( ii ) 4 [or clause ( iii )] of`
  line `sub-section ( 1 ) of section 35;`
  line `( ii ) in sub-section ( 3 ), in clause ( a ), for the words “charitable or religious purposes”, the`
  line `words “the purposes of 5 [scientific research or research in social science or statistical`
  line `research]” shall be substituted; and`
  line `6 [( b ) does not invest or deposit its funds, other than —`
  line `( i ) any assets held by the 3 [research association] where such assets form part of the`
  line `corpus of the fund of the association as on the 1st day of June, 1973;`
  line `( ii ) any assets (being debentures issued by, or on behalf of, any company or corporation),`
  line `acquired by the 3 [research association] before the 1st day of March, 1983;`
  line `( iii ) any accretion to the shares, forming part of the corpus of the fund mentioned in`
  line `sub-clause ( i ), by way of bonus shares allotted to the 3 [research association];`
  line `( iv ) voluntary contributions received and maintained in the form of jewellery, furniture or`
  line `any other article as the Board may, by notification in the Official Gazette, specify,`
  line `for any period during the previous year otherwise than in any one or more of the forms or modes`
  line `specified in sub-section ( 5 ) of section 11:]`
  line `7 [Provided further that the exemption under this clause shall not be denied in relation to voluntary`
  line `contribution, other than voluntary contribution in cash or voluntary contribution of the nature referred`
  line `1. Clause ( 20A ) omitted by Act 20 of 2002, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-4-2003).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 3 of 1989, s. 4, for clause ( 21 ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1990). Earlier Clause ( 21 ) amended by Act 11 of 1983, s. 5`
  line `(w.e.f. 1-4-1984) and then omitted by Act 4 of 1988, s. 6 and later restored by Act 3 of 1989, s. 95 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 14 of 2010, s. 5, for “scientific research association” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2011).`
  line `4. Ins. by s. 5, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-2011).`
  line `5. Subs. by s. 5, ibid., for “scientific research” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2011).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 18 of 1992, s. 4, for clause ( b ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1990).`
  line `7. Subs. by Act 49 of 1991, s. 5, for “Provided further” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1990).`
