  line 85
  line `to in clause ( b ) of the first proviso to this clause, subject to the condition that such voluntary`
  line `contribution is not held by the 1 [research association], otherwise than in any one or more of the forms`
  line `or modes specified in sub-section ( 5 ) of section 11, after the expiry of one year from the end of the`
  line `previous year in which such asset is acquired or the 31st day of March, 1992, whichever is later:`
  line `Provided also] that nothing contained in this clause shall apply in relation to any income of the`
  line `1 [research association], bei ng profits and gains of business, unless the business is incidental to the`
  line `attainment of its objectives and separate books of account are maintained by it in respect of such`
  line `business:]`
  line `2 [Provided also that where the 1 [research association] is approved by the Central Government and`
  line `subsequently that Government is satisfied that —`
  line `( i ) the 1 [research association] has not applied its income in accordance with the provisions`
  line `contained in clause ( a ) of the first proviso; or`
  line `( ii ) the 1 [research association] has not invested or deposited its funds in accordance with the`
  line `provisions contained in clause ( b ) of the first proviso; or`
  line `( iii ) the activities of the 1 [research association] are not genuine; or`
  line `( iv ) the activities of the 1 [research association] are not being carried out in accordance with all`
  line `or any of the conditions subject to which such association was approved,`
  line `it may, at any time after giving a reasonable opportunity of showing cause against the proposed`
  line `withdrawal to the concerned association, by order, withdraw the approval and forward a copy of`
  line `the order withdrawing the approval to such association and to the Assessing Officer;]`
  line `3 * * * * *`
  line `4 [( 22B ) any income of such news agency set up in India solely for collection and distribution of`
  line `news as the Central Government may, by notification in the Official Gazette, specify in this behalf:`
  line `Provided that the news agency applies its income or accumulates it for application solely for`
  line `collection and distribution of news and does not distribute its income in any manner to its members:`
  line `Provided further that any notification issued by the Central Government under this clause shall, at`
  line `any one time, have effect for such assessment year or years, not exceeding three assessment years`
  line `(including an assessment year or years commencing before the date on which such notification is`
  line `issued) as may be specified in the notification:]`
  line `2 [Provided also that where the news agency has been specified, by notification, by the Central`
  line `Government and subsequently that Government is satisfied that such news agency has not applied or`
  line `accumulated or distributed its income in accordance with the provisions contained in the first proviso,`
  line `it may, at any time after giving a reasonable opportunity of showing cause, rescind the notification`
  line `and forward a copy of the order rescinding the notification to such agency and to the Assessing`
  line Officer;]
  line `5 * * * * *`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 14 of 2010, s. 5, for “scientific research association” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2011).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-4-2003).`
  line `3. Clause ( 22 ) and ( 22A ) omitted by Act 21 of 1998, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-1999).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 32 of 1994, s. 6 (w.e.f. 1-4-1994).`
  line `5. Clause ( 23 ) omitted by Act 20 of 2002, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-4-2003). Earlier Clause ( 23 ) omitted by Act 4 of 1988, s. 6`
  line `(w.e.f. 1-4-1989) and then restored by Act 3 of 1989, s. 95 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
