  content obj_root_law_sections_90_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_90_footnotes
  sourcePage 90
obj_root_law_sections_90_content:
  string
  line 90
  line `1 [( iv ) any other fund or institution established for charitable purposes 2 [which may be`
  line `approved by the prescribed authority], having regard to the objects of the fund or institution and`
  line `its importance throughout India or throughout any State or States; or`
  line `( v ) any trust (including any other legal obligation) or institution wholly for public religious`
  line `purposes or wholly for public religious and charitable purposes, 2 [which may be approved by the`
  line `prescribed authority], having regard to the manner in which the affairs of the trust or institution`
  line `are administered and supervised for ensuring that the income accruing thereto is properly applied`
  line `for the objects thereof;`
  line `3 [( vi ) any university or other educational institution existing solely for educational purposes`
  line `and not for purposes of profit, other than those mentioned in sub-clause ( iiiab ) or`
  line `sub-clause ( iiiad ) and which may be approved by the prescribed authority; or`
  line `( via ) any hospital or other institution for the reception and treatment of persons suffering`
  line `from illness or mental defectiveness or for the reception and treatment of persons during`
  line `convalescence or of persons requiring medical attention or rehabilitation, existing solely for`
  line `philanthropic purposes and not for purposes of profit, other than those mentioned in`
  line `sub-clause ( iiiac ) or sub-clause ( iiiae ) and which may be approved by the prescribed authority:]`
  line `Provided that the fund or trust or institution 3 [or any university or other educational institution or`
  line `any hospital or other medical institution] referred to in sub-clause ( iv ) or sub-clause ( v ) 3 [or`
  line `sub-clause ( vi ) or sub-clause ( via )] shall make an application in the prescribed form and manner to the`
  line `prescribed authority for the purpose of grant of the exemption, or continuance thereof, under`
  line `sub-clause ( iv ) or sub-clause ( v ) 3 [or sub-clause ( vi ) or sub-clause ( via )]:`
  line `4 [Provided further that the prescribed authority, before approving any fund or trust or institution`
  line `or any university or other educational institution or any hospital or other medical institution, under`
  line `sub-clause ( iv ) or sub-clause ( v ) or sub-clause ( vi ) or sub-clause ( via ), may call for such documents`
  line `(including audited annual accounts) or information from the fund or trust or institution or any`
  line `university or other educational institution or any hospital or other medical institution, as the case may`
  line `be, as it thinks necessary in order to satisfy itself about the genuineness of the activities of such fund`
  line `or trust or institution or any university or other educational institution or any hospital or other medical`
  line `institution, as the case may be, and the prescribed authority may also make such inquiries as it deems`
  line `necessary in this behalf:]`
  line `Provided also that the fund or trust or institution 3 [or any university or other educational`
  line `institution or any hospital or other medical institution] referred to in sub-clause ( iv ) or sub-clause ( v )`
  line `3 [or sub-clause ( vi ) or sub-clause ( via )] —`
  line `5 [( a ) applies its income, or accumulates it for application, wholly and exclusively to the`
  line `objects for which it is established and in a case where more than fifteen per cent. of its income is`
  line `accumulated on or after the 1st day of April, 2002, the period of the accumulation of the amount`
  line `exceeding fifteen per cent. of its income shall in no case exceed five years; and]`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 3 of 1989, s. 4, for sub-clauses ( iv ) and ( v ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1990).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 22 of 2007, s. 6, for “which may be notified by the Central Government in the Official Gazette.”`
  line `(w.e.f. 1-6-2007)`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 21 of 1998, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-1999).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 22 of 2007, s. 6, for the proviso (w.e.f. 1-6-2007).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 4, for clause ( a ) (w.e.f. 1-4-2003).`
obj_root_law_sections_90_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_91:
  kind page
  sectionId pdf-page-91
  sectionNo (91)
  orderNo 91
  title `Page 91`
  content obj_root_law_sections_91_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_91_footnotes
  sourcePage 91
obj_root_law_sections_91_content:
  string
  line 91
  line `1 [( b ) does not invest or deposit its funds, other than —`
  line `( i ) any assets held by the fund, trust or institution 2 [or any university or other educational`
  line `institution or any hospital or other medical institution] where such assets form part of the`
  line `corpus of the fund, trust or institution 2 [or any university or other educational institution or`
  line `any hospital or other medical institution] as on the 1st day of June, 1973;`
  line `3 [( ia ) any asset, being equity shares of a public company, held by any university or other`
  line `educational institution or any hospital or other medical institution where such assets form part`
  line `of the corpus of any university or other educational institution or any hospital or other`
  line `medical institution as on the 1st day of June, 1998;]`
  line `( ii ) any assets (being debentures issued by, or on behalf of, any company or corporation),`
  line `acquired by the fund, trust or institution 2 [or any university or other educational institution or any`
  line `hospital or other medical institution] before the 1st day of March, 1983;`
  line `( iii ) any accretion to the shares, forming part of the corpus mentioned in sub-clause ( i ) 3 [and`
  line `sub-clause ( ia )], by way of bonus shares allotted to the fund, trust or institution 2 [or any`
  line `university or other educational institution or any hospital or other medical institution];`
  line `( iv ) voluntary contributions received and maintained in the form of jewellery, furniture or any`
  line `other article as the Board may, by notification in the Official Gazette, specify,`
  line `for any period during the previous year otherwise than in any one or more of the forms or modes`
  line `specified in sub-section ( 5 ) of section 11:]`
  line `Provided also that the exemption under sub-clause ( iv ) or sub-clause ( v ) shall not be denied in`
  line `relation to any funds invested or deposited before the 1st day of April, 1989, otherwise than in any`
  line `one or more of the forms or modes specified in sub-section ( 5 ) of section 11 if such funds do not`
  line `continue to remain so invested or deposited after the 4 [30th day of March, 5 [1993]]:`
  line `2 [Provided also that the exemption under sub-clause ( vi ) or sub-clause ( via ) shall not be denied in`
  line `relation to any funds invested or deposited before the 1st day of June, 1998, otherwise than in any`
  line `one or more of the forms or modes specified in sub-section ( 5 ) of section 11 if such funds do not`
  line `continue to remain so invested or deposited after the 30th day of March, 2001:]`
  line `6 [Provided also that the exemption under sub-clause ( iv ) or sub-clause ( v ) 2 [or sub-clause ( vi )`
  line `or sub-clause ( via )] shall not be denied in relation to voluntary contribution, other than voluntary`
  line `contribution in cash or voluntary contribution of the nature referred to in clause ( b ) of the third`
  line `proviso to this sub-clause, subject to the condition that such voluntary contribution is not held by the`
  line `trust or institution 2 [or any university or other educational institution or any hospital or other medical`
  line `institution], otherwise than in any one or more of the forms or modes specified in sub-section ( 5 )`
  line `of section 11, after the expiry of one year from the end of the previous year in which such asset is`
  line `acquired or the 31st day of March, 1992, whichever is later:]`
  line `Provided also that nothing contained in sub-clause ( iv ) or sub-clause ( v ) 2 [or sub-clause ( vi ) or`
  line `sub-clause ( via )] shall apply in relation to any income of the fund or trust or institution 2 [or any`
  line `university or other educational institution or any hospital or other medical institution], being profits`
  line `and gains of business, unless the business is incidental to the attainment of its objectives and separate`
  line `books of account are maintained by it in respect of such business:`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 18 of 1992, s. 4, for sub-clause ( b ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1990).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 21 of 1998, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-1999).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 14 of 2001, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-2001).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 49 of 1991, s. 5, for “the 30th day of March, 1990” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1990).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 18 of 1992, s. 4, for “1992’ (w.e.f. 1 -4-1992).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 49 of 1991, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-1990).`
obj_root_law_sections_91_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_92:
  kind page
  sectionId pdf-page-92
  sectionNo (92)
  orderNo 92
  title `Page 92`
  content obj_root_law_sections_92_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_92_footnotes
  sourcePage 92
obj_root_law_sections_92_content:
  string
  line 92
  line `Provided also that any 1 [notification issued by the Central Government under sub-clause ( iv ) or`
  line `sub-clause ( v ), before the date on which the Taxation Laws (Amendment) Bill, 2006 receives the`
  line `assent of the President, shall, at any one time, have effect for such assessment year or years], not`
  line `exceeding three assessment years (including an assessment year or years commencing before the date`
  line `on which such notification is issued) as may be specified in the notification:]`
  line `2 [Provided also that where an application under the first proviso is made on or after the date on`
  line `which the Taxation Laws (Amendment) Bill, 2006 receives the assent of the President, every`
  line `notification under sub-clause ( iv ) or sub-clause ( v ) shall be issued or approval under 3 [sub-clause ( iv )`
  line `or sub-clause ( v ) or] sub-clause ( vi ) or sub-clause ( via ) shall be granted or an order rejecting the`
  line `application shall be passed within the period of twelve months from the end of the month in which`
  line `such application was received:`
  line `Provided also that where the total income, of the fund or trust or institution or any university or`
  line `other educational institution or any hospital or other medical institution referred to in sub-clause ( iv )`
  line `or sub-clause ( v ) or sub-clause ( vi ) or sub-clause ( via ), without giving effect to the provisions of the`
  line `said sub-clauses, exceeds the maximum amount which is not chargeable to tax in any previous year,`
  line `such trust or institution or any university or other educational institution or any hospital or other`
  line `medical institution shall get its accounts audited in respect of that year by an accountant as defined in`
  line `the Explanation below sub-section ( 2 ) of section 288 and furnish along with the return of income for`
  line `the relevant assessment year, the report of such audit in the prescribed form duly signed and verified`
  line `by such accountant and setting forth such particulars as may be prescribed:]`
  line `4 [Provided also that any amount of donation received by the fund or institution in terms of`
  line `clause ( d ) of sub-section ( 2 ) of section 80G 5 [in respect of which accounts of income and expenditure`
  line `have not been rendered to the authority prescribed under clause ( v ) of sub-section ( 5C ) of that section,`
  line `in the manner specified in that clause, or] which has been utilised for purposes other than providing`
  line `relief to the victims of earthquake in Gujarat or which remains unutilised in terms of sub-section ( 5C )`
  line `of section 80G and not transferred to the Prime Minister's National Relief Fund on or before the 31st`
  line `day of March, 6 [2004] shall be deemed to be the income of the previous year and shall accordingly be`
  line `charged to tax:]`
  line `7 [Provided also that any amount credited or paid out of income of any fund or trust or institution`
  line `or any university or other educational institution or any hospital or other medical institution referred`
  line `to in sub-clause ( iv ) or sub-clause ( v ) or sub-clause ( vi ) or sub-clause ( via ), to any trust or institution`
  line `registered under section 12AA, being voluntary contribution made with a specific direction that they`
  line `shall form part of the corpus of the trust or institution, shall not be treated as application of income to`
  line `the objects for which such fund or trust or institution or university or educational institution or`
  line `hospital or other medical institution, as the case may be, is established:]`
  line `8 [Provided also that for the purposes of determining the amount of application under item ( a ) of`
  line `the third proviso, the provisions of sub-clause ( ia ) of clause ( a ) of section 40 and sub-sections ( 3 ) and`
  line `( 3A ) of section 40A, shall, mutatis mutandis, apply as they apply in computing the income chargeable`
  line `under the head “Profits and gains of business or profession.]`
  line `9 * * * * *`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 29 of 2006, s. 3, for certain words, brackets, figures and letters (w.e.f. 1-4-2006).`
  line `2. Ins. by s. 3, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-2006).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 22 of 2007, s. 6, for certain words, brackets, figures and letters (w.e.f. 1-6-2007).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 4 of 2001, s. 4 (w.e.f. 3-2-2001).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 4 (w.e.f. 3-2-2001).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 6, for “2003” (w.e.f. 3 -2-2001).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 6 (w.e.f. 1-4-2018).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 13 of 2018, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-2018).`
  line `9. The proviso omitted by Act 20 of 2002, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-4-2002).`
obj_root_law_sections_92_footnotes:
