obj_root_law_sections_93:
  kind page
  sectionId pdf-page-93
  sectionNo (93)
  orderNo 93
  title `Page 93`
  content obj_root_law_sections_93_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_93_footnotes
  sourcePage 93
obj_root_law_sections_93_content:
  string
  line 93
  line `1 [Provided also that where the fund or trust or institution or any university or other educational`
  line `institution or any hospital or other medical institution referred to in sub-clause ( iv ) or sub-clause ( v )`
  line `or sub-clause ( vi ) or sub-clause ( via ) does not apply its income during the year of receipt and`
  line `accumulates it, any payment or credit out of such accumulation to any trust or institution registered`
  line `under section 12AA or to any fund or trust or institution or any university or other educational`
  line `institution or any hospital or other medical institution referred to in sub-clause ( iv ) or sub-clause ( v )`
  line `or sub-clause ( vi ) or sub-clause ( via ) shall not be treated as application of income to the objects for`
  line `which such fund or trust or institution or university or educational institution or hospital or other`
  line `medical institution, as the case may be, is established:`
  line `Provided also that where the fund or institution referred to in sub-clause ( iv ) or trust or institution`
  line `referred to in sub-clause ( v ) is notified by the Central Government 2 [or is approved by the prescribed`
  line `authority, as the case may be,] or any university or other educational institution referred to in sub-`
  line `clause ( vi ) or any hospital or other medical institution referred to in sub-clause ( via ), is approved by`
  line `the prescribed authority and subsequently that Government or the prescribed authority is satisfied`
  line `that —`
  line `( i ) such fund or institution or trust or any university or other educational institution or any`
  line `hospital or other medical institution has not —`
  line `( A ) applied its income in accordance with the provisions contained in clause ( a ) of the`
  line `third proviso; or`
  line `( B ) invested or deposited its funds in accordance with the provisions contained in clause`
  line `(b) of the third proviso; or`
  line `( ii ) the activities of such fund or institution or trust or any university or other educational`
  line `institution or any hospital or other medical institution —`
  line `( A ) are not genuine; or`
  line `( B ) are not being carried out in accordance with all or any of the conditions subject to`
  line `which it was notified or approved,`
  line `it may, at any time after giving a reasonable opportunity of showing cause against the proposed action`
  line `to the concerned fund or institution or trust or any university or other educational institution or any`
  line `hospital or other medical institution, rescind the notification or, by order, withdraw the approval, as`
  line `the case may be, and forward a copy of the order rescinding the notification or withdrawing the`
  line `approval to such fund or institution or trust or any university or other educational institution or any`
  line `hospital or other medical institution and to the Assessing Officer:]`
  line `3 [Provided also that in case the fund or trust or institution or any university or other educational`
  line `institution or any hospital or other medical institution referred to in the first proviso makes an application`
  line `on or after the 1st day of June, 2006 for the purposes of grant of exemption or continuance thereof, such`
  line `application shall be 4 [made on or before the 30th day of September of the relevant assessment year] from`
  line `which the exemption is sought:]`
  line `5 [Provided also that any anonymous donation referred to in section 115BBC on which tax is payable`
  line `in accordance with the provisions of the said section shall be included in the total income:]`
  line `2 [Provided also that all pending applications, on which no notification has been issued under sub-`
  line `clause ( iv ) or sub-clause ( v ) before the 1st day of June, 2007, shall stand transferred on that day to the`
  line `prescribed authority and the prescribed authority may proceed with such applications under those sub-`
  line `clauses from the stage at which they were on that day:]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-4-2003).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 22 of 2007, s. 6 (w.e.f. 1-6-2007).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 21 of 2006, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-6-2006).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 33 of 2 009, s. 4 for “made at any time during the financial year immediately preceding the year”`
  line `(w.e.f. 1-4-2009).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 21 of 2006, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-4-2007).`
obj_root_law_sections_93_footnotes:
