obj_root_law_sections_94:
  kind page
  sectionId pdf-page-94
  sectionNo (94)
  orderNo 94
  title `Page 94`
  content obj_root_law_sections_94_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_94_footnotes
  sourcePage 94
obj_root_law_sections_94_content:
  string
  line 94
  line `1 [Provided also that the income of a trust or institution referred to in sub-clause ( iv ) or sub-clause ( v )`
  line `shall be included in its total income of the previous year if the provisions of the first proviso to clause`
  line `( 15 ) of section 2 become applicable to such trust or institution in the said previous year, whether or not`
  line `any approval granted or notification issued in respect of such trust or institution has been withdrawn or`
  line `rescinded:]`
  line `2 [Provided also that where the fund or institution referred to in sub-clause ( iv ) or the trust or`
  line `institution referred to in sub-clause ( v ) has been notified by the Central Government or approved by the`
  line `prescribed authority, as the case may be, or any university or other educational institution referred to in`
  line `sub-clause ( vi ) or any hospital or other medical institution referred to in sub-clause ( via ), has been`
  line `approved by the prescribed authority, and the notification or the approval is in force for any previous`
  line `year, then, nothing contained in any other provision of this section [other than clause ( 1 ) thereof] shall`
  line `operate to exclude any income received on behalf of such fund or trust or institution or university or other`
  line `educational institution or hospital or other medical institution, as the case may be, from the total income`
  line `of the person in receipt thereof for that previous year.`
  line `Explanation. — In this clause, where any income is required to be applied or accumulated, then,`
  line `for such purpose the income shall be determined without any deduction or allowance by way of`
  line `depreciation or otherwise in respect of any asset, acquisition of which has been claimed as an application`
  line `of income under this clause in the same or any other previous year;]`
  line `3 [( 23D ) 4 [ 5 [ 6 *** 7 [subject to the provisions of Chapter XII-E, any income of] — ]`
  line `( i ) a Mutual Fund registered under the Securities and Exchange Board of India`
  line `Act, 1992 (15 of 1992) or regulations made thereunder;`
  line `( ii ) such other Mutual Fund set up by a public sector bank or a public financial institution or`
  line `authorised by the Reserve Bank of India and subject to such conditions as the Central`
  line `Government may, by notification in the Official Gazette, specify in this behalf.]`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this clause, —`
  line `( a ) the expression “public sector bank” means the State Bank of India constituted under the`
  line `State Bank of India Act, 1955 (23 of 1955), a subsidiary bank as defined in the State Bank of`
  line `India (Subsidiary Banks) Act, 1959 (38 of 1959), a corresponding new Bank constituted under`
  line `section 3 of the Banking Companies (Acquisition and Transfer of Under-takings) Act, 1970 (5 of`
  line `1970), or under section 3 of the Banking Companies (Acquisition and Transfer of Undertakings)`
  line `Act, 1980 (40 of 1980) 8 [and a bank included in the category “other public sector banks” by the`
  line `Reserve Bank of India;]`
  line `( b ) the expre ssion “public financial institution” shall have the meaning assigned to it in`
  line `section 4A of the Companies Act, 1956 (1 of 1956);]`
  line `9 [( c ) the expression “Securities and Exchange Board of India” shall have the meaning`
  line `assigned to it in clause ( a ) of sub-section ( 1 ) of section 2 of the Securities and Exchange Board of`
  line `India Act, 1992 (15 of 1992);]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-2009).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 25 of 2014, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-2015).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 4 of 1988, s. 6 (w.e.f. 1-4-1988).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 22 of 1995, s. 4, for certain words (w.e.f. 1-7-1995).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 27 of 1999, s. 6, for “any income of—” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2000).`
  line `6. The words figures and letter “subject t o the provisions of Chapter XII- E,” omitted by Act 20 of 2002, s. 4`
  line `(w.e.f. 1-4-2003).`
  line `7. Subs. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 6, for “any income of ” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2004).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 33 of 2009, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-4-2010).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 18 of 1992, S. 4 (w.e.f. 1-4-1993).`
