  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_97_footnotes
  sourcePage 97
obj_root_law_sections_97_content:
  string
  line 97
  line `( c ) any clearing member contributing to the Core Settlement Guarantee Fund;]`
  line `1 [( 23F ) any income by way of dividends or long-term capital gains of a venture capital fund or a`
  line `venture capital company from investments made by way of equity shares in a venture capital`
  line `undertaking:`
  line `Provided that such venture capital fund or venture capital company is approved for the purposes`
  line `of this clause by the prescribed authority in accordance with the rules made in this behalf and satisfies`
  line `the prescribed conditions:`
  line `Provided further that any approval by the prescribed authority shall, at any one time, have effect`
  line `for such assessment year or years, not exceeding three assessment years, as may be specified in the`
  line `order of approval:`
  line `2 [Provided also that nothing contained in this clause shall apply in respect of any investment`
  line `made after the 31st day of March, 1999.]`
  line `3 * * * * *`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this clause, —`
  line `( a ) “venture capital fund” means such fund, operating under a trust deed registered under the`
  line `provisions of the Registration Act, 1908 (16 of 1908), established to raise monies by the trustees`
  line `for investments mainly by way of acquiring equity shares of a venture capital undertaking in`
  line `accordance with the prescribed guidelines;`
  line `( b ) “venture capital company” means such company as has made investments by way of`
  line `acquiring equity shares of venture capital undertakings in accordance with the prescribed`
  line guidelines;
  line `4 [( c ) “venture capital undertaking” means such domestic company whose shares are not listed`
  line `in a recognised stock exchange in India and which is engaged in the business of generation or`
  line `generation and distribution of electricity or any other form of power or engaged in the business of`
  line `providing telecommunication services or in the business of developing, maintaining and`
  line `operating any infrastructure facility or engaged in the manufacture or production of such articles`
  line `or things (including computer software) as may be notified by the Central Government in this`
  line behalf;and
  line `( d ) “ infrastructure facility ” means a road, highway, bridge, airport, port, rail system, a water`
  line `supply project, irrigation project, sanitation and sewerage system or any other public facility of a`
  line `similar nature as may be notified by the Board in this behalf in the Official Gazette and which`
  line `fulfils the conditions specified in sub-section ( 4A ) of section 80-IA;]]`
  line `2 [( 23FA ) any income by way of 5 [dividends, other than dividends referred to in section 115-O], or`
  line `long-term capital gains of a venture capital fund or a venture capital company from investments made`
  line `by way of equity shares in a venture capital undertaking:`
  line `Provided that such venture capital fund or venture capital company is approved, for the purposes`
  line `of this clause, by the Central Government on an application made to it in accordance with the`
  line `rules made in this behalf and which satisfies the prescribed conditions:`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 22 of 1995, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-4-1996).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 27 of 1999, s. 6 (w.e.f. 1-4-2000).`
  line `3. The third and fourth provisos omitted by Act 21 of 1998, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-1999).`
  line `4. Subs. by s. 5, ibid., for clause ( c ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1999).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 6, for “dividends” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2004).`
obj_root_law_sections_97_footnotes:
