obj_root_law_sections_100_content:
  string
  line 100
  line `1 [( 23FBA ) any income of an investment fund other than the income chargeable under the head`
  line `“Profits and gains of business or profession”;`
  line `( 23FBB ) any income referred to in section 115UB, accruing or arising to, or received by, a unit`
  line `holder of an investment fund, being that proportion of income which is of the same nature as income`
  line `chargeable under the head “Profits and gains of business or profession”.`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of clauses ( 23FBA ) and ( 23FBB ), the expression “investment`
  line `fund” shall have the meaning assigned to it in clause ( a ) of the Explanation 1 to section 115UB;]`
  line `2 [( 23FC ) any income of a business trust 3 [by way of —`
  line `( a ) interest received or receivable from a special purpose vehicle; or`
  line `( b ) divided referred to in sub-section ( 7 ) of section 115-O].`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this clause, the expression "special purpose vehicle" means an`
  line `Indian company in which the business trust holds controlling interest and any specific percentage of`
  line `shareholding or interest, as may be required by the regulations under which such trust is granted`
  line registration;
  line `1 [( 23FCA ) any income of a business trust, being a real estate investment trust, by way of renting`
  line `or leasing or letting out any real estate asset owned directly by such business trust.`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this clause, the expression "real estate asset" shall have the`
  line `same meaning as assigned to it in clause ( zj ) of sub-regulation ( 1 ) of regulation 2 of the Securities and`
  line `Exchange Board of India (Real Estate Investment Trusts) Regulations, 2014 made under the`
  line `Securities and Exchange Board of India Act, 1992 (15 of 1992);]`
  line `( 23FD ) any distributed income, referred to in section 115UA, received by a unit holder from the`
  line `business trust, not being that proportion of the income which is of the same nature as the income`
  line `referred to 4 [in sub-clause ( a ) of clause ( 23FC )] 3 [or clause ( 23FCA )];]`
  line `5 * * * * *`
  line `6 [( 24 ) any income chargeable under the heads “Income from house property” and “Income from`
  line `other sources” of —`
  line `( a ) a registered union within the meaning of the Trade Unions Act, 1926 (16 of 1926),`
  line `formed primarily for the purpose of regulating the relations between workmen and employers or`
  line `between workmen and workmen;`
  line `( b ) an association of registered unions referred to in sub-clause ( a );]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 20 of 2015, s. 7 (w.e.f. 1-4-2016).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 25 of 2014, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-2015).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 27 of 2016, s. 7, for “by way of interest received or receivable from a special purpose`
  line `vehicle” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2017).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 27 of 2016, s. 7, for “in clause ( 23FC )” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2017).`
  line `5. Clause ( 23G ) omitted by Act 21 of 2006, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-4-2007).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 33 of 1996, s. 4, for clause ( 24 ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1997).`
