obj_root_law_sections_106_content:
  string
  line 106
  line `( b ) “ specified company ” means a company as referred to in clause ( h ) of section 2 of the Unit`
  line `Trust of India (Transfer of Undertaking and Repeal) Act, 2002 (58 of 2002);`
  line `1 [( 35A ) any income by way of distributed income referred to in section 115TA received from a`
  line `securitisation trust by any person being an investor of the said trust.`
  line `2 [Provided that nothing contained in this clause shall apply to any income by way of distributed`
  line `income referred to in the said section, received on or after the 1st day of June, 2016.]`
  line `Explanation. —For the purposes of this clause, the expressions “investor” and “securitisation`
  line `trust” shall have the meanings respectively assigned to them in the Explanation below 3 [section`
  line 115TCA];
  line `( 36 ) any income arising from the transfer of a long-term capital asset, being an eligible equity`
  line `share in a company purchased on or after the 1st day of March, 2003 and before the 1st day of March,`
  line `2004 and held for a period of twelve months or more.`
  line `Explanation. —For the purposes of this clause, “eligible equity share” means,—`
  line `( i ) any equity share in a company being a constituent of BSE-500 Index of the Stock`
  line `Exchange, Mumbai as on the 1st day of March, 2003 and the transactions of purchase and sale of`
  line `such equity share are entered into on a recognised stock exchange in India;`
  line `( ii ) any equity share in a company allotted through a public issue on or after the 1st day of`
  line `March, 2003 and listed in a recognised stock exchange in India before the 1st day of March, 2004`
  line `and the transaction of sale of such share is entered into on a recognised stock exchange in India;]`
  line `4 [( 37 ) in the case of an assessee, being an individual or a Hindu undivided family, any income`
  line `chargeable under the head “Capital gains” arising from the transfer of agricultural land, where—`
  line `( i ) such land is situate in any area referred to in item (a) or item (b) of sub-clause ( iii ) of`
  line `clause ( 14 ) of section 2;`
  line `( ii ) such land, during the period of two years immediately preceding the date of transfer, was`
  line `being used for agricultural purposes by such Hindu undivided family or individual or a parent of`
  line his;
  line `( iii ) such transfer is by way of compulsory acquisition under any law, or a transfer the`
  line `consideration for which is determined or approved by the Central Government or the Reserve`
  line `Bank of India;`
  line `( iv ) such income has arisen from the compensation or consideration for such transfer received`
  line `by such assessee on or after the 1st day of April, 2004.`
  line `Explanation. —For the purposes of this clause, the expression “compensation or`
  line `consideration” includes the compensation or consideration enhanced or further enhanced by any`
  line `court, Tribunal or other authority;`
  line `5 [( 37A ) any income chargeable under the head “Capital gains” in respect of transfer of a specified`
  line `capital asset arising to an assessee, being an individual or a Hindu undivided family, who was the`
  line `owner of such specified capital asset as on the 2nd day of June, 2014 and transfers that specified`
  line `capital asset under the Land Pooling Scheme (herein referred to as “the scheme”) covered under the`
  line `Andhra Pradesh Capital City Land Pooling Scheme (Formulation and Implementation) Rules, 2015`
  line `made under the provisions of the Andhra Pradesh Capital Region Development Authority Act, 2014`
  line `(Andhra Pradesh 11 of 2014) and the rules, regulations and Schemes made under the said Act.`
  line `Explanation. —For the purposes of this clause, “specified capital asset” means,—`
  line `( a ) the land or building or both owned by the assessee as on the 2nd day of June, 2014 and`
  line `which has been transferred under the scheme; or`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 17 of 2013, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-2014).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 7 (w.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
  line `3. Subs. by s. 7, ibid., for “section 115TC” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2017).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 23 of 2004, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-2005).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 6 (w.e.f. 1-4-2015).`
