obj_root_law_sections_107_content:
  string
  line 107
  line `( b ) the land pooling ownership certificate issued under the scheme to the assessee in`
  line `respect of land or building or both referred to in clause ( a ); or`
  line `( c ) the reconstituted plot or land, as the case may be, received by the assessee in lieu of land`
  line `or building or both referred to in clause ( a ) in accordance with the scheme, if such plot or land, as`
  line `the case may be, so received is transferred within two years from the end of the financial year in`
  line `which the possession of such plot or land was handed over to him;]`
  line `( 38 ) any income arising from the transfer of a long-term capital asset, being an equity share in a`
  line `company or a unit of an equity oriented fund 1 [or a unit of a business trust] where —`
  line `( a ) the transaction of sale of such equity share or unit is entered into on or after the date on`
  line `which Chapter VII of the Finance (No. 2) Act, 2004 comes into force; and`
  line `( b ) such transaction is chargeable to securities transaction tax under that Chapter:`
  line `2 [Provided that the income by way of long-term capital gain of a company shall be taken into`
  line `account in computing the book profit and income-tax payable under section 115JB:]`
  line `3 * * * * *`
  line `4 [Provided also that nothing contained in sub-clause ( b ) shall apply to a transaction`
  line `undertaken on a recognised stock exchange located in any International Financial Services Centre`
  line `and where the consideration for such transaction is paid or payable in foreign currency.]`
  line `5 [Provided also that nothing contained in this clause shall apply to any income arising from`
  line `the transfer of a long-term capital asset, being an equity share in a company, if the transaction of`
  line `acquisition, other than the acquisition notified by the Central Government in this behalf, of such`
  line `equity share is entered into on or after the 1st day of October, 2004 and such transaction is not`
  line `chargeable to securities transaction tax under Chapter VII of the Finance (No. 2) Act, 2004`
  line `(23 of 2004).]`
  line `6 [ Provided also that nothing contained in this clause shall apply to any income arising from`
  line `the transfer of long-term capital asset, being an equity share in a company or a unit of an equity`
  line `oriented fund or a unit of a business trust, made on or after the 1st day of April, 2018.]`
  line `7 [ Explanation. — For the purposes of this clause, —`
  line `( a ) “equity oriented fund” means a fund—`
  line `( i ) where the investible funds are invested by way of equity shares in domestic companies`
  line `to the extent of more than sixty-five per cent.. of the total proceeds of such fund; and`
  line `( ii ) which has been set up under a scheme of a Mutual Fund specified under`
  line `clause ( 23D ):`
  line `Provided that the percentage of equity share holding of the fund shall be computed with`
  line `reference to the annual average of the monthly averages of the opening and closing figures;]`
  line `( b ) “International Financial Services Centre” shal l have the same meaning as assigned to it in`
  line `clause ( q ) of section 2 of the Special Economic Zones Act, 2005 (28 of 2005);`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 25 of 2014, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-2015).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 21 of 2006, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-4-2007).`
  line `3. The second proviso omitted by Act 20 of 2015, s. 7 (w.e.f. 1-4-2016).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 7 (w.e.f. 1-4-2016).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 6 (w.e.f. 1-4-2018).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 13 of 2018, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-2018).`
  line `7. Subs. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 7, for the Explanation (w.e.f. 1-4-2016).`
