obj_root_law_sections_109_content:
  string
  line 109
  line `1 [( 46 ) any specified income arising to a body or authority or Board or Trust or Commission (by`
  line `whatever name called) 2 [, or a class thereof] which —`
  line `( a ) has been established or constituted by or under a Central, State or Provincial Act, or`
  line `constituted by the Central Government or a State Government, with the object of regulating or`
  line `administering any activity for the benefit of the general public;`
  line `( b ) is not engaged in any commercial activity; and`
  line `( c ) is notified by the Central Government in the Official Gazette for the purposes of this`
  line clause.
  line `Explanation. —For the purposes of this clause, “specified income” means the income, of the`
  line `nature and to the extent arising to a body or authority or Board or Trust or Commission (by whatever`
  line `name called) 2 [, or a class thereof] referred to in this clause, which the Central Government may, by`
  line `notification in the Official Gazette, specify in this behalf;`
  line `( 47 ) any income of an infrastructure debt fund, set up in accordance with the guidelines as may`
  line `be prescribed, which is notified by the Central Government in the Official Gazette for the purposes of`
  line `this clause;]`
  line `3 [( 48 ) any income received in India in Indian currency by a foreign company on account of 4 [sale`
  line `of crude oil, any other goods or rendering of services, as may be notified by the Central Government`
  line `in this behalf, to any person] in India:`
  line `Provided that —`
  line `( i ) receipt of such income in India by the foreign company is pursuant to an agreement or an`
  line `arrangement entered into by the Central Government or approved by the Central Government;`
  line `( ii ) having regard to the national interest, the foreign company and the agreement or`
  line `arrangement are notified by the Central Government in this behalf; and`
  line `( iii ) the foreign company is not engaged in any activity, other than receipt of such income, in`
  line India;]
  line `5 [( 48A ) any income accruing or arising to a foreign company on account of storage of crude oil in`
  line `a facility in India and sale of crude oil therefrom to any person resident in India:`
  line `Provided that —`
  line `( i ) the storage and sale by the foreign company is pursuant to an agreement or an arrangement`
  line `entered into by the Central Government or approved by the Central Government; and`
  line `( ii ) having regard to the national interest, the foreign company and the agreement or`
  line `arrangement are notified by the Central Government in this behalf;]`
  line `6 [( 48B ) any income accruing or arising to a foreign company on account of sale of leftover stock of`
  line `crude oil, if any, from the facility in India after the expiry of the agreement or the arrangement referred to`
  line `in clause ( 48A ) 7 [or on termination of the said agreement or the arrangement, in accordance with the`
  line `terms mentioned therein, as the case may be,] subject to such conditions as may be notified by the`
  line `Central Government in this behalf;]`
  line `8 [( 49 ) any income of the National Financial Holdings Company Limited, being a company set up`
  line `by the Central Government, of any previous year relevant to any assessment year commencing on or`
  line `before the 1st day of April, 2014;]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 8 of 2011, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-6-2011).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 13 of 2018, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-2018).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-2012).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 17 of 2013, s. 5, for “sale of crude oil to any person” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2014).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 7 (w.e.f. 1-4-2016).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 6 (w.e.f. 1-4-2018).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 13 of 2018, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-2019).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 17 of 2013, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-2014).`
