  content obj_root_law_sections_111_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_111_footnotes
  sourcePage 111
obj_root_law_sections_111_content:
  string
  line 111
  line `1 [Provided that no deduction under this section shall be allowed to an assessee who does not`
  line `furnish a return of his income on or before the due date specified under sub-section ( 1 ) of section`
  line 139.]
  line `( 1B ) The deduction under clause ( ii ) of sub-section ( 1A ) shall be allowed only if the following`
  line `conditions are fulfilled, namely: —`
  line `( a ) the amount credited to the Special Economic Zone Re-investment Allowance Reserve`
  line `Account is to be utilised —`
  line `( i ) for the purposes of acquiring new machinery or plant which is first put to use before the`
  line `expiry of a period of three years next following the previous year in which the reserve was`
  line `created; and`
  line `( ii ) until the acquisition of new machinery or plant as aforesaid, for the purposes of the`
  line `business of the undertaking other than for distribution by way of dividends or profits or for`
  line `remittance outside India as profits or for the creation of any asset outside India;`
  line `( b ) the particulars, as may be prescribed in this behalf, have been furnished by the assessee in`
  line `respect of new machinery or plant along with the return of income for the assessment year relevant to`
  line `the previous year in which such plant or machinery was first put to use.`
  line `( 1C ) Where any amount credited to the Special Economic Zone Re-investment Allowance Reserve`
  line `Account under clause ( ii ) of sub-section ( 1A ), —`
  line `( a ) has been utilised for any purpose other than those referred to in sub-section ( 1B ), the amount`
  line `so utilised; or`
  line `( b ) has not been utilised before the expiry of the period specified in sub-clause ( i ) of clause ( a ) of`
  line `sub-section ( 1B ), the amount not so utilised,`
  line `shall be deemed to be the profits, —`
  line `( i ) in a case referred to in clause ( a ), in the year in which the amount was so utilised; or`
  line `( ii ) in a case referred to in clause ( b ), in the year immediately following the period of three years`
  line `specified in sub-clause ( i ) of clause ( a ) of sub-section ( 1B ),`
  line `and shall be charged to tax accordingly.]`
  line `( 2 ) This section applies to any undertaking which fulfils all the following conditions, namely: —`
  line `( i ) it has begun or begins to manufacture or produce articles or things or computer software`
  line `during the previous year relevant to the assessment year —`
  line `( a ) commencing on or after the 1st day of April, 1981, in any free trade zone; or`
  line `( b ) commencing on or after the 1st day of April, 1994, in any electronic hardware technology`
  line `park, or, as the case may be, software technology park;`
  line `( c ) commencing on or after the 1st day of April, 2001 in any special economic zone;`
  line `( ii ) it is not formed by the splitting up, or the reconstruction, of a business already in existence:`
  line `Provided that this condition shall not apply in respect of any undertaking which is formed as a`
  line `result of the re-establishment, reconstruction or revival by the assessee of the business of any such`
  line `undertakings as is referred to in section 33B, in the circumstances and within the period specified in`
  line `that section;`
  line `( iii ) it is not formed by the transfer to a new business of machinery or plant previously used for`
  line `any purpose.`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 18 of 2005, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-2006).`
obj_root_law_sections_111_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_112:
  kind page
  sectionId pdf-page-112
