  content obj_root_law_sections_113_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_113_footnotes
  sourcePage 113
obj_root_law_sections_113_content:
  string
  line 113
  line `( 7 ) The provisions of sub-section ( 8 ) and sub-section ( 10 ) of section 80-IA shall, so far as may be,`
  line `apply in relation to the undertaking referred to in this section as they apply for the purposes of the`
  line `undertaking referred to in section 80-IA.`
  line `1 [( 7A ) Where any undertaking of an Indian company which is entitled to the deduction under this`
  line `section is transferred, before the expiry of the period specified in this section, to another Indian company`
  line `in a scheme of amalgamation or demerger, —`
  line `( a ) no deduction shall be admissible under this section to the amalgamating or the demerged`
  line `company for the previous year in which the amalgamation or the demerger takes place; and`
  line `( b ) the provisions of this section shall, as far as may be, apply to the amalgamated or the resulting`
  line `company as they would have applied to the amalgamating or the demerged company if the`
  line `amalgamation or demerger had not taken place.]`
  line `2 [( 7B ) The provisions of this section shall not apply to any undertaking, being a Unit referred to in`
  line `clause (zc) of section 2 of the Special Economic Zones Act, 2005, which has begun or begins to`
  line `manufacture or produce articles or things or computer software during the previous year relevant to the`
  line `assessment year commencing on or after the 1st day of April, 2006 in any Special Economic Zone.`
  line `( 8 ) Notwithstanding anything contained in the foregoing provisions of this section, where the`
  line `assessee, before the due date for furnishing the return of income under sub-section ( 1 ) of section`
  line `139,furnishes to the Assessing Officer a declaration in writing that the provisions of this section may not`
  line `be made applicable to him, the provisions of this section shall not apply to him for any of the relevant`
  line `assessment years.`
  line `3 * * * * *`
  line `4 * * * * *`
  line `Explanation 2. — For the purposes of this section, —`
  line `( i ) “computer software” means—`
  line `( a ) any computer programme recorded on any disc, tape, perforated media or other`
  line `information storage device; or`
  line `( b ) any customized electronic data or any product or service of similar nature, as may be`
  line `notified by the Board,`
  line `which is transmitted or exported from India to any place outside India by any means;`
  line `( ii ) “convertible foreign exchange” means foreign exchange which is for the time being treated by`
  line `the Reserve Bank of India as convertible foreign exchange for the purposes of 5 [the Foreign Exchange`
  line `Management Act, 1999 (42 of 1999), and any rules made thereunder or any other corresponding law`
  line `for the time being in force;`
  line `( iii ) “electronic hardware technology park” means any park set up in accordance with the`
  line `Electronic Hardware Technology Park (EHTP) Scheme notified by the Government of India in the`
  line `Ministry of Commerce and Industry;`
  line `( iv ) “export turnover” means the consideration 6 [in respect of export by the undertaking] of`
  line `articles or things or computer software received in, or brought into, India by the assessee in`
  line `convertible foreign exchange in accordance with sub-section ( 3 ), but does not include freight,`
  line `telecommunication charges or insurance attributable to the delivery of the articles or things or`
  line `computer software outside India or expenses, if any, incurred in foreign exchange in providing the`
  line `technical services outside India;`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 7 (w.e.f. 1-4-2004).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 28 of 2005, s. 37 and the Second Schedule (w.e.f. 10-2-2006).`
  line `3. Sub-sections ( 9 ) and ( 9A ) omitted by Act 32 of 2003, s. 7 (w.e.f. 1-4-2003).`
  line `4. Explanation 1 omitted by s. 7, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-2004).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 17 of 2013, s. 4, for “Foreign Exchange Regulation Act, 1973 (46 of 1973)” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2013).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 14 of 2001, s. 6, for “in respect of export” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2001).`
