obj_root_law_sections_115_content:
  string
  line 115
  line `( i ) for the purposes of acquiring machinery or plant which is first put to use before the expiry`
  line `of a period of three years following the previous year in which the reserve was created; and`
  line `( ii ) until the acquisition of the machinery or plant as aforesaid, for the purposes of the`
  line `business of the undertaking other than for distribution by way of dividends or profits or for`
  line `remittance outside India as profits or for the creation of any asset outside India;`
  line `( b ) the particulars, as may be specified by the Central Board of Direct Taxes in this behalf, under`
  line `clause ( b ) of sub-section ( 1B ) of section 10A have been furnished by the assessee in respect of`
  line `machinery or plant along with the return of income for the assessment year relevant to the previous`
  line `year in which such plant or machinery was first put to use.`
  line `( 3 ) Where any amount credited to the Special Economic Zone Re-investment Reserve Account under`
  line `clause ( ii ) of sub-section ( 1 ), —`
  line `( a ) has been utilised for any purpose other than those referred to in sub-section ( 2 ), the amount so`
  line `utilised; or`
  line `( b ) has not been utilised before the expiry of the period specified in sub-clause ( i ) of clause ( a ) of`
  line `sub-section ( 2 ), the amount not so utilised,`
  line `shall be deemed to be the profits, —`
  line `( i ) in a case referred to in clause ( a ), in the year in which the amount was so utilised; or`
  line `( ii ) in a case referred to in clause ( b ), in the year immediately following the period of three years`
  line `specified in sub-clause ( i ) of clause ( a ) of sub-section ( 2 ),`
  line `and shall be charged to tax accordingly:`
  line `Provided that where in computing the total income of the Unit for any assessment year, its profits`
  line `and gains had not been included by application of the provisions of sub-section ( 7B ) of section 10A,`
  line `the undertaking, being the Unit shall be entitled to deduction referred to in this sub-section only for`
  line `the unexpired period of ten consecutive assessment years and thereafter it shall be eligible for`
  line `deduction from income as provided in clause ( ii ) of sub-section ( 1 ).`
  line `Explanation. — For the removal of doubts, it is hereby declared that an undertaking, being the`
  line `Unit, which had already availed, before the commencement of the Special Economic Zones Act,`
  line `2005, the deductions referred to in section 10A for ten consecutive assessment years, such Unit shall`
  line `not be eligible for deduction from income under this section:`
  line `Provided further that where a Unit initially located in any free trade zone or export processing`
  line `zone is subsequently located in a Special Economic Zone by reason of conversion of such free trade`
  line `zone or export processing zone into a Special Economic Zone, the period of ten consecutive`
  line `assessment years referred to above shall be reckoned from the assessment year relevant to the`
  line `previous year in which the Unit began to manufacture, or produce or process such articles or things or`
  line `services in such free trade zone or export processing zone:`
  line `Provided also that where a Unit initially located in any free trade zone or export processing zone`
  line `is subsequently located in a Special Economic Zone by reason of conversion of such free trade zone`
  line `or export processing zone into a Special Economic Zone and has completed the period of ten`
  line `consecutive assessment years referred to above, it shall not be eligible for deduction from income as`
  line `provided in clause ( ii ) of sub-section ( 1 ) with effect from the 1st day of April, 2006.`
obj_root_law_sections_115_footnotes:
