obj_root_law_sections_126_content:
  string
  line 126
  line `the period for which the income is to be accumulated or set apart, which shall in no case exceed five`
  line years;
  line `( b ) the money so accumulated or set apart is invested or deposited in the forms or modes`
  line `specified in sub-section ( 5 );`
  line `( c ) the statement referred to in clause ( a ) is furnished on or before the due date specified under`
  line `sub-section ( 1 ) of section 139 for furnishing the return of income for the previous year:`
  line `Provided that in computing the period of five years referred to in clause ( a ), the period during`
  line `which the income could not be applied for the purpose for which it is so accumulated or set apart, due`
  line `to an order or injunction of any court, shall be excluded.]]`
  line `1 [ Explanation. — Any amount credited or paid, out of income referred to in clause ( a ) or clause ( b ) of`
  line `sub-section ( 1 ), read with the Explanation to that sub-section, which is not applied, but is accumulated or`
  line `set apart, to any trust or institution registered under section 12AA or to any fund or institution or trust or`
  line `any university or other educational institution or any hospital or other medical institution referred to in`
  line `sub-clause ( iv ) or sub-clause ( v ) or sub-clause ( vi ) or sub-clause ( via ) of clause ( 23C ) of section 10, shall`
  line `not be treated as application of income for charitable or religious purposes, either during the period of`
  line `accumulation or thereafter.]`
  line `2 [( 3 ) Any income referred to in sub-section ( 2 ) which —`
  line `( a ) is applied to purposes other than charitable or religious purposes as aforesaid or ceases to be`
  line `accumulated or set apart for application thereto, or`
  line `3 [( b ) ceases to remain invested or deposited in any of the forms or modes specified in`
  line `sub-section ( 5 ), or]`
  line `( c ) is not utilised for the purpose for which it is so accumulated or set apart during the period`
  line `referred to in clause ( a ) of that sub-section or in the year immediately following the expiry thereof,`
  line `1 [( d ) is credited or paid to any trust or institution registered under section 12AA or to any fund or`
  line `institution or trust or any university or other educational institution or any hospital or other medical`
  line `institution referred to in sub-clause ( iv ) or sub-clause ( v ) or sub-clause ( vi ) or sub-clause ( via ) of`
  line `clause ( 23C ) of section 10,]`
  line `shall be deemed to be the income of such person of the previous year in which it is so applied or ceases to`
  line `be so accumulated or set apart or ceases to remain so invested or deposited or credited or paid or, as the`
  line `case may be, of the previous year immediately following the expiry of the period aforesaid.`
  line `4 [( 3A ) Notwithstanding anything contained in sub-section ( 3 ), where due to circumstances beyond the`
  line `control of the person in receipt of the income, any income invested or deposited in accordance with the`
  line `provisions of clause ( b ) of sub-section ( 2 ) cannot be applied for the purpose for which it was accumulated`
  line `or set apart, the 5 [Assessing Officer ]may, on an application made to him in this behalf, allow such person`
  line `to apply such income for such other charitable or religious purpose in India as is specified in the`
  line `application by such person and as is in conformity with the objects of the trust; and thereupon the`
  line `provisions of sub-section ( 3 ) shall apply as if the purpose specified by such person in the application`
  line `under this sub-section were a purpose specified in the notice given to the 5 [Assessing Officer] under`
  line `clause ( a ) ofsub-section ( 2 ):`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 7 (w.e.f. 1-4-2003).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 19 of 1970, s. 5, for sub-section ( 3 ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1971).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 11 of 1983, s. 39, for clause ( b ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1983).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 41 of 1975, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-4-1976).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 4 of 1988, s. 2, for “Income - tax Officer” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1988).`
