  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_133_footnotes
  sourcePage 133
obj_root_law_sections_133_content:
  string
  line 133
  line `1 [ 13. Section 11 not to apply in certain cases. — ( 1 ) 2 [Nothing contained in section 11 or`
  line `section 12] shall operate so as to exclude from the total income of the previous year of the person in`
  line `receipt thereof —`
  line `( a ) any part of the income from the property held under a trust for private religious purposes`
  line `which does not enure for the benefit of the public;`
  line `( b ) in the case of a trust for charitable purposes or a charitable institution created or established`
  line `after the commencement of this Act, any income thereof if the trust or institution is created or`
  line `established for the benefit of any particular religious community or caste;`
  line `3 * * * * *`
  line `( c ) in the case of a trust for charitable or religious purposes or a charitable or religious institution,`
  line `any income thereof —`
  line `( i ) if such trust or institution has been created or established after the commencement of this`
  line `Act and under the terms of the trust or the rules governing the institution, any part of such income`
  line `enures, or`
  line `( ii ) if any part of such income or any property of the trust or the institution (whenever created`
  line `or established) is during the previous year used or applied,`
  line `directly or indirectly for the benefit of any person referred to in sub-section ( 3 ):`
  line `Provided that in the case of a trust or institution created or established before the`
  line `commencement of this Act, the provisions of sub-clause ( ii ) shall not apply to any use or`
  line `application, whether directly or indirectly, of any part of such income or any property of the trust`
  line `or institution for the benefit of any person referred to in sub-section ( 3 ), if such use or application`
  line `is by way of compliance with a mandatory term of the trust or a mandatory rule governing the`
  line `institution:`
  line `Provided further that in the case of a trust for religious purposes or a religious institution`
  line `(whenever created or established) or a trust for charitable purposes or a charitable institution`
  line `created or established before the commencement of this Act, the provisions of sub-clause ( ii )`
  line `shall not apply to any use or application, whether directly or indirectly, of any part of such`
  line `income or any property of the trust or institution for the benefit of any person referred to in`
  line `sub-section ( 3 ) insofar as such use or application relates to any period before the 1st day of June,`
  line 1970;
  line `4 [( d ) in the case of a trust for charitable or religious purposes or a charitable or religious`
  line `institution, any income thereof, if for any period during the previous year —`
  line `( i ) any funds of the trust or institution are invested or deposited after the 28th day of`
  line `February, 1983 otherwise than in any one or more of the forms or modes specified in`
  line `sub-section ( 5 ) of section 11; or`
  line `( ii ) any funds of the trust or institution invested or deposited before the 1st day of March,`
  line `1983 otherwise than in any one or more of the forms or modes specified in sub-section ( 5 ) of`
  line `section 11 continue to remain so invested or deposited after the 30th day of November, 1983; or`
  line `1. Restored by Act 3 of 1989, s. 95 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989). Earlier section 13 omitted by Act 4 of 1988, s. 7 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 1 6 of 1972, s. 7, for “Nothing contained in section 11 ” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1973).`
  line `3. Clause ( bb ) omitted by Act 11 of 1983, s. 7 (w.e.f. 1-4-1984).`
  line `4. Subs. by s. 7, ibid., for clause ( d ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1983).`
obj_root_law_sections_133_footnotes:
