  content obj_root_law_sections_134_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_134_footnotes
  sourcePage 134
obj_root_law_sections_134_content:
  string
  line 134
  line `1 [( iii ) any shares in a company, other than —`
  line `( A ) shares in a public sector company;`
  line `( B ) shares prescribed as a form or mode of investment under clause ( xii ) of`
  line `sub-section ( 5 ) of section 11,`
  line `are held by the trust or institution after the 30th day of November, 1983:]`
  line `Provided that nothing in this clause shall apply in relation to —`
  line `( i ) any assets held by the trust or institution where such assets form part of the corpus of the trust`
  line `or institution as on the 1st day of June, 1973 2 ***;`
  line `3 [( ia ) any accretion to the shares, forming part of the corpus mentioned in clause ( i ), by way of`
  line `bonus shares allotted to the trust or institution;]`
  line `( ii ) any assets (being debentures issued by, or on behalf of, any company or corporation) acquired`
  line `by the trust or institution before the 1st day of March, 1983;`
  line `4 [( iia ) any asset, not being an investment or deposit in any of the forms or modes specified in`
  line `sub-section ( 5 ) of section 11, where such asset is not held by the trust or institution, otherwise than in`
  line `any of the forms or modes specified in sub-section ( 5 ) of section 11, after the expiry of one year from`
  line `the end of the previous year in which such asset is acquired or the 31st day of March, 5 [1993],`
  line `whichever is later;]`
  line `( iii ) any funds representing the profits and gains of business, being profits and gains of any`
  line `previous year relevant to the assessment year commencing on the 1st day of April, 1984 or any`
  line `subsequent assessment year.`
  line `Explanation. — Where the trust or institution has any other income in addition to profits and gains`
  line `of business, the provisions of clause ( iii ) of this proviso shall not apply unless the trust or institution`
  line `maintains separate books of account in respect of such business.]`
  line `6 [ Explanation. — For the purposes of sub-clause ( ii ) of clause ( c ), in determining whether any part of`
  line `the income or any property of any trust or institution is during the previous year used or applied, directly`
  line `or indirectly, for the benefit of any person referred to in sub-section ( 3 ), insofar as such use or application`
  line `relates to any period before the 1st day of July, 1972, no regard shall be had to the amendments made to`
  line `this section by section 7 [other than sub-clause ( ii ) of clause ( a ) thereof] of the Finance Act, 1972.]`
  line `( 2 ) Without prejudice to the generality of the 7 [provisions of clause ( c ) and clause ( d )] of`
  line `sub-section ( 1 ), the income or the property of the trust or institution or any part of such income or`
  line `property shall, for the purposes of that clause, be deemed to have been used or applied for the benefit of a`
  line `person referred to in sub-section ( 3 ), —`
  line `( a ) if any part of the income or property of the trust or institution is, or continues to be, lent to any`
  line `person referred to in sub-section ( 3 ) for any period during the previous year without either adequate`
  line `security or adequate interest or both;`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 22 of 2007, s. 10, for sub-clause ( iii ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1999).`
  line `2. The words “and such assets were not purchased by the trust or institution or acquired by it by conversion or in exchange`
  line `for, any other asset” omitted by Act 18 of 1992, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-1983).`
  line `3. Ins. by s. 5, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-1983).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 49 of 1991, s. 8 (w.e.f. 1-4-1983).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 18 of 1992, s. 5, for “1992” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1992).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 16 of 1972, s. 7 (w.e.f. 1-4-1973).`
  line `7. Subs. by Act 11 of 1983, s. 7, for “provisions of clause ( c )” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1983).`
