  line `( ii ) 1 [in the case of any block of assets, such percentage on the written down value thereof as may`
  line `be prescribed:]`
  line `2 * * * * *`
  line `3 [Provided 4 *** that no deduction shall be allowed under this clause in respect of —`
  line `( a ) any motor car manufactured outside India, where such motor car is acquired by the assessee`
  line `after the 28th day of February, 1975 5 [but before the 1st day of April, 2001], unless it is used —`
  line `( i ) in a business of running it on hire for tourists; or`
  line `( ii ) outside India in his business or profession in another country; and`
  line `( b ) any machinery or plant if the actual cost thereof is allowed as a deduction in one or more`
  line `years under an agreement entered into by the Central Government undersection 42:]`
  line `6 [Provided further that where an asset referred to in clause ( i ) 7 [or clause ( ii ) or clause ( iia )] 8 [or the`
  line `first proviso to clause ( iia )], as the case may be, is acquired by the assessee during the previous year and`
  line `is put to use for the purposes of business or profession for a period of less than one hundred and eighty`
  line `days in that previous year, the deduction under this sub-section in respect of such asset shall be restricted`
  line `to fifty per cent. of the amount calculated at the percentage prescribed for an asset under clause ( i )`
  line `7 [or clause ( ii ) or clause ( iia )], as the case may be:]`
  line `8 [Provided also that where an asset referred to in clause ( iia ) or the first proviso to clause ( iia ), as the`
  line `case may be, is acquired by the assessee during the previous year and is put to use for the purposes of`
  line `business for a period of less than one hundred and eighty days in that previous year, and the deduction`
  line `under this sub-section in respect of such asset is restricted to fifty per cent. of the amount calculated at the`
  line `percentage prescribed for an asset under clause ( iia ) for that previous year, then, the deduction for the`
  line `balance fifty per cent. of the amount calculated at the percentage prescribed for such asset under`
  line `clause ( iia ) shall be allowed under this sub-section in the immediately succeeding previous year in respect`
  line `of such asset:]`
  line `9 [Provided also that where an asset being commercial vehicle is acquired by the assessee on or after`
  line `the 1st day of October, 1998 but before the 1st day of April, 1999 and is put to use before the 1st day of`
  line `April, 1999 for the purposes of business or profession, the deduction in respect of such asset shall be`
  line `allowed on such percentage on the written down value thereof as may be prescribed.`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 46 of 1986, s. 5, for the opening paragraph (w.e.f. 1-4-1988).`
  line `2. The first proviso omitted by Act 22 of 1995, s. 7 (w.e.f. 1-4-1996).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 49 of 1991, s. 11, for the second proviso (w.e.f. 1-4-1992).`
  line `4. The word “further” omitted by Act 22 of 1995, s. 7 (w.e.f. 1 -4-1996).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 14 of 2001, s. 21 (w.e.f. 1-4-2002).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 7 of 1998, s. 2, for the second proviso (w.e.f. 1-4-1998).`
  line `7. Subs. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 14, for “or clause ( ii )” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2003).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 20 of 2015, s. 10 (w.e.f. 1-4-2016).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 11 of 1999, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-1999).`
