obj_root_law_sections_156_content:
  string
  line 156
  line `1 [ 32A. Investment allowance. — ( 1 ) In respect of a ship or an aircraft or machinery or plant specified`
  line `in sub-section ( 2 ), which is owned by the assessee and is wholly used for the purposes of the business`
  line `carried on by him, there shall, in accordance with and subject to the provisions of this section, be allowed`
  line `a deduction, in respect of the previous year in which the ship or aircraft was acquired or the machinery or`
  line `plant was installed or, if the ship, aircraft, machinery or plant is first put to use in the immediately`
  line `succeeding previous year, then, in respect of that previous year, of a sum by way of investment allowance`
  line `equal to twenty-five per cent.. of the actual cost of the ship, aircraft, machinery or plant to the assessee:`
  line `2 [Provided that in respect of a ship or an aircraft or machinery or plant specified in sub-section ( 8B ),`
  line `this sub-section shall have effect as if for the words “twenty -five per cent. ”, the words “twenty per cent. ”`
  line `had been substituted:`
  line `Provided further that] no deduction shall be allowed under this section in respect of —`
  line `( a ) any machinery or plant installed in any office premises or any residential accommodation,`
  line `including any accommodation in the nature of a guest-house;`
  line `( b ) anyoffice appliances or road transport vehicles;`
  line `( c ) any ship, machinery or plant in respect of which the deduction by way of development rebate`
  line `is allowable under section 33; and`
  line `( d ) any machinery or plant, the whole of the actual cost of which is allowed as a deduction`
  line `(whether by way of depreciation or otherwise) in computing the income chargeable under the head`
  line `“Profits and gains of business or profession” of any one previous year.`
  line `2 [ Explanation. — For the purposes of this sub- section, “actual cost” means the actual cost of the`
  line `ship, aircraft, machinery or plant to the assessee as reduced by that part of such cost which has been`
  line `met out of the amount released to the assessee under sub-section ( 6 ) of section 32AB.]`
  line `( 2 ) The ship or aircraft or machinery or plant referred to in sub-section ( 1 ) shall be the following,`
  line `namely: —`
  line `( a ) a new ship or new aircraft acquired after the 31st day of March, 1976, by an assessee engaged`
  line `in the business of operation of ships or aircraft;`
  line `( b ) any new machinery or plant installed after the 31st day of March, 1976, —`
  line `( i ) for the purposes of business of generation or distribution of electricity or any other form`
  line `of power; or`
  line `3 [( ii ) in a small-scale industrial undertaking for the purposes of business of manufacture or`
  line `production of any article or thing; or`
  line `( iii ) in any other industrial undertaking for the purposes of business of construction,`
  line `manufacture or productionof any article or thing, not being an article or thing specified in the list`
  line `in the Eleventh Schedule:]`
  line `2 [Provided that nothing contained in clauses ( a ) and ( b ) shall apply in relation to, —`
  line `( i ) a new ship or new aircraft acquired, or`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 66 of 1976, s. 8 (w.e.f. 1-4-1976).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 3 of 1989, s. 6 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 29 of 1977, s. 9, for sub-clauses ( ii ) and ( iii ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1978).`
