obj_root_law_sections_157_content:
  string
  line 157
  line `( ii ) any new machinery or plant installed,`
  line `after the 31st day of March, 1987 but before the 1st day of April, 1988, unless such ship or`
  line `aircraft is acquired or such machinery or plant is installed in the circumstances specified in`
  line `clause ( a ) of sub-section ( 8B ) and the assessee furnishes evidence to the satisfaction of the`
  line `Assessing Officer as specified in that clause;]`
  line `1 [( c ) any new machinery or plant installed after the 31st day of March, 1983, but before the 2 [1st`
  line `day of April, 1987,] for the purposes of business of repairs to ocean-going vessels or other powered`
  line `craft if the business is carried on by an Indian company and the business so carried on is for the time`
  line `being approved for the purposes of this clause by the Central Government.]`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of 3 [this sub-section and sub-sections ( 2B ), ( 2C ) and ( 4 )], —`
  line `4 [( 1 ) ( a ) “new ship” or “new aircraft” includes a ship or aircraft which before the date of`
  line `acquisition by the assessee was used by any other person, if it was not at any time previous to the`
  line `date of such acquisition owned by any person resident in India;`
  line `( b ) “new machinery or plant” includes machinery or plant which before its installation by the`
  line `assessee was used outside India by any other person, if the following conditions are fulfilled,`
  line `namely: —`
  line `( i ) such machinery or plant was not, at any time previous to the date of such installation`
  line `by the assessee, used in India;`
  line `( ii ) such machinery or plant is imported into India from any country outside India; and`
  line `( iii ) no deduction on account of depreciation in respect of such machinery or plant has`
  line `been allowed or is allowable under the provisions of the Indian Income-tax Act, 1922 (11 of`
  line `1922), or this Act in computing the total income of any person for any period prior to the date`
  line `of the installation of the machinery or plant by the assessee,]`
  line `( 2 ) an industrial undertaking shall be deemed to be a small-scale industrial undertaking, if the`
  line `aggregate value of the machinery and plant (other than tools, jigs, dies and moulds) installed, as`
  line `on the last day of the previous year, for the purposes of 5 [the business of the undertaking does not`
  line `exceed, —`
  line `6 [( i ) in a case where the previous year ends before the 1st day of August, 1980, ten lakh`
  line rupees;
  line `( ii ) in a case where the previous year ends after the 31st day of July, 1980, but before the`
  line `18th day of March, 1985, twenty lakh rupees; and`
  line `( iii ) in a case where the previous year ends after the 17th day of March, 1985, thirty-five`
  line `lakh rupees,]]`
  line `and for this purpose the value of any machinery or plant shall be, —`
  line `( a ) in the case of any machinery or plant owned by the assessee, the actual cost thereof to the`
  line `assessee; and`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 11 of 1983, s. 11 (w.e.f. 1-4-1984).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 23 of 1986, s. 7, for “1st day of April, 1988,” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1987).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 11 of 1983, s. 11, fo r “this sub -section and sub-sections ( 2B ) and ( 4 )” (w.e.f. 1 -6-1983).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 46 of 1986, s. 32, for clause ( 1 ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1988).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 16 of 1981, s. 5, for certain words (w.e.f. 1-4-1981).`
  line `6. Subs.by Act 23 of 1986, s. 7, for sub-clause ( i ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1985).`
