obj_root_law_sections_158_content:
  string
  line 158
  line `( b ) in the case of any machinery or plant hired by the assessee, the actual cost thereof as in`
  line `the case of the owner of such machinery or plant.`
  line `1 [( 2A ) The deduction under sub-section ( 1 ) shall not be denied in respect of any machinery or`
  line `plant installed and used mainly for the purposes of business of construction, manufacture or`
  line `production of any article or thing, not being an article or thing specified in the list in the Eleventh`
  line `Schedule, by reason only that such machinery or plant is also used for the purposes of business of`
  line `construction, manufacture or production of any article or thing specified in the said list.`
  line `( 2B ) Where any new machinery or plant is installed after the 30th day of June, 1977, 2 [but`
  line `before the 1st day of April, 1987], for the purposes of business of manufacture or production of`
  line `any article or thing and such article or thing —`
  line `( a ) is manufactured or produced by using any technology (including any process) or other`
  line `know how developed in, or`
  line `( b ) is an article or thing invented in,`
  line `a laboratory owned or financed by the Government, or a laboratory owned by a public sector`
  line `company or a University or by an institution recognised in this behalf by the prescribed`
  line `authority,the provisions of sub-section ( 1 ) shall have effect in relation to such machinery or plant`
  line `as if for the words “twenty -five per cent..”, the words “thirty -five per cent..” had been substituted,`
  line `if the following conditions are fulfilled, namely: —`
  line `( i ) the right to use such technology (including any process) or other know-how or to`
  line `manufacture or produce such article or thing has been acquired from the owner of such laboratory`
  line `or any person deriving title from such owner;`
  line `( ii ) the assessee furnishes, along with his return of income for the assessment year for which`
  line `the deduction is claimed, a certificate from the prescribed authority to the effect that such article`
  line `or thing is manufactured or produced by using such technology (including any process) or other`
  line `knowhow developed in such laboratory or is an article or thing invented in such laboratory; and`
  line `( iii ) the machinery or plant is not used for the purpose of business of manufacture or`
  line `production of any article or thing specified in the list in the Eleventh Schedule.`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this sub-section, —`
  line `( a ) “laboratory financed by the Government” means a laboratory owned by any body`
  line `including a society registered under the Societies Registration Act, 1860 (21 of 1860) and`
  line `financed wholly or mainly by the Government;`
  line `3 * * * * *`
  line `( c ) “University” means a University established or incorporated by or under a Central,`
  line `State or Provincial Act and includes an institution declared under section 3 of the University`
  line `Grants Commission Act, 1956 (3 of 1956) to be a University for the purposes of that Act.]`
  line `4 [( 2C ) Where any new machinery or plant, being machinery or plant which would assist in`
  line `control of pollution or protection of environment and which has been notified in this behalf by the`
  line `Central Government in the Official Gazette, is installed after the 31st day of May, 1983 but`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 29 of 1977, s. 9 (w.e.f. 1-4-1978).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 14 of 1982, s. 8, for “but before the 1st day of April, 1982” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1982).`
  line `3. Clause ( b ) omitted by Act 11 of 1987, s. 74 (w.e.f. 1-4-1987).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 11 of 1983, s. 11 (w.e.f. 1-6-1983).`
