obj_root_law_sections_159_content:
  string
  line 159
  line `before the 1st day of April, 1987, in any industrial undertaking referred to in sub-clause ( i ) or`
  line `sub-clause ( ii ) or sub-clause ( iii ) of clause ( b ) of sub-section ( 2 ), the provisions of sub-section ( 1 )`
  line `shall have effect in relation to such machinery or plant as if for the words “twenty -five per cent. ”,`
  line `the words “thirty -five per cent..” had been substituted.]`
  line `( 3 ) Where the total income of the assessee assessable for the assessment year relevant to the`
  line `previous year in which the ship or aircraft was acquired or the machinery or plant was installed,`
  line `or, as the case may be, the immediately succeeding previous year (the total income for this`
  line `purpose being computed after deduction of the allowances under section 33 and section 33A, but`
  line `without making any deduction under sub-section ( 1 ) of this section or any deduction under`
  line `Chapter VI-A) is nil or is less than the full amount of the investment allowance, —`
  line `( i ) the sum to be allowed by way of investment allowance for that assessment year under`
  line `sub-section ( 1 ) shall be only such amount as is sufficient to reduce the said total income`
  line `to nil; and`
  line `( ii ) the amount of the investment allowance, to the extent to which it has not been`
  line `allowed as aforesaid, shall be carried forward to the following assessment year, and the`
  line `investment allowance to be allowed for the following assessment year shall be such amount`
  line `as is sufficient to reduce the total income of the assessee assessable for that assessment year,`
  line `computed in the manner aforesaid, to nil, and the balance of the investment allowance, if any,`
  line `still outstanding shall be carried forward to the following assessment year and so on, so,`
  line `however, that no portion of the investment allowance shall be carried forward for more than`
  line `eight assessment years immediately succeeding the assessment year relevant to the previous`
  line `year in which the ship or aircraft was acquired or the machinery or plant was installed or, as`
  line `the case may be, the immediately succeeding previous year.`
  line `Explanation. — Where for any assessment year, investment allowance is to be allowed in`
  line `accordance with the provisions of this sub-section in respect of any ship or aircraft acquired or`
  line `any machinery or plant installed in more than one previous year, and the total income of the`
  line `assessee assessable for that assessment year (the total income for this purpose being computed`
  line `after deduction of the allowances under section 33 and section 33A, but without making any`
  line `deduction under sub-section ( 1 ) of this section or any deduction under Chapter VI-A) is less than`
  line `the aggregate of the amounts due to be allowed in respect of the assets aforesaid for that`
  line `assessment year, the following procedure shall be followed, namely: —`
  line `( a ) the allowance under clause ( ii ) shall be made before any allowance under clause ( i ) is`
  line `made; and`
  line `( b ) where an allowance has to be made under clause ( ii ) in respect of amounts carried`
  line `forward from more than one assessment year, the amount carried forward from an earlier`
  line `assessment year shall be allowed before any amount carried forward from a later assessment`
  line year.
  line `( 4 ) The deduction under sub-section ( 1 ) shall be allowed only if the following conditions are`
  line `fulfilled, namely: —`
  line `( i ) the particulars prescribed in this behalf have been furnished by the assessee in respect`
  line `of the ship or aircraft or machinery or plant;`
  line `( ii ) an amount equal to seventy-five per cent. of the investment allowance to be actually`
  line `allowed is debited to the profit and loss account of 1 [any previous year in respect of which the`
  line `deduction is to be allowed under sub-section ( 3 ) or any earlier previous year (being a`
  line `previous year not earlier than the year in which the ship or aircraft was acquired or the`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 12 of 1990, s. 7, for “the previous year in respect of which the deduction is to be allowed” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1976).`
