obj_root_law_sections_160_content:
  string
  line 160
  line `machinery or plant was installed or the ship, aircraft, machinery or plant was first put to use)]`
  line `and credited to a reserve account (to be called the “Investment Allowance Reserve Account”)`
  line `to be utilised —`
  line `( a ) for the purposes of acquiring, before the expiry of a period of ten years next`
  line `following the previous year in which the ship or aircraft was acquired or the machinery or`
  line `plant was installed, a new ship or a new aircraft or new machinery or plant [other than`
  line `machinery or plant of the nature referred to in clauses ( a ), ( b ) and ( d ) of 1 [the second`
  line `proviso] to sub-section ( 1 )] for the purposes of the business of the undertaking; and`
  line `( b ) until the acquisition of a new ship or a new aircraft or new machinery or plant as`
  line `aforesaid, for the purposes of the business of the undertaking other than for distribution`
  line `by way of dividends or profits or for remittance outside India as profits or for the creation`
  line `of any asset outside India:`
  line `Provided that this clause shall have effect in respect of a ship as if for the word`
  line `“seventy - five”, the word “fifty” had been substituted.`
  line `Explanation. — Where the amount debited to the profit and loss account and credited to the`
  line `Investment Allowance Reserve Account under this sub-section is not less than the amount`
  line `required to be so credited on the basis of the amount of deduction in respect of investment`
  line `allowance claimed in the return made by the assessee under section 139, but a higher deduction in`
  line `respect of the investment allowance is admissible on the basis of the total income as proposed to`
  line `be computed by the 2 [Assessing Officer] under section 143, the 2 [Assessing Officer] shall, by`
  line `notice in writing in this behalf, allow the assessee an opportunity to credit within the time`
  line `specified in the notice or within such further time as the 2 [Assessing Officer] may allow, a further`
  line `amount to the Investment Allowance Reserve Account out of the profits and gains of the previous`
  line `year in which such notice is served on the assessee or of the immediately preceding previous`
  line `year, if the accounts for that year have not been made up; and, if the assessee credits any further`
  line `amount to such account within the time aforesaid, the amount so credited shall be deemed to have`
  line `been credited to the Investment Allowance Reserve Account of the previous year in which the`
  line `deduction is admissible and such amount shall not be taken into account in determining the`
  line `adequacy of the reserve required to be created by the assessee in respect of the previous year in`
  line `which such further credit is made:`
  line `Provided that such opportunity shall not be allowed by the 2 [Assessing Officer] in a case`
  line `where the difference in the total income as proposed to be computed by him and the total income`
  line `as returned by the assessee arises out of the application of the proviso to sub-section ( 1 ) of`
  line `section 145 or sub-section ( 2 ) of that section or the omission by the assessee to disclose his`
  line `income fully and truly.`
  line `( 5 ) Any allowance made under this section in respect of any ship, aircraft, machinery or`
  line `plant shall be deemed to have been wrongly made for the purposes of this Act —`
  line `( a ) if the ship, aircraft, machinery or plant is sold or otherwise transferred by the assessee`
  line `to any person at any time before the expiry of eight years from the end of the previous year in`
  line `which it was acquired or installed; or`
  line `( b ) if at any time before the expiry of ten years from the end of the previous year in`
  line `which the ship or aircraft was acquired or the machinery or plant was installed, the assessee`
  line `does not utilise the amount credited to the reserve account under sub-section ( 4 ) for the`
  line `purposes of acquiring a new ship or a new aircraft or new machinery or plant [other than`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 3 of 1989, s. 6, for “the proviso” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1989).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 4 of 19 88, s. 2, for “Income - tax Officer” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1988).`
