obj_root_law_sections_167_content:
  string
  line 167
  line `1 [32AC. Investment in new plant or machinery. — ( 1 ) Where an assessee, being a company,`
  line `engaged in the business of manufacture or production of any article or thing, acquires and installs new`
  line `asset after the 31st day of March, 2013 but before the 1st day of April, 2015 and the aggregate amount of`
  line `actual cost of such new assets exceeds one hundred crore rupees, then, there shall be allowed a`
  line `deduction, —`
  line `( a ) for the assessment year commencing on the 1st day of April, 2014, of a sum equal to fifteen`
  line `per cent. of the actual cost of new assets acquired and installed after the 31st day of March, 2013 but`
  line `before the 1st day of April, 2014, if the aggregate amount of actual cost of such new assets exceeds`
  line `one hundred crore rupees; and`
  line `( b ) for the assessment year commencing on the 1st day of April, 2015, of a sum equal to fifteen`
  line `per cent. of the actual cost of new assets acquired and installed after the 31st day of March, 2013 but`
  line `before the 1st day of April, 2015, as reduced by the amount of deduction allowed, if any, under`
  line `clause ( a ).`
  line `2 [( 1A ) Where an assessee, being a company, engaged in the business of manufacture or production of`
  line `any article or thing, acquires and installs new assets and the amount of actual cost of such new assets`
  line `3 [acquired during any previous year exceeds twenty-five crore rupees and such assets are installed on or`
  line `before the 31st day of March, 2017], then, there shall be allowed a deduction of a sum equal to fifteen per`
  line `cent. of the actual cost of such new assets for the assessment year relevant to that previous year:`
  line `4 [Provided that where the installation of the new assets are in a year other than the year of acquisition,`
  line `the deduction under this sub-section shall be allowed in the year in which the new assets are installed:]`
  line `5 [Provided further that] no deduction under this sub-section shall be allowed for the assessment year`
  line `commencing on the 1st day of April, 2015 to the assessee, which is eligible to claim deduction under`
  line `sub-section ( 1 ) for the said assessment year.`
  line `( 1B ) No deduction under sub-section ( 1A ) shall be allowed for any assessment year commencing on`
  line `or after the 1st day of April, 2018.]`
  line `( 2 ) If any new asset acquired and installed by the assessee is sold or otherwise transferred, except in`
  line `connection with the amalgamation or demerger, within a period of five years from the date of its`
  line `installation, the amount of deduction allowed under sub-section ( 1 ) 6 [or sub-section ( 1A )] in respect of`
  line `such new asset shall be deemed to be the income of the assessee chargeable under the he ad “Profits and`
  line `gains of business or profession” of the previous year in which such new asset is sold or otherwise`
  line `transferred, in addition to taxability of gains, arising on account of transfer of such new asset.`
  line `( 3 ) Where the new asset is sold or otherwise transferred in connection with the amalgamation or`
  line `demerger within a period of five years from the date of its installation, the provisions of sub-section ( 2 )`
  line `shall apply to the amalgamated company or the resulting company, as the case may be, as they would`
  line `have applied to the amalgamating company or the demerged company.`
  line `( 4 ) For the purposes of this section, “new asset” means any new plant or machinery (other than ship`
  line `or aircraft) but does not include —`
  line `( i ) any plant or machinery which before its installation by the assessee was used either within or`
  line `outside India by any other person;`
  line `( ii ) any plant or machinery installed in any office premises or any residential accommodation,`
  line `including accommodation in the nature of a guest house;`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 17 of 2013, s. 6 (w.e.f. 1-4-2014).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 25 of 2014, s. 11 (w.e.f. 1-4-2015).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 14, for “acquired and installed during any previous year exceeds twenty - five crore rupees”`
  line `(w.e.f. 1-4-2016).`
  line `4. The proviso inserted by s. 14, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-2016).`
  line `5. Subs. by s. 14, ibid., for “Provided that” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2016).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 25 of 2014, s. 11 (w.e.f. 1-4-2015).`
