obj_root_law_sections_169_content:
  string
  line 169
  line `33. Development rebate. — 1 [( 1 ) ( a ) In respect of a new ship or new machinery or plant (other than`
  line `office appliances or road transport vehicles) which is owned by the assessee and is wholly used for the`
  line `purposes of the business carried on by him, there shall, in accordance with and subject to the provisions`
  line `of this section and of section 34, be allowed a deduction, in respect of the previous year in which the ship`
  line `was acquired or the machinery or plant was installed or, if the ship, machinery or plant is first put to use`
  line `in the immediately succeeding previous year, then, in respect of that previous year, a sum by way of`
  line `development rebate as specified in clause ( b ).`
  line `( b ) The sum referred to in clause (a) shall be —`
  line `( A ) in the case of a ship, forty per cent. of the actual cost thereof to the assessee;`
  line `( B ) in the case of machinery or plant, —`
  line `( i ) where the machinery or plant is installed for the purposes of business of construction,`
  line `manufacture or production of any one or more of the articles or things specified in the list in the`
  line `Fifth Schedule, —`
  line `( a ) thirty-five per cent. of the actual cost of the machinery or plant to the assessee, where`
  line `it is installed before the 1st day of April, 1970, and`
  line `( b ) twenty-five per cent. of such cost, where it is installed after the 31st day of`
  line `March, 1970;`
  line `( ii ) where the machinery or plant is installed after the 31st day of March, 1967, by an assessee`
  line `being an Indian company in premises used by it as a hotel and such hotel is for the time being`
  line `approved in this behalf by the Central Government, —`
  line `( a ) thirty-five per cent. of the actual cost of the machinery or plant to the assessee, where`
  line `it is installed before the 1st day of April, 1970, and`
  line `( b ) twenty-five per cent. of such cost, where it is installed after the 31st day of`
  line `March, 1970;`
  line `( iii ) where the machinery or plant is installed after the 31st day of March, 1967, being an`
  line `asset representing expenditure of a capital nature on scientific research related to the business`
  line `carried on by the assessee, —`
  line `( a ) thirty-five per cent. of the actual cost of the machinery or plant to the assessee, where`
  line `it is installed before the 1st day of April, 1970, and`
  line `( b ) twenty-five per cent. of such cost, where it is installed after the 31st day of`
  line `March, 1970;`
  line `( iv ) in any other case, —`
  line `( a ) twenty per cent. of the actual cost of the machinery or plant to the assessee, where it is`
  line `installed before the 1st day of April, 1970, and`
  line `( b ) fifteen per cent. of such cost, where it is installed after the 31st day of March, 1970.]`
  line `2 [( 1A ) ( a ) An assessee who, after the 31st day of March, 1964, acquires any ship which before the`
  line `date of acquisition by him was used by any other person shall, subject to the provisions of section 34, also`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 20 of 1967, s. 33 and the Third Schedule, for sub-section ( 1 ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1968).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 5 of 1964, s. 8 (w.e.f. 1-4-1964).`
