  title `Page 175`
  content obj_root_law_sections_175_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_175_footnotes
  sourcePage 175
obj_root_law_sections_175_content:
  string
  line 175
  line `( 6 ) Where a firm is succeeded to by a company in the business carried on by it as a result of which`
  line `the firm sells or otherwise transfers to the company any land on which development allowance has been`
  line `allowed, the provisions of clauses ( a ) and ( b ) of sub-section ( 5 ) shall, so far as may be, apply to the firm`
  line `and the company.`
  line `Explanation. — The provisions of this sub-section shall apply if the conditions laid down in`
  line `the Explanation to sub-section ( 4 ) of section 33 are fulfilled.`
  line `( 7 ) For the purposes of this section, “actual cost of planting” means the aggregate of—`
  line `( i ) the cost of preparing the land;`
  line `( ii ) the cost of seeds, cutting and nurseries;`
  line `( iii ) the cost of planting and replanting; and`
  line `( iv ) the cost of upkeep thereof for the previous year in which the land has been prepared and the`
  line `three successive previous years next following such previous year,`
  line `reduced by that portion of the cost, if any, as has been met directly or indirectly by any other person or`
  line `authority:`
  line `1 [Provided that where such cost exceeds —`
  line `( i ) forty thousand rupees per hectare in respect of land situate in a hilly area comprised in the`
  line `district of Darjeeling; or`
  line `( ii ) thirty-five thousand rupees per hectare in respect of land situate in a hilly area comprised in`
  line `an area other than the district of Darjeeling; or`
  line `( iii ) thirty thousand rupees per hectare in any other area,`
  line `then, the excess shall be ignored.`
  line `Explanation. —For the purposes of this proviso, “district of Darjeeling” means the district of`
  line `Darjeeling as on the 28th day of February, 1981, being the date of introduction of the Finance Bill, 1981,`
  line `in the House of the People.]`
  line `( 8 ) The Board may, having regard to the elevation and topography, by general or special order,`
  line `declare any areas to be hilly areas for the purposes of this section and such order shall not be questioned`
  line `before any court of law or any other authority.`
  line `2 [ Explanation. — For the purposes of this section, an assessee having a leasehold or other right of`
  line `occupancy in any land shall be deemed to own such land and where the assessee transfers such right, he`
  line `shall be deemed to have sold or otherwise transferred such land.]`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 16 of 1981, s. 6, for the proviso and Explanation (w.e.f. 1-4-1982).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 25 of 1975, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-1962).`
obj_root_law_sections_175_footnotes:
