  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_182_footnotes
  sourcePage 182
obj_root_law_sections_182_content:
  string
  line 182
  line `1 [Provided also that no deduction shall be allowed under this section for any assessment year`
  line `commencing on or after the 1st day of April, 2005.]`
  line `( 2 ) The amount credited to the reserve account under sub-section ( 1 ) shall be utilised by the assessee`
  line `before the expiry of a period of eight years next following the previous year in which the amount was`
  line `credited —`
  line `( a ) for acquiring a new ship for the purposes of the business of the assessee; and`
  line `( b ) until the acquisition of a new ship, for the purposes of the business of the assessee other than`
  line `for distribution by way of dividends or profits or for remittance outside India as profits or for the`
  line `creation of any asset outside India.`
  line `( 3 ) Where any amount credited to the reserve account under sub-section ( 1 ), —`
  line `( a ) has been utilised for any purpose other than that referred to in clause ( a ) or clause ( b ) of`
  line `sub-section ( 2 ), the amount so utilised; or`
  line `( b ) has not been utilised for the purpose specified in clause ( a ) of sub-section ( 2 ), the amount not`
  line `so utilised; or`
  line `( c ) has been utilised for the purpose of acquiring a new ship as specified in clause ( a ) of`
  line `sub-section ( 2 ), but such ship is 2 [sold or otherwise transferred, other than in any scheme of`
  line `demerger] by the assessee to any person at any time before the expiry of 3 [three years] from the end`
  line `of the previous year in which it was acquired, the amount so utilised in acquiring the ship,`
  line `shall be deemed to be the profits, —`
  line `( i ) in a case referred to in clause ( a ), in the year in which the amount was so utilised; or`
  line `( ii ) in a case referred to in clause ( b ), in the year immediately following the period of eight years`
  line `specified in sub-section ( 2 ); or`
  line `( iii ) in a case referred to in clause ( c ), in the year in which the sale or transfer took place,`
  line `and shall be charged to tax accordingly.`
  line `4 [( 4 ) Where the ship is sold or otherwise transferred (other than in any scheme of demerger) after the`
  line `expiry of the period specified in clause ( c ) of sub-section ( 3 ) and the sale proceeds are not utilised for the`
  line `purpose of acquiring a new ship within a period of one year from the end of the previous year in which`
  line `such sale or transfer took place, 5 [so much of such sale proceeds which represent the amount credited to`
  line `the reserve account and utilised for the purposes mentioned in clause ( c ) of sub-section ( 3 )] shall be`
  line `deemed to be the profits of the assessment year immediately following the previous year in which the ship`
  line `is sold or transferred.]`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this section, —`
  line `( a ) “public company” shall have the meaning assigned to it in section 3 of the Companies`
  line `Act, 1956 (1 of 1956);`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 23 of 2004, s. 9 (w.e.f. 1-4-2005).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 27 of 1999, s. 14, for “sold or otherwise transferred” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2000).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 17, for “eight years” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2004).`
  line `4. Ins. by s. 17, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-2004).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 18 of 2005, s. 9, for “such sale proceeds” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2004).`
