obj_root_law_sections_185_content:
  string
  line 185
  line `1 [35. Expenditure on scientific research. — ( 1 ) In respect of expenditure on scientific research, the`
  line `following deductions shall be allowed —`
  line `( i ) any expenditure (not being in the nature of capital expenditure) laid out or expended on`
  line `scientific research related to the business.`
  line `2 [ Explanation. — Where any such expenditure has been laid out or expended before the`
  line `commencement of the business (not being expenditure laid out or expended before the 1st day of`
  line `April, 1973) on payment of any salary [as defined in Explanation 2 below sub-section ( 5 ) of`
  line `section 40A] to an employee engaged in such scientific research or on the purchase of materials used`
  line `in such scientific research, the aggregate of the expenditure so laid out or expended within the three`
  line `years immediately preceding the commencement of the business shall, to the extent it is certified by`
  line `the prescribed authorityto have been laid out or expended on such scientific research, be deemed to`
  line `have been laid out or expended in the previous year in which the business is commenced;]`
  line `( ii ) 3 [an amount equal to 4 [one and one half] times of any sum paid] to a 5 [research association]`
  line `which has as its object the undertaking of scientific research or to a university, college or other`
  line `institution to be used for scientific research:`
  line `6 [Provided that such association, university, college or other institution for the purposes of this`
  line `clause —`
  line `( A ) is for the time being approved, in accordance with the guidelines, in the manner and`
  line `subject to such conditions as may be prescribed; and`
  line `( B ) such association, university, college or other institution is specified as such, by`
  line `notification in the Official Gazette, by the Central Government;]`
  line `7 [Provided further that where any sum is paid to such association, university, college or`
  line `other institution in a previous year relevant to the assessment year beginning on or after the 1st day of`
  line `April, 2021, the deduction under this clause shall be equal to the sum so paid;]`
  line `8 [( iia ) 9 *** any sum paid to a company to be used by it for scientific research:`
  line `Provided that such company —`
  line `( A ) is registered in India,`
  line `( B ) has as its main object the scientific research and development,`
  line `( C ) is, for the purposes of this clause, for the time being approved by the prescribed authority`
  line `in the prescribed manner, and`
  line `( D ) fulfils such other conditions as may be prescribed;]`
  line `1. Restored by Act 3 of 1989, s. 95 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989). Earlier omitted by Act 4 of 1988, s. 10 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 26 of 1974, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-1974).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 27 of 1999, s. 15, for “any sum paid” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2000).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 15 for “one and three fourth” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2018).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 14 of 2010, s. 9, for “scientific research association” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2011).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 29 of 2006, s. 5, for the proviso (w.e.f. 1-4-2006).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 15 (we.f. 1-4-2018).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 18 of 2008, s. 7 (w.e.f. 1-4-2009).`
  line `9. The words “ an amount equal to one and one-fourth times of ” omitted by Act 28 of 2016, s. 15 (w.e.f. 1 -4-2018).`
