obj_root_law_sections_186_content:
  string
  line 186
  line `1 [( iii ) 2 [ 3 *** 4 [any sum paid] to a research association which has as its object the undertaking of`
  line `research in social science or statistical research or to a university], college or other institution to be used`
  line `for research in social science or statistical research:`
  line `5 [Provided that 6 [such association, university], college or other institution for the purposes of this`
  line `clause —`
  line `( A ) is for the time being approved, in accordance with the guidelines, in the manner and subject`
  line `to such conditions as may be prescribed; and`
  line `( B ) 6 [such association, university], college or other institution is specified as such, by notification`
  line `in the Official Gazette, by the Central Government.]]`
  line `7 [ Explanation. — The deduction, to which the assessee is entitled in respect of any sum paid to a`
  line `8 [research association], university, college or other institution to which clause ( ii ) or clause ( iii )`
  line `applies, shall not be denied merely on the ground that, subsequent to the payment of such sum by the`
  line `assessee, the approval granted to the association, university, college or other institution referred to in`
  line `clause ( ii ) or clause ( iii ) has been withdrawn;]`
  line `( iv ) in respect of any expenditure of a capital nature on scientific research related to the business`
  line `carried on by the assessee, such deduction as may be admissible under the provisions of sub-section ( 2 ):`
  line `9 [Provided that the 8 [research association], university, college or other institution referred to in`
  line `clause ( ii ) or clause ( iii ) shall make an application in the prescribed form and manner to the 10 [Central`
  line `Government] for the purpose of grant of approval, or continuance thereof, under`
  line `clause ( ii ) or, as the case may be, clause ( iii ):`
  line `Provided further that the 10 [Central Government] may, before granting approval under clause ( ii ) or`
  line `clause ( iii ), call for such documents (including audited annual accounts) or information from the`
  line `8 [research association], university, college or other institution as it thinks necessary in order to satisfy`
  line `itself about the genuineness of the activities of the 8 [research association], university, college or other`
  line `institution and that 11 [Government] may also make such inquiries as it may deem necessary in this behalf:`
  line `Provided also that any 12 [notification issued, by the Central Government under clause ( ii ) or`
  line `clause ( iii ), before the date on which the Taxation Laws (Amendment) Bill, 2006 receives the assent of`
  line `the President, shall, at any one time, have effect for such assessment year or years, not exceeding three`
  line `assessment years] (including an assessment year or years commencing before the date on which such`
  line `notification is issued) as may be specified in the notification:]`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 49 of 1991, s. 12, for clause ( iii ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1992).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 27 of 1999, s. 15, for “any sum paid” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2000).`
  line `3. The words “an amount equal to one and one - fourth times of” omitted by Act 28 of 2016, s. 15 (w.e.f. 1 -4-2018).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 14 of 2010, s. 9, for “any sum paid to a university” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2011).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 29 of 2006, s. 5, for the proviso (w.e.f. 1-4-2006).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 14 of 2010, s. 9, for “such university” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2011).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 29 of 2006, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-2006).`
  line `8. Subs. by Act 14 of 2010, s. 9, for “scientific research association” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2011).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 3 of 1989, s. 8 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `10. Subs. by Act 27 of 1999, s. 15, for “prescribed authority” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2000).`
  line `11. Subs. by Act 29 of 2006, s. 5, for “authority” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2006).`
  line `12. Subs. by s. 5, ibid., for “notification issued by the Central Government under clause (ii) or clause (iii) shall, at any one`
  line `time, have effect for such assessment year or years, not exceeding three assessment years” ( w.e.f. 1-4-2006).`
