obj_root_law_sections_188_content:
  string
  line 188
  line `( b ) no deduction shall be allowed under that clause for that previous year or for any`
  line `subsequent previous year;`
  line `( iii ) if the asset mentioned in clause ( ii ) is sold, without having been used for other purposes, in`
  line `the year of cessation, the sale price shall be taken to be the value of the asset at the time of the`
  line `cessation; and if the asset is sold, without having been used for other purposes, in a previous year`
  line `subsequent to the year of cessation, and the sale price falls short of the value of the asset taken into`
  line `account at the time of cessation, an amount equal to the deficiency shall be allowed as a deduction for`
  line `the previous year in which the sale took place;`
  line `( iv ) where a deduction is allowed for any previous year under this section in respect of`
  line `expenditure represented wholly or partly by an asset, no deduction shall be allowed under 1 [clause ( ii )`
  line `of sub-section ( 1 )] of section 32 2 [for the same or any other previous year] in respect of that asset;`
  line `( v ) 3 [where the asset mentioned in clause ( ii )is used] in the business after it ceases to be used for`
  line `scientific research related to that business, depreciation shall be admissible under 4 [clause ( ii ) of`
  line `sub-section ( 1 )] of section 32.`
  line `5 [( 2A ) 6 [Where, before the 1st day of March, 1984,the assessee pays any sum] 7 [(being any sum paid`
  line `with a specific direction that the sum shall not be used for the acquisition of any land or building or`
  line `construction of any building)] to a scientific research association or university or college or other`
  line `institution referred to in clause ( ii ) of sub-section ( 1 ) 8 [or to a public sector company] to be used for`
  line `scientific research undertaken under a programme approved in this behalf by the prescribed authority`
  line `having regard to the social, economic and industrial needs of India, then, —`
  line `( a ) there shall be allowed a deduction of a sum equal to one and one-third times the sum so paid;`
  line and
  line `( b ) no deduction in respect of such sum shall be allowed under clause ( ii ) of sub-section ( 1 ) for`
  line `the same or any other assessment year.]`
  line `8 [ Explanation. — For the purposes of this sub- section, “public sector company” shall have the same`
  line `meaning as in clause ( b ) of the Explanation below sub-section ( 2B ) of section 32A.]`
  line `9 [( 2AA ) Where the assessee pays any sum to a National Laboratory 10 [or a 11 [University or an Indian`
  line `Institute of Technology or a specified person] with a specific direction that the said sum shall be used for`
  line `scientific research undertaken under a programme approved in this behalf by the prescribed authority,`
  line `then —`
  line `( a ) there shall be allowed a deduction of a sum equal to 12 [one and one-half times] the sum so`
  line `paid; and`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 46 of 1986, s. 32, for “clauses ( i ), ( ii ), ( iia ), ( iii ) and ( iv ) of sub-section ( 1 ) or under sub-section ( 1A )”`
  line `(w.e.f. 1-4-1988).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 44 of 1980, s. 7, for “for the same previous year” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1962).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 20 of 1967, s. 33 and the Third Schedule, for “where the asset is used” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1968).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 46 of 1986, s. 32, for “clauses ( i ), ( ii ) and ( iii ) of sub-section ( 1 )” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1988).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 26 of 1974, s. 5 (w.e.f. 1-4-1974).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 21 of 1984, s. 6, for “Where the assessee pays any sum” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1984).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 11 of 1983, s. 12 (w.e.f. 1-4-1984).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 44 of 1980, s. 7 (w.e.f. 1-9-1980).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 38 of 1993, s. 9 (w.e.f. 1-4-1994).`
  line `10. Ins. by Act 32 of 1994, s. 13 (w.e.f. 1-4-1995).`
  line `11. Subs. by Act 14 of 2001, s. 23, for “University or an Indian Institute of Technology” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2002).`
  line `12. Subs. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 15, for “ two times” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2018).`
