obj_root_law_sections_199_content:
  string
  line 199
  line `Chapter VIA under the heading ” C. —Deductions in respect of certain incomes” in relation to such`
  line `specified business for the same or any other assessment year.]`
  line `( 4 ) No deduction in respect of the expenditure referred to in sub-section ( 1 ) shall be allowed to the`
  line `assessee under any other section in any previous year or under this section in any other previous year.`
  line `( 5 ) The provisions of this section shall apply to the specified business referred to in sub-section ( 2 ) if`
  line `it commences its operations, —`
  line `( a ) on or after the 1st day of April, 2007, where the specified business is in the nature of laying`
  line `and operating a cross-country natural gas pipeline network for distribution, including storage facilities`
  line `being an integral part of such network; 1 ***`
  line `2 [( aa ) on or after the 1st day of April, 2010, where the specified business is in the nature of`
  line `building and operating a new hotel of two-star or above category as classified by the Central`
  line Government;
  line `( ab ) on or after the 1st day of April, 2010, where the specified business is in the nature of`
  line `building and operating a new hospital with at least one hundred beds for patients;`
  line `( ac ) on or after the 1st day of April, 2010, where the specified business is in the nature of`
  line `developing and building a housing project under a scheme for slum redevelopment or rehabilitation`
  line `framed by the Central Government or a State Government, as the case may be, and which is notified`
  line `by the Board in this behalf in accordance with the guidelines as may be prescribed; 3 ***]`
  line `4 [( ad ) on or after the 1st day of April, 2011, where the specified business is in the nature of`
  line `developing and building a housing project under a scheme for affordable housing framed by the`
  line `Central Government or a State Government, as the case may be, and notified by the Board in this`
  line `behalf in accordance with the guidelines as may be prescribed;`
  line `( ae ) on or after the 1st day of April, 2011, in a new plant or in a newly installed capacity in an`
  line `existing plant for production of fertilizer; 5 ***]`
  line `6 ( af ) on or after the 1st day of April, 2012, where the specified business is in the nature of setting`
  line `up and operating an inland container depot or a container freight station notified or approved under`
  line `the Customs Act, 1962 (52 of 1962);`
  line `( ag ) on or after the 1st day of April, 2012, where the specified business is in the nature of bee-`
  line `keeping and production of honey and beeswax;`
  line `( ah ) on or after the 1st day of April, 2012, where the specified business is in the nature of setting`
  line `up and operating a warehousing facility for storage of sugar; 7 ***]`
  line `8 [( ai ) on or after the 1st day of April, 2014, where the specified business is in the nature of laying`
  line `and operating a slurry pipeline for the transportation of iron ore;`
  line `( aj ) on or after the 1st day of April, 2014, where the specified business is in the nature of setting`
  line `up and operating a semi-conductor wafer fabrication manufacturing unit, and which is notified by the`
  line `Board in accordance with such guidelines as may be prescribed; 9 ***]`
  line `1. The word “and” omitted by Act 14 of 2010, s. 10 (w.e.f. 1 -4-2011).`
  line `2. Ins. by s. 10, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-2011).`
  line `3. The word “and” omitted by Act 8 of 2011, s. 6 (w.e.f. 1 -4-2012).`
  line `4. Ins. by s. 6, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-2012).`
  line `5. The word “and” omitted by Act 23 of 2012, s. 9 (w.e.f. 1-4-2013).`
  line `6. Ins. by s. 9, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-2013).`
  line `7. The word “and” omitted by Act 25 of 2014, s. 12 (w.e.f. 1 -4-2015).`
  line `8. Ins. by s. 12, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-2015).`
  line `9. The word “and” omitted by Act 28 of 2016, s. 18 (w.e.f. 1 -4-2018).`
