obj_root_law_sections_200_content:
  string
  line 200
  line `1 [( ak ) on or after the 1st day of April, 2017, where the specified business is in the nature of`
  line `developing or operating and maintaining or developing, operating and maintaining, any infrastructure`
  line `facility; and]`
  line `( b ) on or after the 1st day of April, 2009, in all other cases not falling under 2 [any of the above`
  line clauses.]
  line `( 6 ) The assessee carrying on the business of the nature referred to in clause ( a ) of sub-section ( 5 ) shall`
  line `be allowed, in addition to deduction under sub-section ( 1 ), a further deduction in the previous year`
  line `relevant to the assessment year beginning on the 1st day of April, 2010, of an amount in respect of`
  line `expenditure of capital nature incurred during any earlier previous year, if —`
  line `( a ) the business referred to in clause ( a ) of sub-section ( 5 ) has commenced its operation at any`
  line `time during the period beginning on or after the 1st day of April, 2007 and ending on the 31st day of`
  line `March, 2009; and`
  line `( b ) no deduction for such amount has been allowed or is allowable to the assessee in any earlier`
  line `previous year.`
  line `3 [( 6A ) Where the assessee builds a hotel of two-star or above category as classified by the Central`
  line `Government and subsequently, while continuing to own the hotel, transfers the operation thereof to`
  line `another person, the assessee shall be deemed to be carrying on the specified business referred to in sub-`
  line `clause ( iv ) of clause ( c ) of sub-section ( 8 ).]`
  line `( 7 ) The provisions contained in sub-section ( 6 ) of section 80A and the provisions of sub-sections ( 7 )`
  line `and ( 10 ) of section 80-IA shall, so far as may be, apply to this section in respect of goods or services or`
  line `assets held for the purposes of the specified business.`
  line `4 [( 7A ) Any asset in respect of which a deduction is claimed and allowed under this section shall be`
  line `used only for the specified business, for a period of eight years beginning with the previous year in which`
  line `such asset is acquired or constructed.`
  line `( 7B ) Where any asset, in respect of which a deduction is claimed and allowed under this section, is`
  line `used for a purpose other than the specified business during the period specified in sub-section ( 7A ),`
  line `otherwise than by way of a mode referred to in clause ( vii ) of section 28, the total amount of deduction so`
  line `claimed and allowed in one or more previous years, as reduced by the amount of depreciation allowable`
  line `in accordance with the provisions of section 32, as if no deduction under this section was allowed, shall`
  line `be deemed to be the income of the assessee chargeable under the head “Profits and gains of business or`
  line `profession” of the previous year in which the asset is so used.`
  line `( 7C ) Nothing contained in sub-section ( 7B ) shall apply to a company which has become a sick`
  line `industrial company under sub-section ( 1 ) of section 17 of the Sick Industrial Companies (Special`
  line `Provisions) Act, 1985 (1 of 1986), during the period specified in sub-section ( 7A ).]`
  line `( 8 ) For the purposes of this section, —`
  line `( a ) an“associated person”, in relation to the assessee, means a person,—`
  line `( i ) who participates, directly or indirectly, or through one or more intermediaries in the`
  line `management or control or capital of the assessee;`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 18 (w.e.f. 1-4-2018).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 9, for “clause ( a ), clause ( aa ), clause ( ab ) and clauses ( ac )” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2013).`
  line `3. Ins. by s. 9, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-2011).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 25 of 2014, s. 12 (w.e.f. 1-4-2015).`
