obj_root_law_sections_201_content:
  string
  line 201
  line `( ii ) who holds, directly or indirectly, shares carrying not less than twenty-six per cent of the`
  line `voting power in the capital of the assessee;`
  line `( iii ) who appoints more than half of the Board of directors or members of the governing`
  line `board, or one or more executive directors or executive members of the governing board of the`
  line `assessee; or`
  line `( iv ) who guarantees not less than ten per cent of the total borrowings of the assessee;`
  line `( b ) “cold chain facility” means a chain of facilities for storage or transportation of agricultural`
  line `and forest produce, meat and meat products, poultry, marine and dairy products, products of`
  line `horticulture, floriculture and apiculture and processed food items under scientifically controlled`
  line `conditions including refrigeration and other facilities necessary for the preservation of such produce;`
  line `1 [( ba ) “infrastructure facility” means—`
  line `( i ) a road including toll road, a bridge or a rail system;`
  line `( ii ) a highway project including housing or other activities being an integral part of the`
  line `highway project;`
  line `( iii ) a water supply project, water treatment system, irrigation project, sanitation and`
  line `sewerage system or solid waste management system;`
  line `( iv ) a port, airport, inland waterway, inland port or navigational channel in the sea;]`
  line `( c ) “specified business” means any one or more of the following business, namely:—`
  line `( i ) setting up and operating a cold chain facility;`
  line `( ii ) setting up and operating a warehousing facility for storage of agricultural produce;`
  line `( iii ) laying and operating a cross-country natural gas or crude or petroleum oil pipeline`
  line `network for distribution, including storage facilities being an integral part of such network;`
  line `2 [( iv ) building and operating, anywhere in India, a 3 [hotel] of two-star or above category as`
  line `classified by the Central Government;`
  line `( v ) building and operating, anywhere in India, a 4 [hospital] with at least one hundred beds for`
  line patients;
  line `( vi ) developing and building a housing project under a scheme for slum redevelopment or`
  line `rehabilitation framed by the Central Government or a State Government, as the case may be, and`
  line `notified by the Board in this behalf in accordance with the guidelines as may be prescribed;`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 18 (w.e.f. 1-4-2018).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 14 of 2010, s. 10 (w.e.f. 1-4-2011).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 8 of 2011, s. 6, for “new hotel” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2011).`
  line `4. Subs. by s. 6, ibid., for “new hospital” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2011).`
