obj_root_law_sections_202_content:
  string
  line 202
  line `1 [( vii ) developing and building a housing project under a scheme for affordable housing`
  line `framed by the Central Government or a State Government, as the case may be, and notified by the`
  line `Board in this behalf in accordance with the guidelines as may be prescribed;`
  line `( viii ) production of fertilizer in India;]`
  line `2 [( ix ) setting up and operating an inland container depot or a container freight station notified`
  line `or approved under the Customs Act, 1962 (52 of 1962);`
  line `( x ) bee-keeping and production of honey and beeswax;`
  line `( xi ) setting up and operating a warehousing facility for storage of sugar;]`
  line `3 [( xii ) laying and operating a slurry pipeline for the transportation of iron ore;`
  line `( xiii ) setting up and operating a semi-conductor wafer fabrication manufacturing unit notified`
  line `by the Board in accordance with such guidelines as may be prescribed;]`
  line `4 [( xiv ) developing or maintaining and operating or developing, maintaining and operating a`
  line `new infrastructure facility;]`
  line `( d ) any machinery or plant which was used outside India by any person other than the assessee`
  line `shall not be regarded as machinery or plant previously used for any purpose, if —`
  line `( i ) such machinery or plant was not, at any time prior to the date of the installation by the`
  line `assessee, used in India;`
  line `( ii ) such machinery or plant is imported into India from any country outside India; and`
  line `( iii ) no deduction on account of depreciation in respect of such machinery or plant has been`
  line `allowed or is allowable under the provisions of this Act in computing the total income of any`
  line `person for any period prior to the date of installation of the machinery or plant by the assessee;`
  line `( e ) where in the case of a specified business, any machinery or plant or any part thereof`
  line `previously used for any purpose is transferred to the specified business and the total value of the`
  line `machinery or plant or part so transferred does not exceed twenty per cent of the total value of the`
  line `machinery or plant used in such business, then, for the purposes of clause ( ii ) of sub-section ( 2 ), the`
  line `condition specified therein shall be deemed to have been complied with;`
  line `( f ) any expenditure of capital nature shall not include 5 [any expenditure in respect of which the`
  line `payment or aggregate of payments made to a person in a day, otherwise than by an account payee`
  line `cheque drawn on a bank or an account payee bank draft or use of electronic clearing system through a`
  line `bank account, exceeds ten thousand rupees or] any expenditure incurred on the acquisition of any land`
  line `or goodwill or financial instrument.]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 8 of 2011, s. 6 (w.e.f. 1-4-2012).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 9 (w.e.f. 1-4-2013).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 25 of 2014, s. 12 (w.e.f. 1-4-2015).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 18 (w.e.f. 1-4-2018).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 13 (w.e.f. 1-4-2018).`
