obj_root_law_sections_203_content:
  string
  line 203
  line `35B. [ Export markets development allowance. ] — Omitted by the Direct Tax Laws (Amendment)`
  line `Act, 1987 (4 of 1988), s. 10 as amended by Act 3 of 1989, s. 95 ( w.e.f. 1-4-1989). Earlier inserted by Act`
  line `19 of 1968, s. 5 ( w.e.f. 1-4-1968).`
  line `35C. [ Agricultural development allowance.] — Omitted by s. 10, ibid. ( w.e.f. 1-4-1988) as amended`
  line `by s. 95, ibid. ( w.e.f. 1-4-1989). Earlier inserted s. 5, ibid. ( w.e.f. 1-4-1968).`
  line `35CC. [ Rural development allowance.] — Omitted by s. 10, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-1988) as amended by`
  line `s. 95, ibid. ( w.e.f. 1-4-1989). Earlier inserted s. 5, ibid. ( w.e.f. 1-4-1968).`
  line `1 [ 35CCA.Expenditure by way of payment to associations and institutions for carrying out rural`
  line `development programmes. — 2 [( 1 ) Where an assessee incurs any expenditure by way of payment of any`
  line `sum —`
  line `( a ) to an association or institution, which has as its object the undertaking of any programme of`
  line `rural development, to be used for carrying out any programme of rural development approved by the`
  line `prescribed authority; or`
  line `( b ) to an association or institution, which has as its object the training of persons for`
  line `implementing programmes of rural development; 3 [or]`
  line `4 [( c ) to a rural development fund set up and notified by the Central Government in this 5 [behalf;`
  line or]
  line `6 [( d ) to the National Urban Poverty Eradication Fund set up and notified by the Central`
  line `Government in this behalf,]`
  line `the assessee shall, subject to the provisions of sub-section ( 2 ), be allowed a deduction of the amount of`
  line `such expenditure incurred during the previous year.]`
  line `7 [( 2 ) The deduction under clause ( a ) of sub-section ( 1 ) shall not be allowed in respect of expenditure`
  line `by way of payment of any sum to any association or institution referred to in the said clause unless the`
  line `assessee furnishes a certificate from such association or institution to the effect that —`
  line `( a ) the programme of rural development had been approved by the prescribed authority before`
  line `the 1st day of March, 1983; and`
  line `( b ) where such payment is made after the 28th day of February, 1983, such programme involves`
  line `work by way of construction of any building or other structure (whether for use as a dispensary,`
  line `school, training or welfare centre, workshop or for any other purpose) or the laying of any road or the`
  line `construction or boring of a well or tube-well or the installation of any plant or machinery, and such`
  line `work has commenced before the 1st day of March, 1983.]`
  line `( 2A ) The deduction under clause ( b ) of sub-section ( 1 ) shall not be allowed in respect of expenditure`
  line `by way of payment of any sum to any association or institution unless the assessee furnishes a certificate`
  line `from such association or institution to the effect that —`
  line `( a ) the prescribed authority had approved the association or institution before the 1st day of`
  line `March, 1983; and`
  line `1. Restored by Act 3 of 1989, s. 95 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989). Earlier omitted by Act 4 of 1988, s. 10 (w.e.f 1-4-1988). Original`
  line `s. 35CCA ins. by Act 19 of 1978, s. 7 (w.e.f. 1-6-1978).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 21 of 1979, s. 5, for sub-section ( 1 ) (w.e.f. 1-6-1979).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 11 of 1983, s. 16 (w.e.f. 1-4-1983).`
  line `4. Ins. by s. 16, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-1983).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 22 of 1995, s. 9, for “behalf” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1996).`
  line `6. Ins. by s. 9, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-1996).`
  line `7. Subs. by Act 11 of 1983, s. 16 for sub-section ( 2 ), ( 2A ) and ( 2B ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1983).`
