obj_root_law_sections_205_content:
  string
  line 205
  line `1 [Provided that for the assessment year beginning on or after the 1st day of April, 2021, the provisions`
  line `of this sub- section shall have effect as if for the words “a sum equal to one and one - half times of”, the`
  line `words “a sum equal to” had been s ubstituted.]`
  line `( 2 ) Where a deduction under this section is claimed and allowed for any assessment year in respect of`
  line `any expenditure referred to in sub-section ( 1 ), deduction shall not be allowed in respect of such`
  line `expenditure under any other provisions of this Act for the same or any other assessment year.]`
  line `2 [35CCD. Expenditure on skill development project. — ( 1 ) Where a company incurs any`
  line `expenditure (not being expenditure in the nature of cost of any land or building) on any skill development`
  line `project notified by the Board in this behalf in accordance with the guidelines as may be prescribed, then,`
  line `there shall be allowed a deduction of a sum equal to one and one-half times of such expenditure.]`
  line `3 [Provided that for the assessment year beginning on or after the 1st day of April, 2021, the provisions`
  line `of this sub- section shall have effect, as if for the words “an amount equal to one and one - half times of”,`
  line `the words “a sum equal to” had been substituted.]`
  line `( 2 ) Where a deduction under this section is claimed and allowed for any assessment year in respect of`
  line `any expenditure referred to in sub-section ( 1 ), deduction shall not be allowed in respect of such`
  line `expenditure under any other provisions of this Act for the same or any other assessment year.]`
  line `4 [35D. Amortisation of certain preliminary expenses. — ( 1 ) Where an assessee, being an Indian`
  line `company or a person (other than a company) who is resident in India, incurs, after the 31st day of March,`
  line `1970, any expenditure specified in sub-section ( 2 ), —`
  line `( i ) before the commencement of his business, or`
  line `( ii ) after the commencement of his business, in connection with the extension of his`
  line `5 [undertaking] or in connection with his setting up a new 6 [unit],`
  line `the assessee shall, in accordance with and subject to the provisions of this section, be allowed a`
  line `deduction of an amount equal to one-tenth of such expenditure for each of the ten successive previous`
  line `years beginning with the previous year in which the business commences or, as the case may be, the`
  line `previous year in which the extension of the 5 [undertaking] is completed or the new 6 [unit] commences`
  line `production or operation:`
  line `7 [Provided that where an assessee incurs after the 31st day of March, 1998, any expenditure specified`
  line `in sub-section ( 2 ), the provisions of this sub-section shall have effect as if for the words “an amount equal`
  line `to one- tenth of such expenditure for each of the ten successive previous years”, the words “an amount`
  line `equal to one- fifth of such expenditure for each of the five successive previous years” had been`
  line substituted.]
  line `( 2 ) The expenditure referred to in sub-section ( 1 ) shall be the expenditure specified in any one or`
  line `more of the following clauses, namely: —`
  line `( a ) expenditure in connection with —`
  line `( i ) preparation of feasibility report;`
  line `( ii ) preparation of project report;`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 19 (w.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 10 (w.e.f. 1-4-2013).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 20 (w.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 42 of 1970, s. 8 (w.e.f. 1-4-1971).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 18 of 2008, s. 8, for “industrial undertaking” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2009).`
  line `6. Subs. by s. 8, ibid., for “industrial unit” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2009).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 21 of 1998, s. 14 (w.e.f. 1-4-1999).`
