obj_root_law_sections_207_content:
  string
  line 207
  line `completed or, as the case may be, the new 1 [unit] commences production or operation, in so far as`
  line `such fixed assets have been acquired or developed in connection with the extension of the`
  line `2 [undertaking] or the setting up of the new 1 [unit] of the assessee;`
  line `( b ) “capital employed in the business of the company” means—`
  line `( i ) in a case referred to in clause ( i ) of sub-section ( 1 ), the aggregate of the issued share`
  line `capital, debentures and long-term borrowings as on the last day of the previous year in which the`
  line `business of the company commences;`
  line `( ii ) in a case referred to in clause ( ii ) of sub-section ( 1 ), the aggregate of the issued share`
  line `capital, debentures and long-term borrowings as on the last day of the previous year in which the`
  line `extension of the 2 [undertaking] is completed or, as the case may be, the new 1 [unit] commences`
  line `production or operation, in so far as such capital, debentures and long-term borrowings have been`
  line `issued or obtained in connection with the extension of the 2 [undertaking] or the setting up of the`
  line `new 2 [unit] of the company;`
  line `( c ) “long -ter m borrowings” means—`
  line `( i ) any moneys borrowed by the company from Government or the Industrial Finance`
  line `Corporation of India or the Industrial Credit and Investment Corporation of India or any other`
  line `financial institution 3 [which is eligible for deduction under clause ( viii ) of sub-section ( 1 ) of`
  line `section 36] or any banking institution (not being a financial institution referred to above), or`
  line `( ii ) any moneys borrowed or debt incurred by it in a foreign country in respect of the`
  line `purchase outside India of capital plant and machinery, where the terms under which such moneys`
  line `are borrowed or the debt is incurred provide for the repayment thereof during a period of not less`
  line `than seven years.`
  line `( 4 ) Where the assessee is a person other than a company or a co-operative society, no deduction shall`
  line `be admissible under sub-section ( 1 ) unless the accounts of the assessee for the year or years in which the`
  line `expenditure specified in sub-section ( 2 ) is incurred have been audited by an accountant as defined in`
  line `the Explanation below sub-section ( 2 ) of section 288, and the assessee furnishes, along with his return of`
  line `income for the first year in which the deduction under this section is claimed, the report of such audit in`
  line `the prescribed form duly signed and verified by such accountant and setting forth such particulars as may`
  line `be prescribed.`
  line `( 5 ) Where the undertaking of an Indian company which is entitled to the deduction under`
  line `sub-section ( 1 ) is transferred, before the expiry of the period of ten years specified in sub-section ( 1 ), to`
  line `another Indian company in a scheme of amalgamation, —`
  line `( i ) no deduction shall be admissible under sub-section ( 1 ) in the case of the amalgamating`
  line `company for the previous year in which the amalgamation takes place; and`
  line `( ii ) the provisions of this section shall, as far as may be, apply to the amalgamated company as`
  line `they would have applied to the amalgamating company if the amalgamation had not taken place.`
  line `4 [( 5A ) Where the undertaking of an Indian company which is entitled to the deduction under sub-`
  line `section ( 1 ) is transferred, before the expiry of the period specified in sub-section (1), to another company`
  line `in a scheme of demerger, —`
  line `( i ) no deduction shall be admissible under sub-section ( 1 ) in the case of the demerged company`
  line `for the previous year in which the demerger takes place; and`
  line `1. Subs. by Act of 18 of 2008, s. 8, for “industrial unit" (w.e.f. 1 -4-2009).`
  line `2. Subs. by s. 8, ibid., for “industrial undertaking” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2009).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 10 of 2000, s. 17, for “which is for the time being approved by the Central Government for the purposes of`
  line `clause ( viii ) of sub-section ( 1 ) of section 36” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2000).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 27 of 1999, s. 19 (w.e.f. 1-4-2000).`
