obj_root_law_sections_213_content:
  string
  line 213
  line `1 [Provided that in the case of 2 [an assesse] to which clause ( viia ) applies, the amount of the deduction`
  line `relating to any such debt or part thereof shall be limited to the amount by which such debt or part thereof`
  line `exceeds the credit balance in the provision for bad and doubtful debts account made under that clause:]`
  line `3 [Provided further that where the amount of such debt or part thereof has been taken into account in`
  line `computing the income of the assessee of the previous year in which the amount of such debt or part`
  line `thereof becomes irrecoverable or of an earlier previous year on the basis of income computation and`
  line `disclosure standards notified under sub-section ( 2 ) of section 145 without recording the same in the`
  line `accounts, then, such debt or part thereof shall be allowed in the previous year in which such debt or part`
  line `thereof becomes irrecoverable and it shall be deemed that such debt or part thereof has been written off as`
  line `irrecoverable in the accounts for the purposes of this clause.]`
  line `4 [ 5 [E xplanation 1]. — For the purposes of this clause, any bad debt or part thereof written off as`
  line `irrecoverable in the accounts of the assessee shall not include any provision for bad and doubtful debts`
  line `made in the accounts of the assessee;]`
  line `6 [ Explanation 2. — For the removal of doubts, it is hereby clarified that for the purposes of the proviso`
  line `to clause (vii) of this sub-section and clause ( v ) of sub-section ( 2 ), the account referred to therein shall be`
  line `only one account in respect of provision for bad and doubtful debts under clause ( viia ) and such account`
  line `shall relate to all types of advances, including advances made by rural branches;]`
  line `7 [( viia ) 8 [in respect of any provision for bad and doubtful debts made by —`
  line `( a ) a scheduled bank [not being 9 *** a bank incorporated by or under the laws of a country`
  line `outside India] or a non-scheduled bank 10 [or a co-operative bank other than a primary agricultural`
  line `credit society or a primary co-operative agricultural and rural development bank], an amount 11 [not`
  line `exceeding 12 [eight and one-half per cent.]] of the total income (computed before making any`
  line `deduction under this clause and Chapter VIA) and an amount not exceeding 13 [ten per cent.] of the`
  line `aggregate average advances made by the rural branches of such bank computed in the prescribed`
  line `manner:`
  line `14 [Provided that a scheduled bank or a non-scheduled bank referred to in this sub-clause shall, at`
  line `its option, be allowed in any of the relevant assessment years, deduction in respect of any provision`
  line `made by it for any assets classified by the Reserve Bank of India as doubtful assets or loss assets in`
  line `accordance with the guidelines issued by it in this behalf, for an amount not exceeding five per cent`
  line `of the amount of such assets shown in the books of account of the bank on the last day of the previous`
  line `year:]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 32 of 1985, s. 10 (w.e.f. 1-4- 1985).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 26 of 1997, s. 7, for “a bank” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1992).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 20 of 2015, s. 13 (w.e.f. 1-4-2016).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 14 of 2001, s. 25 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `5. Explanation renumbered as Explanation 1 thereof by Act 17 of 2013, s. 7 (w.e.f. 1-4-2014).`
  line `6. Ins. by s. 7, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-2014).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 21 of 1979, s. 6 (w.e.f. 1-4-1980).`
  line `8. Subs. by Act 26 of 1986, s. 2, for certain words (w.e.f. 1-4-1987).`
  line `9. The word s “a bank approved by the Central Government for the purpose of clause ( viiia ) or” omitted by Act 32 of 1994,`
  line `s. 14 (w.e.f. 1-4-1995).`
  line `10. Ins. by Act 22 of 2007, s. 13 (w.e.f. 1-4-2007).`
  line `11. Subs. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 19, for “not exceeding five per cent.” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2003).`
  line `12. Subs. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 14 for “seven and one - half per cent.” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2018).`
  line `13. Subs. by Act 32 of 1994, s. 14, for “four per cent.” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1995).`
  line `14. Ins. by Act 27 of 1999, s. 22 (w.e.f. 1-4-2000).`
