obj_root_law_sections_215_content:
  string
  line 215
  line `1 [( ii ) “scheduled bank” means the State Bank of India constituted under the State Bank of`
  line `India Act, 1955 (23 of 1955), a subsidiary bank as defined in the State Bank of India (Subsidiary`
  line `Banks) Act, 1959 (38 of 1959), a corresponding new bank constituted under section 3`
  line `of the Banking Companies (Acquisition and Transfer of Undertakings) Act, 1970 (5 of 1970),`
  line `or under section 3 of the Banking Companies (Acquisition and Transfer of Undertakings)`
  line `Act, 1980 (40 of 1980), or any other bank being a bank included in the Second Schedule to the`
  line `Reserve Bank of India Act, 1934 (2 of 1934) 2 ***;]`
  line `3 [( iii ) “public financial institution” shall have the meaning assigned to it in section 4A of the`
  line `Companies Act, 1956 (1 of 1956);`
  line `( iv ) “State financial corporation” means a financial corporation established under section 3 or`
  line `section 3A or an institution notified under section 46 of the State Financial Corporations`
  line `Act, 1951 (63 of 1951);`
  line `( v ) “State industrial investment corporation” means a Government company within the`
  line `meaning of section 617 of the Companies Act, 1956 (1 of 1956), engaged in the business of`
  line `providing long-term finance for industrial projects and 4 [eligible for deduction under clause ( viii )`
  line `of this sub-section];]`
  line `5 [( vi ) “co - operative bank”, “primary agricultural credit society” and “primary co -operative`
  line `agricultural and rural development bank” shall have the meanings respec tively assigned to them`
  line `in the Explanation to sub-section ( 4 ) of section 80P;]`
  line `6 [( vii ) “non - banking financial company” shall have the meaning assigned to it in clause ( f ) of`
  line `section 45-I of the Reserve Bank of India Act, 1934 (2 of 1934);]`
  line `7 [( viii ) in respect of any special reserve created and maintained by a specified entity, an`
  line `amount not exceeding twenty per cent of the profits derived from eligible business computed`
  line `under the head “Profits and gains of business or profession” (before making any deductio n under`
  line `this clause) carried to such reserve account:`
  line `Provided that where the aggregate of the amounts carried to such reserve account from time`
  line `to time exceeds twice the amount of the paid up share capital and of the general reserves of the`
  line `specified entity, no allowance under this clause shall be made in respect of such excess.`
  line `Explanation. — In this clause, —`
  line `( a ) “specified entity” means,—`
  line `( i ) a financial corporation specified in section 4A of the Companies`
  line `Act, 1956 (1 of 1956);`
  line `( ii ) a financial corporation which is a public sector company;`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 4 of 1988, s. 10, for clause ( ii ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `2. The words “but does not include a co - operative bank” omitted by Act 22 of 2007, s. 11 (w.e.f. 1-4-2007).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 49 of 1991, s. 12 (w.e.f. 1-4-1992).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 10 of 2000, s. 18, for “a sum equal to one and one - fourth times of the expenditure” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2000).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 22 of 2007, s. 13 (w.e.f. 1-4-2007).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 21 (w.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
  line `7. Subs. by Act 22 of 2007, s. 13, for clause ( viii ) (w.e.f. 1-4-2008).`
