  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_216_footnotes
  sourcePage 216
obj_root_law_sections_216_content:
  string
  line 216
  line `( iii ) a banking company;`
  line `( iv ) a co-operative bank other than a primary agricultural credit society or a primary`
  line `co-operative agricultural and rural development bank;`
  line `( v ) a housing finance company; and`
  line `( vi ) any other financial corporation including a public company;`
  line `( b ) “eligible business” means,—`
  line `1 [( i ) in respect of the specified entity referred to in sub-clause ( i ) or sub-clause ( ii ) or`
  line `sub-clause ( iii ) or sub-clause ( iv ) of clause ( a ), the business of providing long-term`
  line `finance for —`
  line `( A ) industrial or agricultural development;`
  line `( B ) development of infrastructure facility in India; or`
  line `( C ) development of housing in India;]`
  line `( ii ) in respect of the specified entity referred to in sub-clause ( v ) of clause ( a ), the`
  line `business of providing long-term finance for the construction or purchase of houses in`
  line `India for residential purposes; and`
  line `( iii ) in respect of the specified entity referred to in sub-clause ( vi ) of clause ( a ), the`
  line `business of providing long-term finance for development of infrastructure facility in`
  line India;
  line `( c ) “banking company” means a company to which the Banking Regulation`
  line `Act, 1949 (10 of 1949) applies and includes any bank or banking institution referred to in`
  line `section 51 of that Act;`
  line `( d ) “co - operative bank”, “primary agricultural credit society” and “primary co -operative`
  line `agricultural and rural development bank” shall have the meanings respectively assigned to`
  line `them in the Explanation to sub-section ( 4 ) of section 80P;`
  line `( e ) “housing finance company” means a public company formed or registered in India`
  line `with the main object of carrying on the business of providing long-term finance for`
  line `construction or purchase of houses in India for residential purposes;`
  line `( f ) “public company” shall have the meaning assigned to it in section 3 of the Companies`
  line `Act, 1956 (1 of 1956);`
  line `( g ) “infrastructure facility” means—`
  line `( i ) an infrastructure facility as defined in the Explanation to clause ( i ) of`
  line `sub-section ( 4 ) of section 80-IA, or any other public facility of a similar nature as may be`
  line `notified by the Board in this behalf in the Official Gazette and which fulfils the`
  line `conditions as may be prescribed;`
  line `( ii ) an undertaking referred to in clause ( ii ) or clause ( iii ) or clause ( iv ) or clause ( vi )`
  line `of sub-section ( 4 ) of section 80-IA; and`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 33 of 2009, s. 14, for clause ( i ) (w.e.f. 1-4-2010).`
