obj_root_law_sections_242_content:
  string
  line 242
  line `Explanation 3. — Where the assessee has entered into a contract with an authorised dealer as defined`
  line `in section 2 of the Foreign Exchange Management Act, 1999 (42 of 1999), for providing him with a`
  line `specified sum in a foreign currency on or after a stipulated future date at the rate of exchange specified in`
  line `the contract to enable him to meet the whole or any part of the liability aforesaid, the amount, if any, to be`
  line `added to, or deducted from, the actual cost of the asset or the amount of expenditure of a capital nature or,`
  line `as the case may be, the cost of acquisition of the capital asset under this section shall, in respect of so`
  line `much of the sum specified in the contract as is available for discharging the liability aforesaid, be`
  line `computed with reference to the rate of exchange specified therein.]`
  line `1 [ 43AA. Taxation of foreign exchange fluctuation. — ( 1 ) Subject to the provisions of section 43A,`
  line `any gain or loss arising on account of any change in foreign exchange rates shall be treated as income or`
  line `loss, as the case may be, and such gain or loss shall be computed in accordance with the income`
  line `computation and disclosure standards notified under sub-section ( 2 ) of section 145.`
  line `( 2 ) For the purposes of sub-section ( 1 ), gain or loss arising on account of the effects of change in`
  line `foreign exchange rates shall be in respect of all foreign currency transactions, including those relating`
  line `to —`
  line `( i ) monetary items and non-monetary items;`
  line `( ii ) translation of financial statements of foreign operations;`
  line `( iii ) forward exchange contracts;`
  line `( iv ) foreign currency translation reserves.]`
  line `2 [ 43B. Certain deductions to be only on actual payment. — Notwithstanding anything contained in`
  line `any other provision of this Act, a deduction otherwise allowable under this Act in respect of —`
  line `3 [( a ) any sum payable by the assessee by way of tax, duty, cess or fee, by whatever name called,`
  line `under any law for the time being in force, or]`
  line `( b ) any sum payable by the assessee as an employer by way of contribution to any provident fund`
  line `or superannuation fund or gratuity fund or any other fund for the welfare of employees, 4 [or]`
  line `4 [( c ) any sum referred to in clause ( ii ) of sub-section ( 1 ) of section 36,] 5 [or]`
  line `5 [( d ) any sum payable by the assessee as interest on any loan or borrowing from any public`
  line `financial institution 6 [or a State financial corporation or a State industrial investment corporation], in`
  line `accordance with the terms and conditions of the agreement 7 [governing such loan or borrowing; or]`
  line `8 [( e ) any sum payable by the assessee as interest on any 9 [loan or advances] from a scheduled`
  line `bank 10 [or a co-operative bank other than a primary agricultural credit society or a primary`
  line `co-operative agricultural and rural development bank] in accordance with the terms and conditions of`
  line `the agreement governing 11 [such loan or advances], 12 [or]`
  line `12 [( f ) any sum payable by the assessee as an employer in lieu of any leave at the credit of his`
  line `13 [employee, or]]`
  line `14 [( g ) any sum payable by the assessee to the Indian Railways for the use of railway assets,]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 13 of 2018, s. 13 (w.r.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 11 of 1983, s. 18 (we.f. 1-4-1984).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 26 of 1988, s. 12, for clause ( a ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 4 of 1988, s. 15 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 26 of 1988, s. 12 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 12 of 1990, s. 13 (w.e.f. 1-4-1991).`
  line `7. Subs. by Act 33 of 1996, s. 18, for “governing such loan or borrowing” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1997).`
  line `8. Ins. by s. 18, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-1997).`
  line `9. Subs. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 21, for “term loan” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2004).`
  line `10. Ins. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 17 (w.e.f. 1-4-2018).`
  line `11. Subs. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 21, for “such loan” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2004).`
  line `12. Ins. by Act 14 of 2001, s. 27 (w.e.f. 1-4-2002).`
  line `13. Subs. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 23, for “employee” ( w.e.f. 1 -4-2017).`
  line `14. Ins. by s. 23, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
