obj_root_law_sections_243_content:
  string
  line 243
  line `shall be allowed (irrespective of the previous year in which the liability to pay such sum was incurred by`
  line `the assessee according to the method of accounting regularly employed by him) only in computing the`
  line `income referred to in section 28 of that previous year in which such sum is actually paid by him:`
  line `1 [Provided that nothing contained in this section shall apply in relation to any sum 2 *** which is`
  line `actually paid by the assessee on or before the due date applicable in his case for furnishing the return of`
  line `income under sub-section ( 1 ) of section 139 in respect of the previous year in whichthe liability to pay`
  line `such sum was incurred as aforesaid and the evidence of such payment is furnished by the assessee along`
  line `with such return.`
  line `3 * * * * *]`
  line `Explanation 4 [1]. — For the removal of doubts, it is hereby declared that where a deduction in respect`
  line `of any sum referred to in clause ( a ) or clause ( b ) of this section is allowed in computing the income`
  line `referred to in section 28 of the previous year (being a previous year relevant to the assessment year`
  line `commencing on the 1st day of April, 1983, or any earlier assessment year) in which the liability to pay`
  line `such sum was incurred by the assessee, the assessee shall not be entitled to any deduction under this`
  line `section in respect of such sum in computing the income of the previous year in which the sum is actually`
  line `paid by him:]`
  line `5 [ Explanation 2. — For the purposes of clause ( a ), as in force at all material times, “any sum payable”`
  line `means a sum for which the assessee incurred liability in the previous year even though such sum might`
  line `not have been payable within that year under the relevant law.]`
  line `6 [ Explanation 7 [3]. — For the removal of doubts it is hereby declared that where a deduction in respect`
  line `of any sum referred to in clause ( c ) 8 [or clause ( d )] of this section is allowed in computing the income`
  line `referred to in section 28 of the previous year (being a previous year relevant to the assessment year`
  line `commencing on the 1st day of April, 1988, or any earlier assessment year) in which the liability to pay`
  line `such sum was incurred by the assessee, the assessee shall not be entitled to any deduction under this`
  line `section in respect of such sum in computing the income of the previous year in which the sum is actually`
  line `paid by him.]`
  line `9 [ Explanation 3A. — For the removal of doubts, it is hereby declared that where a deduction in respect`
  line `of any sum referred to in clause ( e ) of this section is allowed in computing the income referred to in`
  line `section 28 of the previous year (being a previous year relevant to the assessment year commencing on the`
  line `1st day of April, 1996, or any earlier assessment year) in which the liability to pay such sum was incurred`
  line `by the assessee, the assessee shall not be entitled to any deduction under this section in respect of such`
  line `sum in computing the income of the previous year in which the sum is actually paid by him.]`
  line `10 [ Explanation 3B. — For the removal of doubts, it is hereby declared that where a deduction in`
  line `respect of any sum referred to in clause ( f ) of this section is allowed in computing the income, referred to`
  line `in section 28, of the previous year (being a previous year relevant to the assessment year commencing on`
  line `the 1st day of April, 2001, or any earlier assessment year) in which the liability to pay such sum was`
  line `incurred by the assessee, the assessee shall not be entitled to any deduction under this section in respect of`
  line `such sum in computing the income of the previous year in which the sum is actually paid by him.]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 11 of 1987, s. 10 (w.e.f. 1-4-1988).`
  line `2. The words “referred to in clause ( a ) or clauses ( c ) or clause ( d ) or clause ( f )” omitted by Act 32 of 2003,`
  line `s. 21 (w.e.f. 1-4-2004).`
  line `3. The second proviso omitted by s. 21, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-2004).`
  line `4. The Explanation numbered as Explanation 1 thereof by Act 4 of 1988, s. 15 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 13 of 1989, s. 9 (w.e.f. 1-4-1984).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 4 of 1988, s. 15 (w.e.f 1-4-1989).`
  line `7. Explanation 2 renumbered as Explanation 3 thereof by Act 13 of 1989, s. 9 (w.e.f. 1-4-1984).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 26 of 1988, s. 12 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 33 of 1996, s. 18 (w.e.f. 1-4-1997).`
  line `10.Ins. by Act 14 of 2001, s. 27 (w.e.f. 1-4-2002).`
