obj_root_law_sections_249_content:
  string
  line 249
  line `1 [44AB. Audit of accounts of certain persons carrying on business or profession. — Every`
  line `person, —`
  line `( a ) carrying on business shall, if his total sales, turnover or gross receipts, as the case may be, in`
  line `business exceed or exceeds 2 [one crore rupees] in any previous year 3 ***; or`
  line `( b ) carrying on profession shall, if his gross receipts in profession exceed 4 [fifty lakh rupees] in`
  line `any 5 [previous year; or`
  line `( c ) carrying on the business shall, if the profits and gains from the business are deemed to be the`
  line `profits and gains of such person under 6 [section 44AE] 7 [or section 44BB or section 44BBB], as the`
  line `case may be, and he has claimed his income to be lower than the profits or gains so deemed to be the`
  line `profits and gains of his business, as the case may be, in any 8 [previous year; or] 3 ***]`
  line `9 [( d ) carrying on the 10 [profession] shall, if the profits and gains from the 10 [profession] are`
  line `deemed to be the profits and gains of such person 11 [under section 44ADA] and he has claimed such`
  line `income to be lower than the profits and gains so deemed to be the profits and gains of`
  line `his 10 [profession] and his income exceeds the maximum amount which is not chargeable to`
  line `income-tax in any 12 [previous year; or]]`
  line `13 [( e ) carrying on the business shall, if the provisions of sub-section ( 4 ) of section 44AD are`
  line `applicable in his case and his income exceeds the maximum amount which is not chargeable to`
  line `income-tax in any previous year,]`
  line `get his accounts of 14 [such previous year] audited by an accountant before the specified date and 15 [furnish`
  line `by] that date the report of such audit in the prescribed form duly signed and verified by such accountant`
  line `and setting forth such particulars as may be prescribed:`
  line `16 [Provided that this section shall not apply to the person, who declares profits and gains for the`
  line `previous year in accordance with the provisions of sub-section ( 1 ) of section 44AD and his total sales,`
  line `turnover or gross receipts, as the case may be, in business does not exceed two crore rupees in such`
  line `previous year:]`
  line `17 [ 18 [Provided further that] this section shall not apply to the person, who derives income of the nature`
  line `referred to in 19 *** section 44B or 20 [section 44BBA], on and from the 1st day of April, 1985 or, as the`
  line `case may be, the date on which the relevant section came into force, whichever is later:`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 21 of 1984, s. 11 (w.e.f. 1-4-1985).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 13, for “sixty lakh rupees” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2013).`
  line `3. The words and figures “or years relevant to the assessment year commencing on the first day of April, 1985, or any`
  line `subsequent assessment year” omitted by Act 26 of 1988, s. 14 (w.e.f. 1 -4-1989).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 25, for “twenty - five lakh rupees” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2017).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 26 of 1997, s. 11, for “previous year” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1998).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 33 of 2009, s. 19, for “section 44AD or section 44AE or section 44AF” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2011).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 23 (w.e.f. 1-4-2004).`
  line `8. Subs. by Act 33 of 2009, s. 19, for “previous year,” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2011).`
  line `9. Ins. by s. 19, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-2011).`
  line `10. Subs. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 25, for “Business” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2017).`
  line `11. Subs. by s. 25, ibid., for “under section 44AD” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2017).`
  line `12. Subs. by s. 25, ibid., for “previous year” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2017).`
  line `13. Ins. by s. 25, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
  line `14. Subs. by Act 26 of 1988, s. 14, for “such previous year or years” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1989).`
  line `15. Subs. by Act 22 of 1995, s. 13, for “obtain before” (w.e.f. 1 -7-1995).`
  line `16. Ins. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 20 (w.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
  line `17. Subs. by Act 18 of 1992, s. 20, for “Provided that” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1985).`
  line `18. Subs. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 20, for “Provided that” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2017).`
  line `19. The words, figures and letters “section 44AC or” omitted by Act 22 of 1995, s. 13 (w.e.f. 1 -7-1995).`
  line `20. Subs. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 23, for “section 44BB or section 44BBA or section 44BBB” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2004).`
