obj_root_law_sections_263_content:
  string
  line 263
  line `1 [( c ) where in the assessment for any year, the capital gain arising from the transfer of a capital`
  line `asset is computed by taking the compensation or consideration referred to in clause ( a ) or, as the case`
  line `may be, enhanced compensation or consideration referred to in clause ( b ), and subsequently such`
  line `compensation or consideration is reduced by any court, Tribunal or other authority, such assessed`
  line `capital gain of that year shall be recomputed by taking the compensation or consideration as so`
  line `reduced by such court, Tribunal or other authority to be the full value of the consideration.]`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this sub-section, —`
  line `( i ) in relation to the amount referred to in clause ( b ), the cost of acquisition and the cost of`
  line `improvement shall be taken to be nil;`
  line `( ii ) the provisions of this sub-section shall apply also in a case where the transfer took place`
  line `prior to the 1st day of April, 1988;`
  line `( iii ) where by reason of the death of the person who made the transfer, or for any other`
  line `reason, the enhanced compensation or consideration is received by any other person, the amount`
  line `referred to in clause ( b ) shall be deemed to be the income, chargeable to tax under the head`
  line `“Capital gains”, of such other person.]`
  line `2 [( 5A ) Notwithstanding anything contained in sub-section ( 1 ), where the capital gain arises to an`
  line `assessee, being an individual or a Hindu undivided family, from the transfer of a capital asset, being land`
  line `or building or both, under a specified agreement, the capital gains shall be chargeable to income-tax as`
  line `income of the previous year in which the certificate of completion for the whole or part of the project is`
  line `issued by the competent authority; and for the purposes of section 48, the stamp duty value, on the date of`
  line `issue of the said certificate, of his share, being land or building or both in the project, as increased by the`
  line `consideration received in cash, if any, shall be deemed to be the full value of the consideration received or`
  line `accruing as a result of the transfer of the capital asset:`
  line `Provided that the provisions of this sub-section shall not apply where the assessee transfers his share in`
  line `the project on or before the date of issue of the said certificate of completion, and the capital gains shall be`
  line `deemed to be the income of the previous year in which such transfer takes place and the provisions of this`
  line `Act, other than the provisions of this sub-section, shall apply for the purpose of determination of full value`
  line `of consideration received or accruing as a result of such transfer.`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this sub-section, the expression —`
  line `( i ) “competent authority” means the authority empowered to approve the building plan by or`
  line `under any law for the time being in force;`
  line `( ii ) “specified agreement” means a registered agreement in which a person owning land or`
  line `building or both, agrees to allow another person to develop a real estate project on such land or`
  line `building or both, in consideration of a share, being land or building or both in such project, whether`
  line `with or without payment of part of the consideration in cash;`
  line `( iii ) “stamp duty value” means the value adopted or assessed or assessable by any authority of the`
  line `Government for the purpose of payment of stamp duty in respect of an immovable property being land`
  line `or building or both.’.]`
  line `3 [( 6 ) Notwithstanding anything contained in sub-section ( 1 ), the difference between the repurchase`
  line `price of the units referred to in sub-section ( 2 ) of section 80CCB and the capital value of such units shall`
  line `be deemed to be the capital gains arising to the assessee in the previous year in which such repurchase`
  line `takes place or the plan referred to in that section is terminated and shall be taxed accordingly.`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this sub- section, “capital value of such units” means any`
  line `amount invested by the assessee in the units referred to in sub-section ( 2 ) of section 80CCB.]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 29 (w.e.f. 1-4-2004).`
  line `2. I ns. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 22 (w.e.f 1-4-2018).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 12 of 1990, s. 15 (w.e.f. 1-4-1991).`
