obj_root_law_sections_267_content:
  string
  line 267
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this clause, —`
  line `( a ) “International Financial Services Centre” shall have the meaning assigned to it in`
  line `clause ( q ) of section 2 of the Special Economic Zones Act, 2005;`
  line `( b ) “recognised stock exchange” shall have the meaning assigned to it in clause ( ii ) of`
  line `Explanation 1 to clause ( 5 ) of section 43;`
  line `( c ) “derivative” shall have the meaning assigned to it in clause ( ac ) of section 2 of the`
  line `Securities Contracts (Regulation) Act, 1956.]`
  line `1 [( viib ) any transfer of a capital asset, being a Government Security carrying a periodic payment`
  line `of interest, made outside India through an intermediary dealing in settlement of securities, by a non-`
  line `resident to another non-resident.`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this claus e, “Government Security” shall have the meaning`
  line `assigned to it in clause ( b ) of section 2 of the Securities Contracts (Regulation) Act, 1956 (42 of`
  line `1956);]`
  line `2 [( viic ) any transfer of Sovereign Gold Bond issued by the Reserve Bank of India under the`
  line `Sovereign Gold Bond Scheme, 2015, by way of redemption, by an assessee being an individual;]`
  line `3 [( viii ) any transfer of agricultural land in India effected before the 1st day of March, 1970;]`
  line `4 [( ix ) any transfer of a capital asset, being any work of art, archaeological, scientific or art`
  line `collection, book, manuscript, drawing, painting, photograph or print, to the Government or a`
  line `University or the National Museum, National Art Gallery, National Archives or any such other public`
  line `museum or institution as may be notified by the Central Government in the Official Gazette to be of`
  line `national importance or to be of renown throughout any State or States.`
  line `Explanation. —For the purposes of this clause, “University” means a University established or`
  line `incorporated by or under a Central, State or Provincial Act and includes an institution declared under`
  line `section 3 of the University Grants Commission Act, 1956 (3 of 1956), to be a University for the`
  line `purposes of that Act;]`
  line `5 [( x ) any transfer by way of 6 [conversion of bonds or debentures], debenture-stock or deposit`
  line `certificates in any form, of a company into shares or debentures of that company;]`
  line `7 [( xa ) any transfer by way of conversion of bonds referred to in clause ( a ) of sub-section ( 1 )`
  line `of section 115AC into shares or debentures of any company;]`
  line `8 [( xb ) any transfer by way of conversion of preference shares of a company into equity shares of`
  line `that company;]`
  line `9 [( xi ) any transfer made on or before the 10 [31st day of December, 1998] by a person (not being a`
  line `company) of a capital asset being membership of a recognised stock exchange to a company in`
  line `exchange of shares allotted by that company to the transferor.`
  line `Explanation. —For the purposes of this clause, the expression “membership of a recognised stock`
  line `exchange” means the membership of a stock ex change in India which is recognised under the`
  line `provisions of the Securities Contracts (Regulation) Act, 1956 (42 of 1956);`
  line `( xii ) any transfer of a capital asset, being land of a sick industrial company, made under a scheme`
  line `prepared and sanctioned under section 18 of the Sick Industrial Companies (Special Provisions)`
  line `Act, 1985 (1 of 1986) where such sick industrial company is being managed by its workers’`
  line `co-operative:`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 25 of 2014, s. 18 (w.e.f. 1-4-2015).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 28 (w.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 19 of 1970, s. 11 (w.e.f. 1-4-1970).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 66 of 1976, s. 11 (w.e.f. 1-4-1977).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 49 of 1991, s. 18 (w.e.f. 1-4-1962).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 18 of 1992, s. 23 for “conversion of debentures” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1962).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 18 of 2008, s. 14 (w.e.f. 1-4-2008).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 23 (w.e.f. 1-4-2018).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 26 of 1997, s. 16 (w.e.f. 1-4-1998).`
  line `10. Subs. by Act 21 of 1998, s. 21 for “31st day of December, 1997” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1998).`
