obj_root_law_sections_271_content:
  string
  line 271
  line `with the Securities and Exchange Board of India (Mutual Funds) Regulations, 1996 made under`
  line `the Securities and Exchange Board of India Act, 1992 (15 of 1992);`
  line `( b ) “consolidated plan” means the plan with which the consolidating plan merges or which is`
  line `formed as a result of such merger;`
  line `( c ) “mutual fund” means a mutual fund specified under clause ( 23D ) of section 10.]`
  line `1 [47A. Withdrawal of exemption in certain cases. — ( 1 ) Where at any time before the expiry of a`
  line `period of eight years from the date of the transfer of a capital asset referred to in clause ( iv ) or, as the case`
  line `may be, clause (v) of section 147, —`
  line `( i ) such capital asset is converted by the transferee company into, or is treated by it as, stock-in-`
  line `trade of its business; or`
  line `( ii ) the parent company or its nominees or, as the case may be, the holding company ceases or`
  line `cease to hold the whole of the share capital of the subsidiary company,`
  line `the amount of profits or gains arising from the transfer of such capital asset not charged under`
  line `section 45 by virtue of the provisions contained in clause ( iv ) or, as the case may be, clause ( v ) of`
  line `section 47 shall, notwithstanding anything contained in the said clauses, be deemed to be income`
  line `chargeable under the head “Capital gains” of the previous year in which such transfer took place.]`
  line `2 [( 2 ) Where at any time, before the expiry of a period of three years from the date of the transfer of a`
  line `capital asset referred to in clause ( xi ) of section 47, any of the shares allotted to the transferor in exchange`
  line `of a membership in a recognised stock exchange are transferred, the amount of profits and gains not`
  line `charged under section 45 by virtue of the provisions contained in clause ( xi ) of section 47 shall,`
  line `notwithstanding anything contained in the said clause, be deemed to be the income chargeable under the`
  line `head “Capital gains” of the previous year in which such shares are transferred.]`
  line `3 [( 3 ) Where any of the conditions laid down in the proviso to clause ( xiii ) or the proviso to clause`
  line `( xiv ) of section 47 are not complied with, the amount of profits or gains arising from the transfer of such`
  line `capital asset or intangible asset not charged under section 45 by virtue of conditions laid down in the`
  line `proviso to clause ( xiii ) or the proviso to clause ( xiv ) of section 47 shall be deemed to be the profits and`
  line `gains chargeable to tax of the successor company for the previous year in which the requirements of the`
  line `proviso to clause ( xiii ) or the proviso to clause ( xiv ), as the case may be, are not complied with.]`
  line `4 [( 4 ) Where any of the conditions laid down in the proviso to clause ( xiiib ) of section 47 are not`
  line `complied with, the amount of profits or gains arising from the transfer of such capital asset or intangible`
  line `assets or share or shares not charged under section 45 by virtue of conditions laid down in the said`
  line `proviso shall be deemed to be the profits and gains chargeable to tax of the successor limited liability`
  line `partnership or the shareholder of the predecessor company, as the case may be, for the previous year in`
  line `which the requirements of the said proviso are not complied with.]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 67 of 1984, s. 13 (w.e.f. 1-4-1985).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 26 of 1997, s. 17 (w.e.f. 1-4-1998).`
  line `3. Ins.by Act 21 of 1998, s. 22 (w.e.f. 1-4-1999).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 14 of 2010, s. 19 (w.e.f. 1-4-2011).`
