obj_root_law_sections_275_content:
  string
  line 275
  line `1 [( 2AE ) Where the capital asset, being equity share of a company, became the property of the assessee in`
  line `consideration of a transfer referred to in clause ( xb ) of section 47, the cost of acquisition of the asset shall be`
  line `deemed to be that part of the cost of the preference share in relation to which such asset is acquired by the`
  line assessee.]
  line `2 [( 2AF ) Where the capital asset, being a unit or units in a consolidated plan of a mutual fund scheme,`
  line `became the property of the assessee in consideration of a transfer referred to in clause ( xix ) of section 47,`
  line `the cost of acquisition of the asset shall be deemed to be the cost of acquisition to him of the unit or units in`
  line `the consolidating plan of the scheme of the mutual fund.]`
  line `3 * * * * *`
  line `4 [( 2C ) The cost of acquisition of the shares in the resulting company shall be the amount which bears`
  line `to the cost of acquisition of shares held by the assessee in the demerged company the same proportion as`
  line `the net book value of the assets transferred in a demerger bears to the net worth of the demerged company`
  line `immediately before such demerger.`
  line `( 2D ) The cost of acquisition of the original shares held by the shareholder in the demerged company`
  line `shall be deemed to have been reduced by the amount as so arrived at under sub-section ( 2C ).]`
  line `5 [( 2E ) The provisions of sub-section ( 2 ), sub-section ( 2C ) and sub-section ( 2D ) shall, as far as may`
  line `be, also apply in relation to business reorganisation of a co-operative bank as referred to in`
  line `section 44DB.]`
  line `Explanation. —For the purposes of this section, “net worth” shall mean the aggregate of the paid up`
  line `share capital and general reserves as appearing in the books of account of the demerged company`
  line `immediately before the demerger.]`
  line `6 [( 3 ) Notwithstanding anything contained in sub-section ( 1 ), where the capital gain arising from the`
  line `transfer of a capital asset referred to in clause ( iv ) or, as the case may be, clause ( v ) of section 47 is`
  line `deemed to be income chargeable under the head “Capital gains” by virtue of the provisions contained in`
  line `section 47A, the cost of acquisition of such asset to the transferee-company shall be the cost for which`
  line `such asset was acquired by it.]`
  line `7 [( 4 ) Where the capital gain arises from the transfer of a property, the value of which has been subject`
  line `to income-tax under clause ( vii ) 8 [or clause ( viia )] 2 [or clause ( x )] of sub-section ( 2 ) of section 56, the cost`
  line `of acquisition of such property shall be deemed to be the value which has been taken into account for the`
  line `purposes of the said clause ( vii ) 8 [or clause ( viia )] 2 [or clause ( x )].]`
  line `9 [( 5 ) Where the capital gain arises from the transfer of an asset declared under the Income Declaration`
  line `Scheme, 2016, and the tax, surcharge and penalty have been paid in accordance with the provisions of the`
  line `Scheme on the fair market value of the asset as on the date of commencement of the Scheme, the cost of`
  line `acquisition of the asset shall be deemed to be the fair market value of the asset which has been taken into`
  line `account for the purposes of the said Scheme.]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 25 (w.e.f. 1-4-2018).`
  line `2. Ins. by s. 25, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
  line `3. Sub-section ( 2B ) omitted by Act 10 of 2000, s. 23 (w.e.f. 1-4-2000).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 27 of 1999, s. 35 (w.e.f. 1-4-2000).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 22 of 2007, s. 17 (w.e.f. 1-4-2008).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 67 of 1984, s. 14 (w.e.f. 1-4-1985).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 33 of 2009, s. 23 (w.e.f. 1-10-2009).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 14 of 2010, s. 20 (w.e.f. 1-6-2010).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 30 (w.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
