obj_root_law_sections_284_content:
  string
  line 284
  line `( iv ) debentures specified by the Central Government for the purposes of clause ( ii ) of`
  line `sub-section ( 1 ) of section 80L;`
  line `( v ) shares in any Indian company which are issued to the public or are listed in a recognised`
  line `stock exchange in India in accordance with the Securities Contracts (Regulation) Act, 1956 (42 of`
  line `1956), and any rules made thereunder, where the investment in such shares is made before the 1st`
  line `day of March, 1978;`
  line `1 [( va ) equity shares forming part of any eligible issue of capital, where the investment in such`
  line `shares is made after the 28th day of February, 1978;]`
  line `( vi ) deposits for a period of not less than three years with the State Bank of India established`
  line `under the State Bank of India Act, 1955 (23 of 1955), or any subsidiary bank as defined in the`
  line `State Bank of India (Subsidiary Banks) Act, 1959 (38 of 1959) or any nationalised bank, that is to`
  line `say, any corresponding new bank, constituted under section 3 of the Banking Companies`
  line `(Acquisition and Transfer of Undertakings) Act, 1970 (5 of 1970), or any co-operative society`
  line `engaged in carrying on the business of banking (including a co-operative land mortgage bank or a`
  line `co-operative land development bank);`
  line `2 [( b ) in a case where the original asset is transferred after the 28th day of February, 1979 3 [but`
  line `before the 1st day of March, 1983], such National Rural Development Bonds as the Central`
  line `Government may notify in this behalf in the Official Gazette;]`
  line `3 [( c ) in a case where the original asset is transferred after the 28th day of February, 1983 4 [but`
  line `before the 1st day of April, 1986], any of the following assets, namely: —`
  line `( i ) securities of the Central Government which that Government may, by notification in the`
  line `Official Gazette, specify in this behalf;`
  line `( ii ) special series of units of the Unit Trust of India established under the Unit Trust of India`
  line `Act, 1963 (52 of 1963), which the Central Government may, by notification in the Official`
  line `Gazette, specify in this behalf;`
  line `( iii ) such National Rural Development Bonds as have been notified under clause ( b )`
  line `of Explanation 1 or as may be notified in this behalf under this clause by the Central`
  line Government;
  line `( iv ) such debentures issued by the Housing and Urban Development Corporation Limited [a`
  line `Government company as defined in section 617 of the Companies Act, 1956 (1 of 1956)], as the`
  line `Central Government may, by notification in the Official Gazette, specify in this behalf;]`
  line `4 [( d ) in a case where the original asset is transferred after the 31st day of March, 1986, any of the`
  line `assets specified in clause ( c ) and such bonds issued by any public sector company, as the Central`
  line `Government may, by notification in the Official Gazette, specify in this behalf;]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 19 of 1978, s. 13 (w.e.f. 1-4-1978).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 21 of 1979, s. 8 (w.e.f. 1-4-1979).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 11 of 1983, s. 20 (w.e.f. 1-4-1983).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 23 of 1986, s. 12 (w.e.f. 1-4-1987).`
