  line 285
  line `1 * * * * *]`
  line `2 [( e ) in a case where the original asset is transferred after the 31st day of March, 1989, any of the`
  line `assets specified in clauses ( c ) and ( d ) and such debentures or bonds issued by the National Housing`
  line `Bank established under section 3 of the National Housing Bank Act, 1987 (53 of 1987), as the Central`
  line `Government may, by notification in the Official Gazette, specify in this behalf.]`
  line `3 [ Explanation 2. —“Eligible issue of capital” shall have the meaning assigned to it in sub -section ( 3 )`
  line `of section 80CC.`
  line `Explanation 3. — An assessee shall not be deemed to have invested 4 [the whole or any part of the net`
  line `consideration in any equity shares referred to in sub-clause ( va ) of clause ( a )] of Explanation 1, unless the`
  line `assessee has subscribed to or purchased the shares in the manner specified in sub-section ( 4 ) of`
  line `section 80CC. ]`
  line `5 [ Explanation 4]. —“Cost”, in rel ation to any new asset, being a deposit referred to in 6 [sub-clause ( vi )`
  line `of clause ( a )] of Explanation 1, means the amount of such deposit.`
  line `7 [ Explanation 5. —”Net consideration”, in relation to the transfer of a capital asset, means the full`
  line `value of the consideration received or accruing as a result of the transfer of the capital asset as reduced by`
  line `any expenditure incurred wholly and exclusively in connection with such transfer.]`
  line `8 [( 1A ) Where the assessee deposits after the 27th day of April, 1978, the 9 [whole or any part of the net`
  line `consideration in respect] of the original asset in any new asset, being a deposit 10 [referred to in`
  line `sub-clause ( vi ) of clause ( a )] of Explanation 1 below sub-section ( 1 ), the cost of such new asset shall not`
  line `be taken into account for the purposes of that sub-section unless the following conditions are fulfilled,`
  line `namely: —`
  line `( a ) the assessee furnishes, along with the deposit, a declaration in writing, to the bank or the`
  line `co-operative society referred to in the 11 [said sub-clause ( vi )] with which such deposit is made, to the`
  line `effect that the assessee will not take any loan or advance on the security of such deposit during a`
  line `period of three years from the date on which the deposit is made;`
  line `( b ) the assessee furnishes, along with the return of income for the assessment year relevant to the`
  line `previous year in which the transfer of the original asset was effected or within such further time as`
  line `may be allowed by the 12 [Assessing Officer], a copy of the declaration referred to in clause ( a ) duly`
  line `attested by an officer not below the rank of sub-agent, agent or manager of such bank or an officer of`
  line `corresponding rank of such co-operative society.`
  line `1. The Explanation omitted by Act 11 of 1987, s. 74 (w.e.f. 1-4-1987).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 13 of 1989, s. 12 (w.e.f. 1-4-1990).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 19 of 1978, s. 13 (w.e.f. 1-4-1978).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 21 of 1979, s. 8, for “the full value of the consideration or any part there of in any equity shares referred to in`
  line `clause ( va )” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1979).`
  line `5. Explanation 2 renumbered as Explanation 4 by Act 19 of 1978, s. 13 (w.e.f. 1-4-1978).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 21 of 1979, s. 8, for “clause ( vi )” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1979).`
  line `7. Ins. by s. 8, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-1979).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 19 of 1978, s. 13 (w.e.f. 1-4-1978).`
  line `9. Subs. by Act 21 of 1979, s. 8, for “full value of the consideration or any part thereof received or accruing as a result o f the`
  line `transfer” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1979).`
  line `10. Subs. by s. 8, ibid., f or “referred to in clause ( vi )” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1979).`
  line `11. Subs. by s. 8, ibid., for “said clause ( vi )” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1979).`
  line `12. Subs. by Act 4 of 1988, s. 2, “Income - tax Officer” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1988).`
