obj_root_law_sections_286_content:
  string
  line 286
  line `( 1B ) Where on the fulfilment of the conditions specified in sub-section ( 1A ), the cost of the new asset`
  line `referred to in that sub-section is taken into account for the purposes of sub-section ( 1 ), the assessee shall,`
  line `within a period of ninety days from the expiry of the period of three years reckoned from the date of such`
  line `deposit, furnish to the 1 [Assessing Officer] a certificate from the officer referred to in clause ( b ) of`
  line `sub-section ( 1A ) to the effect that the assessee has not taken any loan or advance on the security of such`
  line `deposit during the said period of three years.]`
  line `2 [( 1C ) Notwithstanding anything contained in sub-section ( 1 ), where the capital gain arises from the`
  line `transfer of the original asset, made after the 31st day of March, 1992, in respect of which the assessee had`
  line `received any amount by way of advance on or before the 29th day of February, 1992 and had invested or`
  line `deposited the whole or any part of such amount in the new asset on or before the later date, then, the`
  line `provisions of clauses ( a ) and ( b ) of sub-section ( 1 ) shall apply in the case of such investment or deposit as`
  line `they apply in the case of investment or deposit under that sub-section.]`
  line `( 2 ) Where the new asset is transferred, or converted (otherwise than by transfer) into money, within a`
  line `period of three years from the date of its acquisition, the amount of capital gain arising from the transfer`
  line `of the original asset not charged under section 45 on the basis of the cost of such new asset as provided in`
  line `clause ( a ) or, as the case may be, clause ( b ), of sub-section ( 1 ) shall be deemed to be income chargeable`
  line `under the head “Capital gains” relating to 3 [long-term capital assets] of the previous year in which the`
  line `new asset is transferred or converted (otherwise than by transfer) into money.]`
  line `4 [ 5 [ Explanation1 ]. — Where the assessee deposits after the 27th day of April, 1978, the 6 [whole or any`
  line `part of the net consideration in respect] of the original asset in any new asset, being a deposit referred to`
  line `in 7 [sub-clause ( vi ) of clause ( a )] of Explanation 1 below sub-section ( 1 ), and such assessee takes any`
  line `loan or advance on the security of such deposit, he shall be deemed to have converted (otherwise than by`
  line `transfer) such deposit into money on the date on which such loan or advance is taken.]`
  line `8 [ Explanation 2. — In a case where the original asset is transferred after the 28th day of February,`
  line `1983 and the assessee invests the whole or any part of the net consideration in respect of the original asset`
  line `in any new asset and such assessee takes any loan or advance on the security of such new asset, he shall`
  line `be deemed to have converted (otherwise than by transfer) such new asset on the date on which such loan`
  line `or advance is taken.]`
  line `9 * * * * *`
  line `10 [( 3 )] Where the cost of the equity shares referred to in 11 [sub-clause ( va ) of clause ( a )] of`
  line `Explanation 1 below sub-section ( 1 ) is taken into account for the purposes of clause ( a ) or clause ( b ) of`
  line `sub-section ( 1 ) 12 ***, a deduction with reference to such cost shall not be allowed under section 80CC.`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 4 of 1988, s. 2, for “Income - tax Officer” (w. e.f. 1-4-1988).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 18 of 1992, s. 30 (w.e.f. 1-4-1992).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 11 of 1987, s. 22, for “capital assets other than short - term capital assets” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1988).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 19 of 1978, s. 13 (w.e.f. 1-4-1978).`
  line `5. The Explanation numbered as Explanation 1 by Act 11 of 1983, s. 20 (w.e.f. 1-4-1983).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 21 of 1979, s. 8, for “full value of the consideration or any part thereof received or accruing as a result o f the`
  line `transfer” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1979).`
  line `7. Subs. by s. 8, ibid., for “clause ( vi )” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1979).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 11 of 1983, s. 20 (w.e.f. 1-4-1983).`
  line `9. Sub-sections ( 3 ), ( 4 ) and ( 5 ) omitted by Act 11 of 1987, s. 22 (w.e.f. 1-4-1988).`
  line `10. Sub-section ( 6 ) renumbered as sub-section ( 3 ) by s. 22, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-1988).`
  line `11. Subs. by Act 21 of 1979, s. 8, for “clause ( va )” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1979).`
  line `12. The words, brackets, letters and figure “or clause ( a ) or clause ( b ) of sub-section ( 3 )” omitted by Act 11 of 1987, s. 22`
  line `(w.e.f. 1-4-1988).`
