obj_root_law_sections_290_content:
  string
  line 290
  line `( i ) by the National Highways Authority of India constituted under section 3 of the`
  line `National Highways Authority of India Act, 1988 (68 of 1988); or`
  line `( ii ) by the Rural Electrification Corporation Limited, a company formed and registered`
  line `under the Companies Act, 1956 (1 of 1956),`
  line `and notified by the Central Government in the Official Gazette for the purposes of this section with such`
  line `conditions (including the condition for providing a limit on the amount of investment by an assessee in`
  line `such bond) as it thinks fit:]`
  line `1 [Provided that where any bond has been notified before the 1st day of April, 2007, subject to the`
  line `conditions specified in the notification, by the Central Government in the Official Gazette under the`
  line `provisions of clause ( b ) as they stood immediately before their amendment by the Finance Act, 2007`
  line `(22 of 2007), such bond shall be deemed to be a bond notified under this clause;]`
  line `2 [( ba ) “long - term specified asset” for making any investment under this section,––`
  line `( i ) on or after the 1st day of April, 2007 but before the 1st day of April, 2018, means any`
  line `bond, redeemable after three years and issued on or after the 1st day of April, 2007 but before the`
  line `1st day of April, 2018;`
  line `( ii ) on or after the 1st day of April, 2018, means any bond, redeemable after five years and`
  line `issued on or after the 1st day of April, 2018, by the National Highways Authority of India`
  line `constituted under section 3 of the National Highways Authority of India Act, 1988 or by the`
  line `Rural Electrification Corporation Limited, a company formed and registered under the`
  line `Companies Act, 1956 or any other bond notified in the Official Gazette by the Central`
  line `Government in this behalf.]`
  line `3 [ 54ED. Capital gain on transfer of certain listed securities or unit not to be charged in certain`
  line `cases. — ( 1 ) Where the capital gain arises 4 [from the transfer before the 1st day of April, 2006, of a long-`
  line `term capital asset,] being listed securities or unit (the capital asset so transferred being hereafter in this`
  line `section referred to as the original asset), and the assessee has, within a period of six months after the date`
  line `of such transfer, invested the whole or any part of the capital gain in acquiring equity shares forming part`
  line `of an eligible issue of capital (such equity shares being hereafter in this section referred to as the specified`
  line `equity shares), the said capital gain shall be dealt with in accordance with the following provisions of this`
  line `section, that is to say, —`
  line `( a ) if the cost of the specified equity shares is not less than the capital gain arising from the`
  line `transfer of the original asset, the whole of such capital gain shall not be charged under section 45;`
  line `( b ) if the cost of the specified equity shares is less than the capital gain arising from the transfer`
  line `of the original asset, so much of the capital gain as bears to the whole of the capital gain the same`
  line `proportion as the cost of the specified equity shares acquired bears to the whole of the capital gain`
  line `shall not be charged under section 45.`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this sub-section, —`
  line `( i ) “eligible issue of capital” means an issue of equity shares which satisfies the following`
  line `conditions, namely: —`
  line `( a ) the issue is made by a public company formed and registered in India;`
  line `( b ) the shares forming part of the issue are offered for subscription to the public;`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 22 of 2007, s. 18 (w.e.f. 1-4-2006).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 13 of 2018, s. 21, for clause ( ba ) (w.e.f. 1-4-2019) which was earlier inserted by Act 22 of 2007, s. 18`
  line `(w.e.f. 1-4-2006) and later amended by Act 7 of 2017, s. 27 (w.e.f. 1-4-2018).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 14 of 2001, s. 32 (w.e.f. 1-4-2002).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 21 of 2006, s. 14, for “from the transfer of a long - term capital asset” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2007).`
