  title `Page 293`
  content obj_root_law_sections_293_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_293_footnotes
  sourcePage 293
obj_root_law_sections_293_content:
  string
  line 293
  line `1 *** “net c onsideration”, in relation to the transfer of a capital asset, means the full value of the`
  line `consideration received or accruing as a result of the transfer of the capital asset as reduced by any`
  line `expenditure incurred wholly and exclusively in connection with such transfer.`
  line `( 2 ) Where the assessee purchases, within the period of 2 [two years] after the date of the transfer of the`
  line `original asset, or constructs, within the period of three years after such date, any residential house, the`
  line `income from which is charge able under the head “Income from house property”, other than the new asset,`
  line `the amount of capital gain arising from the transfer of the original asset not charged under section 45 on`
  line `the basis of the cost of such new asset as provided in clause ( a ), or, as the case may be, clause ( b ), of sub-`
  line `section ( 1 ), shall be deemed to be income chargeable under the head “Capital gains” relating to long -term`
  line `capital assets of the previous year in which such residential house is purchased or constructed.`
  line `( 3 ) Where the new asset is transferred within a period of three years from the date of its purchase or,`
  line `as the case may be, its construction, the amount of capital gain arising from the transfer of the original`
  line `asset not charged under section 45 on the basis of the cost of such new asset as provided in clause ( a ) or,`
  line `as the case may be, clause ( b ), of sub-section ( 1 ) shall be deemed to be income chargeable under the head`
  line `“Capital gains” relating to long -term capital assets of the previous year in which such new asset is`
  line transferred.]
  line `3 [( 4 ) The amount of the net consideration which is not appropriated by the assessee towards the`
  line `purchase of the new asset made within one year before the date on which the transfer of the original asset`
  line `took place, or which is not utilised by him for the purchase or construction of the new asset before the`
  line `date of furnishing the return of income under section 139, shall be deposited by him before furnishing`
  line `such return [such deposit being made in any case not later than the due date applicable in the case of the`
  line `assessee for furnishing the return of income under sub-section ( 1 ) of section 139] in an account in any`
  line `such bank or institution as may be specified in, and utilised in accordance with, any schemewhich the`
  line `Central Government may, by notification in the Official Gazette, frame in this behalf and such return`
  line `shall be accompanied by proof of such deposit; and, for the purposes of sub-section ( 1 ), the amount, if`
  line `any, already utilised by the assessee for the purchase or construction of the new asset together with the`
  line `amount so deposited shall be deemed to be the cost of the new asset:`
  line `Provided that if the amount deposited under this sub-section is not utilised wholly or partly for the`
  line `purchase or construction of the new asset within the period specified in sub-section ( 1 ), then, —`
  line `( i ) the amount by which —`
  line `( a ) the amount of capital gain arising from the transfer of the original asset not charged`
  line `under section 45 on the basis of the cost of the new asset as provided in clause ( a ) or, as the case`
  line `may be, clause ( b ) of sub-section ( 1 ), exceeds`
  line `( b ) the amount that would not have been so charged had the amount actually utilised by the`
  line `assessee for the purchase or construction of the new asset within the period specified in`
  line `sub-section ( 1 ) been the cost of the new asset,`
  line `shall be charged under section 45 as income of the previous year in which the period of three years from`
  line `the date of the transfer of the original asset expires; and`
  line `1. The bracket and figure “( ii )” omitted byAct 11 of 1987, s. 23 (w.e.f. 1 -4-1988).`
  line `2. Subs. by s. 23, ibid., for “one year” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1988).`
  line `3. Ins. by s. 23, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-1988).`
