  title `Page 299`
  content obj_root_law_sections_299_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_299_footnotes
  sourcePage 299
obj_root_law_sections_299_content:
  string
  line 299
  line `1 [Provided that in the case of an eligible start-up, being a technology driven start-up so certified by`
  line `the Inter-Ministerial Board of Certification notified by the Central Government in the Official Gazette,`
  line `the new asset shall include computers or computer software.]`
  line `2 [54H. Extension of time for acquiring new asset or depositing or investing amount of capital`
  line `gain. — Notwithstanding anything contained in sections 54, 54B, 54D 3 *** 4 [, 54EC] and 54F, where the`
  line `transfer of the original asset is by way of compulsory acquisition under any law and the amount of`
  line `compensation awarded for such acquisition is not received by the assessee on the date of such transfer,`
  line `the period for acquiring the new asset by the assessee referred to in those sections or, as the case may be,`
  line `the period available to the assessee under those sections for depositing or investing the amount of capital`
  line `gain in relation to such compensation as is not received on the date of the transfer, shall be reckoned from`
  line `the date of receipt of such compensation:`
  line `Provided that where the compensation in respect of transfer of the original asset by way of`
  line `compulsory acquisition under any law is received before the 1st day of April, 1991, the aforesaid period`
  line `or periods, if expired, shall extend up to the 31st day of December, 1991.]`
  line `55. Meaning of “adjusted”, “cost of improvement” and “cost of acquisition”. — ( 1 ) For the`
  line `purposes of 5 [sections 48 and 49], —`
  line `6 * * * * *`
  line `7 [( b ) “cost of any improvement”,—`
  line `( 1 ) in relation to a capital asset being goodwill of a business 8 [or a right to manufacture,`
  line `produce or process any article or thing] 9 [or right to carry on any business 10 [or profession]] shall`
  line `be taken to be nil; and`
  line `( 2 ) in relation to any other capital asset, — ]`
  line `( i ) where the capital asset became the property of the previous owner or the assessee`
  line `before the 11 [1st day of April, 2001], 12 *** means all expenditure of a capital nature incurred`
  line `in making any additions or alterations to the capital asset on or after the said date by the`
  line `previous owner or the assessee, and`
  line `( ii ) in any other case, means all expenditure of a capital nature incurred in making any`
  line `additions or alterations to the capital asset by the assessee after it became his property, and,`
  line `where the capital asset became the property of the assessee by any of the modes specified in`
  line `13 [sub-section ( 1 ) of section 49], by the previous owner,`
  line `but does not include any expenditure which is deductible in computing the income chargeable under`
  line `the head “Interest on securities”, “Income from house property”, “Profits and gains of business or`
  line `profession”, or “Income from other sources”, and the expression “improvement” shall be construed`
  line accordingly.
  line `1. Ins. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 33 (w.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 49 of 1991, s. 21 (w.e.f. 1-10-1991).`
  line `3. The figures and letter “, 54E” omitted by Act 18 of 1992, s. 33 (w.e.f 1 -4-1992).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 14 of 2001, s. 33, for “, 54EA, 54EB” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2001).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 46 of 1986, s. 32, for “sections 48, 49 and 50” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1988).`
  line `6. Clause ( a ) omitted by s. 32, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-1988).`
  line `7. Subs. by 11 of 1987, s. 25, for clause ( b ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1988).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 26 of 1997, s. 19 (w.e.f. 1-4-1998).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 26 (w.e.f. 1-4-2003).`
  line `10. Ins. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 34 (w.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
  line `11. Subs. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 28, for “1st day of April, 1981” (w.e.f. 1 -4- 2018). Earlier “1st day of April, 1974” was`
  line `substituted by Act 23 of 1986, s. 13, for “1st day of January, 1964” (w.e.f. 1 -4- 1987) and later “1981” was substituted`
  line `by Act 18 of 1992, s. 34, for “1974” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1993).`
  line `12. The words “and the fair market value of the asset on that day is taken as the cost of acquisition at the option of the`
  line `assessee,” omit ted by s. 34, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-1993).`
  line `13. Subs. by Act 20 of 1967, s. 21, for “section 49” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1967).`
