obj_root_law_sections_301_content:
  string
  line 301
  line `1 [( ac ) subject to the provisions of sub-clauses ( i ) and ( ii ) of clause ( b ), in relation to a long-term`
  line `capital asset, being an equity share in a company or a unit of an equity oriented fund or a unit of a`
  line `business trust referred to in section 112A, acquired before the 1st day of February, 2018, shall be`
  line `higher of —`
  line `( i ) the cost of acquisition of such asset; and`
  line `( ii ) lower of —`
  line `( A ) the fair market value of such asset; and`
  line `( B ) the full value of consideration received or accruing as a result of the transfer of the`
  line `capital asset.`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this clause, —`
  line `( a ) “ fair market value ” means, —`
  line `( i ) in a case where the capital asset is listed on any recognised stock exchange as on the`
  line `31st day of January, 2018, the highest price of the capital asset quoted on such exchange on`
  line `the said date:`
  line `Provided that where there is no trading in such asset on such exchange on the 31st day of`
  line `January, 2018, the highest price of such asset on such exchange on a date immediately`
  line `preceding the 31st day of January, 2018 when such asset was traded on such exchange shall`
  line `be the fair market value;`
  line `( ii ) in a case where the capital asset is a unit which is not listed on a recognised stock`
  line `exchange as on the 31st day of January, 2018, the net asset value of such unit as on the said`
  line date;
  line `( iii ) in a case where the capital asset is an equity share in a company which is —`
  line `( A ) not listed on a recognised stock exchange as on the 31st day of January, 2018 but`
  line `listed on such exchange on the date of transfer;`
  line `( B ) listed on a recognised stock exchange on the date of transfer and which became`
  line `the property of the assessee in consideration of share which is not listed on such`
  line `exchange as on the 31st day of January, 2018 by way of transaction not regarded as`
  line `transfer under section 47,`
  line `an amount which bears to the cost of acquisition the same proportion as Cost Inflation Index for`
  line `the financial year 2017-2018 bears to the Cost Inflation Index for the first year in which the asset`
  line `was held by the assessee or for the year beginning on the first day of April, 2001, whichever is`
  line later;
  line `( b ) “ Cost Inflation Index ” shall have the meaning assigned to it in clause ( v ) of the`
  line `Explanation to section 48;`
  line `( c ) “ recognised stock exchange ” shall have the meaning assigned to it in clause ( ii ) of`
  line `Explanation 1 to clause ( 5 ) of section 43.]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 13 of 2018, s. 22 (w.e.f. 1-4-2018).`
