obj_root_law_sections_307_content:
  string
  line 307
  line `1 [( e ) “ relative ” means,—`
  line `( i ) in case of an individual —`
  line `( A ) spouse of the individual;`
  line `( B ) brother or sister of the individual;`
  line `( C ) brother or sister of the spouse of the individual;`
  line `( D ) brother or sister of either of the parents of the individual;`
  line `( E ) any lineal ascendant or descendant of the individual;`
  line `( F ) any lineal ascendant or descendant of the spouse of the individual;`
  line `( G ) spouse of the person referred to in items ( B ) to ( F ); and`
  line `( ii ) in case of a Hindu undivided family, any member thereof;]`
  line `( f ) “stamp duty value” means the value adopted or assessed or assessable by any authority of the`
  line `Central Government or a State Government for the purpose of payment of stamp duty in respect of an`
  line `immovable property;]`
  line `2 [( viia ) where a firm or a company not being a company in which the public are substantially`
  line `interested, receives, in any previous year, from any person or persons, on or after the 1st day of`
  line `June, 2010 3 [but before the 1st day of April, 2017], any property, being shares of a company not`
  line `being a company in which the public are substantially interested, —`
  line `( i ) without consideration, the aggregate fair market value of which exceeds fifty`
  line `thousand rupees, the whole of the aggregate fair market value of such property;`
  line `( ii ) for a consideration which is less than the aggregate fair market value of the property`
  line `by an amount exceeding fifty thousand rupees, the aggregate fair market value of such`
  line `property as exceeds such consideration:`
  line `Provided that this clause shall not apply to any such property received by way of a`
  line `transaction not regarded as transfer under clause ( via ) or clause ( vic ) or clause ( vicb ) or clause`
  line `( vid ) or clause ( vii ) of section 47.`
  line `Explanation. — For the purpos es of this clause, “fair market value” of a property, being shares of a`
  line `company not being a company in which the public are substantially interested, shall have the meaning`
  line `assigned to it in the Explanation to clause ( vii );]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 21 (w.e.f. 1-10-2009).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 14 of 2010, s. 21 (w.e.f. 1-6-2010).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 29 (w.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
