obj_root_law_sections_310_content:
  string
  line 310
  line `57. Deductions. — The income chargeable under th e head “Income from other sources” shall be`
  line `computed after making the following deductions, namely: —`
  line `( i ) 1 [in the case of dividends, other than dividends referred to in section 115-O], 2 [or interest on`
  line `securities], any reasonable sum paid by way of commission or remuneration to a banker or any other`
  line `person for the purpose of realising such dividend 2 [or interest] on behalf of the assessee;`
  line `3 [( ia ) in the case of income of the nature referred to in sub-clause ( x ) of clause ( 24 ) of`
  line `section 2 which is chargeable to income- tax under the head “Income from other sources”, deductions,`
  line `so far as may be, in accordance with the provisions of clause ( va ) of sub-section ( 1 ) of section 36;]`
  line `( ii ) in the case of income of the nature referred to in clauses ( ii ) and ( iii ) of sub-section ( 2 ) of`
  line `section 56, deductions, so far as may be, in accordance with the provisions of sub-clause ( ii ) of`
  line `clause ( a ) and clause ( c ) of section 30, section 31 and 4 [sub-sections ( 1 ) 5 *** and ( 2 ) of`
  line `section 32] and subject to the provisions of 6 [section 38];`
  line `7 [( iia ) in the case of income in the nature of family pension, a deduction of a sum equal to`
  line `thirty-three and one-third per cent of such income or 8 [fifteen thousand rupees], whichever is less.`
  line `Explanation. —For the purposes of this clause, “family pension” means a regular monthly amount`
  line `payable by the employer to a person belonging to the family of an employee in the event of his death;]`
  line `( iii ) any other expenditure (not being in the nature of capital expenditure) laid out or expended`
  line `wholly and exclusively for the purposeof making or earning such income;`
  line `9 [( iv ) in the case of income of the nature referred to in clause ( viii ) of sub-section ( 2 ) of`
  line `section 56, a deduction of a sum equal to fifty per cent of such income and no deduction shall be`
  line `allowed under any other clause of this section.]`
  line `10 * * * * *`
  line `11 * * * * *`
  line `58. Amounts not deductible. — 12 [( 1 )] Notwithstanding anything to the contrary contained in`
  line `section 57, the following amounts shall not be deductible in computing the income chargeable under the`
  line `head “Income from other sources”, namely:—`
  line `( a ) in the case of any assessee, —`
  line `( i ) any personal expenses of the assessee;`
  line `13 [( ia ) any expenditure of the nature referred to in sub-section ( 12 ) of section 40A;]`
  line `( ii ) any interest chargeable under this Act which is payable outside India (not being interest`
  line `on a loan issued for public subscription before the 1st day of April, 1938) on which tax has not`
  line `been paid or deducted under Chapter XVII-B 14 ***;`
  line `( iii ) any payment which is chargeable under the head “Salaries”, if it is payable outside India,`
  line `unless tax has been paid thereon or deducted therefrom under Chapter XVII-B;`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 32, for “in the case of dividends” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2004).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 26 of 1988, s.19 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 11 of 1987, s. 27 (w.e.f. 1-4-1988).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 42 of 1970, s. 14, for “sub -sections ( 1 ) and ( 2 ) of section 32” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1970).`
  line `5. The brackets, figure and letter “( 1A )” omitted by Act 46 of 1986, s. 32 (w.e.f. 1 -4-1988).`
  line `6. Subs. by s. 32, ibid., for “sections 34 and 38” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1988).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 13 of 1989, s. 13 (w.e.f. 1-4-1990).`
  line `8. Subs. by Act 26 of 1997, s. 20, for “twelve thousand rupees” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1998).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 33 of 2009, s. 27 (w.e.f. 1-4-2010).`
  line `10. The proviso omitted by Act 32 of 1994, s. 19 (w.e.f. 1-1995).`
  line `11. The Explanation omitted by Act 26 of 1988, s. 19 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `12. Section 58 renumbered as sub-section ( 1 ) thereof by Act 19 of 1968, s.8 (w.e.f. 1-4-1968).`
  line `13. Ins. by Act 32 of 1985, s. 15 (w.e.f. 1-4-1986).`
  line `14. The words “and in respect of which there is no person in India who may be treated as in agent under section 163”`
  line `omitted by Act 26 of 1988, s. 20 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
obj_root_law_sections_310_footnotes:
  string
