obj_root_law_sections_313_content:
  string
  line 313
  line `1 [( viii ) to any person or association of persons from assets transferred directly or indirectly on or`
  line `after the 1st day of June, 1973, otherwise than for adequate consideration, to the person or association`
  line `of persons by such individual, to the extent to which the income from such assets is for the immediate`
  line `or deferred benefit of his son ’ s wife 2 ***.]`
  line `3 [ Explanation 1. — For the purposes of clause ( ii ), the individual in computing whose total income the`
  line `income referred to in that clause is to be included, shall be the husband or wife whose total income`
  line `(excluding the income referred to in that clause) is greater; and where any such income is once included`
  line `in the total income of either spouse, any such income arising in any succeeding year shall not be included`
  line `in the total income of the other spouse unless the Assessing Officer is satisfied, after giving that spouse an`
  line `opportunity of being heard, that it is necessary so to do.]`
  line `Explanation 2. — For the purposes of clause ( ii ), an individual shall be deemed to have a substantial`
  line `interest in a concern —`
  line `( i ) in a case where the concern is a company, if its shares (not being shares entitled to a fixed rate`
  line `of dividend whether with or without a further right to participate in profits) carrying not less than`
  line `twenty per cent of the voting power are, at any time during the previous year, owned beneficially by`
  line `such person or partly by such person and partly by one or more of his relatives;`
  line `( ii ) in any other case, if such person is entitled, or such person and one or more of his relatives are`
  line `entitled in the aggregate, at any time during the previous year, to not less than twenty per cent of the`
  line `profits of such concern.`
  line `4 * * * * *`
  line `5 [ Explanation 3. — For the purposes of clauses ( iv ) and ( vi ), where the assets transferred directly or`
  line `indirectly by an individual to his spouse or son's wife (hereafter in this Explanation referred to as “the`
  line `transferee”) are invested by the transferee,—`
  line `( i ) in any business, such investment being not in the nature of contribution of capital as a partner`
  line `in a firm or, as the case may be, for being admitted to the benefits of partnership in a firm, that part of`
  line `the income arising out of the business to the transferee in any previous year, which bears the same`
  line `proportion to the income of the transferee from the business as the value of the assets aforesaid as on`
  line `the first day of the previous year bears to the total investment in the business by the transferee as on`
  line `the said day;`
  line `( ii ) in the nature of contribution of capital as a partner in a firm, that part of the interest receivable`
  line `by the transferee from the firm in any previous year, which bears the same proportion to the interest`
  line `receivable by the transferee from the firm as the value of investment aforesaid as on the first day of`
  line `the previous year bears to the total investment by way of capital contribution as a partner in the firm`
  line `as on the said day,`
  line `shall be included in the total income of the individual in that previous year.]`
  line `6 [( 1A ) In computing the total income of any individual, there shall be included all such income as`
  line `arises or accrues to his minor child 7 [, not being a minor child suffering from any disability of the nature`
  line `specified in section 80U:]`
  line `Provided that nothing contained in this sub-section shall apply in respect of such income as arises or`
  line `accrues to the minor child on account of any —`
  line `( a ) manual work done by him; or`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 67 of 1984, s. 17 (w.e.f. 1-4-1985).`
  line `2. The words “or minor child or both” omitted by Act 18 of 1992, s. 35 (w.e.f. 1 -4-1993).`
  line `3. Subs. by s. 35, ibid., for Explanations 1 and 1A (w.e.f. 1-4-1993).`
  line `4. Explanation 2A omitted by s. 35, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-1993).`
  line `5. Subs. by s. 35, ibid., for Explanation 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-1993).`
  line `6. Ins. by s. 35, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-1993).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 32 of 1994, s. 20 (w.e.f. 1-4-1995).`
