obj_root_law_sections_328_content:
  string
  line 328
  line `1 [CHAPTER VIA`
  line `D EDUCTIONS TO BE MADE IN COMPUTING TOTAL INCOME`
  line `A. — General`
  line `80A. Deductions to be made in computing total income. — ( 1 ) In computing the total income of an`
  line `assessee, there shall be allowed from his gross total income, in accordance with and subject to the`
  line `provisions of this Chapter, the deductions specified in section 80C to 2 [80U].`
  line `( 2 ) The aggregate amount of the deductions under this Chapter shall not, in any case, exceed the gross`
  line `total income of the assessee.`
  line `3 [( 3 ) Where, in computing the total income of an association of persons or a body of`
  line `individuals, any deduction is admissible under section 80G or section 80GGA 4 [or section 80GGC] or`
  line `section 80HH or section 80HHA or section 80HHB or section 80HHC or section 80HHD or`
  line `section 80-I or section 80-IA 5 [or section 80-IB] 6 [or section 80-IC] 7 [or section 80-ID or`
  line `section 80-IE] 8 *** 9 ***, no deduction under the same section shall be made in computing the total`
  line `income of a member of the association of persons or body of individuals in relation to the share of such`
  line `member in the income of the association of persons or body of individuals.]`
  line `10 [( 4 ) Notwithstanding anything to the contrary contained in section 10A or section 10AA or section`
  line `10B or section 10BA or in any provisions of this Chapter under the heading ” C. — Deductions in respect`
  line `of certain incomes ”, where, in the case of an assessee, any amount of profits and gains of an undertaking`
  line `or unit or enterprise or eligible business is claimed and allowed as a deduction under any of those`
  line `provisions for any assessment year, deduction in respect of, and to the extent of, such profits and gains`
  line `shall not be allowed under any other provisions of this Act for such assessment year and shall in no case`
  line `exceed the profits and gains of such undertaking or unit or enterprise or eligible business, as the case may`
  line be.
  line `( 5 ) Where the assessee fails to make a claim in his return of income for any deduction under section`
  line `10A or section 10AA or section 10B or section 10BA or under any provision of this Chapter under the`
  line `heading ” C. — Deductions in respect of certain incomes ”, no deduction shall be allowed to him`
  line thereunder.]
  line `( 6 ) Notwithstanding anything to the contrary contained in section 10A or section 10AA or`
  line `section 10B or section 10BA or in any provisions of this Chapter under the heading ” C. — Deductions in`
  line `respect of certain incomes ”, where any goods or services held for the purposes of the undertaking or unit`
  line `or enterprise or eligible business are transferred to any other business carried on by the assessee or where`
  line `any goods or services held for the purposes of any other business carried on by the assessee are`
  line `transferred to the undertaking or unit or enterprise or eligible business and, the consideration, if any, for`
  line `such transfer as recorded in the accounts of the undertaking or unit or enterprise or eligible business does`
  line `not correspond to the market value of such goods or services as on the date of the transfer, then, for the`
  line `purposes of any deduction under this Chapter, the profits and gains of such undertaking or unit or`
  line `enterprise or eligible business shall be computed as if the transfer, in either case, had been made at the`
  line `market value of such goods or services as on that date.`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this sub- section, the expression “market value”,—`
  line `( i ) in relation to any goods or services sold or supplied, means the price that such goods or`
  line `services would fetch if these were sold by the undertaking or unit or enterprise or eligible business in`
  line `the open market, subject to statutory or regulatory restrictions, if any;`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 20 of 1967, s. 33 and the Third Schedule, for Chapter VIA (w.e.f. 1-4-1968).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 32 of 1985, s. 36, for “80VV” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1986).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 18 of 1992, s. 41, for sub-section ( 3 ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1993). Earlier substituted by Act 4 of 1988, s. 21`
  line `(w.e.f. 1-4-1989) and then restored by Act 3 of 1989, s. 95 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 46 of 2003, s. 9, for “section 80GGA” (w.e.f. 11 -9-2003).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 27 of 1999, s. 90 (w.e.f. 1-4-2000).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 22 of 2007, s. 22 (w.r.e.f. 1-4-2004).`
  line `7. Ins. by s. 22, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-2008).`
  line `8. Section 80J omitted by Act 33 of 1996, s. 29 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `9. Section 80JJ omitted by Act 26 of 1997, s. 26 (w.e.f. 1-4-1988).`
  line `10. Ins. by Act 33 of 2009, s. 29 (w.e.f. 1-4-2003).`
