obj_root_law_sections_329_content:
  string
  line 329
  line `( ii ) in relation to any goods or services acquired, means the price that such goods or services`
  line `would cost if these were acquired by the undertaking or unit or enterprise or eligible business from`
  line `the open market, subject to statutory or regulatory restrictions, if any;]`
  line `1 [( iii ) in relation to any goods or services sold, supplied or acquired means the arm’s length price`
  line `as defined in clause ( ii ) of section 92F of such goods or services, if it is a specified domestic`
  line `transaction referred to in section 92BA.]`
  line `2 [( 7 ) Where a deduction under any provision of this Chapter under the heading ”C.— Deductions in`
  line `respect of certain incomes” is claimed and allowed in respect of profits of any of the specified business`
  line `referred to in clause ( c ) of sub-section ( 8 ) of section 35D for any assessment year, no deduction shall be`
  line `allowed under the provisions of section 35AD in relation to such specified business for the same or any`
  line `other assessment year.]`
  line `80AA. [ Computation of deduction under section 80M]. — Omitted by the Finance Act, 1997 (26 of`
  line `1997), s. 21 ( w.e.f. 1-4-1998)]. Earlier inserted by Act 44 of 1980, s. 12 (w.e.f. 1-4-1968).`
  line `3 [ 80AB. Deductions to be made with reference to the income included in the gross total`
  line `income. Where any deduction is required to be made or allowed under any section 4 *** included in this`
  line `Chapter under the heading ” C. — Deductions in respect of certain incomes ” in respect of any income of the`
  line `nature specified in that section which is included in the gross total income of the assessee, then,`
  line `notwithstanding anything contained in that section, for the purpose of computing the deduction under that`
  line `section, the amount of income of that nature as computed in accordance with the provisions of this Act`
  line `(before making any deduction under this Chapter) shall alone be deemed to be the amount of income of`
  line `that nature which is derived or received by the assessee and which is included in his gross total income.]`
  line `5 [80AC. Deduction not to be allowed unless return furnished. — Where in computing the total`
  line `income of an assessee of any previous year relevant to the assessment year commencing on or after —`
  line `( i ) the 1st day of April, 2006 but before the 1st day of April, 2018, any deduction is admissible`
  line `under section 80-IA or section 80-IAB or section 80-IB or section 80-IC or section 80-ID or`
  line `section 80-IE;`
  line `( ii ) the 1st day of April, 2018, any deduction is admissible under any provision of this Chapter`
  line `under the heading “C.— Deductions in respect of certain incomes ”,`
  line `no such deduction shall be allowed to him unless he furnishes a return of his income for such assessment`
  line `year on or before the due date specified under sub-section ( 1 ) of section 139.]`
  line `80B. Definitions. — In this Chapter —`
  line `6 * * * * *`
  line `7 * * * * *`
  line `8 * * * * *`
  line `9 * * * * *`
  line `( 5 ) “gross total income” means the total income computed in accordance with the provisions of`
  line `this Act, before making any deduction under this Chapter 10 *** 11 ***;`
  line `12 * * * * *`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 23 (w.e.f. 1-4-2013).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 14 of 2010, s. 23 (w.e.f. 1-4-2011).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 44 of 1980, s. 12 (w.e.f. 1-4-1968).`
  line `4. The bracke ts, words, figures and letters “(except section 80M)” omitted by Act 26 of 1997, s. 22 (w.e.f. 1 -4-1998).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 13 of 2009, s. 25, for section 80AC (w.e.f. 1-4-2018) which was earlier inserted by Act 21 of 2006,`
  line `s. 15 (w.e.f. 1-4-2006).`
  line `6. Clause ( 1 ) omitted by Act 41 of 1975, s. 17 (w.e.f. 1-4-1976).`
  line `7. Clause ( 2 ) omitted by Act 4 of 1988, s. 22 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `8. Clause ( 3 ) omitted by Act 19 of 1968, s. 30 and the Third Schedule (w.e.f. 1-4-1969).`
  line `9. Clause ( 4 ) omitted by Act 4 of 1988, s. 22 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `10. The words, figures and letter “or under section 280 - O” omitted by Act 26 of 1988, s. 54 (w.e.f. 1 -4-1988).`
  line `11. The words and figures “and without applying the provisions of section 64” omitted by Act 42 of 1970, s. 18 (w.e.f. 1-4-1968).`
  line `12. Clause ( 6 ) omitted by Act 4 of 1988, s. 22 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
