obj_root_law_sections_348_content:
  string
  line 348
  line `80G. Deduction in respect of donations to certain funds, charitable institutions, etc. — 1 [( 1 ) In`
  line `computing the total income of an assessee, there shall be deducted, in accordance with and subject to the`
  line `provisions of this section, —`
  line `2 [( i ) in a case where the aggregate of the sums specified in sub-section ( 2 ) includes any sum or`
  line `sums of the nature specified 3 [in sub-clause ( i ) or in 4 [sub-clause ( iiia )] 5 [or in sub-clause ( iiiaa ) 6 [or`
  line `in sub-clause ( iiiab )] 7 [or in sub-clause ( iiib )] 8 [or in sub-clause ( iiie )] 9 [or in sub-clause ( iiif )] 10 [or in`
  line `sub-clause ( iiig )] 11 [or in sub-clause ( iiiga )] 12 [or sub-clause ( iiih )] 13 [or sub-clause ( iiiha ) or`
  line `sub-clause ( iiihb ) or sub-clause ( iiihc )] 14 [or sub-clause ( iiihd )] 15 [or sub-clause ( iiihe )] 16 [or sub-`
  line `clause ( iiihf )] 17 [or sub-clause ( iiihg ) or sub-clause ( iiihh )] 18 [or sub-clause ( iiihi )] 19 [or sub-clause`
  line `( iiihj )] or] 20 [sub-clause ( iiihk ) or sub-clause ( iiihl ) or] 20 [sub-clause ( iiihm ) or] in] sub-clause ( vii ) of`
  line `clause ( a ) 21 [or in clause ( c )] 11 [or in clause ( d )] thereof, an amount equal to the whole of the sum or,`
  line `as the case may be, sums of such nature plus fifty per cent of the balance of such aggregate; and]`
  line `( ii ) in any other case, an amount equal to fifty per cent of the aggregate of the sums specified in`
  line `sub-section ( 2 ).]`
  line `( 2 ) The sums referred to in sub-section ( 1 ) shall be the following, namely: —`
  line `( a ) any sums paid by the assessee in the previous year as donations to —`
  line `( i ) the National Defence Fund set up by the Central Government; or`
  line `( ii ) the Jawaharlal Nehru Memorial Fund referred to in the Deed of Declaration of Trust`
  line `adopted by the National Committee at its meeting held on the 17th day of August, 1964; or`
  line `( iii ) the Prime Minister’s Drought Relief Fund; or`
  line `22 [( iiia ) the Prime Minister's National Relief Fund; or]`
  line `5 [( iiiaa ) the Prime Minister's Armenia Earthquake Relief Fund; or]`
  line `23 [( iiiab ) the Africa (Public Contributions-India) Fund; or]`
  line `24 [( iiib ) the National Children's Fund; or]`
  line `25 [( iiic ) the Indira Gandhi Memorial Trust, the deed of declaration in respect whereof was`
  line `registered at New Delhi on the 21st day of February, 1985; or]`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 66 of 1976, s. 17, for sub-section ( 1 ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1977).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 32 of 1985, s. 18, for clause ( i ) (1-4-1986).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 28 of 1999, s. 2, for “in sub -clause ( iiia )” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2000).`
  line `4. Restored by Act 3 of 1989 s. 95, Earlier subs. by Act 4 of 1988, s. 25 (w.e.f. 1-1989).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 11 of 1989, s. 3 (w.e.f. 24-1-1989).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 49 of 1991, s. 26 (w.e.f. 1-4-1991).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 17 of 2013, s. 16 (w.e.f. 1-4-2014).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 38 of 1993, s. 13 (w.e.f. 1-4-1993).`
  line `9. Ins. by s. 13, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-1994).`
  line `10. Ins. by Act 32 of 1994, s. 26 (w.e.f. 1-4-1994).`
  line `11. Ins. by Act 4 of 2001, s. 6 (w.e.f. 3-2-2001).`
  line `12. Ins. by Act 22 of 1995, s. 16 (w.e.f. 1-4-1996).`
  line `13. Ins. by Act 33 of 1996, s. 24 (w.e.f. 1-4-1997).`
  line `14. Ins. by Act 35 of 1996, s. 2 (w.e.f. 14-11-1996).`
  line `15. Ins. by Act 14 of 1997, s. 3 (w.e.f. 1-4-1997).`
  line `16. Ins. by Act 26 of 1997, s. 23 (w.e.f. 1-4-1998).`
  line `17. Ins. by Act 21 of 1998, s. 29 (w.e.f. 1-4-1999).`
  line `18. Ins. b y Act 27 of 1999, s. 43 (w.e.f. 1-4-2000).`
  line `19. Ins. by Act 14 of 2001, s. 39 (w.e.f. 1-4-2002).`
  line `20. Ins. by Act 20 of 2015, s. 22 (w.e.f. 1-4-2016).`
  line `21. Ins. by Act 10 of 2000, s. 31 (w.e.f. 1-4-2001).`
  line `22. Ins. by Act 1 of 1976, s. 2 (w.e.f. 9-9-1975).`
  line `23. Ins. by Act 49 of 1991, s. 26 (w.e.f. 1-4-1991).`
  line `24. Ins. by Act 14 of 1982, s. 15 (w.e.f 1-4-1983).`
  line `25. Ins. by Act 32 of 1985, s. 18 (w.e.f. 1-4-1985).`
