obj_root_law_sections_351_content:
  string
  line 351
  line `1 [( c ) any sums paid by the assessee, being a company, in the previous year as donations to the`
  line `Indian Olympic Association or to any other association or institution 2 [established in India, as the`
  line `Central Government may, having regard to the prescribed guidelines, by notification in the Official`
  line `Gazette, specify in this behalf] for —`
  line `( i ) the development of infrastructure for sports and games; or`
  line `( ii ) the sponsorship of sports and games,`
  line `in India;]`
  line `3 [ ( d ) any sums paid by the assessee, during the period beginning on the 26th day of January,`
  line `2001 and ending on the 30th day of September, 2001, to any trust, institution or fund to which this`
  line `section applies for providing relief to the victims of earthquake in Gujarat.]`
  line `4 * * * * *`
  line `5 [( 4 ) Where the aggregate of the sums referred to in sub-clauses ( iv ), ( v ), 6 [( vi ), ( via ) and ( vii )] of`
  line `clause (a) and in 7 [clauses ( b ) and ( c )] of sub-section ( 2 ) exceeds ten per cent of the gross total income (as`
  line `reduced by any portion thereof on which income-tax is not payable under any provision of this Act and by`
  line `any amount in respect of which the assessee is entitled to a deduction under any other provision of this`
  line `Chapter), then the amount in excess of ten per cent of the gross total income shall be ignored for the`
  line `purpose of computing the aggregate of the sums in respect of which deduction is to be allowed under sub-`
  line `section ( 1 ).]`
  line `( 5 ) This section applies to donations to any institution or fund referred to in sub-clause ( iv ) of`
  line `clause (a) of sub-section ( 2 ), only if it is established in India for a charitable purpose and if it fulfils the`
  line `following conditions, namely: —`
  line `8 [( i ) where the institution or fund derives any income, such income would not be liable to`
  line `inclusion in its total income under the provisions of sections 11 and 12 9 *** 10 *** 11 [or clause ( 23AA )`
  line `or clause ( 23C )] of section 10:]`
  line `12 [Provided that where an institution or fund derives any income, being profits and gains of`
  line `business, the condition that such income would not be liable to inclusion in its total income under the`
  line `provisions of section 11 shall not apply in relation to such income, if —`
  line `( a ) the institution or fund maintains separate books of account in respect of such business;`
  line `( b ) the donations made to the institution or fund are not used by it, directly or indirectly, for`
  line `the purposes of such business; and`
  line `( c ) the institution or fund issues to a person making the donation a certificate to the effect that`
  line `it maintains separate books of account in respect of such business and that the donations received`
  line `by it will not be used, directly or indirectly, for the purposes of such business;]`
  line `( ii ) the instrument under which the institution or fund is constituted does not, or the rules`
  line `governing the institution or fund do not, contain any provision for the transfer or application at any`
  line `time of the whole or any part of the income or assets of the institution or fund for any purpose other`
  line `than a charitable purpose;`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 10 of 2000, s. 31 (w.e.f. 1-4-2001).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 30, for “as notified by the Central Government under clause ( 23 ) of section 10”`
  line `(w.e.f. 1-4-2003).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 4 of 2001, s. 6 (w.e.f. 3-2-2001).`
  line `4. Sub-section ( 3 ) omitted by Act 32 of 1994, s. 24 (w.e.f. 1-4-1994).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 4 of 1988, s. 25, for sub-section ( 4 ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 22 of 1995, s. 16, for “( vi ) and ( vii )” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1995).`
  line `7. Subs. by Act 10 of 2000, s. 31, for “clause ( b )” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2001).`
  line `8. Restored by Act 3 of 1989, s. 95 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989). Earlier subs. by Act 4 of 1988, s. 25 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `9. The words, brackets, figures and letter “or clause ( 22 ) or clause ( 22A )” omitted by Act 21 of 1998, s. 29 (w.e.f. 1-4-1999).`
  line `10. The words, brackets and figures “or clause ( 23 )” omitted by Act 20 of 2002, s. 30 (w.e.f. 1 -4-2003).`
  line `11. Subs. by Act 11 of 1987, s. 35, for “or clause ( 23C )” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1988).`
  line `12. The proviso added by Act 11 of 1983, s. 39 (w.e.f. 1-4-1984).`
