obj_root_law_sections_352_content:
  string
  line 352
  line `( iii ) the institution or fund is not expressed to be for the benefit of any particular religious`
  line `community or caste;`
  line `( iv ) the institution or fund maintains regular accounts of its receipts and expenditure; 1 ***`
  line `( v ) the institution or fund is either constituted as a public charitable trust or is`
  line `registered under the Societies Registration Act, 1860 (21 of 1860), or under any law corresponding to`
  line `that Act in force in any part of India or under section 25 of the Companies Act, 1956 (1 of 1956), or is`
  line `a University established by law, or is any other educational institution recognised by the Government`
  line `or by a University established by law, or affiliated to any University established by law, 2 *** or is an`
  line `institution financed wholly or in part by the Government or a local authority; 3 ***`
  line `4 [( vi ) in relation to donations made after the 31st day of March, 1992, the institution or fund is for`
  line `the time being approved by the Commissioner in accordance with the rules 5 [made in this behalf;`
  line and]]
  line `6 * * * * *`
  line `7 [( vii ) where any institution or fund had been approved under clause ( vi ) for the previous year`
  line `beginning on the 1st day of April, 2007 and ending on the 31st day of March, 2008, such institution`
  line `or fund shall, for the purposes of this section and notwithstanding anything contained in the proviso`
  line `to clause (15) of section 2, be deemed to have been, —`
  line `( a ) established for charitable purposes for the previous year beginning on the 1st day of April,`
  line `2008 and ending on the 31st day of March, 2009; and`
  line `( b ) approved under the said clause ( vi ) for the previous year beginning on the 1st day of`
  line `April, 2008 and ending on the 31st day of March, 2009.]`
  line `8 [( 5A ) Where a deduction under this section is claimed and allowed for any assessment year in respect`
  line `of any sum specified in sub-section ( 2 ), the sum in respect of which deduction is so allowed shall not`
  line `qualify for deduction under any other provision of this Act for the same or any other assessment year.]`
  line `9 [( 5B ) Notwithstanding anything contained in clause ( ii ) of sub-section ( 5 ) and Explanation 3, an`
  line `institution or fund which incurs expenditure, during any previous year, which is of a religious nature for`
  line `an amount not exceeding five per cent of its total income in that previous year shall be deemed to be an`
  line `institution or fund to which the provisions of this section apply.]`
  line `10 [( 5C ) 11 [This section] applies in relation to amounts referred to in clause ( d ) of sub-section ( 2 ) only`
  line `if the trust or institution or fund is established in India for a charitable purpose and it fulfils the following`
  line `conditions, namely: —`
  line `( i ) it is approved in terms of clause ( vi ) of sub-section ( 5 );`
  line `( ii ) it maintains separate accounts of income and expenditure for providing relief to the victims of`
  line `earthquake in Gujarat;`
  line `( iii ) the donations made to the trust or institution or fund are applied only for providing relief to`
  line `the earthquake victims of Gujarat 12 [on or before the 31st day of March, 13 [2004]];`
  line `1. The word “and” omitted by Act 32 of 1994, s. 24 (w.e.f. 1 -4-1994).`
  line `2. The words, brackets and figures “or is an institution approved by the Central Government for the purposes of clause (23)`
  line `of section 10”, omitted by Act 20 of 2002, s. 30 ( w.e.f. 1-4-2003).`
  line `3. The word “and” omitted by Act 33 of 2009, s. 33 (w.e.f. 1 -4-2009).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 49 of 1991, s. 26 (w.e.f. 1-10-1991).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 33 of 2009, s. 33, for “made in this behalf:” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2009).`
  line `6. The proviso omitted by s. 33, ibid., (w.e.f. 1-10-2009).`
  line `7. Ins. by s. 33, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-10-2009).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 44 of 1980, s. 15 (w.r.e.f. 1-4-1962).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 27 of 1999, s. 43 (w.e.f. 1-4-2000).`
  line `10. Ins. by Act 4 of 2001, s. 6 (w.e.f. 3-2-2001).`
  line `11. Subs. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 30, for “This sub - section” (w.e.f. 3 -2-2001).`
  line `12. Subs. by s. 30, ibid., for “on or before the 31st day of March, 2002” (w.e.f. 3 -2-2001).`
  line `13. Subs. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 36, for “2003” (w.e.f. 3 -2-2001).`
