obj_root_law_sections_353_content:
  string
  line 353
  line `1 [( iv ) the amount of donation remaining unutilised on the 31st day of March, 2 [2004] is`
  line `transferred to the Prime Minister’s National Relief Fund on or before the 31st day of March, 2 [2004];]`
  line `( v ) it renders accounts of income and expenditure to such authority and in such manner as may be`
  line `prescribed, 3 [on or before the 30th day of June, 2 [2004]].]`
  line `4 [( 5D ) No deduction shall be allowed under this section in respect of donation of any sum exceeding`
  line `5 [two thousand rupees] unless such sum is paid by any mode other than cash.]`
  line `Explanation 1. — An institution or fund established for the benefit of Scheduled Castes, backward`
  line `classes, Scheduled Tribes or of women and children shall not be deemed to be an institution or fund`
  line `expressed to be for the benefit of a religious community or caste within the meaning of clause ( iii ) of`
  line `sub-section ( 5 ).`
  line `6 [ Explanation 2. — For the removal of doubts, it is hereby declared that a deduction to which the`
  line `assessee is entitled in respect of any donation made to an institution or fund to which sub-section ( 5 )`
  line `applies shall not be denied merely on either or both of the following grounds, namely: —`
  line `7 [( i ) that, subsequent to the donation, any part of the income of the institution or fund has become`
  line `chargeable to tax due to non-compliance with any of the provisions of 8 [section 11, section 12 or`
  line `section 12A;`
  line `( ii ) that, under clause ( c ) of sub-section ( 1 ) of section 13, the exemption under 9 [section 11 or`
  line `section 12] is denied to the institution or fund in relation to any income arising to it from any`
  line `investment referred to in clause ( h ) of sub-section ( 2 ) of section 13 where the aggregate of the funds`
  line `invested by it in a concern referred to in the said clause ( h ) does not exceed five per cent of the capital`
  line `of that concern].]`
  line `Explanation 3. —In this section, “charitable purpose” does not include any purpose the whole or`
  line `substantially the whole of which is of a religious nature.`
  line `10 [ Explanation 4. — For the purposes of this section, an association or institution having as its object`
  line `the control, supervision, regulation or encouragement in India of such games or sports as the Central`
  line `Government may, by notification in the Official Gazette, specify in this behalf, shall be deemed to be an`
  line `institution established in India for a charitable purpose.]`
  line `11 [ Explanation 5. — For the removal of doubts, it is hereby declared that no deduction shall be allowed`
  line `under this section in respect of any donation unless such donation is of a sum of money.]`
  line `12 * * * * *`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 30, for clause ( iv ) (w.e.f. 3-2-2001).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 36, for “2003” (w.e.f. 3 -2-2001).`
  line `3. Subs. by s. 30, ibid., for “on or before the 30th day of June, 2002” (w.e.f. 3 -2-2001).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 28 (w.e.f. 1-4-2013).`
  line `5. Subs by Act 7 of 2017, s. 35 for “ten thousand rupees” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2018).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 19 of 1970, s. 13, for the Explanation 2 (w.e.f. 1-4-1971) earlier substituted by Act 20 of 1967, s. 33 and the`
  line `Third Schedule (w.e.f. 1-4-1967).`
  line `7. Restored by Act 3 of 1989, s. 95 ( h ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1989). Earlier subs. by Act 4 of 1988, s. 25 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `8. Subs. by Act 16 of 1972, s. 17, for “section 11” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1973).`
  line `9. Subs. by s. 17, for “section 11” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1973).`
  line `10. Subs. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 30, for the Explanation 4 (w.e.f. 1-4-2003).`
  line `11. Ins. by Act 66 of 1976, s. 17 (w.e.f. 1-4-1976).`
  line `12. Sub-section ( 6 ) omitted by Act 19 of 1968, s. 30 and the Third Schedule (w.e.f. 1-4-1969).`
