obj_root_law_sections_355_content:
  string
  line 355
  line `Provided that 1 [such association, University], college or institution is for the time being approved`
  line `for the purposes of clause ( iii ) of sub-section ( 1 ) of section 35.]`
  line `2 [ Explanation. — The deduction, to which the assessee is entitled in respect of any sum paid to a`
  line `3 [research association], University, college or other institution to which clause ( a ) or clause ( aa )`
  line `applies, shall not be denied merely on the ground that, subsequent to the payment of such sum by the`
  line `assessee, the approval to such association, University, college or other institution referred to in`
  line `clause ( a ) or clause ( aa ), as the case may be, has been withdrawn;]`
  line `( b ) any sum paid by the assessee in the previous year —`
  line `( i ) to an association or institution, which has as its object the undertaking of any programme`
  line `of rural development, to be used for carrying out any programme of rural development approved`
  line `for the purposes of section 35CCA; or`
  line `( ii ) to an association or institution which has as its object the training of persons for`
  line `implementing programmes of rural development:`
  line `4 [Provided that the assessee furnishes the certificate referred to in sub-section ( 2 ) or, as the`
  line `case may be, sub-section ( 2A ) of section 35CCA from such association or institution.]`
  line `2 [ Explanation. — The deduction, to which the assessee is entitled in respect of any sum paid to an`
  line `association or institution for carrying out the programme of rural development to which this clause`
  line `applies, shall not be denied merely on the ground that subsequent to the payment of such sum by the`
  line `assessee, the approval granted to such programme, or as the case may be, to the association or institution`
  line `has been withdrawn;]`
  line `5 [( bb ) any sum paid by the assessee in the previous year to a public sector company or a local`
  line `authority or to an association or institution approved by the National Committee, for carrying out any`
  line `eligible project or scheme:`
  line `Provided that the assessee furnishes the certificate referred to in clause ( a ) of sub-section ( 2 ) of`
  line `section 35AC from such public sector company or local authority or, as the case may be, association`
  line `or institution.`
  line `2 [ Explanation 1. — The deduction, to which the assessee is entitled in respect of any sum paid to a`
  line `public sector company, or to a local authority or to an association or institution for carrying out the`
  line `eligible project or scheme referred to in section 35AC, shall not be denied merely on the ground that`
  line `subsequent to the payment of such sum by the assessee, —`
  line `( a ) the approval granted to such association or institution has been withdrawn; or`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 14 of 2010 s. 26, for “such University” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2011).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 29 of 2006, s. 11 (w.e.f. 1-4-2006).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act of 2010, s. 26, for “scientific research association” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2011).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 23 of 1983, s. 23, for the proviso (w.e.f. 1-4-1983).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 49 of 1991, s. 27 (w.e.f. 1-4-1992).`
