obj_root_law_sections_356_content:
  string
  line 356
  line `( b ) the notification notifying the eligible project or scheme referred to in section 3535AC carried`
  line `out by the public sector company, or local authority or association or institution has been withdrawn.]`
  line `Explanation 1 [ 2 ]. —For the purposes of this clause, the expressions “National Committee” and`
  line `“eligible project or scheme” shall have the meanings respectively assigned to them in the Explanation to`
  line `section 35AC;]`
  line `2 [( c ) 3 [any sum paid by the assessee in any previous year ending on or before the 31st day of`
  line `March, 2002] to an association or institution, which has as its object the undertaking of any`
  line `programme of conservation of natural resources 4 [or of afforestation], to be used for carrying out any`
  line `programme of conservation of natural resources 4 [or of afforestation] approved for the purposes of`
  line `section 35CCB:`
  line `Provided that the association or institution is for the time being approved for the purposes of sub-`
  line `section (2) of section 35CCB;]`
  line `4 [( cc ) any sum paid by the assessee in any previous year ending on or before the 31st day of`
  line `March, 2002 to such fund for afforestation as is notified by the Central Government under clause ( b )`
  line `of sub-section ( 1 ) of section 35CCB;]`
  line `5 [( d ) any sum paid by the assessee in the previous year to a rural development fund set up and`
  line `notified by the Central Government for the purposes of clause ( c ) of sub-section ( 1 ) of section`
  line 35CCA;]
  line `6 [( e ) any sum paid by the assessee in the previous year to the National Urban Poverty Eradication`
  line `Fund set up and notified by the Central Government for the purposes of clause ( d ) of sub-section ( 1 )`
  line `of section 35CCA.]`
  line `7 [( 2A ) No deduction shall be allowed under this section in respect of any sum exceeding ten thousand`
  line `rupees unless such sum is paid by any mode other than cash.]`
  line `( 3 ) Notwithstanding anything contained in sub-section ( 1 ), no deduction under this section shall be`
  line `allowed in the case of an assessee whose gross total income includes income which is chargeable under`
  line `the head “Profits and gains of business or profession”.`
  line `( 4 ) Where a deduction under this section is claimed and allowed for any assessment year in respect of`
  line `any payments of the nature specified in sub-section ( 2 ), deduction shall not be allowed in respect of such`
  line `payments under any other provision of this Act for the same or any other assessment year.]`
  line `8 [ 80GGB. Deduction in respect of contributions given by companies to political parties. — In`
  line `computing the total income of an assessee, being an Indian company, there shall be deducted any sum`
  line `contributed by it, in the previous year to any political party 9 [or an electoral trust]:`
  line `1. Explanation renumbered as Explanation 2 thereof by Act 29 of 2006, s. 11 (w.e.f. 1-4-2006).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 14 of 1982, s. 17 (w.e.f. 1-6-1982).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 31, for “any sum paid by the assessee in the previous year” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2003).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 12 of 1990, s. 19 (w.e.f. 1-4-1991).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 23 of 1983, s. 23 (w.e.f. 1-4-1983).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 22 of 1995, s. 17 (w.e.f. 1-4-1996).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 29 (w.e.f. 1-4-2013).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 46 of 2003, s. 10 (w.e.f. 11-9-2003).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 33 of 2009, s. 34 (w.e.f. 1-4-2010).`
