obj_root_law_sections_370_content:
  string
  line 370
  line `( b ) who owns any undertaking which manufactures or produces goods or merchandise anywhere`
  line `in India (outside any special economic zone) and sells the same to any undertaking situated in a`
  line `special economic zone which is eligible for deduction under section 10A and such sale shall be`
  line `deemed to be export out of India for the purposes of this section.]`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this section, —`
  line `( a ) “convertible foreign exchange” means foreign exchange which is for the time being treated`
  line `by the Reserve Bank of India as convertible foreign exchange for the purposes of 1 [the Foreign`
  line `Exchange Management Act, 1999 (42 of 1999)], and any rules made thereunder;`
  line `2 [( aa ) “export out of India” shall not include any transaction by way of sale or otherwise, in a`
  line `shop, emporium or any other establishment situate in India, not involving clearance at any customs`
  line `station as defined in the Customs Act, 1962 (52 of 1962);]`
  line `( b ) “export turnover” means the sale proceeds 3 [received in, or brought into, India] by the`
  line `assessee in convertible foreign exchange 4 [in accordance with clause ( a ) of sub-section ( 2 )] of any`
  line `goods or merchandise to which this section applies and which are exported out of India, but does not`
  line `include freight or insurance attributable to the transport of the goods or merchandise beyond the`
  line `customs station as defined in the Customs Act, 1962 (52 of 1962);]`
  line `5 [( ba ) “total turnover” shall not include freight or insurance attributable to the transport of the`
  line `goods or merchandise beyond the customs station as defined in the Customs Act, 1962 (52 of 1962):`
  line `Provided that in relation to any assessment year commencing on or after the 1st day of`
  line `April, 1991, the expression “total turnover” shall have effect as if it also excluded any sum referred to`
  line `in clauses ( iiia ), ( iiib ) 6 [, ( iiic ), ( iiid ) and ( iiie )] of section 28;]`
  line `7 [( baa ) “profits of the business” means the profits of the business as computed under the head`
  line `“Profits and gains of business or profession” as reduced by—`
  line `( 1 ) ninety per cent. of any sum referred to in clauses ( iiia ), ( iiib ) 5 [, ( iiic ), ( iiid ) and ( iiie )]`
  line `of section 28 or of any receipts by way of brokerage, commission, interest, rent, charges or any`
  line `other receipt of a similar nature included in such profits; and`
  line `( 2 ) the profits of any branch, office, warehouse or any other establishment of theassessee`
  line `situate outside India;`
  line `8 * * * * *`
  line `9 [ 10 [( c )] “Export House Certificate” or “Trading House Certificate” means a valid Export House`
  line `Certificate or Trading House Certificate, as the case may be, issued by the Chief Controller of`
  line `Imports and Exports, Government of India;`
  line `11 [( d )] “supporting manufacturer” means a person being an Indian company or a person (other`
  line `than a company) resident in India, 12 [manufacturing (including processing) goods] or merchandise`
  line `and selling such goods or merchandise to an Export House or a Trading House for the purposes of`
  line export;
  line `13 [( e ) “special economic zone” shall have the meaning assigned to it in clause ( viii ) of`
  line `the Explanation 2 to section 10A.]`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 17 of 2013, s. 4, for “the Foreign Exchange Regulation Act, 1973 (46 of 1973)” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2013).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 49 of 1991, s. 28 (w.e.f. 1-4-1986).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 12 of 1990, s. 22, for “receivable” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1991).`
  line `4. Ins. by s. 22, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-1991).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 49 of 1991, s. 28 (w.e.f. 1-4-1987).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 55 of 2005, s. 4, for “and ( iiic )” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1998).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 49 of 1991, s. 28 (w.e.f. 1-4-1992).`
  line `8. Clause ( bb ) omitted s. 28, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-1991).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 26 of 1988, s. 24 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `10. Clause ( d ) relettered as clause ( c ) thereof by Act 3 of 1989, s. 15 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `11. Clause ( e ) relettered as clause ( d ) thereof by s. 15, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `12. Subs. by 12 of 1990, s. 22, for “manufacturing goods” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1991).`
  line `13. Ins. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 37 (w.e.f. 1-4-2004).`
