obj_root_law_sections_373_content:
  string
  line 373
  line `( 4 ) The amount credited to the reserve account under clause ( b ) of sub-section ( 1 ), shall be utilised by`
  line `the assessee before the expiry of a period of five years next following the previous year in which the`
  line `amount was credited for the following purposes, namely: —`
  line `( a ) construction of new hotels approved by the prescribed authority in this behalf or expansion of`
  line `facilities in existing hotels already so approved;`
  line `( b ) purchase of new cars and new coaches by tour operators already so approved or by travel`
  line agents;
  line `( c ) purchase of sports’ equipment for mountaineering, trekking, golf, river -rafting and other`
  line `sports in or on water;`
  line `( d ) construction of conference or convention centres;`
  line `( e ) provision of such new facilities for the growth of Indian tourism as the Central Government`
  line `may, by notification in the Official Gazette, specify in this behalf;`
  line `1 [( f ) subscription to equity shares forming part of any eligible issue of capital made by a public`
  line `company:]`
  line `Provided that where any of the activities referred to in 2 [clauses ( a ) to ( f )] would result in creation`
  line `of any asset owned by the assessee outside India, such asset should be created only after obtaining`
  line `prior approval of the prescribed authority.`
  line `( 5 ) Where any amount credited to the reserve account under clause ( b ) of sub-section ( 1 ), —`
  line `( a ) has been utilised for any purpose other than those referred to in sub-section ( 4 ), the amount so`
  line `utilised; or`
  line `( b ) has not been utilised in the manner specified in sub-section ( 4 ), the amount not so utilised,`
  line `shall be deemed to be the profits, —`
  line `( i ) in a case referred to in clause ( a ), in the year in which the amount was so utilised; or`
  line `( ii ) in a case referred to in clause ( b ), in the year immediately following the period of five years`
  line `specified in sub-section ( 4 ),`
  line `and shall be charged to tax accordingly.`
  line `3 [( 5A ) Where any amount credited to the reserve account under clause ( b ) of sub-section ( 1 ) has been`
  line `utilised for subscription to any equity shares referred to in clause ( f ) of sub-section ( 4 ) and either whole or`
  line `any part of such equity shares are transferred or converted into money by the assessee at any time within a`
  line `period of three years from the date of their acquisition, the aggregate amount so utilised in respect of such`
  line `equity shares shall be deemed to be the profits of the previous year in which the equity shares are`
  line `transferred or converted into money.`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 27 of 1999, s. 47 (w.e.f. 1-4-2000).`
  line `2. Subs. by s. 47, ibid., for “clauses ( a ) to ( e )” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2000).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 27 of 1999, s. 47 (w.e.f. 1-4-2000).`
