obj_root_law_sections_399_content:
  string
  line 399
  line `1 [( e ) not more than one residential unit in the housing project is allotted to any person not being`
  line `an individual; and`
  line `( f ) in a case where a residential unit in the housing project is allotted to a person being an`
  line `individual, no other residential unit in such housing project is allotted to any of the following persons,`
  line `namely: —`
  line `( i ) the individual or the spouse or the minor children of such individual,`
  line `( ii ) the Hindu undivided family in which such individual is the karta,`
  line `( iii ) any person representing such individual, the spouse or the minor children of such`
  line `individual or the Hindu undivided family in which such individual is the karta.]`
  line `2 [ Explanation. — For the removal of doubts, it is hereby declared that nothing contained in this sub-`
  line `section shall apply to any undertaking which executes the housing project as a works contract awarded by`
  line `any person (including the Central or State Government).]`
  line `( 11 ) Notwithstanding anything contained in clause ( iii ) of sub-section ( 2 ) and sub-sections ( 3 ), ( 4 )`
  line `and ( 5 ), the amount of deduction in a case of industrial undertaking deriving profit from the business of`
  line `setting up and operating a cold chain facility for agricultural produce, shall be hundred per cent of the`
  line `profits and gains derived from such industrial undertaking for five assessment years beginning with the`
  line `initial assessment year and thereafter, twenty-five per cent. (or thirty per cent where the assessee is a`
  line `company) of the profits and gains derived from the operation of such facility in a manner that the total`
  line `period of deduction does not exceed ten consecutive assessment years (or twelve consecutive assessment`
  line `years where the assessee is a co-operative society) and subject to fulfilment of the condition that it begins`
  line `to operate such facility on or after the 1st day of April, 1999 but before the 3 [1st day of April, 2004].`
  line `4 [( 11A ) The amount of deduction in a case of 5 [an undertaking deriving profit from the business of`
  line `processing, preservation and packaging of fruits or vegetables or 1 [meat and meat products or poultry or`
  line `marine or dairy products or from] the integrated business of handling, storage and transportation of`
  line `foodgrains, shall be hundred per cent of the profits and gains derived from such undertaking for five`
  line `assessment years beginning with the initial assessment year and thereafter, twenty-five per cent. (or thirty`
  line `per cent. where the assessee is a company) of the profits and gains derived from the operation of such`
  line `business in a manner that the total period of deduction does not exceed ten consecutive assessment years`
  line `and subject to fulfilment of the condition that it begins to operate such business on or after the 1st day of`
  line `April, 2001]:`
  line `1 [Provided that the provisions of this section shall not apply to an undertaking engaged in the business`
  line `of processing, preservation and packaging of meat or meat products or poultry or marine or dairy products`
  line `if it begins to operate such business before the 1st day of April, 2009.]`
  line `6 [( 11B ) The amount of deduction in the case of an undertaking deriving profits from the business of`
  line `operating and maintaining a hospital in a rural area shall be hundred per cent. of the profits and gains of`
  line `such business for a period of five consecutive assessment years, beginning with the initial assessment`
  line `year, if —`
  line `( i ) such hospital is constructed at any time during the period beginning on the 1st day of October,`
  line `2004 and ending on the 31st day of March, 2008;`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 33 of 2009, s. 37 (w.e.f. 1-4-2010).`
  line `2. Ins. by s. 37, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-2001).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 39, for “31st day of March, 2004” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2004).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 14 of 2001, s. 45 (w.e.f. 1-4-2002).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 23 of 2004, s. 18, for “an undertaking deriving profit from” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2005).`
  line `6. Ins. by s. 18, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-2005).`
