  title `Page 401`
  content obj_root_law_sections_401_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_401_footnotes
  sourcePage 401
obj_root_law_sections_401_content:
  string
  line 401
  line `( vii ) Ahmedabad urban agglomeration;`
  line `( viii ) District of Faridabad;`
  line `( ix ) District of Gurgaon;`
  line `( x ) District of Gautam Budh Nagar;`
  line `( xi ) District of Ghaziabad;`
  line `( xii ) District of Gandhinagar; and`
  line `( xiii ) City of Secunderabad;`
  line `( d ) the area comprising an urban agglomeration shall be the area included in such urban`
  line `agglomeration on the basis of the 2001 census.]`
  line `( 12 ) Where any undertaking of an Indian company which is entitled to the deduction under this`
  line `section is transferred, before the expiry of the period specified in this section, to another Indian company`
  line `in a scheme of amalgamation or demerger —`
  line `( a ) no deduction shall be admissible under this section to the amalgamating or the demerged`
  line `company for the previous year in which the amalgamation or the demerger takes place; and`
  line `( b ) the provisions of this section shall, as far as may be, apply to the amalgamated or the resulting`
  line `company as they would have applied to the amalgamating or the demerged company if the`
  line `amalgamation or demerger had not taken place.`
  line `( 13 ) The provisions contained in sub-section ( 5 ) and sub-sections ( 7 ) to ( 12 ) of section 80-IA shall, so`
  line `far as may be, apply to the eligible business under this section.`
  line `( 14 ) For the purposes of this section, —`
  line `1 [( a ) “built - up area” means the inner measurements of the residential unit at the floor level,`
  line `including the projections and balconies, as increased by the thickness of the walls but does not`
  line `include the common areas shared with other residential units;]`
  line `2 [( aa )]“cold chain facility” mea ns a chain of facilities for storage or transportation of agricultural`
  line `produce under scientifically controlled conditions including refrigeration and other facilities`
  line `necessary for the preservation of such produce;`
  line `3 [ 4 [( ab )]“convention centre” means a buil ding of a prescribed area comprising of convention halls`
  line `to be used for the purpose of holding conferences and seminars, being of such size and number and`
  line `having such other facilities and amenities, as may be prescribed;]`
  line `( b ) “hilly area” means any area lo cated at a height of one thousand metres or more above the sea`
  line level;
  line `( c ) “initial assessment year”—`
  line `( i ) in the case of an industrial undertaking or cold storage plant or ship or hotel, means the`
  line `assessment year relevant to the previous year in which the industrial undertaking begins to`
  line `manufacture or produce articles or things, or to operate its cold storage plant or plants or the cold`
  line `chain facility or the ship is first brought into use or the business of the hotel starts functioning;`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 23 of 2004, s. 18 (w.e.f. 1-4-2005).`
  line `2. Clause ( a ) re-lettered as clause ( aa ) thereof by s. 18, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-2005).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 34 (w.e.f. 1-4-2003).`
  line `4. Clause ( aa ) re-lettered as clause ( ab ) thereof by Act 23 of 2004, s. 18 (w.e.f. 1-4-2005).`
obj_root_law_sections_401_footnotes:
