obj_root_law_sections_402_content:
  string
  line 402
  line `( ii ) in the case of a company carrying on scientific and industrial research and development,`
  line `means the assessment year relevant to the previous year in which the company is approved by the`
  line `prescribed authority for the purposes of sub-section ( 8 );`
  line `( iii ) in the case of an undertaking engaged in the business of commercial production or`
  line `refining of mineral oil referred to in sub-section ( 9 ), means the assessment year relevant to the`
  line `previous year in which the undertaking commences the commercial production or refining of`
  line `mineral oil;`
  line `1 [( iv ) in the case of an undertaking engaged 2 [in the business of processing, preservation and`
  line `packaging of fruits or vegetables or] in the integrated business of handling, storage and`
  line `transportation of foodgrains, means the assessment year relevant to the previous year in which the`
  line `undertaking begins such business;]`
  line `3 [( v ) in the case of a multiplex theatre, means the assessment year relevant to the previous`
  line `year in which a cinema hall, being a part of the said multiplex theatre, starts operating on a`
  line `commercial basis;`
  line `( vi ) in the case of a convention centre, means the assessment year relevant to the previous`
  line `year in which the convention centre starts operating on a commercial basis;]`
  line `2 [( vii ) in the case of an undertaking engaged in operating and maintaining a hospital in a rural`
  line `area, means the assessment year relevant to the previous year in which the undertaking begins to`
  line `provide medical services;]`
  line `( d ) “North - Eastern Region” means the region comprising the States of Arunachal Pradesh,`
  line `Assam, Manipur, Meghalaya, Mizoram, Nagaland, Sikkim and Tripura;`
  line `3 [( da ) “multiplex theatre” means a building of a prescribed area, comprising of two or more`
  line `cinema theatres and commercial shops of such size and number and having such other facilities and`
  line `amenities as may be prescribed;]`
  line `( e ) “place of pilgrimage” means a place where any temple, mosque, gurdwara, church or other`
  line `place of public worship of renown throughout any State or States is situated;`
  line `( f ) “rural area” means any area other than—`
  line `( i ) an area which is comprised within the jurisdiction of a municipality (whether known as a`
  line `municipality, municipal corporation, notified area committee, town area committee or by any`
  line `other name) or a cantonment board and which has a population of not less than ten thousand`
  line `according to the preceding census of which relevant figures have been published before the first`
  line `day of the previous year; or`
  line `( ii ) an area within such distance not being more than fifteen kilometres from the local limits`
  line `of any municipality or cantonment board referred to in sub-clause ( i ), as the Central Government`
  line `may, having regard to the stage of development of such area including the extent of, and scope`
  line `for, urbanisation of such area and other relevant considerations specify in this behalf by`
  line `notification in the Official Gazette;`
  line `( g ) “small - scale industrial undertaking” means an industrial undertaking which is, as on the last`
  line `day of the previous year, regarded as a small-scale industrial undertaking under section 11B of the`
  line `Industries (Development and Regulation) Act, 1951 (65 of 1951).`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 14 of 2001, s. 45 (w.e.f. 1-4-2002).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 23 of 2004, s. 18 (w.e.f. 1-4-2005).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 34 (w.e.f. 1-4-2003).`
obj_root_law_sections_402_footnotes:
