obj_root_law_sections_414_content:
  string
  line 414
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this section, —`
  line `( a ) “International Financial Services Centre” shall have the same meaning as assigned to it in`
  line `clause ( q ) of section 2 of the Special Economic Zones Act, 2005;`
  line `( b ) “scheduled bank” shall have the same meaning as assigned to it in clause ( e ) of section 2 of`
  line `the Reserve Bank of India Act, 1934 (2 of 1934);`
  line `( c ) “Special Economic Zone” shall have the same meaning as assigned to it in clause ( za ) of`
  line `section 2 of the Special Economic Zones Act, 2005;`
  line `( d ) “Unit” shall have the same meaning as assigned to it in clause ( zc ) of section 2 of the Special`
  line `Economic Zones Act, 2005.]`
  line `80M. [ Deduction in respect of certain inter-corporate dividends]. — Omitted by the Finance`
  line `Act, 2003 (32 of 2003), s. 43 ( w.e.f. 1-4-2004).`
  line `80MM. [Deduction in the case of an Indian company in respect of royalties, etc., received from`
  line `any concern in India ]. — Omitted by the Finance Act, 1983 (11 of 1983), s. 29 ( w.e.f. 1-4-1984).`
  line `Original section was inserted by the Finance Act, 1969 (14 of 1969), s. 9 ( w.e.f. 1-4-1970).`
  line `80N. [Deduction in respect of dividends received from certain foreign companies ]. — Omitted by`
  line `the Finance Act, 1985 (32 of 1985), s. 22 ( w.e.f. 1-4-1986). Section 85B which was inserted by the`
  line `Finance Ac t, 1966 (13 of 1966), s. 17 ( w.e.f. 1-4-1966). Omitted section 80N was inserted in place of`
  line `section 85B which was deleted by the Finance ( No. 2) Act, 1967 (20 of 1967), s. 33 and the Third`
  line `Schedule ( w.e.f. 1-4-1968).`
  line `1 [ 80-O.Deduction in respect of royalties, etc., from certain foreign enterprises. — 2 [Where the`
  line `gross total income of an assessee, being an Indian company] 3 [or a person (other than a company) who is`
  line `resident in India],] includes 4 [any income received by the assessee from the Government of a foreign`
  line `State or foreign enterprise in consideration for the use outside India of any patent, invention, design or`
  line `registered trade mark] 5 *** 6 [and such income is received in convertible foreign exchange in India, or`
  line `having been received in convertible foreign exchange outside India, or having been converted into`
  line `convertible foreign exchange outside India, is brought into India, by or on behalf of the assessee in`
  line `accordance with any law for the time being in force for regulating payments and dealings in foreign`
  line `exchange, there shall be allowed, in accordance with and subject to the provisions of this section, 7 [a`
  line `deduction of an amount equal to —`
  line `( i ) forty per cent. for an assessment year beginning on the 1st day of April, 2001;`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 32 of 1971, s. 21, for section 80-O (w.e.f. 1-4-1972). Earlier was inserted by Act 13 of 1966, s. 17 (w.e.f. 1-`
  line `4-1966). Section 80N was inserted in place of section 85B which was deleted by the Finance (No. 2) Act, 1967 (20 of`
  line `1967), s. 33 and the Third Schedule (w.e.f. 1-4-1968).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 20 of 1974, s. 9, for “( 1 ) Where the gross total income of an assessee, being an Indian company or a person`
  line `(other than a company) who is resident in India,” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1975).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 49 of 1991, s. 34 (w.e.f. 1-4-1992).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 26 of 1997, s. 29, for certain words (w.e.f. 1-4-1998). Earlier amended by Act 49 of 1991, s. 34`
  line `(w.e.f. 1-4-1992).`
  line `5. The words “under an agreement approved in this behalf by the Chief Commissioner or the Director General;” omitted by`
  line `Act 49 of 1991, s. 34 (w.e.f. 1-4-1992).Earlier these words were substituted by Act 26 of 1988, s. 26 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 26 of 1988, s. 26, for certain words (w.e.f. 1-4-1988). Earlier section was amended by Act 20 of 1974, s. 9`
  line `(w.e.f. 1-4-1972). Later on amended by Act 21 of 1984, s. 18 (w.e.f. 1-4-1985).`
  line `7. Subs. by Act 10 of 2000, s. 41, for certain words (w.e.f. 1-4-2001).`
