obj_root_law_sections_417_content:
  string
  line 417
  line `( i ) where such co- operative society is a consumers’ co -operative society, 1 [one hundred`
  line `thousand rupees]; and`
  line `( ii ) in any other case, 2 [fifty thousand rupees].`
  line `Explanation. — In this clause, “consumers’ co - operative society” means a society for the benefit of the`
  line consumers;]
  line `( d ) in respect of any income by way of interest or dividends derived by the co-operative society`
  line `from its investments with any other co-operative society, the whole of such income;`
  line `( e ) in respect of any income derived by the co-operative society from the letting of godowns or`
  line `warehouses for storage, processing or facilitating the marketing of commodities, the whole of such`
  line income;
  line `( f ) in the case of a co-operative societ y, not being a housing society or an urban consumers’`
  line `society or a society carrying on transport business or a society engaged in the performance of any`
  line `manufacturing operations with the aid of power, where the gross total income does not exceed twenty`
  line `thousand rupees, the amount of any income by way of interest on securities 3 *** or any income from`
  line `house property chargeable under section 22.`
  line `Explanation. —For the purposes of this section, an “urban consumers’ co - operative society” means a`
  line `society for the benefit of the consumers within the limits of a municipal corporation, municipality,`
  line `municipal committee, notified area committee, town area or cantonment.`
  line `( 3 ) In a case where the assessee is entitled also to the deduction under 4 [ 5 *** 6 [section 80HH or`
  line `section 80HHA] 7 [or section 80HHB 8 [or section 80HHC 9 [or section 80HHD]]] 10 [or section 80-I] 11 [or`
  line `section 80-IA]] 12 *** 13 ***], the deduction under sub-section ( 1 ) of this section, in relation to the sums`
  line `specified in clause ( a ) or clause ( b ) or clause ( c ) of sub-section ( 2 ), shall be allowed with reference to the`
  line `income, if any, as referred to in those clauses included in the gross total income as reduced by the`
  line `14 [deductions under 15 [section 80HH, 16 [section HHA, 17 [section 80HHB, section HHC, 18 [section`
  line `80HHD], section 80-I, 19 [section 80-IA], 20 [section 80J and section 80JJ]]].`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 21 of 1998, s. 37, for “forty thousand rupees” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1999).`
  line `2. Subs. by s. 37, ibid., for “twenty thousand rupees” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1999).`
  line `3. The word “chargeable under section 18” omitted by Act 26 of 1988, s. 27 (w.e.f. 1 -4-1989).`
  line `4. Subs.by Act 26 of 1974, s. 11, for “section 80H or section 80J” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1974).`
  line `5. The words, figures, and letter “section 80H or” omitted by Act 41 of 1975, s. 24 (w.e.f. 1 -4-1976).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 29 of 1977, s. 29, for “section 80HH or section 80J” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1978).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 14 of 1982, s. 32 (w.e.f. 1-4-1983).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 11 of 1983, s. 39 (w.e.f. 1-4-1983).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 3 of 1989, s. 57 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `10. Ins. by Act 44 of 1980, s. 35 (w.e.f. 1-4-1981).`
  line `11. Ins. by Act 38 of 1993, s. 18 (w.e.f. 1-4-1991).`
  line `12. Now section 80J omitted by Act 33 of 1996, s. 29 (w.r.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `13. The words, figures and letters “or section 80JJA” omitted by Act 11 of 1983, s. 39 (w.e.f. 1-4-1984). Earlier which was`
  line `inserted by Act 21 of 1979, s. 22 (w.e.f 1-4-1976).`
  line `14. Subs. by Act 41 of 1975, s. 24, for “deduction under section 80H, section 80HH, section 80J and section 80JJ”`
  line `(w.e.f. 1-4-1976). Section 80J also omitted by s. 25 (w.e.f. 1-4-1976).`
  line `15. Subs. by Act 29 of 1977, s. 29, for “section 80HH or section 80J” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1978).`
  line `16. Subs. by Act 16 of 1981, s. 25,for “section 80HHA, section 80J” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1981).`
  line `17. Subs. by Act 11 of 1983, s. 39, for “section 80J, section 80JJ or section 80 JJA” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1983).`
  line `18. Ins. by Act 3 of 1989, s. 57 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `19. Ins. by Act 38 of 1993, s. 18 (w.e.f. 1-4-1991).`
  line `20. Subs. by Act 11 of 1983, s. 39, for “section 80J, section 80JJ and section 80JJA” (w.e.f. 1-4-1984). Now, section 80J`
  line `omitted by Act 33 of 1996, s. 29 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989) and section 80JJ omitted by Act 26 of 1997, s. 26 (w.e.f. 1-4-1998).`
