obj_root_law_sections_427_content:
  string
  line 427
  line `CHAPTER VI-B`
  line `R ESTRICTION ON CERTAIN DEDUCTIONS IN THE CASE OF COMPANIES`
  line `[Chapter VI-B, omitted by the Finance Act, 1987 (11 of 1987), s. 40 ( w.e.f. 1-4-1988). Original`
  line `Chapter was inserted by the Finance Act, 1983 (11 of 1983), s. 32 ( w.e.f. 1-4-1984) and amended by the`
  line `Finance Act, 1985, ( w.e.f. 1-4-1986) and Finance Act, 1986 (32 of 1985), s. 25( w.e.f. 1-4-1987).]`
  line `CHAPTER VII`
  line `I NCOMES FORMING PART OF TOTAL INCOME ON WHICH NO INCOME-TAX IS PAYABLE`
  line `81. to 85C. Omitted by the Finance (No. 2) Act, 1967 (20 of 1967), s. 33 and the Third Schedule`
  line `(w.e.f. 1-4-1968). Provisions of sections 81, 82, 83, 84, 85, 85A, 85B and 85C were incorporated from`
  line `the same date in sections 80P, 80Q, 10(29), 80J ( now omitted ), 80 K ( now omitted ), 80M ( now omitted ),`
  line `80N ( now omitted ) and 80-O, respectively.`
  line `1 [86.Share of member of an association of persons or body of individuals in the income of the`
  line `association or body. — Where the assessee is a member of an association of persons or body of`
  line `individuals (other than a company or a co-operative society or a society registered under the Societies`
  line `Registration Act, 1860 (21 of 1860), or under any law corresponding to that Act in force in any part of`
  line `India),income-tax shall not be payable by the assessee in respect of his share in the income of the`
  line `association or body computed in the manner provided in section 67A:`
  line `Provided that, —`
  line `( a ) where the association or body is chargeable to tax on its total income at the maximum`
  line `marginal rate or any higher rate under any of the provisions of this Act, the share of a member`
  line `computed as aforesaid shall not be included in his total income;`
  line `( b ) in any other case, the share of a member computed as aforesaid shall form part of his total`
  line `income:`
  line `Provided further that where no income-tax is chargeable on the total income of the association or`
  line `body, the share of a member computed as aforesaid shall be chargeable to tax as part of his total`
  line `income and nothing contained in this section shall apply to the case.]`
  line `86A. [ Deduction from tax on certain securities.] Omitted by the Finance Act, 1988 (26 of 1988), s. 28`
  line `( w.e.f. 1-4-1989). Original section was inserted by the Finance Act, 1965 (10 of 1985), s. 22`
  line `( w.e.f. 1-4-1965).`
  line `CHAPTER VIII`
  line `2 [REBATES AND RELIEFS]`
  line `3 [ A. — Rebate of income-tax ]`
  line `87. Rebate to be allowed in computing income-tax. — ( 1 ) In computing the amount of income-tax`
  line `on the total income of an assessee with which he is chargeable for any assessment year, there shall be`
  line `allowed from the amount of income-tax (as computed before allowing the deductions under this Chapter),`
  line `in accordance with and subject to the provisions of 4 [ 5 [sections 87A, 88], 88A, 88B, 88C, 88D and 88E],`
  line `the deductions specified in those sections.`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 18 of 1992, s. 49, for section 86 (w.e.f. 1-4-1993).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 12 of 1990, s. 30, for Heading (w.e.f. 1-4-1991).`
  line `3. Ins. by s. 30, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-1991).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 23 of 2004, s. 20, for “section 88, 88A, 88B and 88C” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2005). Earlier section amended by`
  line `Act 18 of 1992, s. 50 (w.e.f. 1-4-1993) and Act`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 17 of 2013, s. 21, for “sections 88” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2014).`
