obj_root_law_sections_429_content:
  string
  line 429
  line `Provided that such contract does not contain a provision for the exercise by the insured of an`
  line `option to receive a cash payment in lieu of the payment of the annuity;`
  line `( iii ) by way of deduction from the salary payable by or on behalf of the Government to any`
  line `individual being a sum deducted in accordance with the conditions of his service, for the purpose of`
  line `securing to him a deferred annuity or making provision for his wife or children, in so far as the sum`
  line `so deducted does not exceed one-fifth of the salary;`
  line `( iv ) as a contribution by an individual to any provident fund to which the Provident Funds Act,`
  line `1925 (19 of 1925), applies;`
  line `( v ) as a contribution to any provident fund set up by the Central Government and notified by it in`
  line `this behalf in the Official Gazette, where such contribution is to an account standing in the name of`
  line `any person specified in sub-section ( 4 );`
  line `( vi ) as a contribution by an employee to a recognised provident fund;`
  line `( vii ) as a contribution by an employee to an approved superannuation fund;`
  line `( viii ) in a ten-year account or a fifteen-year account under the Post Office Savings Bank`
  line `(Cumulative Time Deposits) Rules, 1959, as amended from time to time, where such sums are`
  line `deposited in an account standing in the name of the persons specified in sub-section ( 4 );`
  line `( ix ) as subscription to any such security of the Central Government 1 [or any such deposit scheme]`
  line `as that Government may, by notification in the Official Gazette, specify in this behalf;`
  line `( x ) as subscription to the National Savings Certificates (VI Issue) and National Savings`
  line `Certificates (VII Issue) issued under the Government Savings Certificates Act, 1959 (46 of 1959);`
  line `( xi ) as subscription to any such savings certificate as defined in clause ( c ) of section 2 of the`
  line `Government Savings Certificates Act, 1959 (46 of 1959), as the Central Government may, by`
  line `notification in the Official Gazette, specify in this behalf;`
  line `( xii ) as a contribution, 2 [in the name of any person] specified in sub-section ( 4 ), for participation`
  line `in the Unit-linked Insurance Plan, 1971 (hereafter in this section referred to as the Unit-linked`
  line `Insurance Plan) deemed to have been made under sub-clause ( a ) of clause ( 8 ) of section 19 of the`
  line `Unit Trust of India Act, 1963 (52 of 1963);`
  line `( xiii ) as a contribution 3 [in the name of any person specified in sub-section ( 4 )] for participation`
  line `in any such unit-linked insurance plan of the LIC Mutual Fund notified under clause ( 23D ) of section`
  line `10, as the Central Government may, by notification in the Official Gazette, specify in this behalf;`
  line `1 [( xiiia ) to effect or to keep in force a contract for such annuity plan of the Life Insurance`
  line `Corporation 4 [or any other insurer] as the Central Government may, by notification in the Official`
  line `Gazette, specify;`
  line `( xiiib ) as subscription, not exceeding ten thousand rupees, to any units of any Mutual Fund`
  line `notified under clause ( 23D ) of section 10 or the Unit Trust of India established under the Unit Trust`
  line `of India Act, 1963 (52 of 1963), under any plan formulated in accordance with such scheme as the`
  line `Central Government may, by notification in the Official Gazette, specify in this behalf;`
  line `( xiiic ) as a contribution by an individual to any pension fund set up by any Mutual Fund notified`
  line `under clause ( 23D ) of section 10 5 [or by the Unit Trust of India established under the Unit Trust of`
  line `India Act, 1963 (52 of 1963)], as the Central Government may, by notification in the Official Gazette,`
  line `specify in this behalf;]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 18 of 1992, s. 51 (w.e.f. 1-4-1993).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 32 of 1994, s. 29, for “by any person” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1991)`
  line `3. Subs. by s. 29, ibid., for “by any individual” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1991).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 14 of 2001, s. 47 (w.e.f. 1-4-2002).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 32 of 1994, s. 29 (w.e.f. 1-4-1995).`
