obj_root_law_sections_430_content:
  string
  line 430
  line `( xiv ) as subscription to any such deposit scheme of 1 [, or as a contribution to any such pension`
  line `fund set up by], the National Housing Bank established under section 3 of the National Housing Bank`
  line `Act, 1987 (53 of 1987) (hereafter in this section referred to as the National Housing Bank), as the`
  line `Central Government may, by notification in the Official Gazette, specify in this behalf;`
  line `2 [( xiva ) as subscription to any such deposit scheme of —`
  line `( a ) a public sector company which is engaged in providing long-term finance for construction`
  line `or purchase of houses in India for residential purposes; or`
  line `( b ) any authority constituted in India by or under any law enacted either for the purpose of`
  line `dealing with and satisfying the need for housing accommodation or for the purpose of planning,`
  line `development or improvement of cities, towns and villages, or for both,`
  line `not being a scheme the interest on deposits whereunder qualifies for the purposes of computing the`
  line `deduction under section 80L, as the Central Government may, by notification in the Official Gazette,`
  line `specify in this behalf;]`
  line `3 [( xivb ) as tuition fees (excluding any payment towards any development fees or donation or`
  line `payment of similar nature), whether at the time of admission or thereafter, —`
  line `( a ) to any university, college, school or other educational institution situated within India;`
  line `( b ) for the purpose of full-time education of any of the persons specified in sub-section ( 4 );]`
  line `( xv ) for the purposes of purchase or construction of a residential house property 4 *** the income`
  line `from which is chargeable to tax under the head “Income from house property” (or which would, if it`
  line `had not b een used for the assessee’s own residence, have been chargeable to tax under that head),`
  line `where such payments are made towards or by way of —`
  line `( a ) any instalment or part payment of the amount due under any self-financing or other`
  line `scheme of any development authority, housing board or other authority engaged in the`
  line `construction and sale of house property on ownership basis; or`
  line `( b ) any instalment or part payment of the amount due to any company or co-operative society`
  line `of which the assessee is a shareholder or member towards the cost of the house property allotted`
  line `to him; or`
  line `( c ) repayment of the amount borrowed by the assessee from —`
  line `( 1 ) the Central Government or any State Government, or`
  line `( 2 ) any bank, including a co-operative bank, or`
  line `( 3 ) the Life Insurance Corporation, or`
  line `( 4 ) the National Housing Bank, or`
  line `( 5 ) any public company formed and registered in India with the main object of carrying`
  line `on the business of providing long-term finance for construction or purchase of houses in India`
  line `for residential purposes 5 [which is eligible for deduction under clause ( viii ) of sub-section ( 1 )`
  line `of section 36], or`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 18 of 1992, s. 51 (w.e.f. 1-4-1993).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 49 of 1991, s. 38 (w.e.f. 1-4-1992).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 47 (w.e.f. 1-4-2004).`
  line `4. The words “construction of which is completed after the 31st day of March, 1987, and the” omitted by Act 49 of 1991,`
  line `s. 38 (w.e.f. 1-4-1992).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 10 of 2000, s. 46, for “which is approved for the purposes of clause ( viii ) of sub-section ( 1 ) of section 36`
  line `(w.e.f. 1-4-2000).`
