obj_root_law_sections_462_content:
  string
  line 462
  line `1 [ 112. Tax on long-term capital gains. — ( 1 ) Where the total income of an assessee includes any`
  line `income, arising from the transfer of a long- term capital asset, which is chargeable under the head “Capital`
  line `gains”, the tax payable by the assessee on the total income shall be the aggregate of, —`
  line `( a ) in the case of an individual or a Hindu undivided family, 2 [being a resident,] —`
  line `( i ) the amount of income-tax payable on the total income as reduced by the amount of such`
  line `long-term capital gains, had the total income as so reduced been his total income; and`
  line `( ii ) the amount of income-tax calculated on such long-term capital gains at the rate of twenty`
  line `per cent.:`
  line `Provided that where the total income as reduced by such long-term capital gains is below the`
  line `maximum amount which is not chargeable to income-tax, then, such long-term capital gains shall`
  line `be reduced by the amount by which the total income as so reduced falls short of the maximum`
  line `amount which is not chargeable to income-tax and the tax on the balance of such long-term`
  line `capital gains shall be computed at the rate of twenty per cent.;`
  line `( b ) in the case of a 3 [domestic company], —`
  line `( i ) the amount of income-tax payable on the total income as reduced by the amount of such`
  line `long-term capital gains, had the total income as so reduced been its total income; and`
  line `( ii ) the amount of income-tax calculated on such long-term capital gains at the rate of`
  line `4 [twenty per cent.]:`
  line `5 * * * * *`
  line `2 [( c ) in the case of a non-resident (not being a company) or a foreign company, —`
  line `( i ) the amount of income-tax payable on the total income as reduced by the amount of such`
  line `long-term capital gains, had the total income as so reduced been its total income; and`
  line `6 [( ii ) the amount of income-tax calculated on long-term capital gains [except where such gain`
  line `arises from transfer of capital asset referred to in sub-clause ( iii )] at the rate of twenty per cent.;`
  line and]
  line `( iii ) the amount of income-tax on long-term capital gains arising from the transfer of a capital`
  line `asset, being 7 [unlisted securities or shares of a company not being a company in which the public`
  line `are substantially interested ], calculated at the rate of ten per cent. on the capital gains in respect of`
  line `such asset as computed without giving effect to the first and second proviso to section 48;]]`
  line `8 [( d )] in any other case 9 [of a resident], —`
  line `( i ) the amount of income-tax payable on the total income as reduced by the amount of`
  line `long-term capital gains, had the total income as so reduced been its total income; and`
  line `( ii ) the amount of income-tax calculated on such long-term capital gains at the rate of`
  line `10 [twenty per cent.; and]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 18 of 1992, s. 53 (w.e.f. 1-4-1993). Earlier section 112 was omitted by 20 of 1967, s. 33 and the Third`
  line `Schedule (w.e.f. 1-4-1968)`
  line `2. Ins. by 32 of 1994, s. 31 (w.e.f. 1-4-1995).`
  line `3. Subs. by s. 31, ibid., for “company” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1995).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 33 of 1996, s. 37, for “thirty per cent.” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1997).Earlier substituted by Act 32 of 1994, s. 31, for`
  line `“forty per cent.” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1995).`
  line `5. Proviso omitted by Act 22 of 1995, s. 23 (w.e.f. 1-4-1996). Prior to its omission, the proviso, as amended by the 22 of`
  line `1995, s. 23 (w.e.f. 1-4-1996). Prior to its omission, the proviso, as amended by the 32 of 1994, s. 31 (1-4-1995).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 43, for sub-clause ( ii ) (w.e.f. 1-4-2013).`
  line `7. Subs. by 28 of 2016, s. 50, for “unlisted securities” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2017).`
  line `8. Clause ( c ) relettered as Clause ( d ) thereof by Act 32 of 1994, s. 31 (w.e.f. 1-4-1995).`
  line `9. Ins. by s. 31, ibid., (w.e.f. 1-4-1995).`
  line `10. Subs. by Act 33 of 19 96, s. 37, for “thirty per cent.” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1997).`
