obj_root_law_sections_465_content:
  string
  line 465
  line `1 [113. Tax in the case of block assessment of search cases. — The total undisclosed income of the`
  line `block period, determined under section 158BC, shall be chargeable to tax at the rate of sixty per cent.:]`
  line `2 [Provided that the tax chargeable under this section shall be increased by a surcharge, if any, levied`
  line `by any Central Act and applicable in the assessment year relevant to the previous year in which the search`
  line `is initiated under section 132 or the requisition is made under section 132A.]`
  line `114. [ Tax on capital gains in cases of assessees other than companies.] — Omitted by the Finance`
  line `( No. 2) Act, 1967, w.e.f. 1-4-1968 and reintroduced with material modifications in section 80T. Section`
  line `114 was substituted first by the Finance ( No. 2) Act, 1962, w.e.f. 1-4-1962 and later on amended by the`
  line `Finance Act, 1964, w.e.f. 1-4-1964, the Finance Act, 1965, w.e.f. 1-4-1965, the Finance ( No. 2) Act, 1965,`
  line `w.e.f. 11-9-1965 and the Finance Act, 1966, w.e.f. 1-4-1966.`
  line `115. [ Tax on capital gains in case of companies.] — Omitted by the Finance Act, 1987 (11 of 1987),`
  line `s. 42 ( w.e.f. 1-4-1988).`
  line `3 [115A. Tax on dividends, royalty and technical service fees in the case of foreign`
  line `companies. — 4 [( 1 ) Where the total income of —`
  line `( a ) a non-resident (not being a company) or of a foreign company, includes any income by way`
  line `of —`
  line `( i ) 5 [dividends other than dividends referred to in section 115-O]; or`
  line `( ii ) interest received from Government or an Indian concern on monies borrowed or debt`
  line `incurred by Government or the Indian concern in foreign currency 6 [not being interest of the`
  line `nature referred to in 7 [sub-clause ( iia ) or sub-clause ( iiaa )]]; or`
  line `6 [( iia ) interest received from an infrastructure debt fund referred to in clause ( 47 ) of`
  line `section 10; or]`
  line `8 [( iiaa ) interest of the nature and extent referred to in section 194LC; or]`
  line `9 [( iiab ) interest of the nature and extent referred to in section 194LD; or]`
  line `10 [( iiac ) distributed income being interest referred to in sub-section ( 2 ) of section 194LBA;]`
  line `( iii ) income received in respect of units, purchased in foreign currency, of a Mutual Fund`
  line `specified under clause ( 23D ) of section 10 or of the Unit Trust of India,`
  line `the income-tax payable shall be aggregate of —`
  line `( A ) the amount of income-tax calculated on the amount of income by way of 5 [dividends`
  line `other than dividends referred to in section 115-O], if any, included in the total income, at the rate`
  line `of twenty per cent;`
  line `( B ) the amount of income-tax calculated on the amount of income by way of interest referred`
  line `to in sub-clause ( ii ), if any, included in the total income, at the rate of twenty per cent.;`
  line `6 [( BA ) the amount of income-tax calculated on the amount of income by way of interest`
  line `referred to in sub-clause ( iia ) 11 [or sub-clause ( iiaa )] 9 [or sub-clause ( iiab )] 10 [or sub-clause`
  line `( iiac )], if any, included in the total income, at the rate of five per cent.;]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 22 of 1995, s. 24 (w.e.f. 1-7- 1995). Earlier section 113 dealing with “Tax in the case of non - resident” omitted`
  line `by Act 10 of 1965, s. 35 (w.e.f. 1-4-1965).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 44 (w.e.f. 1-6-2002).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 66 of 1976, s. 20 (w.e.f. 1-6-1976).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 32 of 1994, s. 32, for sub-section ( 1 ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1995).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 50, for “dividends” (w.e.f. 1 -4- 2004). Earlier the word “dividends” substituted by Act 26 of`
  line `1997, s. 32 (w.e.f. 1-4- 1998) and the words, figures and letter “other than dividends referred to in section 115 - O” omitted`
  line `by Act 20 of 2002, s. 45 (w.e.f. 1-4-2003).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 8 of 2011, s. 16 (w.e.f. 1-6-2011).`
  line `7. Subs. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 44, for “clause ( iia )” (w.e.f. 1 -7-2012).`
  line `8. Ins. by s. 44, ibid (w.e.f. 1-7-2012).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 17 of 2013, s. 27 (w.e.f. 1-4-2014).`
  line `10. Ins. by Act 25 of 2014, s. 36 (w.e.f. 1-4-2015).`
  line `11. Ins. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 44 (w.e.f. 1-7-2012).`
