obj_root_law_sections_482_content:
  string
  line 482
  line `1 [CHAPTER XII-B`
  line `S PECIAL PROVISIONS RELATING TO CERTAIN COMPANIES`
  line `115J. Special provisions relating to certain companies. — ( 1 ) Notwithstanding anything contained`
  line `in any other provision of this Act, where in the case of an assessee being a company 2 [(other than a`
  line `company engaged in the business of generation or distribution of electricity)], the total income, as`
  line `computed under this Act in respect of any previous year relevant to the assessment year commencing on`
  line `or after the 1st day of April, 1988 3 [but before the 1st day of April, 1991] (hereafter in this section`
  line `referred to as the relevant previous year), is less than thirty per cent of its book profit, the total income of`
  line `such assessee chargeable to tax for the relevant previous year shall be deemed to be an amount equal to`
  line `thirty per cent of such book profit.`
  line `4 [( 1A ) Every assessee, being a company, shall, for the purposes of this section, prepare its profit and`
  line `loss account for the relevant previous year in accordance with the provisions of Parts II and III of`
  line `Schedule VI to the Companies Act, 1956 (1 of 1956).]`
  line `Explanation. —For the purposes of this section, “book profit” means the net profit as shown in the`
  line `profit and loss account for the relevant previous year 5 [prepared under sub-section ( 1A )], as increased`
  line `by —`
  line `( a ) the amount of income-tax paid or payable, and the provision therefor; or`
  line `( b ) the amounts carried to any reserves 2 [(other than the reserves specified in section 80HHD`
  line `6 [or sub-section ( 1 ) of section 33AC])], by whatever name called; or`
  line `( c ) the amount or amounts set aside to provisions made for meeting liabilities, other than`
  line `ascertained liabilities; or`
  line `( d ) the amount by way of provision for losses of subsidiary companies; or`
  line `( e ) the amount or amounts of dividends paid or proposed; or`
  line `( f ) the amount or amounts of expenditure relatable to any income to which any of the provisions`
  line `of Chapter III 7 [applies; or]`
  line `2 [( g ) the amount withdrawn from the reserve account under section 80HHD, where it has been`
  line `utilised for any purpose other than those referred to in sub-section ( 4 ) of that section; or`
  line `( h ) the amount credited to the reserve account under section 80HHD, to the extent that amount`
  line `has not been utilised within the period specified in sub-section ( 4 ) of that section;]`
  line `6 [( ha ) the amount deemed to be the profits under sub-section ( 3 ) of section 33AC,]`
  line `8 [if any amount referred to in clauses ( a ) to ( f ) is debited or, as the case may be, the amount referred to in`
  line `clauses ( g ) and ( h ) is not credited] to the profit and loss account, and as reduced by, —`
  line `( i ) the amount withdrawn from reserves 2 [(other than the reserves specified in section 80HHD)]`
  line `or provisions, if any such amount is credited to the 9 [profit and loss account:`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 11 of 1987, s. 43 (w.e.f. 1-4-1988).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 3 of 1989, s. 19 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 12 of 1990, s. 32 (w.e.f. 1-4-1990).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 13 of 1989, s. 19 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `5. Subs. by s. 19, ibid., for “prepared in accordance with the provisions of Parts II and III of the Sixth Schedule to the`
  line `Companies Act, 1956 (1 of 1956)” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1989).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 36 of 1989, s. 12 (w.e.f. 1-4-1990).`
  line `7. Subs. by A ct 3 of 1989, s. 19, for “applies,” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1989).`
  line `8. Subs. by s. 19, ibid., for “if any such amount is debited” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1989).`
  line `9. Subs. by Act 13 of 1989, s. 19, for “profit and loss account; or” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1988).`
