obj_root_law_sections_483_content:
  string
  line 483
  line `Provided that, where this section is applicable to an assessee in any previous year (including the`
  line `relevant previous year), the amount withdrawn from reserves created or provisions made in a`
  line `previous year relevant to the assessment year commencing on or after the 1st day of April, 1988 shall`
  line `not be reduced from the book profit unless the book profit of such year has been increased by those`
  line `reserves or provisions (out of which the said amount was withdrawn) under this Explanation; or]`
  line `( ii ) the amount of income to which any of the provisions of Chapter III applies, if any such`
  line `amount is credited to the profit and loss account; or`
  line `1 [( iii ) the amounts [as arrived at after increasing the net profit by the amounts referred to in`
  line `clauses ( a ) to ( f ) and reducing the net profit by the amounts referred to in clauses ( i ) and ( ii )]`
  line `attributable to the business, the profits from which are eligible for deduction under section 80HHC or`
  line `section 80HHD; so, however, that such amounts are computed in the manner specified in`
  line `sub-section ( 3 ) or sub-section ( 3A ) of section 80HHC or sub-section ( 3 ) of section 80HHD, as the`
  line `case may be; or]`
  line `2 [( iv )] the amount of the loss or the amount of depreciation which would be required to be set off`
  line `against the profit of the relevant previous year as if the provisions of clause ( b ) of the first proviso to`
  line `sub-section ( 1 ) of section 205 of the Companies Act, 1956 (1 of 1956), are applicable.`
  line `( 2 ) Nothing contained in sub-section ( 1 ) shall affect the determination of the amounts in relation to`
  line `the relevant previous year to be carried forward to the subsequent year or years under the provisions of`
  line `sub-section ( 2 ) of section 32 or sub-section ( 3 ) of section 32A or clause ( ii ) of sub-section ( 1 ) of section`
  line `72 or section 73 or section 74 or sub-section ( 3 ) of section 74A or sub-section ( 3 ) of section 80J.]`
  line `3 [115JA. Deemed income relating to certain companies. — ( 1 ) Notwithstanding anything contained`
  line `in any other provisions of this Act, where in the case of an assessee, being a company, the total income,`
  line `as computed under this Act in respect of any previous year relevant to the assessment year commencing`
  line `on or after the 1st day of April, 1997 4 [but before the 1st day of April, 2001] (hereafter in this section`
  line `referred to as the relevant previous year) is less than thirty per cent of its book profit, the total income of`
  line `such assessee chargeable to tax for the relevant previous year shall be deemed to be an amount equal to`
  line `thirty per cent of such book profit.`
  line `( 2 ) Every assessee, being a company, shall, for the purposes of this section prepare its profit and loss`
  line `account for the relevant previous year in accordance with the provisions of Parts II and III of Schedule VI`
  line `to the Companies Act, 1956 (1 of 1956):`
  line `Provided that while preparing profit and loss account, the depreciation shall be calculated on the same`
  line `method and rates which have been adopted for calculating the depreciation for the purpose of preparing`
  line `the profit and loss account laid before the company at its annual general meeting in accordance with the`
  line `provisions of section 210 of the Companies Act, 1956 (1 of 1956):`
  line `Provided further that where a company has adopted or adopts the financial year under the Companies`
  line `Act, 1956 (1 of 1956), which is different from the previous year under the Act, the method and rates for`
  line `calculation of depreciation shall correspond to the method and rates which have been adopted for`
  line `calculating the depreciation for such financial year or part of such financial year falling within the`
  line `relevant previous year.`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 3 of 1989, s. 19 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `2. Clause ( iii ) renumbered as clause ( iv ) by s. 19, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 33 of 1996, s. 39 (w.e.f. 1-4-1997).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 10 of 2000, s. 50 (w.e.f. 1-4-2001).`
obj_root_law_sections_483_footnotes:
  string
