obj_root_law_sections_488_content:
  string
  line 488
  line `shall correspond to the accounting policies, accounting standards and the method and rates for`
  line `calculating the depreciation which have been adopted for preparing such accounts including`
  line `1 [statement of profit and loss] for such financial year or part of such financial year falling within the`
  line `relevant previous year.`
  line `Explanation 2 [ 1 ]. —For the purposes of this section, “book profit” means the 3 [profit] as shown in the`
  line `1 [statement of profit and loss] for the relevant previous year prepared under sub-section ( 2 ), as increased`
  line `by —`
  line `( a ) the amount of income-tax paid or payable, and the provision therefor; or`
  line `( b ) the amounts carried to any reserves, by whatever name called 4 [, other than a reserve specified`
  line `under section 33AC]; or`
  line `( c ) the amount or amounts set aside to provisions made for meeting liabilities, other than`
  line `ascertained liabilities; or`
  line `( d ) the amount by way of provision for losses of subsidiary companies; or`
  line `( e ) the amount or amounts of dividends paid or proposed; or`
  line `( f ) the amount or amounts of expenditure relatable to any income to which 5 [section 10 (other`
  line `than the provisions contained in clause ( 38 ) thereof) or 6 *** section 11 or section 12 apply; or]`
  line `7 [( fa ) the amount or amounts of expenditure relatable to income, being share of the assessee in the`
  line `income of an association of persons or body of individuals, on which no income-tax is payable in`
  line `accordance with the provisions of section 86; or`
  line `( fb ) the amount or amounts of expenditure relatable to income accruing or arising to an assessee,`
  line `being a foreign company, from, —`
  line `( A ) the capital gains arising on transactions in securities; or`
  line `( B ) the interest, royalty or fees for technical services chargeable to tax at the rate or rates`
  line `specified in Chapter XII,`
  line `if the income-tax payable thereon in accordance with the provisions of this Act, other than the`
  line `provisions of this Chapter, is at a rate less than the rate specified in sub-section ( 1 ); or`
  line `( fc ) the amount representing notional loss on transfer of a capital asset, being share of a special`
  line `purpose vehicle, to a business trust in exchange of units allotted by the trust referred to in`
  line `clause ( xvii ) of section 47 or the amount representing notional loss resulting from any change in`
  line `carrying amount of said units or the amount of loss on transfer of units referred to in`
  line `clause ( xvii ) of section 47; or]`
  line `8 [( fd ) the amount or amounts of expenditure relatable to income by way of royalty in respect of`
  line `patent chargeable to tax under section 115BBF; or]`
  line `9 [( g ) the amount of depreciation,]`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 47, for “profit and loss account” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2017).`
  line `2. The Explanation numbered as Explanation 1 by Act 18 of 2008, s. 23 (w.e.f. 1-4-2001).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 47, for “net profit” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2017).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 52 (w.e.f. 1-4-2003).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 21 of 2006, s. 24, for “section 10 (other th an the provisions contained in clause (23G) thereof) or section`
  line `10A or section 10B or section 11 or section 12 apply,” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2007).`
  line `6. The words, figures and letters “section 10A or section 10B or” omitted by Act 22 of 2007, s. 34 (w.e.f. 1 -4-2008).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 20 of 2015, s. 30 (w.e.f. 1-4-2016).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 55 (w.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 21 of 2006, s. 24 (w.e.f. 1-4-2007).`
