obj_root_law_sections_489_content:
  string
  line 489
  line `1 [( h ) the amount of deferred tax and the provision therefor,`
  line `2 [( i ) the amount or amounts set aside as provision for diminution in the value of any asset,`
  line `3 [( j ) the amount standing in revaluation reserve relating to revalued asset on the retirement or`
  line `disposal of such asset,`
  line `4 [( k ) the amount of gain on transfer of units referred to in clause ( xvii ) of section 47 computed by`
  line `taking into account the cost of the shares exchanged with units referred to in the said clause or the`
  line `carrying amount of the shares at the time of exchange where such shares are carried at a value other`
  line `than the cost through 5 [statement of profit and loss], as the case may be;]`
  line `if any amount referred to in clauses ( a ) to ( i ) is debited to the 5 [statement of profit and loss] or`
  line `if any amount referred to in clause ( j ) is not credited to the 5 [statement of profit and loss], and as reduced`
  line `by, — ]]]`
  line `6 [( i ) the amount withdrawn from any reserve or provision (excluding a reserve created before the`
  line `1st day of April, 1997 otherwise than by way of a debit to the 5 [statement of profit and loss]), if any`
  line `such amount is credited to the 5 [statement of profit and loss]:`
  line `Provided that where this section is applicable to an assessee in any previous year, the amount`
  line `withdrawn from reserves created or provisions made in a previous year relevant to the assessment`
  line `year commencing on or after the 1st day of April, 1997 shall not be reduced from the book profit`
  line `unless the book profit of such year has been increased by those reserves or provisions (out of which`
  line `the said amount was withdrawn) under this Explanation or Explanation below the second proviso`
  line `to section 115JA, as the case may be; or]`
  line `( ii ) the amount of income to which any of the provisions of 7 [section 10 (other than the provisions`
  line `contained in clause ( 38 ) thereof)] or 8 *** section 11 or section 12 apply, if any such amount is`
  line `credited to the 5 [statement of profit and loss]; or`
  line `9 [( iia ) the amount of depreciation debited to the 5 [statement of profit and loss] (excluding the`
  line `depreciation on account of revaluation of assets); or`
  line `( iib ) the amount withdrawn from revaluation reserve and credited to the 5 [statement of profit and`
  line `loss], to the extent it does not exceed the amount of depreciation on account of revaluation of assets`
  line `referred to in clause ( iia ); or]`
  line `10 [( iic ) the amount of income, being the share of the assessee in the income of an association of`
  line `persons or body of individuals, on which no income-tax is payable in accordance with the provisions`
  line `of section 86, if any, such amount is credited to the 5 [statement of profit and loss]; or`
  line `( iid ) the amount of income accruing or arising to an assessee, being a foreign company, from, —`
  line `( A ) the capital gains arising on transactions in securities; or`
  line `( B ) the interest, royalty or fees for technical services chargeable to tax at the rate or rates`
  line `specified in Chapter XII,`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 18 of 2008, s. 23, for the portion beginning with the words “if any amount referred” and ending with the`
  line `words “as reduced by—” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2001).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 33 of 2009, s. 46, for “if any amount referred to in clauses ( a ) to ( h ) is debited to the profit and loss account,`
  line `and as reduced by —“ (1 -4-2001)`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 48, for “if any amount referred to in clauses ( a ) to ( i ) is debited to the profit and loss account,`
  line `and as reduced by, —” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2013).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 20 of 2015, s. 30 (w.e.f. 1-4-2016).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 47, for “profit or loss account” (w.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 52, for clause ( i ) and the proviso (w.e.f. 1-4-2001).`
  line `7. Subs. by Act 21 of 2006, s. 24, for “section 10 (other than the provisions contained in clause (23G) thereof)”`
  line `(w.e.f. 1-4-2007).`
  line `8. The words, figures and letters “section 10A or section 10B or” omitted by Act 22 of 2007, s. 34 (w.e.f. 1 -4-2008).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 21 of 2006, s. 24 (w.e.f. 1-4-2007).`
  line `10. Ins. by Act 20 of 2015, s. 30 (w.e.f. 1-4-2016).`
