obj_root_law_sections_490_content:
  string
  line 490
  line `if such income is credited to the 1 [statement of profit and loss] and the income-tax payable thereon in`
  line `accordance with the provisions of this Act, other than the provisions of this Chapter, is at a rate less than`
  line `the rate specified in sub-section ( 1 ); or`
  line `( iie ) the amount representing, —`
  line `( A ) notional gain on transfer of a capital asset, being share of a special purpose vehicle to a`
  line `business trust in exchange of units allotted by that trust referred to in clause ( xvii ) of section 47;`
  line or
  line `( B ) notional gain resulting from any change in carrying amount of said units; or`
  line `( C ) gain on transfer of units referred to in clause ( xvii ) of section 47,`
  line `if any, credited to the 1 [statement of profit and loss]; or`
  line `( iif ) the amount of loss on transfer of units referred to in clause ( xvii ) of section 47 computed by`
  line `taking into account the cost of the shares exchanged with units referred to in the said clause or the`
  line `carrying amount of the shares at the time of exchange where such shares are carried at a value other`
  line `than the cost through profit or loss account, as the case may be; or]`
  line `2 [( iig ) the amount of income by way of royalty in respect of patent chargeable to tax under`
  line `section 115BBF;] or`
  line `3 [( iih ) the aggregate amount of unabsorbed depreciation and loss brought forward in case of a`
  line `company against whom an application for corporate insolvency resolution process has been admitted`
  line `by the Adjudicating Authority under section 7 or section 9 or section 10 of the Insolvency and`
  line `Bankruptcy Code, 2016.`
  line `Explanation. ––For the purposes of this clause, the expression “Adjudicating Authority” shall`
  line `have the meaning assigned to it in clause ( 1 ) of section 5 of the Insolvency and Bankruptcy Code,`
  line `2016 and the loss shall not include depreciation; or;]`
  line `4 [( iii ) the amount of loss brought forward or unabsorbed depreciation, whichever is less as per`
  line `books of account 3 [in case of a company other than the company referred to in clause ( iih )].`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this clause, —`
  line `( a ) the loss shall not include depreciation;`
  line `( b ) the provisions of this clause shall not apply if the amount of loss brought forward or`
  line `unabsorbed depreciation is nil; or]`
  line `5 * * * * *`
  line `( vii ) the amount of profits of sick industrial company for the assessment year commencing on and`
  line `from the assessment year relevant to the previous year in which the said company has become a sick`
  line `industrial company under sub-section ( 1 ) of section 17 of the Sick Industrial Companies (Special`
  line `Provisions) Act, 1985 (1 of 1986) and ending with the assessment year during which the entire net`
  line `worth of such company becomes equal to or exceeds the accumulated losses.`
  line `Explanation. —For the purposes of this clause, “net worth” shall have the meaning assigned to it`
  line `in clause ( ga ) of sub-section ( 1 ) of section 3 of the Sick Industrial Companies (Special Provisions)`
  line `Act, 1985 (1 of 1986); or`
  line `6 [( viii ) the amount of deferred tax, if any such amount is credited to the 1 [statement of profit and`
  line loss].]
  line `1. Subs. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 47, for “profit and loss account” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2017).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 55 (w.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 13 of 2018, s. 37 (w.e.f. 1-4-2018).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 52, for clause ( iii ) and the Explanation (w.e.f. 1-4-2001).`
  line `5. Clause ( iv ), clause ( v ) and clause ( vi ) omitted by Act 8 of 2011, s. 18 (w.e.f. 1-4-2005).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 18 of 2008, s. 23 (w.e.f. 1-4-2001).`
