obj_root_law_sections_491_content:
  string
  line 491
  line `1 [ Explanation 2. — For the purposes of clause ( a ) of Explanation 1, the amount of income-tax shall`
  line `include —`
  line `( i ) any tax on distributed profits under section 115-O or on distributed income under`
  line `section 115R;`
  line `( ii ) any interest charged under this Act;`
  line `( iii ) surcharge, if any, as levied by the Central Acts from time to time;`
  line `( iv ) Education Cess on income-tax, if any, as levied by the Central Acts from time to time; and`
  line `( v ) Secondary and Higher Education Cess on income-tax, if any, as levied by the Central Acts`
  line `from time to time.]`
  line `2 [ Explanation 3. — For the removal of doubts, it is hereby clarified that for the purposes of this`
  line `section, the assessee, being a company to which the 3 [second proviso to sub-section ( 1 ) of section 129 of`
  line `the Companies Act, 2013 (18 of 2013)] is applicable, has, for an assessment year commencing on or`
  line `before the 1st day of April, 2012, an option to prepare its 4 [statement of profit and loss] for the relevant`
  line `previous year either in accordance with the provisions of 5 [Schedule III to the Companies Act, 2013 (18`
  line `of 2013)] or in accordance with the provisions of the Act governing such company.`
  line `6 [ Explanation 4. — For the removal of doubts, it is hereby clarified that the provisions of this section`
  line `shall not be applicable and shall be deemed never to have been applicable to an assessee, being a foreign`
  line `company, if —`
  line `( i ) the assessee is a resident of a country or a specified territory with which India has an`
  line `agreement referred to in sub-section ( 1 ) of section 90 or the Central Government has adopted any`
  line `agreement under sub-section ( 1 ) of section 90A and the assessee does not have a permanent`
  line `establishment in India in accordance with the provisions of such agreement; or`
  line `( ii ) the assessee is a resident of a country with which India does not have an agreement of the`
  line `nature referred to in clause ( i ) and the assessee is not required to seek registration under any law for`
  line `the time being in force relating to companies.]`
  line `7 [ Explanation 4A. — For the removal of doubts, it is hereby clarified that the provisions of this section`
  line `shall not be applicable and shall be deemed never to have been applicable to an assessee, being a foreign`
  line `company, where its total income comprises solely of profits and gains from business referred to in section`
  line `44B or section 44BB or section 44BBA or section 44BBB and such income has been offered to tax at the`
  line `rates specified in those sections.]`
  line `8 [ 9 [ Explanation 5 ]. — For the purposes of sub-section ( 2 ), the expression “securities” shall have the`
  line `same meaning as assigned to it in clause ( h ) of section 2 of the Securities Contracts (Regulation) Act,`
  line `1956 (42 of 1956).]`
  line `10 [( 2A ) For a company whose financial statements are drawn up in compliance to the Indian`
  line `Accounting Standards specified in Annexure to the Companies (Indian Accounting Standards) Rules,`
  line `2015, the book profit as computed in accordance with Explanation 1 to sub-section ( 2 ) shall be further ––`
  line `( a ) increased by all amounts credited to other comprehensive income in the statement of profit`
  line `and loss under the head “Items that will not be re -classified to profit or loss;`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 18 of 2008, s. 23 (w.e.f. 1-4-2001).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 48 (w.e.f. 1-4-2013).`
  line `3. Subs. by Ac t 7 of 2017, s. 47, for “ proviso to sub-section ( 2 ) of section 211 of the Companies Act, 1956 (1 of 1956)”`
  line `(w.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
  line `4. Subs. by s. 47, ibid., for “profit and loss account” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2017).`
  line `5. Subs. by s. 47, ibid., for “ Part II and Part III of Schedule VI to the Companies Act, 1956 (1 of 1956)” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2017).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 55 (w.e.f. 1-4-2001).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 13 of 2018, s. 37 (w.e.f. 1-4-2001).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 20 of 2015, s. 30 (w.e.f. 1-4-2016).`
  line `9. Explanation 4 renumbered as Explanation 5 thereof by Act 28 of 2016, s. 55 (w.e.f. 1-4-2001).`
  line `10. Ins. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 47 (w.e.f. 1-4-2018).`
