obj_root_law_sections_493_content:
  string
  line 493
  line `( C ) gains or losses from investments in equity instruments designated at fair value through`
  line `other comprehensive income in accordance with the Indian Accounting Standards 109 adjusted`
  line `on the convergence date;`
  line `( D ) adjustments relating to items of property, plant and equipment and intangible assets`
  line `recorded at fair value as deemed cost in accordance with paragraphs D5 and D7 of the Indian`
  line `Accounting Standards 101 on the convergence date;`
  line `( E ) adjustments relating to investments in subsidiaries, joint ventures and associates recorded`
  line `at fair value as deemed cost in accordance with paragraph D15 of the Indian Accounting`
  line `Standards 101 on the convergence date; and`
  line `( F ) adjustments relating to cumulative translation differences of a foreign operation in`
  line `accordance with paragraph D13 of the Indian Accounting Standards 101 on the convergence date.]`
  line `( 3 ) Nothing contained in sub-section ( 1 ) shall affect the determination of the amounts in relation to`
  line `the relevant previous year to be carried forward to the subsequent year or years under the provisions of`
  line `sub-section ( 2 ) of section 32 or sub-section ( 3 ) of section 32A or clause ( ii ) of sub-section ( 1 ) of`
  line `section 72 or section 73 or section 74 or sub-section ( 3 ) of section 74A.`
  line `( 4 ) Every company to which this section applies, shall furnish a report in the prescribed form from an`
  line `accountant as defined in the Explanation below sub-section ( 2 ) of section 288, certifying that the book`
  line `profit has been computed in accordance with the provisions of this section along with the return of`
  line `income filed under sub-section ( 1 ) of section 139 or along with the return of income furnished in response`
  line `to a notice under clause ( i ) of sub-section ( 1 ) of section 142.`
  line `( 5 ) Save as otherwise provided in this section, all other provisions of this Act shall apply to every`
  line `assessee, being a company, mentioned in this section.]`
  line `1 [( 5A ) The provisions of this section shall not apply to any income accruing or arising to a company`
  line `from life insurance business referred to in section 115B.]`
  line `2 [( 6 ) The provisions of this section shall not apply to the income accrued or arising on or after the 1st`
  line `day of April, 2005 from any business carried on, or services rendered, by an entrepreneur or a Developer,`
  line `in a Unit or Special Economic Zone, as the case may be:]`
  line `3 [Provided that the provisions of this sub-section shall cease to have effect in respect of any previous`
  line `year relevant to the assessment year commencing on or after the 1st day of April, 2012.]`
  line `4 [( 7 ) Notwithstanding anything contained in sub-section ( 1 ), where the assessee referred to therein, is`
  line `a unit located in an International Financial Services Centre and derives its income solely in convertible`
  line `foreign exchange, the provisions of sub-section ( 1 ) shall have the effect as if for the words “eighteen and`
  line `one- half per cent” wherever occurring in th at sub- section, the words “nine per cent” had been substituted.`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this sub-section, —`
  line `( a ) “International Financial Services Centre” shall have the same meaning as assigned to it in`
  line `clause ( q ) of section 2 of the Special Economic Zones Act, 2005 (28 of 2005);`
  line `( b ) “unit” means a unit established in an International Financial Services Centre;`
  line `( c ) “convertible foreign exchange” means a foreign exchange which is for the time being treated`
  line `by the Reserve Bank of India as convertible foreign exchange for the purposes of the Foreign`
  line `Exchange Management Act, 1999 (42 of 1999) and the rules made thereunder.]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 48 (w.e.f. 1-4-2001).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 28 of 2005, s. 27 and the Second Schedule (w.e.f. 10-2-2006).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 8 of 2011, s. 18 (w.e.f. 1-4-2012).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 55 (w.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
