obj_root_law_sections_503_content:
  string
  line 503
  line `115S. Interest payable for non-payment of tax. — Where the person responsible for making`
  line `payment of the income distributed by the 1 [specified company as referred to in clause ( h ) of section 2 of`
  line `the Unit Trust of India (Transfer of Undertaking and Repeal) Act, 2002 (58 of 2002) or a Mutual Fund`
  line `and the specified company] or the Mutual Fund, as the case may be, fails to pay the whole or any part of`
  line `the tax referred to in sub-section ( 1 ) or sub-section ( 2 ) of section 115R, within the time allowed under`
  line `sub-section ( 3 ) of that section, he or it shall be liable to pay simple interest at the rate of 2 [one per cent.]`
  line `every month or part thereof on the amount of such tax for the period beginning on the date immediately`
  line `after the last date on which such tax was payable and ending with the date on which the tax is actually`
  line paid.
  line `115T. Unit Trust of India or Mutual Fund to be an assessee in default. — If any person responsible`
  line `for making payment of the income distributed by the 1 [specified company as referred to in clause ( h ) of`
  line `section 2 of the Unit Trust of India (Transfer of Undertaking and Repeal) Act, 2002`
  line `(58 of 2002) or a Mutual Fund and the specified company] or the Mutual Fund, as the case may be, does`
  line `not pay tax, as is referred to in sub-section ( 1 ) or sub-section ( 2 ) of section 115R, then, he or it shall be`
  line `deemed to be an assessee in default in respect of the amount of tax payable by him or it and all the`
  line `provisions of this Act for the collection and recovery of income-tax shall apply.`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this Chapter, —`
  line `( a ) “Mutual Fund” means a Mutual Fund specified under clause ( 23D ) of section 10;`
  line `3 [( b ) “equity oriented fund” means a fund referred to in clause ( a ) of the Explanation to`
  line `section 112A and the Unit Scheme, 1964 made by the Unit Trust of India;’ ]`
  line `( c ) “Unit Trust of India” means the Unit Trust of India established under the Unit Trust of India`
  line `Act, 1963 (52 of 1963);`
  line `4 [( d ) “money market mutual fund” means a money market mutual fund as defined in`
  line `sub-clause ( p ) of clause ( 2 ) of the Securities and Exchange Board of India (Mutual Funds)`
  line `Regulations, 1996;`
  line `( e ) “liquid fund” means a scheme or plan of a mutual fund which is classified by the Securities`
  line `and Exchange Board of India as a liquid fund in accordance with the guidelines issued by it in this`
  line `behalf under the Securities and Exchange Board of India Act, 1992 (15 of 1992) or regulations made`
  line thereunder.]
  line `1. Subs. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 57, for “Unit Trust of India or a Mutual Fund and the Unit Trust of India” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2003).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 54 of 2003, s. 5, for “one and one - fourth per cent.” (w.e.f. 8 -9-2003).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 13 of 2018, s. 43, for clause ( b ) (w.e.f. 1-4-2018). Earlier it was amended by Act 21 of 2006, s. 27`
  line `(w.e.f. 1-6-2006).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 22 of 2007, s. 37 (w.e.f. 1-4-2007).`
