obj_root_law_sections_509_content:
  string
  line 509
  line `1 [CHAPTER XIIF`
  line `S PECIAL PROVISIONS RELATING TO TAX ON INCOME RECEIVED FROM VENTURE CAPITAL COMPANIES AND`
  line `VENTURE CAPITAL FUNDS`
  line `115U. Tax on income in certain cases. — ( 1 ) Notwithstanding anything contained in any other`
  line `provisions of this Act,any 2 [income accruing or arising to or received] by a person out of investments`
  line `made in a venture capital company or venture capital fund shall be chargeable to income-tax in the same`
  line `manner as if it were the 2 [income accruing or arising to or received] by such person had he made`
  line `investments directly in the venture capital undertaking.`
  line `( 2 ) 3 [The person responsible for crediting or making] payment of the income on behalf of a venture`
  line `capital company or a venture capital fund and the venture capital company or venture capital fund shall`
  line `furnish, within such time as may be prescribed, 4 [to the person who is liable to tax in respect of such`
  line `income] and to the prescribed income-tax authority, a statement in the prescribed form and verified in the`
  line `prescribed manner, giving details of the nature of the 5 [income paid or credited] during the previous year`
  line `and such other relevant details as may be prescribed.`
  line `( 3 ) 5 [The income paid or credited] by the venture capital company and the venture capital fund shall`
  line `be deemed to be of the same nature and in the same proportion in the hands of 6 [the person referred to in`
  line `sub-section ( 1 ) as it had been] received by, or 7 [had accrued or arisen] to, the venture capital company or`
  line `the venture capital fund, as the case may be, during the previous year.`
  line `( 4 ) The provisions of Chapter XII-D or Chapter XII-E or Chapter XVIIB shall not apply to the`
  line `income paid by a venture capital company or venture capital fund under this Chapter.`
  line `8 [( 5 ) The income accruing or arising to or received by the venture capital company or venture capital`
  line `fund, during a previous year, from investments made in venture capital undertaking if not paid or credited`
  line `to the person referred to in sub-section ( 1 ), shall be deemed to have been credited to the account of the`
  line `said person on the last day of the previous year in the same proportion in which such person would have`
  line `been entitled to receive the income had it been paid in the previous year.]`
  line `9 [( 6 ) Nothing contained in this Chapter shall apply in respect of any income, of a previous year`
  line `relevant to the assessment year beginning on or after the 1st day of April, 2016, accruing or arising to, or`
  line `received by, a person from investments made in a venture capital company or venture capital fund, being`
  line `an investment fund specified in clause ( a ) of the Explanation 1 to section 115UB.]`
  line `Explanation 10 [ 1 ]. —For the purposes of this Chapter, “venture capital company”, “venture capital`
  line `fund” and “venture capital undertaking” shall have the meanings respectively assigned to them in clause`
  line `( 23FB ) of section 10.`
  line `11 [ Explanation 2. — For the removal of doubts, it is hereby declared that any income which has been`
  line `included in total income of the person referred to in sub-section ( 1 ) in a previous year, on account of it`
  line `having accrued or arisen in the said previous year, shall not be included in the total income of such person`
  line `in the previous year in which such income is actually paid to him by the venture capital company or the`
  line `venture capital fund.]`
  line `1. Ins. by 10 of 2000, s. 57 (w.e.f. 1-4-2001).`
  line `2. Sub s. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 57, for “income received” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2013).`
  line `3. Subs. by s. 57, ibid., for “The person responsible for making” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2013).`
  line `4. Subs. by s. 57, ibid., for “to the person receiving such income” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2013).`
  line `5. Subs. by s. 57, ibid., for “income paid” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2013).`
  line `6. Subs. by s. 57, ibid., for “the person receiving such income as it had been” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2013).`
  line `7. Subs. by s. 57, ibid., for “had accrued” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2013).`
  line `8. Ins. by s. 57, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-2013).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 20 of 2015, s. 31 (w.e.f. 1-4-2016).`
  line `10. The Explanation renumbered as Explanation 1 thereof by Act 23 of 2012, s. 57 (w.e.f. 1-7-2012).`
  line `11. Ins. by s. 57, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-7-2012).`
