obj_root_law_sections_526_content:
  string
  line 526
  line `( vi ) being the expenditure by way of payment to any advertising agency for the purposes of`
  line `clauses ( i ) to ( v ) above;`
  line `1 [ 2 [( vii ) being the expenditure on distribution of samples either free of cost or at concessional`
  line `rate; and]`
  line `( viii ) being the expenditure by way of payment to any person of repute for promoting the sale`
  line `of goods or services of the business of the employer,]`
  line `shall not be considered as expenditure on sales promotion including publicity;`
  line `( E ) employees’ welfare.`
  line `3 [ Explanation. — For the purposes of this clause, any expenditure incurred or payment made to —`
  line `( i ) fulfil any statutory obligation; or`
  line `( ii ) mitigate occupational hazards; or`
  line `( iii ) provide first aid facilities in the hospital or dispensary run by the employer; or`
  line `( iv ) provide creche facility for the children of the employee; or`
  line `( v ) sponsor a sportsman, being an employee; or`
  line `( vi ) organise sports events for employees,`
  line `shall not be considered as expenditure for employees ’ welfare;]`
  line `( F ) conveyance; 4 ***`
  line `( G ) use of hotel, boarding and lodging facilities;`
  line `( H ) repair, running (including fuel), maintenance of motor cars and the amount of depreciation`
  line thereon;
  line `( I ) repair, running (including fuel) and maintenance of aircrafts and the amount of depreciation`
  line thereon;
  line `( J ) use of telephone (including mobile phone) other than expenditure on leased telephone lines;`
  line `5 * * * *`
  line `( L ) festival celebrations;`
  line `( M ) use of health club and similar facilities;`
  line `( N ) use of any other club facilities;`
  line `( O ) gifts; and`
  line `( P ) scholarships;`
  line `6 [( Q ) tour and travel (including foreign travel).]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 21 of 2006, s. 28 (w.e.f. 1-4-2007).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 22 of 2007, s. 38, for clause (vii) (w.e.f. 1-4-2008).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 18 of 2008, s. 25, for the Explanation (w.e.f. 1-4-2009).`
  line `4. The words and brackets “, tour and travel (including foreign travel)” omitted by Act 21 of 2006, s. 28 (w.e.f. 1 -4-2007).`
  line `5. Clause (k) omitted by Act 18 of 2008, s. 25 (w.e.f. 1-4-2009).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 21 of 2006, s. 28 (w.e.f. 1-4-2007).`
