obj_root_law_sections_543_content:
  string
  line 543
  line `Commissioner or] 1 [Joint Director], 2 [Joint Commissioner], 3 [Assistant Director or Deputy Director],`
  line `4 [Assistant Commissioner or Deputy Commissioner] or Income-tax Officer, or`
  line `( B ) such 5 [Additional Director or Additional Commissioner or] 1 [Joint Director], or 2 [Joint`
  line `Commissioner], as the case may be, may authorise any 3 [Assistant Director or Deputy Director],`
  line `4 [Assistant Commissioner or Deputy Commissioner ]or Income-tax Officer,`
  line `(the officer so authorised in all cases being hereinafter referred to as the authorised officer) to — ]`
  line `( i ) enter and search any 6 [building, place, vessel, vehicle or aircraft] where he has reason to`
  line `suspect that such books of account, other documents, money, bullion, jewellery or other valuable`
  line `article or thing are kept;`
  line `( ii ) break open the lock of any door, box, locker, safe, almirah or other receptacle for exercising`
  line `the powers conferred by clause ( i ) where the keys thereof are not available;`
  line `7 [( iia ) search any person who has got out of, or is about to get into, or is in, the building, place,`
  line `vessel, vehicle or aircraft, if the authorised officer has reason to suspect that such person has secreted`
  line `about his person any such books of account, other documents, money, bullion, jewellery or other`
  line `valuable article or thing;]`
  line `8 [( iib ) require any person who is found to be in possession or control of any books of account or`
  line `other documents maintained in the form of electronic record as defined in clause ( t ) of sub-section ( 1 )`
  line `of section 2 of the Information Technology Act, 2000 (21 of 2000), to afford the authorised officer`
  line `the necessary facility to inspect such books of account or other documents;]`
  line `( iii ) seize any such books of account, other documents, money, bullion, jewellery or other`
  line `valuable article or thing found as a result of such search:`
  line `9 [Provided that bullion, jewellery or other valuable article or thing, being stock-in-trade of the`
  line `business, found as a result of such search shall not be seized but the authorised officer shall make a`
  line `note or inventory of such stock-in-trade of the business;]`
  line `( iv ) place marks of identification on any books of account or other documents or make or cause to`
  line `be made extracts or copies therefrom;`
  line `( v ) make a note or an inventory of any such money, bullion, jewellery or other valuable article or`
  line `thing:`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 21 of 1998, s. 3, for “Deputy Director” (w.e.f. 1 -10- 1998). Earlier substituted as “Deputy Director” for`
  line `“Deputy Director of Inspection” by Act 4 of 1988, s. 2 (w.e.f. 1 -4-1988).`
  line `2. Subs. by s. 3, ibid., for “Deputy Commissioner” (w.e.f. 1 -10- 1998). Earlier substituted as “Deputy Commissioner” for`
  line `“Inspecting Assistant Commissioner” by s. 2, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-1988).`
  line `3. Subs. by s. 3, ibid., for “Assistant Director” (w.e.f. 1 -10- 1998). Earlier substituted as “Assistant Director” for “Assistant`
  line `Director of Inspection” by s. 2, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-1988).`
  line `4. Subs. by s. 3, ibid., “Assistant Commissioner” (w.e.f. 1 -10- 1998). Earlier substituted as “Assistant Commissioner” for`
  line `“or Income tax officer” by s. 37, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-1988).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 33 of 2009, s. 51 (w.e.f. 1-6-1994).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 41 of 1975, s. 35, for “building or place” (w.e.f. 1 -10-1975).`
  line `7. Ins. by s. 35, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-10-1975).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 56 (w.e.f. 1-6-2002).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 59 (w.e.f. 1-6-2003).`
