obj_root_law_sections_557_content:
  string
  line 557
  line `CHAPTER XIV`
  line `P ROCEDURE FOR ASSESSMENT`
  line `139. Return of income. — 1 [( 1 ) Every person, —`
  line `( a ) being a 2 [company or a firm]; or`
  line `( b ) being a person 3 [other than a company or a firm], if his total income or the total income of any`
  line `other person in respect of which he is assessable under this Act during the previous year exceeded the`
  line `maximum amount which is not chargeable to income-tax,`
  line `shall, on or before the due date, furnish a return of his income or the income of such other person during`
  line `the previous year, in the prescribed form and verified in the prescribed manner and setting forth such`
  line `other particulars as may be prescribed:`
  line `Provided that a person referred to in clause ( b ), who is not required to furnish a return under this sub-`
  line `section and residing in such area as may be specified by the Board in this behalf by notification in the`
  line `Official Gazette, and who 4 [during the previous year incurs an expenditure of fifty thousand rupees or`
  line `more towards consumption of electricity or at any time during the previous year]fulfils any one of the`
  line `following conditions, namely: —`
  line `( i ) is in occupation of an immovable property exceeding a specified floor area, whether by way of`
  line `ownership, tenancy or otherwise, as may be specified by the Board in this behalf; or`
  line `( ii ) is the owner or the lessee of a motor vehicle other than a two-wheeled motor vehicle, whether`
  line `having any detachable side car having extra wheel attached to such two-wheeled motor vehicle or`
  line `not; or`
  line `5 * * * * *`
  line `( iv ) has incurred expenditure for himself or any other person on travel to any foreign country; or`
  line `( v ) is the holder of a credit card, not be ing an “add - on” card, issued by any bank or institution; or`
  line `( vi ) is a member of a club where entrance fee charged is twenty-five thousand rupees or more,`
  line `shall furnish a return, of his income 6 [during any previous year ending before the 1st day of April, 2005],`
  line `on or before the due date in the prescribed form and verified in the prescribed manner and setting forth`
  line `such other particulars as may be prescribed:`
  line `Provided further that the Central Government may, by notification in the Official Gazette, specify the`
  line `class or classes of persons to whom the provisions of the first proviso shall not apply:`
  line `Providedalso that every 2 [company or a firm] shall furnish on or before the due date the return in`
  line `respect of its income or loss in every previous year:`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 14 of 2001, s. 59, for sub-section ( 1 ) (w.e.f. 1-4-2001). Earlier substituted by 13 of 1963, s. 8 (w.r.e.f. 1-4-`
  line `1962). As amended by Act 27 of 1967, s. 4 (w.e.f. 1-10-1967). As so amended by Act 42 of 1970, s. 26 (w.e.f. 1-4-1970).`
  line `As amended by Act 16 of 1972, s. 26 (w.e.f. 1-4-1972). Amended by Act 4 of 1988, s. 42 (w.e.f. 1-4-1988). As so`
  line `amended by Act 3 of 1989, s. 20 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).Earlier amended by Act 12 of 1990, s. 34 (w.e.f. 1-4-1991). Amended`
  line `by Act 18 of 1992, s. 59 (w.e.f. 1-4-1993).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 18 of 2005, s. 40, for “company” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2006).`
  line `3. Subs. by s. 40, ibid., for “other than a company” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2006).`
  line `4. Subs. by s. 40, ibid., for “at any time during the previous year” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2006).`
  line `5. Clause ( iii ) omitted by s. 40, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-2006).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 21 of 2006, s. 31, for “during the previous year” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2006).`
