obj_root_law_sections_558_content:
  string
  line 558
  line `1 [Provided also that a person, being a resident other than not ordinarily resident in India within the`
  line `meaning of clause ( 6 ) of section 6, who is not required to furnish a return under this sub-section and who`
  line `at any time during the previous year, —`
  line `( a ) holds, as a beneficial owner or otherwise, any asset (including any financial interest in any`
  line `entity) located outside India or has signing authority in any account located outside India; or`
  line `( b ) is a beneficiary of any asset (including any financial interest in any entity) located outside`
  line India,
  line `shall furnish, on or before the due date, a return in respect of his income or loss for the previous year in`
  line `such form and verified in such manner and setting forth such other particulars as may be prescribed:`
  line `Provided also that nothing contained in the fourth proviso shall apply to an individual, being a`
  line `beneficiary of any asset (including any financial interest in any entity) located outside India where,`
  line `income, if any, arising from such asset is includible in the income of the person referred to in clause ( a ) of`
  line `that proviso in accordance with the provisions of this Act:]`
  line `2 [Provided alsothat every person, being an individual or a Hindu undivided family or an association`
  line `of persons or a body of individuals, whether incorporated or not, or an artificial juridical person, if his`
  line `total income or the total income of any other person in respect of which he is assessable under this Act`
  line `during the previous year, without giving effect to the 3 [provisions of clause ( 38 ) of section 10 or section`
  line `10 or section 10B or section 10BA] or Chapter VIA exceeded the maximum amount which is not`
  line `chargeable to income-tax, shall, on or before the due date, furnish a return of his income or the income of`
  line `such other person during the previous year, in the prescribed form and verified in the prescribed manner`
  line `and setting forth such other particulars as may be prescribed.]`
  line `Explanation 1. — For the purposes of this sub- section, the expression “motor vehicle” shall have the`
  line `meaning assigned to it in clause ( 28 ) of section 2 of the Motor Vehicles Act, 1988 (59 of 1988).`
  line `Explanation 2. — In this sub- section, “due date” means,—`
  line `( a ) where the assessee 4 [other than an assessee referred to in clause ( aa )] is —`
  line `( i ) a company 5 ***; or`
  line `( ii ) a person (other than a company) whose accounts are required to be audited under this Act`
  line `or under any other law for the time being in force; or`
  line `( iii ) a working partner of a firm whose accounts are required to be audited under this Act or`
  line `under any other law for the time being in force,`
  line `The 6 [30th day of September] of the assessment year;`
  line `7 [( aa ) in the case of an assessee 8 [who] is required to furnish a report referred to in section 92E,`
  line `the 30th day of November of the assessment year;`
  line `( b ) in the case of a person other than a company, referred to in the first proviso to this sub-`
  line `section, the 31st day of October of the assessment year;`
  line `( c ) in the case of any other assessee, the 31st day of July of the assessment year.`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 20 of 2015, s. 35, for the proviso (w.e.f. 1-4-2016). Earlier Substituted by Act 23 of 2012,`
  line `s. 59 (w.e.f. 1-4-2012).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 18 of 2005, s. 40 (w.e.f. 1-4-2006).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 67, for “provisions of section 10A” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2017).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 59 (w.e.f. 1-4-2012).`
  line `5. The words, brackets and letter “other than a company referred to in clause ( aa )” omitted by s. 59, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-2012).`
  line `Earlier the words were inserted by Act 8 of 2011, s. 24 (w.e.f. 1-4-2011).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 18 of 2008, s. 30, for “30th day of October” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2008).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 8 of 2011, s. 24 (w.e.f. -4-2011).`
  line `8. Su bs. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 59, for “being a company, which” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2012).`
