obj_root_law_sections_561_content:
  string
  line 561
  line `( f ) trade union referred to in sub-clause ( a ) or association referred to in sub-clause ( b ) of clause`
  line `( 24 ) of section 10;`
  line `1 [( fa ) Board orAuthority referred to in clause ( 29A ) of section 10;]`
  line `2 [( g ) body or authority or Board or Trust or Commission (by whatever name called) referred to in`
  line `clause ( 46 ) of section 10;`
  line `( h ) infrastructure debt fund referred to in clause ( 47 ) of section 10,]`
  line `shall, if the total income in respect of which such 3 [research association], news agency, association or`
  line `institution, 1 [person or] fund or trust or university or other educational institution or any hospital or other`
  line `medical institution or trade union 2 [or body or authority or Board or Trust or Commission or`
  line `infrastructure debt fund] 4 [or Mutual Fund or securitisation trust or venture capital company or venture`
  line `capital fund] is assessable, without giving effect to the provisions of section 10, exceeds the maximum`
  line `amount which is not chargeable to income-tax, furnish a return of such income of the previous year in the`
  line `prescribed form and verified in the prescribed manner and setting forth such other particulars as may be`
  line `prescribed and all the provisions of this Act shall, so far as may be, apply as if it were a return required to`
  line `be furnished under sub-section ( 1 ).]`
  line `5 [( 4D ) Every university, college or other institution referred to in clause ( ii ) and clause ( iii ) of sub-`
  line `section (1) of section 35, which is not required to furnish return of income or loss under any other`
  line `provision of this section, shall furnish the return in respect of its income or loss in every previous year`
  line `and all the provisions of this Act shall, so far as may be, apply as if it were a return required to be`
  line `furnished under sub-section ( 1 ).]`
  line `4 [( 4E ) Every business trust, which is not required to furnish return of income or loss under any other`
  line `provisions of this section, shall furnish the return of its income in respect of its income or loss in every`
  line `previous year and all the provisions of this Act shall, so far as may be, apply if it were a return required to`
  line `be furnished under sub-section ( 1 ).]`
  line `6 [( 4F )Every investment fund referred to in section 115UB, which is not required to furnish return of`
  line `income or loss under any other provisions of this section, shall furnish the return of income in respect of`
  line `its income or loss in every previous year and all the provisions of this Act shall, so far as may be, apply as`
  line `if it were a return required to be furnished under sub-section ( 1 ).]`
  line `7 [( 5 ) If any person, having furnished a return under sub-section ( 1 ) or sub-section ( 4 ), discovers any`
  line `omission or any wrong statement therein, he may furnish a revised return at any time before 8 *** the end`
  line `of the relevant assessment year or before the completion of the assessment, whichever is earlier.]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 55 (w.e.f. 1-4-2018).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 8 of 2011, s. 24 (w.e.f. 1-6-2011).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 14 of 2010, s. 32, for “scientific research association” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2011).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 25 of 2014, s. 49 (w.e.f. 1-4-2015).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 29 of 2006, s. 12 (w.e.f. 1-4-2006).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 20 of 2015, s. 35 (w.e.f. 1-4-2016).`
  line `7. Subs. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 67, for sub-section ( 5 ) (w.e.f. 1-4-2017). Earlier sub-section ( 5 ) was substituted by Act 4 of`
  line `1988, s. 42 (w.e.f. 1-4-1988).`
  line `8. The words “the expiry of one year from” o mitted by Act 7 of 2017, s. 55 (w.e.f. 1-4-2018).`
