obj_root_law_sections_571_content:
  string
  line 571
  line `( e ) in the case of any other association, by any member of the association or the principal`
  line `officer thereof; and`
  line `( f ) in the case of any other person, by that person or by some person competent to act on his`
  line behalf.
  line `1 [ 140A. Self-assessment. — 2 [( 1 ) Where any tax is payable on the basis of any return required to be`
  line `furnished under 3 [ 4 [section 115WD or section 115WH or section 139] or section 142 5 [or section 148 or`
  line `6 [section 153A or, as the case may be, section 158BC]]], 7 [after taking into account, —`
  line `( i ) the amount of tax, if any, already paid under any provision of this Act;`
  line `( ii ) any tax deducted or collected at source;`
  line `( iii ) any relief of tax or deduction of tax claimed under section 90 or section 91 on account of tax`
  line `paid in a country outside India;`
  line `( iv ) any relief of tax claimed under section 90A on account of tax paid in any specified territory`
  line `outside India referred to in that section; and`
  line `( v ) any tax credit claimed to be set off in accordance with the provisions of section`
  line `115JAA 8 [or section 115JD],]`
  line `9 [the assessee shall be liable to pay such tax, together with interest 10 [and fee] payable under any`
  line `provision of this Act for any delay in furnishing the return or any default or delay in payment of advance`
  line `tax, before furnishing the return and the return shall be accompanied by proof of payment of such tax`
  line `11 [interestand fee].]]`
  line `12 [ Explanation. — Where the amount paid by the assessee under this sub-section falls short of the`
  line `aggregate of the tax 13 [interestand fee as aforesaid, the amount so paid shall first be adjusted towards the`
  line `fee payable and thereafter towards] the interest payable as aforesaid and the balance, if any, shall be`
  line `adjusted towards the tax payable.]`
  line `14 [ 15 [( 1A ) For the purposes of sub-section ( 1 ), interest payable, —`
  line `16 [( i ) under section 234A shall be computed on the amount of the tax on the total income as`
  line `declared in the return as reduced by the amount of, —`
  line `( a ) advance tax, if any, paid;`
  line `( b ) any tax deducted or collected at source;`
  line `( c ) any relief of tax or deduction of tax claimed under section 90 or section 91 on account of`
  line `tax paid in a country outside India;`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 42 of 1970, s. 27, for section 140A (w.e.f. 1-4-1971). Earlier section 140A was inserted by Act 5 of 1964,`
  line `s. 34 (w.e.f. 1-4-1964).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 41 of 1975, s. 41, for sub-section ( 1 ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1976).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 49 of 1991, s. 45, for “section 139 or section 148” (w.e.f. 27 -9-1991).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 18 of 2005, s. 43, for “section 139” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2006).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 27 of 1999, s. 63, for “or, as the case may be, section 148” (w.e.f. 1 -6-1999).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 63, for “as the case may be, section 158BC” (w.e.f. 1 -6-2003).`
  line `7. Subs. by Act 21 of 2006, s. 34, for “after taking into account the amount of tax, if any, already paid under any provision`
  line `of this Act” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2007).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 60 (w.e.f. 1-4-2013).`
  line `9. Subs. by Act 4 of 1988, s. 45, for “the assessee shall be liable to pay such tax before furnishing the return and the return`
  line `shall be accompanied by proof of payment of such tax” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1989).`
  line `10. Ins. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 57 (w.e.f. 1-4-2018).`
  line `11. Su bs. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 57, for “and interest” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2018).`
  line `12. Ins. by Act 4 of 1988, s. 45 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `13. Subs. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 57, for “and interest as aforesaid, the amount so paid shall first be adjusted`
  line `towards” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2018).`
  line `14. Ins. by Act 14 of 2001, s. 61 (w.r.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `15. Subs. by Act 18 of 2005, s. 43, for sub-section ( 1A ) (w.e.f. 1-4-2006). Earlier`
  line `16. Subs. by Act 21 of 2006, s. 34, for clause ( i ) (w.e.f. 1-4-2007).`
obj_root_law_sections_571_footnotes:
