obj_root_law_sections_576_content:
  string
  line 576
  line `Provided that no such adjustments shall be made unless an intimation is given to the assessee`
  line `of such adjustments either in writing or in electronic mode:`
  line `Provided further that the response received from the assessee, if any, shall be considered`
  line `before making any adjustment, and in a case where no response is received within thirty days of`
  line `the issue of such intimation, such adjustments shall be made;]`
  line `1 [Provided also that no adjustment shall be made under sub-clause ( vi ) in relation to a return`
  line `furnished for the assessment year commencing on or after the 1st day of April, 2018;]`
  line `( b ) the tax 2 [, interest and fee], if any, shall be computed on the basis of the total income`
  line `computed under clause ( a );`
  line `( c ) the sum payable by, or the amount of refund due to, the assessee shall be determined after`
  line `adjustment of the tax 2 [, interest and fee], if any, computed under clause ( b ) by any tax deducted at`
  line `source, any tax collected at source, any advance tax paid, any relief allowable under an agreement`
  line `under section 90 or section 90A, or any relief allowable under section 91, any rebate allowable under`
  line `Part A of Chapter VIII, any tax paid on self-assessment and any amount paid otherwise by way of tax`
  line `3 [, interest or fee];`
  line `( d ) an intimation shall be prepared or generated and sent to the assessee specifying the sum`
  line `determined to be payable by, or the amount of refund due to, the assessee under clause ( c ); and`
  line `( e ) the amount of refund due to the assessee in pursuance of the determination under clause ( c )`
  line `shall be granted to the assessee:`
  line `Provided that an intimation shall also be sent to the assessee in a case where the loss declared in`
  line `the return by the assessee is adjusted but no tax 3 [, interest or fee] is payable by, or no refund is due`
  line `to, him:`
  line `Provided further that no intimation under this sub-section shall be sent after the expiry of one`
  line `year from the end of the financial year in which the return is made.`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this sub-section, —`
  line `( a ) “an incorrect claim apparent from any information in the return” shall mean a claim, on the`
  line `basis of an entry, in the return, —`
  line `( i ) of an item, which is inconsistent with another entry of the same or some other item in such`
  line return;
  line `( ii ) in respect of which the information required to be furnished under this Act to substantiate`
  line `such entry has not been so furnished; or`
  line `( iii ) in respect of a deduction, where such deduction exceeds specified statutory limit which`
  line `may have been expressed as monetary amount or percentage or ratio or fraction;`
  line `( b ) the acknowledgement of the return shall be deemed to be the intimation in a case where no`
  line `sum is payable by, or refundable to, the assessee under clause ( c ), and where no adjustment has been`
  line `made under clause ( a ).`
  line `( 1A ) For the purposes of processing of returns under sub-section ( 1 ), the Board may make a scheme`
  line `for centralised processing of returns with a view to expeditiously determining the tax payable by, or the`
  line `refund due to, the assessee as required under the said sub-section.`
  line `( 1B ) Save as otherwise expressly provided, for the purpose of giving effect to the scheme made under`
  line `sub-section ( 1A ), the Central Government may, by notification in the Official Gazette, direct that any of`
  line `the provisions of this Act relating to processing of returns shall not apply or shall apply with such`
  line `exceptions, modifications and adaptations as may be specified in that notification; so, however, that no`
  line `direction shall be issued after 4 [the 31st day of March, 2012].`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 13 of 2018, s. 46 (w.e.f. 1-4-2018).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 58, for “and interest” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2018).`
  line `3. Subs. by s. 58, ibid.,for “or interest” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2018).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 8 of 2011, s. 25, for “the 31st day March, 2011” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2011).`
