obj_root_law_sections_577_content:
  string
  line 577
  line `( 1C ) Every notification issued under sub-section ( 1B ), along with the scheme made under`
  line `sub-section ( 1A ), shall, as soon as may be after the notification is issued, be laid before each House of`
  line Parliament.]
  line `1 [( 1D ) Notwithstanding anything contained in sub-section ( 1 ), the processing of a return shall not be`
  line `necessary, where a notice has been issued to the assessee under sub-section ( 2 ):`
  line `Provided that the provisions of this sub-section shall not apply to any return furnished for the`
  line `assessment year commencing on or after the 1st day of April, 2017.]`
  line `2 [( 2 ) Where a return has been furnished under section 139, or in response to a notice under`
  line `sub-section ( 1 ) of section 142, the Assessing Officer or the prescribed income-tax authority, as the case`
  line `may be, if, considers it necessary or expedient to ensure that the assessee has not understated the income`
  line `or has not computed excessive loss or has not under-paid the tax in any manner, shall serve on the`
  line `assessee a notice requiring him, on a date to be specified therein, either to attend the office of the`
  line `Assessing Officer or to produce, or cause to be produced before the Assessing Officer any evidence on`
  line `which the assessee may rely in support of the return:`
  line `Provided that no notice under this sub-section shall be served on the assessee after the expiry of six`
  line `months from the end of the financial year in which the return is furnished.]`
  line `3 [( 3 ) 4 [On the day specified in the notice issued under] sub-section ( 2 ), or as soon afterwards as may`
  line `be, after hearing such evidence as the assessee may produce and such other evidence as the Assessing`
  line `Officer may require on specified points, and after taking into account all relevant material which he has`
  line `gathered, the Assessing Officer shall, by an order in writing, make an assessment of the total income or`
  line `loss of the assessee, and determine the sum payable by him or refund of any amount due to him on the`
  line `basis of such assessment.]`
  line `5 [Provided that in the case of a —`
  line `( a ) 6 [research association] referred to in clause ( 21 ) of section 10;`
  line `( b ) news agency referred to in clause ( 22B ) of section 10;`
  line `( c ) association or institution referred to in clause ( 23A ) of section 10;`
  line `( d ) institution referred to in clause ( 23B ) of section 10;`
  line `( e ) fund or institution referred to in sub-clause ( iv ) or trust or institution referred to in`
  line `sub-clause ( v ) or any university or other educational institution referred to in sub-clause ( vi ) or any`
  line `hospital or other medical institution referred to in sub-clause ( via ) of clause ( 23C ) of section 10,`
  line `which is required to furnish the return of income under sub-section ( 4C ) of section 139, no order making`
  line `an assessment of the total income or loss of such 6 [research association], news agency, association or`
  line `institution or fund or trust or university or other educational institution or any hospital or other medical`
  line `institution, shall be made by the Assessing Officer, without giving effect to the provisions of section 10,`
  line `unless —`
  line `( i ) the Assessing Officer has intimated the Central Government or the prescribed authority the`
  line `contravention of the provisions of clause ( 21 ) or clause ( 22B ) or clause ( 23A ) or clause ( 23B ) or`
  line `sub-clause ( iv ) or sub-clause ( v ) or sub-clause ( vi ) or sub-clause ( via ) of clause ( 23C ) of section 10, as`
  line `the case may be, by such 6 [research association], news agency, association or institution or fund or`
  line `trust or university or other educational institution or any hospital or other medical institution, where`
  line `in his view such contravention has taken place; and`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 58, for sub-section ( ID ) (w.e.f. 1-4-2018).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 68, for sub-section ( 2 ) (w.e.f. 1-6-2016).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 60, for sub-section ( 3 ) (w.e.f. 1-6-2002).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 58, for certain words (w.e.f. 1-6-2016).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 60 (w.e.f. 1-4-2003).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 14 of 2010, s. 34, for “scientific research association” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2011).`
