  line 600
  line `( b ) on any reduction or enhancement made in the income of the association or body under this`
  line `section, section 154, section 250, section 254, section 260, section 262, section 263 or section 264,`
  line `1 [or]`
  line `1 [( c ) on any order passed under sub-section ( 4 ) of section 245D on the application made by the`
  line `association or body,]`
  line `that the share of the member in the income of the association or body, as the case may be, has not been`
  line `included in the assessment of the member or, if included, is not correct, the 2 [Assessing Officer] may`
  line `amend the order of assessment of the member with a view to the inclusion of the share in the assessment`
  line `or the correction thereof, as the case may be; and the provisions of section 154 shall, so far as may be,`
  line `apply thereto, the period of four years specified in sub-section ( 7 ) of that section being reckoned 3 [from`
  line `the end of the financial year in which the final order was passed] in the case of the association or body, as`
  line `the case may be.`
  line `4 * * * * *`
  line `( 4 ) Where as a result of proceedings initiated under section 147, a loss or depreciation has been`
  line `recomputed and in consequence thereof it is necessary to recompute the total income of the assessee for`
  line `the succeeding year or years to which the loss or depreciation allowance has been carried forward and set`
  line `off under the provisions of sub-section ( 1 ) of section 72, or sub-section ( 2 ) of section 73, or 5 [sub-section`
  line `( 1 ) or sub-section ( 3 ) of section 74], 6 [or sub-section ( 3 ) of section 74A], the 2 [Assessing Officer] may`
  line `proceed to recompute the total income in respect of such year or years and make the necessary`
  line `amendment; and the provisions of section 154 shall, so far as may be, apply thereto, the period of four`
  line `years specified in sub-section ( 7 ) of that section being reckoned 7 [from the end of the financial year in`
  line `which the order was passed] under section 147.`
  line `8 [( 4A ) Where an allowance by way of investment allowance has been made wholly or partly to an`
  line `assessee in respect of a ship or an aircraft or any machinery or plant in any assessment year under section`
  line `32A and subsequently —`
  line `( a ) at any time before the expiry of eight years from the end of the previous year in which the`
  line `ship or aircraft was acquired or the machinery or plant was installed, the ship, aircraft, machinery or`
  line `plant is sold or otherwise transferred by the assessee to any person other than the Government, a local`
  line `authority, a corporation established by a Central, State or Provincial Act or a Government company`
  line `as defined in section 617 of the Companies Act, 1956 (1 of 1956), or in connection with any`
  line `amalgamation or succession referred to in sub-section ( 6 ) or sub-section ( 7 ) of section 32A; or`
  line `( b ) at any time before the expiry of ten years from the end of the previous year in which the ship`
  line `or aircraft was acquired or the machinery or plant was installed, the assessee does not utilise the`
  line `amount credited to the reserve account under sub-section ( 4 ) of section 32A for the purposes of`
  line `acquiring a new ship or a new aircraft or new machinery or plant [other than machinery or plant of`
  line `the nature referred to in clauses ( a ), ( b ) and ( d ) of 9 [the second proviso] to sub-section ( 1 ) ofsection`
  line `32A] for the purposes of the business of the undertaking; or`
  line `( c ) at any time before the expiry of ten years referred to in clause ( b ) the assesseeutilises the`
  line `amount credited to the reserve account under sub-section ( 4 ) of section 32A —`
  line `( i ) for distribution by way of dividends or profits; or`
  line `( ii ) for remittance outside India as profits or for the creation of any asset outside India; or`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 67 of 1984, s. 30 (w.e.f. 1-10-1984).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 4 of 1988, s. 2, for “Income - tax Officer” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1988).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 67 of 1984, s. 30, for “from the date of the final order passed” (w.e.f. 1 -10-1984).`
  line `4. Sub-section ( 3 ) omitted by Act 4 of 1988, s. 61 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 11 of 1987, s. 74, for “sub -section ( 1 ) of section 74” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1988).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 20 of 1974, s. 13 (w.e.f. 1-4-1975).`
  line `7. Subs. by Act 67 of 1984, s. 30, for “from the date of the order passed” (w.e.f. 1 -10-1984).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 66 of 1976, s. 21 (w.e.f. 1-4-1976).`
  line `9. Subs. by Act 3 of 1989, s. 25, for “the proviso” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1989).`
