  line 602
  line `( ii ) at any time before the expiry of the eight years referred to in sub-section ( 3 ) of section 33A,`
  line `the assesseeutilises the amount credited to the reserve account under clause ( ii ) of that sub-section —`
  line `( a ) for distribution by way of dividends or profits; or`
  line `( b ) for remittance outside India as profits or for the creation of any asset outside India; or`
  line `( c ) for any other purpose which is not a purpose of the business of the undertaking;`
  line `the development allowance originally allowed shall be deemed to have been wrongly allowed, and the`
  line `1 [Assessing Officer] may, notwithstanding anything contained in this Act, recompute the total income of`
  line `the assessee for the relevant previous year and make the necessary amendment; and the provisions`
  line `of section 154 shall, so far as may be, apply thereto, the period of four years specified in sub-section ( 7 )`
  line `of that section being reckoned from the end of the previous year in which the sale or transfer took place or`
  line `the money was so utilised.]`
  line `2 [ Explanation. — For the purposes of this sub-section, where an assessee having any leasehold or other`
  line `right of occupancy in any land transfers such right, he shall be deemed to have sold or otherwise`
  line `transferred such land.]`
  line `3 [( 5B ) Where any deduction in respect of any expenditure on scientific research has been made in any`
  line `assessment year under sub-section ( 2B ) of section 35 and the assessee fails to furnish a certificate of`
  line `completion of the programme obtained from the prescribed authority within one year of the period`
  line `allowed for its completion by such authority, the deduction originally made in excess of the expenditure`
  line `actually incurred shall be deemed to have been wrongly made, and the 1 [Assessing Officer] may,`
  line `notwithstanding anything contained in this Act, recompute the total income of the assessee for therelevant`
  line `previous year and make the necessary amendment; and the provisions of section 154 shall, so far as may`
  line `be, apply thereto, the period of four years specified in sub-section ( 7 ) of that section being reckoned from`
  line `the end of the previous year in which the period allowed for the completion of the programme by the`
  line `prescribed authority expired.]`
  line `4 * * * * *`
  line `( 7 ) Where as a result of any proceeding under this Act, in the assessment for any year of a company`
  line `in whose case an order under section 104 has been made for that year, it is necessary to recompute the`
  line `distributable income of that company, the 1 [Assessing Officer] may proceed to recompute the`
  line `distributable income and determine 5 [the tax] payable on the basis of such recomputation and make the`
  line `necessary amendment; and the provisions of section 154 shall, so far as may be, apply thereto, the period`
  line `of four years specified in sub-section ( 7 ) of that section being reckoned 6 [from the end of the financial`
  line `year in which the final order was passed] in the case of the company in respect of that proceeding.`
  line `7 * * * * *`
  line `8 [( 7B ) Where in the assessment for any year, the capital gain arising from the transfer of a capital`
  line `asset is not charged under section 45 by virtue of the provisions of clause ( iv ) or, as the case may be,`
  line `clause ( v ) of section 47, but is deemed under section 47A to be income chargeable under the head`
  line `"Capital gains" of the previous year in which the transfer took place by reason of —`
  line `( i ) such capital asset being converted by the transferee company into, or being treated by it, as`
  line `stock-in-trade of its business; or`
  line `( ii ) the parent company or its nominees or, as the case may be, the holding company ceasing to`
  line `hold the whole of the share capital of the subsidiary company,`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 4 of 1988, s. 2, for “Income - tax Officer” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1988).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 25 of 1975, s. 24 (w.e.f. 1-4-1975).`
  line `3. Restored by Act 3 of 1989, s. 95 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989). Sub-section ( 5B ) omitted by Act 4 of 1988, s. 61 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989)`
  line `which was earlier inserted by Act 44 of 1980, s. 26 (w.e.f. 1-4-1981).`
  line `4. Sub-section ( 6 ) omitted by Act 4 of 1988, s. 61 w.e.f. 1-4-1992.`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 10 of 1965, s. 39, for “the super - tax” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1965).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 67 of 1984, s. 30, for “from the date of the final order passed” (w.e.f. 1 -10-1984).`
  line `7. Sub-section ( 7A ) omitted by Act 4 of 1988, s. 61 (w.e.f. 1-4-1992).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 67 of 1984, s. 30 (w.e.f. 1-4-1985).`
