obj_root_law_sections_614_content:
  string
  line 614
  line `( e ) in any case other than those mentioned in clauses ( c ) and ( d ), after the expiry of the financial`
  line `year in which the proceedings, in the course of which action for the imposition of penalty has been`
  line `initiated, are completed, or six months from the end of the month in which action for imposition of`
  line `penalty is initiated, whichever period expires later;`
  line `( f ) in respect of search initiated under section 132 or books of account, other documents or any`
  line `assets requisitioned under section 132A, after the 30th day of June, 1995 but before the 1st day of`
  line `January, 1997.`
  line `Explanation. — In computing the period of limitation for the purpose of this section, —`
  line `( i ) the time taken in giving an opportunity to the assessee to be reheard under the proviso`
  line `to section 129;`
  line `( ii ) the period during which the immunity granted under section 245H remained in force; and`
  line `( iii ) the period during which the proceedings under sub-section ( 2 ) are stayed by an order or`
  line `injunction of any court,`
  line `shall be excluded.`
  line `( 4 ) An income-tax authority on making an order under sub-section ( 2 ) imposing a penalty, unless he`
  line `is himself an Assessing Officer, shall forthwith send a copy of such order to the Assessing Officer.]`
  line `1 [ 158BG. Authority competent to make the block assessment. — The order of assessment for the`
  line `block period shall be passed by an Assessing Officer not below the rank of an 2 [Assistant Commissioner`
  line `or Deputy Commissioner] or an 3 [Assistant Director or Deputy Director], as the case may be:`
  line `Provided that no such order shall be passed without the previous approval of —`
  line `( a ) the 4 [Principal Commissioner or Commissioner] or 5 [Principal Director or Director], as the`
  line `case may be, in respect of search initiated under section 132 or books of account, other documents or`
  line `any assets requisitioned under section 132A, after the 30th day of June, 1995 but before the 1st day of`
  line `January, 1997;`
  line `( b ) the 6 [Joint Commissioner] or the 7 [Joint Director], as the case may be, in respect of search`
  line `initiated under section 132 or books of account, other documents or any assets requisitioned`
  line `under section 132A, on or after the 1st day of January, 1997.]`
  line `158BH. Application of other provisions of this Act. — Save as otherwise provided in this Chapter,`
  line `all other provisions of this Act shall apply to assessment made under this Chapter.]`
  line `8 [ 158BI. Chapter not to apply after certain date. — The provisions of this Chapter shall not apply`
  line `where a search is initiated under section 132, or books of account, other documents or any assets are`
  line `requisitioned under section 132A after the 31st day of May, 2003.]`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 13 of 1997, s. 7, for section 158BG (w.e.f. 1-1-1997).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 21 of 1998, s. 3, for “Assistant Commissioner” (w.e.f. 1 -10-1998).`
  line `3. Subs. by s. 3, ibid., for “Assistant Director” (w.e.f. 1 -10-1998).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 25 of 2014, s. 4, for “Commissioner” (w.e.f. 1 -6-2013).`
  line `5. Subs. by s. 4, ibid., for “Director” (w.e.f. 1 -6-2013).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 21 of 1998, s. 3, for “Deputy Commissioner” (w.e.f. 1 -10-1998).`
  line `7. Subs. by s. 3, ibid., for “Deputy Director” (w.e.f. 1 -10-1998).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 67 (w.e.f. 1-6-2003).`
