  line `1 * * * * *`
  line `( 3 ) The provisions of sub-section ( 1 ) shall not apply —`
  line `2 [( i ) where the amount of such income or, as the case may be, the aggregate of the amounts of`
  line `such income credited or paid or likely to be credited or paid during the financial year by the person`
  line `referred to in sub-section ( 1 ) to the account of, or to, the payee, 3 [does not exceed —`
  line `( a ) 4 [forty thousand] rupees, where the payer is a banking company to which the Banking`
  line `Regulation Act, 1949 (10 of 1949) applies (including any bank or banking institution, referred to`
  line `in section 51 of that Act);`
  line `( b ) 4 [forty thousand] thousand rupees, where the payer is a co-operative society engaged in`
  line `carrying on the business of banking;`
  line `( c ) 4 [forty thousand] rupees, on any deposit with post office under any scheme framed by the`
  line `Central Government and notified by it in this behalf; and`
  line `( d ) five thousand rupees in any other case]:]`
  line `5 [Provided that in respect of the income credited or paid in respect of —`
  line `( a ) time deposits with a banking company to which the Banking Regulation Act, 1949`
  line `(10 of 1949) applies (including any bank or banking institution referred to in section 51 of`
  line `that Act); or`
  line `( b ) time deposits with a co-operative society engaged in carrying on the business of`
  line banking;
  line `( c ) deposits with a public company which is formed and registered in India with the main`
  line `object of carrying on the business of providing long-term finance for construction or purchase`
  line `of houses in India 6 [for residential purposes and which is eligible for deduction under clause`
  line `( viii ) of sub-section ( 1 ) of section 36] 7 ***;`
  line `8 *** the aforesaid amount shall be computed with reference to the income credited or paid by a branch of`
  line `the banking company or the co-operative society or the public company, as the case may be:]`
  line `9 [Provided further that the amount referred to in the first proviso shall be computed with reference to`
  line `the income credited or paid by the banking company or the co-operative society or the public company, as`
  line `the case may be, where such banking company or the co-operative society or the public company has`
  line `adopted core banking solutions;]`
  line `1. Sub-section ( 2 ) omitted by Act 18 of 1992, s. 71 (w.e.f. 1-6-1992).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 25 of 1975, s. 20, for clause ( i ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1975).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 22 of 2007, s. 53, for “does not exceed five thousand rupees” (w.e.f. 1 -6-2007).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 7 of 2019, s. 9, for “ten thousand” (w.e.f. 1-4-2019).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 33 of 1996, s. 49, for the proviso (w.e.f. 1-10-1996).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 10 of 2000, s. 60, for “for residential purposes” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2000).`
  line `7. The certain words, brackets and figures omitted by Act 27 of 1999, s. 69 (w.e.f. 1-4-2000).`
  line `8. The certain words omitted by Act 14 of 2001, s. 69 (w.e.f. 1-6-2001).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 20 of 2015, s. 43 (w.e.f. 1-6-2015).`
