  line `1 [Provided also that in case of payee being a senior citizen, the provisions of sub-clause ( a ),`
  line `sub-clause ( b ), and sub-clause ( c ) shall have effect as if for the words “ 2 [forty thousand] thousand`
  line `rupees”, the words “fifty thousand rupees” had been substituted.`
  line `Explanation. —For the purposes of this clause, “senior citizen” means an individual residen t in`
  line `India who is of the age of sixty years or more at any time during the relevant previous year;]`
  line `3 * * * * *`
  line `( iii ) to such income credited or paid to —`
  line `( a ) any banking company to which the Banking Regulation Act, 1949 (10 of 1949), applies,`
  line `or any co-operative society engaged in carrying on the business of banking (including a`
  line `co-operative land mortgage bank), or`
  line `( b ) any financial corporation established by or under a Central, State or Provincial Act, or`
  line `( c ) the Life Insurance Corporation of India established under the Life Insurance Corporation`
  line `Act, 1956 (31 of 1956), or`
  line `( d ) the Unit Trust of India established under the Unit Trust of India Act, 1963 (52 of 1963),`
  line or
  line `( e ) any company or co-operative society carrying on the business of insurance, or`
  line `( f ) such other institution, association or body 4 [or class of institutions, associations or bodies]`
  line `which the Central Government may, for reasons to be recorded in writing, notify in this behalf in`
  line `the Official Gazette;`
  line `5 [( iv ) to such income credited or paid by a firm to a partner of the firm;]`
  line `( v ) to such income credited or 6 [paid by a co-operative society (other than a co-operative bank) to`
  line `a member thereof or to such income credited or paid by a co-operative society] to any other`
  line `co-operative society;]`
  line `7 [ Explanation. — For the purposes of this clause, “co - operative bank” shall have the same meaning as`
  line `assigned to it in Part V of the Banking Regulation Act, 1949 (10 of 1949);]`
  line `8 [( vi ) to such income credited or paid in respect of deposits under any scheme framed by the`
  line `Central Government and notified by it in this behalf in the Official Gazette;`
  line `9 [( vii ) to such income credited or paid in respect of deposits (other than time deposits made on or`
  line `after the 1st day of July, 1995) with a banking company to which the Banking Regulation Act, 1949`
  line `(10 of 1949) applies (including any bank or banking institution referred to in section 51 of that Act);`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 13 of 2018, s. 49 (w.e.f. 1-4-2018).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 7 of 2019, s. 9, for “ten thousand” (w.e.f. 1-4-2019).`
  line `3. Clause ( ii ) omitted by Act 27 of 1999, s. 69 (w.e.f. 1-4-2000).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 19 of 1968, s. 14 (w.e.f. 1-4-1968).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 3 of 1989, s. 30 (w.e.f. 1-4-1988). Which was omitted by Act 4 of 1988, s. 73 (w.e.f. 1-4-1988). Original`
  line `clause ( iv ) was inserted by Act 19 of 1968, s. 14 (w.e.f. 1-4-1968).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 20 of 2015, s. 43, for “paid by co - operative society to a member thereof or” (w.e.f. 1 -6-2015).`
  line `7. Ins. by s. 43, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-6-2015).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 19 of 1970, s. 23 (w.e.f. 1-4-1970).`
  line `9. Subs. by Act 22 of 1995, s. 33, for clause ( vii ) (w.e.f. 1-7-1995).`
