  line `( viia ) to such income credited or paid in respect of, —`
  line `( a ) deposits with a primary agricultural credit society or a primary credit society or a co-`
  line `operative land mortgage bank or a co-operative land development bank;`
  line `( b ) deposits (other than time deposits made on or after the 1st day of July, 1995) with a co-`
  line `operative society, other than a co-operative society or bank referred to in sub-clause ( a ), engaged`
  line `in carrying on the business of banking;]]`
  line `1 [( viii ) to such income credited or paid by the Central Government under any provision of this`
  line `Act or the Indian Income-tax Act, 1922 (11 of 1922), or the Estate Duty Act, 1953 (34 of 1953), or`
  line `the Wealth-tax Act, 1957 (27 of 1957), or the Gift-tax Act, 1958 (18 of 1958), or the Super Profits`
  line `Tax Act, 1963 (14 of 1963), or the Companies (Profits) Surtax Act, 1964 (7 of 1964), or the`
  line `Interest-tax Act, 1974 (45 of 1974);]`
  line `2 [( ix ) to such income credited by way of interest on the compensation amount awarded by the`
  line `Motor Accidents Claims Tribunal;`
  line `( ixa ) to such income paid by way of interest on the compensation amount awarded by the Motor`
  line `Accidents Claims Tribunal where the amount of such income or, as the case may be, the aggregate of`
  line `the amounts of such income paid during the financial year does not exceed fifty thousand rupees;]`
  line `3 [( x ) to such income which is paid or payable by an infrastructure capital company or`
  line `infrastructure capital fund or a public sector company 4 [or scheduled bank] in relation to a zero`
  line `coupon bond issued on or after the 1st day of June, 2005 by such company or fund or public sector`
  line `company 4 [or scheduled bank];]`
