  line `5. Ins. by Act 25 of 2014, s. 56 (w.e.f. 1-10-2014).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 18 of 2005, s. 48, for the Explanation (w.e.f. 1-6-2005).`
  line `7. Subs. by Act 20 of 2015, s. 43, for “excluding” (w.e.f. 1 -6-2015).`
  line `8. Explanation 2 omitted by Act 21 of 2006 s. 40 (w.e.f. 1-4-2006).`
  line `9. The Explanation omitted by Act 18 of 1992, s. 71 (w.e.f. 1-6-1992).`
