obj_root_law_sections_657_content:
  string
  line 657
  line `1 [Provided that no deduction shall be made under this section from any such income credited or paid`
  line `on or after the 1st day of April, 2003.]`
  line `( 2 ) Notwithstanding anything contained in sub-section ( 1 ), no deduction of tax shall be made from`
  line `any income payable in respect of units of the Unit Trust of India to a non-resident Indian or a non-resident`
  line `Hindu undivided family, where the units have been acquired from the Unit Trust of India out of the funds`
  line `in a Non-resident (External) Account maintained with any bank in India or by remittance of funds in`
  line `foreign currency, in accordance, in either case, with the provisions of 2 [the Foreign Exchange`
  line `Management Act, 1999 (42 of 1999)], and the rules made thereunder.`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this section —`
  line `( a ) “foreign currency” s hall have the meaning assigned to it in 2 [the Foreign Exchange`
  line `Management Act, 1999 (42 of 1999)];`
  line `( b ) “non - resident Indian” shall have the meaning assigned to it in clause ( e ) of section 115C;`
  line `( c ) “Unit Trust of India” means the Unit Trust of India established under the Unit Trust of India`
  line `Act, 1963 (52 of 1963);`
  line `( d ) where any income as aforesaid is credited to any account, whether called “Suspense account”`
  line `or by any other name, in the books of account of the person liable to pay such income, such crediting`
  line `shall be deemed to be credit of such income to the account of the payee and the provisions of this`
  line `section shall apply accordingly.]`
  line `3 [ 196B. Income from units. — 4 [Where any income in respect of units referred to in section 115AB or`
  line `by way of long-term capital gains arising from the transfer of such units is payable to an Offshore Fund],`
  line `the person responsible for making the payment shall, at the time of credit of such income to the account`
  line `of the payee or at the time of payment thereof in cash or by the issue of a cheque or draft or by any other`
  line `mode, whichever is earlier, deduct income-tax thereon at the rate of ten per cent.]`
  line `5 [ 196C. Income from foreign currency bonds or shares of Indian company. — 6 [Where any`
  line `income by way of interest or dividends in respect of 7 [bonds or Global Depository Receipts] referred to`
  line `in section 115AC or by way of long-term capital gains arising from the transfer of such 7 [bonds or Global`
  line `Depository Receipts] is payable to a non-resident], the person responsible for making the payment shall,`
  line `at the time of credit of such income to the account of the payee or at the time of payment thereof in cash`
  line `or by the issue of a cheque or draft or by any other mode, whichever is earlier, deduct income-tax thereon`
  line `at the rate of ten per cent.]:`
  line `8 [Provided that no such deduction shall be made in respect of any dividends referred to in`
  line `section 115-O.]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 81 (w.e.f. 1-4-2003). Earlier the proviso omitted by Act 20 of 2002, s. 82 (w.e.f.1-6-2002)`
  line `which was inserted by Act 27 of 1999, s. 75 (w.e.f.1-6-1999).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 17 of 2013, s. 4, for “the Foreign Exchange Regulation Act, 1973 (46 of 1973)” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2013).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 49 of 1991, s. 58 (w.e.f. 1-10-1991).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 38 of 1993, s. 26, for “Where any income is pay able in respect of units referred to in section 115AB to an`
  line `Offshore Fund” (w.e.f. 1 -6-1993).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 18 of 1992, s. 75 (w.e.f. 1-6-1992).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 38 of 1993, s. 27, for “Where any income by way of interest or dividends is payable in respect of bonds or`
  line `shares referred to in section 115AC to a non- resident” (w.e.f. 1 -6-1993).`
  line `7. Subs. by Act 14 of 2001, s. 72, for “bonds or shares” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2002).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 82 (w.e.f. 1-4-2003). Earlier the proviso was omitted by Act 20 of 2002, s. 83 (w.e.f. 1-6-2002)`
  line `which was inserted by Act 26 of 1997, s. 50 (w.e.f. 1-6-1997).`
