obj_root_law_sections_658_content:
  string
  line 658
  line `1 [ 196D. Income of Foreign Institutional Investors from securities. — ( 1 ) Where 2 [any income in`
  line `respect of securities referred to in clause ( a ) of sub-section ( 1 ) of section 115AD, not being income by`
  line `way of interest referred to in section 194LD, is payable] to a Foreign Institutional Investor, the person`
  line `responsible for making the payment shall, at the time of credit of such income to the account of the payee`
  line `or at the time of payment thereof in cash or by issue of a cheque or draft or by any other mode, whichever`
  line `is earlier, deduct income-tax thereon at the rate of twenty per cent.:`
  line `3 [Provided that no such deduction shall be made in respect of any dividends referred to in section`
  line 115-O.]
  line `( 2 ) No deduction of tax shall be made from any income, by way of capital gains arising from the`
  line `transfer of securities referred to in section 115AD, payable to a Foreign Institutional Investor.]`
  line `197. Certificate for deduction at lower rate. — ( 1 ) 4 [Subject to rules made under sub-section ( 2A ),`
  line `5 [where, in the case of 6 [any income of any person or sum payable to any person], income-tax is required`
  line `to be deducted at the time of credit or, as the case may be, at the time of payment at the rates in force`
  line `under the provisions of sections 192, 193, 7 [194,] 8 [194A, 9 [194C, 194D,194G,194H,194-I, 194J, 194K`
  line `, 194LA 10 [, 194LBB, 194LBC]]] and 195, the Assessing Officer is satisfied]] that the total income 11 ***`
  line `of the recipient justifies the deduction of income-tax 12 *** at any lower rates or no deduction of income-`
  line `tax 12 ***, as the case may be, the 13 [Assessing Officer] shall, on an application made by the assessee in`
  line `this behalf, give to him such certificate as may be appropriate.`
  line `( 2 ) Where any such certificate is given, the person responsible for paying the income shall, until such`
  line `certificate is cancelled by the 13 [Assessing Officer], deduct income-tax 14 *** at the rates specified in such`
  line `certificate or deduct no tax, as the case may be.`
  line `15 [( 2A ) The Board may, having regard to the convenience of assessees and the interests of revenue, by`
  line `notification in the Official Gazette, make rules specifying the cases in which, and the circumstances under`
  line `which, an application may be made for the grant of a certificate under sub-section ( 1 ) and the conditions`
  line `subject to which such certificate may be granted and providing for all other matters connected therewith.]`
  line `16 * * * * *`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 38 of 1993, s. 28 (w.e.f. 1-6-1993).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 17 of 2013, s. 49, for “any income in respect of securities referred to in clause (a) of su b-section ( 1 ) of`
  line `section 115AD is payable” (w.e.f. 1 -6-2013).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 83 (w.e.f. 1-4-2003). Earlier the proviso was omitted by Act 20 of 2002, s. 84 (w.e.f. 1-6-2002)`
  line `which was inserted by Act 26 of 1997, s. 50 (w.e.f. 1-6-1997).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 11 of 1987, s. 51, for “Where in the case of any income of any person other than a company” (w.e.f. 1 -6-`
  line `1987).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 18 of 1992, s. 76, for certain words (w.e.f. 1-6-1992).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 84, for “any income of any person” (w.e.f. 1 -6-2003).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 38 of 1993, s. 29 (w.e.f. 1-6-1993).`
  line `8. Subs. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 84, for “194A, 194D, 194H, 194 - I, 194K, 194L” (w.e.f. 1 -6-2003).`
  line `9. Subs. by Act 23 of 2004, s. 39, for “194C, 194D, 194G, 194H, 194 -I, 194J, 194K” (w.e.f. 1 -10-2004).`
  line `10. Ins. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 85 (w.e.f. 1-6-2016).`
  line `11. The words “or the total world income” omitted by Act 10 of 1965, s. 48 (w.e.f. 1 -4-1965).`
  line `12. The words “or super - tax” omitted by s. 48, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-1965).`
  line `13. Subs. by Act 4 of 1988, s. 2, for “Income - tax Officer” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1988).`
  line `14. The words “and super - tax” omitted by Act 10 of 1965, s. 48 (w.e.f. 1 -4-1965).`
  line `15. Ins. by Act 11 of 1987, s. 51 (w.e.f. 1-6-1987).`
  line `16. Sub-section ( 3 ) omitted by Act 23 of 1986, s. 39 (w.e.f. 1-4-1987).`
