  line 659
  line `1 [ 197A. No deduction to be made in certain cases. — ( 1 ) Notwithstanding anything contained in`
  line `2 *** section 194 3 *** 4 [or section 194EE], no deduction of tax shall be made under any of the said`
  line `sections in the case of an individual, who is resident in India, if such individual furnishes to the person`
  line `responsible for paying any income of the nature referred to in 2 *** section 194 5 [ 3 *** or, as the case may`
  line `be, section 194EE], a declaration in writing in duplicate in the prescribed form and verified in the`
  line `prescribed manner to the effect that 6 [the tax on his estimated total income of the previous year in which`
  line `such income is to be included in computing his total income will be nil.]`
  line `7 [( 1A )Notwithstanding anything contained in 8 [section 192A or section 193 or section`
  line `194A 9 [ or section 194D ] or section 194DA] 10 [or section 194-I] or section 194K, no deduction of tax shall`
  line `be made under 11 [any of] the said sections in the case of a person (not being a company or a firm), if such`
  line `person furnishes to the person responsible for paying any income of the nature referred to in 8 [section`
  line `192A or section 193 or section 194A 9 [ or section 194D ] or section 194DA] 10 [or section 194-I] or section`
  line `194K, as the case may be, a declaration in writing in duplicate in the prescribed form and verified in the`
  line `prescribed manner to the effect that the tax on his estimated total income of the previous year in which`
  line `such income is to be included in computing his total income will be nil. ]`
  line `12 [( 1B ) The provisions of this section shall not apply where the amount of any income of the nature`
  line `referred to in sub-section ( 1 ) or sub-section ( 1A ), as the case may be, or the aggregate of the amounts of`
  line `such incomes credited or paid or likely to be credited or paid during the previous year in which such`
  line `income is to be included exceeds the maximum amount which is not chargeable to income-tax.]`
  line `13 [( 1C ) Notwithstanding anything contained in 14 [section 192A or section 193 or section`
  line `194 or section 194A 9 [ or section 194D ] or section 194DA] or section 194EE 10 [or section 194-I] or`
  line `section 194K or sub-section ( 1B ) of this section, no deduction of tax shall be made in the case of an`
  line `individual resident in India, who is of the age of 15 [sixty years] or more at any time during the previous`
  line `year 16 ***, if such individual furnishes to the person responsible for paying any income of the nature`
  line `referred to in 14 [section 192A or section 193 or section 194 or section 194A 9 [ or section 194D ] or section`
  line `194DA] or section 194EE 10 [or section194-I] or section 194K, as the case may be, a declaration in writing`
  line `in duplicate in the prescribed formand verified in the prescribed manner to the effect that the tax on his`
  line `estimated total income of the previous year in which such income is to be included in computing his total`
  line `income will be nil.]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 14 of 1982, s. 26 (w.e.f. 1-6-1982).`
  line `2. The words and figures “section 193 or” omitted by Act 27 of 1999, s. 77 (w.e.f. 1 -6-1999).`
  line `3. The words and figures “or section 194A” omitted by Act 18 of 1992, s. 77 (w.e.f. 1-6-1992).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 49 of 1991, s. 59 (w.e.f. 1-10-1991).`
  line `5. Subs. by s. 59, ibid., for “or, as the case may be, section 194A” (w.e.f. 1 -10-1991).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 12 of 1990, s. 50, for “his estimated total income of the previous year in which such income is to be`
  line `included in computing his total income will be less than the minimum liable to income- tax” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1990).`
  line `7. Subs. by Act 22 of 1995, s. 39, for sub-section ( 1A ) (w.e.f. 1-7-1995).`
  line `8. Subs. by Act 20 of 2015, s. 50, for “section 193 or section 194A” (w.e.f. 1 -6-2015).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 70 (w.e.f. 1-6-2017).`
  line `10. Ins. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 86 (w.e.f. 1-6-2016).`
  line `11. Subs. by Act 27 of 1999, s. 77, for “either of” (w.e.f. 1 -6-1999).`
  line `12. Ins. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 85 (w.e.f. 1-6-2002).`
  line `13. Ins. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 85 (w.e.f. 1-6-2003).`
  line `14. Subs. by Act 20 of 2015, s. 50, for “section 193 or section 194 or section 194A” (w.e.f. 1 -6-2015).`
  line `15. Subs. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 78, for “sixty - five years” (w.e.f. 1 -7-2012).`
  line `16. The words, f igures and letter “and is entitled to a deduction from the amount of income -tax on his total income referred`
  line `to in section 88B” omitted by Act 22 of 2007, s. 58 (w.e.f. 1 -4-2006).`
