obj_root_law_sections_665_content:
  string
  line 665
  line `1 [ 203AA. Furnishing of statement of tax deducted. — The prescribed income-tax authority or the`
  line `person authorised by such authority referred to in sub-section ( 3 ) of section 200, shall, within the`
  line `prescribed time after the end of each financial year beginning on or after the 2 [1st day of April, 2008]`
  line `prepare and deliver to every person from whose income the tax has been deducted or in respect of whose`
  line `income the tax has been paid a statement in the prescribed form specifying the amount of tax deducted or`
  line `paid and such other particulars as may be prescribed.]`
  line `204. Meaning of“person responsible for paying”. — For the purposes of 3 [the foregoing provisions`
  line `of this Chapter] and section 285, the expression “person responsible for paying” means—`
  line `( i ) in the case of payments of income chargeable under the head “Salaries”, other than payments`
  line `by the Central Government or the Government of a State, the employer himself or, if the employer is`
  line `a company, the company itself, including the principal officer thereof;`
  line `( ii ) in the case of payments of income chargeable under the head “Interest on securities”, other`
  line `than payments made by or on behalf of the Central Government or the Government of a State, the`
  line `local authority, corporation or company, including the principal officer thereof;`
  line `4 [( iia ) in the case of any sum payable to a non-resident Indian, being any sum representing`
  line `consideration for the transfer by him of any foreign exchange asset, which is not a short-term capital`
  line `asset, the 5 [authorised person] responsible for remitting such sum to the non-resident Indian or for`
  line `crediting such sum to his Non-resident (External) Account maintained in accordance with 6 [the`
  line `Foreign Exchange Management Act, 1999 (42 of 1999)], and any rules made thereunder;]`
  line `7 [ ( iib ) in the case of furnishing of information relating to payment to a non-resident, not being a`
  line `company, or to a foreign company, of any sum, whether or not chargeable under the provisions of this`
  line `Act, the payer himself, or, if the payer is a company, the company itself including the principal`
  line `officer thereof; ]`
  line `( iii ) 8 [in the case of credit, or, as the case may be, payment] of any other sum chargeable under`
  line `the provisions of this Act, the payer himself, or, if the payer is a company, the company itself`
  line `including the principal officer thereof;`
  line `9 [( iv ) in the case of credit, or as the case may be, payment of any sum chargeable under the`
  line `provisions of this Act made by or on behalf of the Central Government or the Government of a State,`
  line `the drawing and disbursing officer or any other person, by whatever name called, responsible for`
  line `crediting, or as the case may be, paying such sum.]`
  line `10 [ Explanation. — For the purposes of this section, —`
  line `( a ) “non - resident Indian” and “foreign exchange asset” shall have the meanings assigned to them`
  line `in Chapter XII-A;`
  line `11 [( b ) “authorised person” shall have the meaning assigned to it in clause ( c ) of section 2 of the`
  line `Foreign Exchange Management Act, 1999 (42 of 1999).]]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 23 of 2004, s. 46 (w.e.f. 1-4-2005).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 21 of 2006, s. 45, for “1st day of April, 2005” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2006).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 23 of 2004, s. 47, for certain words, figures and letter (w.e.f. 1-10-2004). Earlier to amended by Act 20 of`
  line `1967, s. 30 (w.e.f. 1-4-1967).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 23 of 1986, s. 32 (w.e.f. 1-6-1986).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 17 of 2013, s. 50, for “authorized dealer” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2013).`
  line `6. Subs. by s. 4, ibid., for “the Foreign Exchange Regulation Act, 1973 (46 of 1973)” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2013).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 71 (w.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
  line `8. Subs. by Act 20 of 1967, s. 30, for “in the case of payment” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1967).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 80 (w.e.f. 1-7-2012).`
  line `10. Added by Act 23 of 1986, s. 32 (w.e.f. 1-6-1986).`
  line `11. Subs. by Act 17 of 2013, s. 50, for clause ( b ) (w.e.f. 1-4-2013).`
obj_root_law_sections_665_footnotes:
