obj_root_law_sections_670_content:
  string
  line 670
  line `1 [( 3A ) In case of an office of the Government, where the amount collected under sub-section ( 1 ) 2 [or`
  line `sub-section ( 1C )] 3 *** has been paid to the credit of the Central Government without the production of a`
  line `challan, the Pay and Accounts Officer or the Treasury Officer or the Cheque Drawing and Disbursing`
  line `Officer or any other person, by whatever name called, who is responsible for crediting such tax to the`
  line `credit of the Central Government, shall deliver or cause to be delivered to the prescribed income-tax`
  line `authority, or to the person authorised by such authority, a statement in such form, verified in such manner,`
  line `setting forth such particulars and within such time as may be prescribed.`
  line `( 3B ) The person referred to in the proviso to sub-section ( 3 ) may also deliver to the prescribed`
  line `authority under the said proviso, a correction statement for rectification of any mistake or to add, delete or`
  line `update the information furnished in the statement delivered under the said proviso in such form and`
  line `verified in such manner, as may be specified by the authority.]`
  line `4 [( 4 ) Any amount collected in accordance with the provisions of this section and paid to the credit of`
  line `the Central Government shall be deemed to be a payment of tax on behalf of the person from whom the`
  line `amount has been collected and credit shall be given to such person for the amount so collected in a`
  line `particular assessment year in accordance with the rules as may be prescribed by the Board from time to`
  line time.]
  line `( 5 ) Every person collecting tax in accordance with the provisions of this section shall within 5 [such`
  line `period as may be prescribed from the time of debit] or receipt of the amount furnish to the 6 [buyer or`
  line `licensee or lessee] to whose account such amount is debited or from whom such payment is received, a`
  line `certificate to the effect that tax has been collected, and specifying the sum so collected, the rate at which`
  line `the tax has been collected and such other particulars as may be prescribed:`
  line `7 [* * * * *`
  line `Provided 8 *** that the prescribed income-tax authority or the person authorised by such authority`
  line `referred to in sub-section ( 3 ) shall, within the prescribed time 9 [after the end of each financial year`
  line `beginning on or after the 1st day of April, 2008], prepare and deliver to the buyer referred to in sub-`
  line `section ( 1 ) or, as the case may be, to the licensee or lessee referred to in sub-section ( 1C ), a statement in`
  line `the prescribed form specifying the amount of tax collected and such other particulars as may be`
  line prescribed.]
  line `10 [( 5A ) Every person 11 [collecting tax before the 1st day of April, 2005] in accordance with the`
  line `provisions of this section shall 12 [prepare within the prescribed time after the end of each financial year],`
  line `and deliver or cause to be delivered to the 13 [prescribed income-tax authority or such other authority or`
  line `agency as may be prescribed] such returns in such form and verified in such manner and setting forth`
  line `such particulars and within such time as may be prescribed:]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 20 of 2015, s. 54 (w.e.f. 1-6-2015).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 23 of 2004, s. 50 (w.e.f. 1-10-2004).`
  line `3. The words “or sub -section ( 1D )” omitted by Act 7 of 2017, s. 72 (w.e.f. 1 -4-2017).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 18 of 2008, s. 48, for sub-section ( 4 ) (w.e.f. 1-4-2008). Earlier inserted by Act 23 of 2004,`
  line `s. 50 (w.e.f. 1-4-2005).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 54 of 2003, s. 9, for “ten days from the date of debit” (w.e.f. 8 -9-2003).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 23 of 2004, s. 50, for “buyer” (w.e.f. 1 -10-2004).`
  line `7. The Proviso omitted by 14 of 2010, s. 44 (w.e.f. 1-4-2010). Earlier provisos inserted by Act 23 of 2004, s. 50`
  line `(w.e.f. 1-4-2005).`
  line `8. The words “Provided further” omitted by s. 44, ibid. (w.e.f. 1-4-2010).`
  line `9. Subs. by Act 21 of 2006, s. 47, for “1st day of April, 2006” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2005).`
  line `10. Ins. by Act 3 of 1989, s. 34 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `11. Subs. by Act 21 of 2006, s. 47, for “after the end of each financial year” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2006).`
  line `12. Subs. by Act 23 of 2004, s. 50, for “prepare half -yearly returns of the period ending on the 30 th Septmebt and 31 st March`
  line `in each financial year” (w.e.f. 1 -10-2004).`
  line `13. Subs. by s. 50, ibid., for “prescribed income - tax authority” (w.e.f. 1 -10-2004).`
