obj_root_law_sections_674_content:
  string
  line 674
  line `1 [206CA. Tax collection account number. — ( 1 ) Every person collecting tax in accordance with the`
  line `provisions of section 206C, shall, within such time as may be prescribed, apply to the Assessing Officer`
  line `for the allotment of a tax collection account number.`
  line `( 2 ) Where a tax collection account number has been allotted to a person, such person shall quote such`
  line `number —`
  line `( a ) in all challans for the payment of any sum in accordance with the provisions of sub-section ( 3 )`
  line `of section 206C;`
  line `( b ) in all certificates furnished under sub-section ( 5 ) of section 206C;`
  line `( c ) in all the returns delivered in accordance with the provisions of sub-section ( 5A ) or sub-`
  line `section ( 5B ) of section 206C to any income-tax authority; and`
  line `( d ) in all other documents pertaining to such transactions as may be prescribed in the interest of`
  line `revenue:]`
  line `2 [Provided that the provisions of this section shall not apply on or after the 1st day of October,`
  line 2004.]
  line `3 [ 206CB. Processing of statements of tax collected at source. — ( 1 ) Where a statement of tax`
  line `collection at source or a correction statement has been made by a person collecting any sum (herein`
  line `referred to as collector) under section 206C, such statement shall be processed in the following manner,`
  line `namely: —`
  line `( a ) the sums collectible under this Chapter shall be computed after making the following`
  line `adjustments, namely: —`
  line `( i ) any arithmetical error in the statement;`
  line `( ii ) an incorrect claim, apparent from any information in the statement;`
  line `( b ) the interest, if any, shall be computed on the basis of the sums collectible as computed in the`
  line statement;
  line `( c ) the fee, if any, shall be computed in accordance with the provisions of section 234E;`
  line `( d ) the sum payable by, or the amount of refund due to, the collector, shall be determined after`
  line `adjustment of the amount computed under clause ( b ) and clause ( c ) against any amount paid`
  line `under section 206C or section 234E and any amount paid otherwise by way of tax or interest or fee;`
  line `( e ) an intimation shall be prepared or generated and sent to the collector specifying the sum`
  line `determined to be payable by, or the amount of refund due to, him under clause ( d ); and`
  line `( f ) the amount of refund due to the collector in pursuance of the determination under clause ( d )`
  line `shall be granted to the collector:`
  line `Provided that no intimation under this sub-section shall be sent after the expiry of the period of`
  line `one year from the end of the financial year in which the statement is filed.`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this sub- section, “an incorrect claim apparent from any`
  line `information in the statement” shall mean a claim, on the basis of an entry, in the statement—`
  line `( i ) of an item,which is inconsistent with another entry of the same or some other item in such`
  line statement;
  line `1. Ins. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 91 (w.e.f. 1-6-2002).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 23 of 2004, s. 51 (w.e.f. 1-10-2004).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 20 of 2015, s. 55 (w.e.f. 1-6-2015).`
