  sourcePage 700
obj_root_law_sections_700_content:
  string
  line 700
  line `Explanation 2. —The expression “distributable income of any previous year” shall mean 1 [the total`
  line `income (as computed before making any deduction under Chapter VIA) assessed for that year] as reduced`
  line `by —`
  line `( i ) the amount of tax payable by the company in respect of 2 [its total income];`
  line `( ii ) the amount of any other tax levied under any law for the time being in force on the company`
  line `by the Government or by a local authority in excess of the amount, if any, which has been allowed in`
  line `computing the total income;`
  line `3 [( iii ) any sum with reference to which a deduction is allowable to the company under the`
  line `provisions of section 80G; and]`
  line `( iv ) in the case of a banking company, the amount actually transferred to a reserve fund under`
  line `section 17 of the Banking Companies Act, 1949 (10 of 1949),`
  line `and as increased by —`
  line `( a ) any profits and gains or receipts of the company, not included in its 4 [total income`
  line `(as computed before making any deduction under Chapter VIA)]; and`
  line `( b ) any amountattributable to any allowance made in computing the profits and gains of the`
  line `company for purposes of assessment, which the company has not taken into account in its profit and`
  line `loss account.`
  line `5 [ 236A. Relief to certain charitable institutions or funds in respect of certain dividends. — ( 1 )`
  line `6 [Where seventy-five per cent of the share capital of any company is throughout the previous year`
  line `beneficially held by an institution or fund established in India for a charitable purpose the income from`
  line `dividend whereof is exempt under section 11], credit shall be given to the institution or fund against the`
  line `tax, if any, payable by it, of a sum calculated in accordance with the provisions of sub-section ( 2 ), in`
  line `respect of its income from dividends (other than dividends on preference shares) declared or distributed`
  line `during the previous year relevant to any assessment year beginning on or after the 7 [1st day of April,`
  line `1966] 8 [by such company], and where the amount of credit so calculated exceeds the tax, if any, payable`
  line `by the said institution or fund, the excess shall be refunded.`
  line `9 [( 2 ) The amount to be given as credit under sub-section ( 1 ) shall be a sum which bears to the amount`
  line `of the tax payable by the company under the provisions of the annual Finance Act with reference to the`
  line `relevant amount of distributions of dividends by it the same proportion as the amount of the dividends`
  line `(other than dividends on preference shares) received by the institution or fund from the company bears to`
  line `the total amount of dividends (other than dividends on preference shares) declared or distributed by the`
  line `company during the previous year.`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 20 of 1967, s. 33 and the Third Schedule for “the total income assessed for that year” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1967).`
  line `2. Subs. by s. 33 and the Third Schedule, ibid., for “the said total income” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1968).`
  line `3. Subs. by s. 33 and the Third Schedule, ibid., for clause ( iii ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1968).`
  line `4. Subs by s. 33 and the Third Schedule, ibid., for “total income” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1968).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 31 of 1964, s. 11(w.e.f. 1-4-1964).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 11 of 1987, s. 74, for “In the case of an institution or fund referred to in clause ( iii ) of sub-section ( 2 ) of`
  line `section 104” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1988).`
  line `7. Subs. by Act 13 of 1966, s. 28, for “1st day of April, 1964” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1966).`
  line `8. Subs. by Act 11 of 1987, s. 74, for “by such a company as is referred to in the said clause” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1988).`
  line `9. Subs. by Act 13 of 1966, s. 28, for sub-section ( 2 ) (w.e.f. 1-4-1966).`
