  title `Page 719`
  content obj_root_law_sections_719_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_719_footnotes
  sourcePage 719
obj_root_law_sections_719_content:
  string
  line 719
  line `( iii ) where such person is a firm or association of persons or body of individuals, any individual`
  line `who was entitled to more than fifty per cent of the profits in such firm, association of persons or body`
  line `of individuals, at any time before the date of application before the Settlement Commission by such`
  line person;
  line `( iv ) where such person is a Hindu undivided family, the karta of that Hindu undivided family.]`
  line `245L. Proceedings before Settlement Commission to be judicial proceedings. — Any proceeding`
  line `under this Chapter before the Settlement Commission shall be deemed to be a judicial proceeding within`
  line `the meaning of sections 193 and 228, and for the purposes of section 196, of the Indian Penal Code (45 of`
  line `1860).`
  line `245M. Certain persons who have filed appeals to the Appellate Tribunal entitled to make`
  line `applications to the Settlement Commission. — [ Omitted by the Finance Act 11 of 1987 s. 67, ( w.e.f. 1-6-`
  line `1987). ]`
  line `1 [CHAPTER XIX-B`
  line `ADVANCE RULINGS`
  line `245N. Definitions. — In this Chapter, unless the context otherwise requires, —`
  line `2 [( a ) “advance ruling” means—`
  line `( i ) a determination by the Authority in relation to a transaction which has been undertaken or`
  line `is proposed to be undertaken by a non-resident applicant; or`
  line `( ii ) a determination by the Authority in relation to the 3 [tax liability of a non-resident arising`
  line `out of] a transaction which has been undertaken or is proposed to be undertaken by a resident`
  line `applicant with 4 [such non-resident]; 5 [or]`
  line `5 [( iia ) a determination by the Authority in relation to the tax liability of a resident applicant,`
  line `arising out of a transaction which has been undertaken or is proposed to be undertaken by such`
  line applicant,]
  line `and such determination shall include the determination of any question of law or of fact specified in`
  line `the application;`
  line `( iii ) a determination or decision by the Authority in respect of an issue relating to`
  line `computation of total income which is pending before any income-tax authority or the Appellate`
  line `Tribunal and such determination or decision shall include the determination or decision of any`
  line `question of law or of fact relating to such computation of total income specified in the`
  line application;
  line `1. Chapter XIX-B, consisting of sections 245N to 245V, inserted by Act 38 of 1993, s. 31 (w.e.f. 1-6-1993).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 10 of 2000, s. 63, for clauses ( a ) and ( b ) (w.e.f. 1-6-2000).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 92 (w.e.f. 1-6-2000).`
  line `4. Subs. by s. 92, ibid., for “a non - resident” (1 -6-2000).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 25 of 2014, s. 66 (w.e.f. 1-10-2014).`
