  line `and any matter arising out of or connected with such appeal and which is so pending shall stand`
  line `transferred to the Commissioner (Appeals) and the Commissioner (Appeals) may proceed with such`
  line `appeal or matter from the stage at which it was on that day.]`
  line `( 2 ) Notwithstanding anything contained in sub-section ( 1 ), any assessee aggrieved by any of the`
  line `following orders (whether made before or after the appointed day) may appeal to the Commissioner`
  line `(Appeals) 3 [before the 1st day of June, 2000] against such order —`
  line `( a ) 4 [an intimation or order specified in sub-section ( 1 ) where such intimation is sent or such`
  line `order] is made by the Deputy Commissioner in exercise of the powers or functions conferred on or`
  line `assigned to him under section 120 or section 124;`
  line `( b ) an order specified in clauses ( a ) to ( e ) (both inclusive) and clauses ( i ) to ( l ) (both inclusive) of`
  line `sub-section ( 1 ) 5 [or an order under section 104, as it stood immediately before the 1st day of April,`
  line `1988 in respect of any assessment for the assessment year commencing on the 1st day of April, 1987`
  line `or any earlier assessment year] made against the assessee, being a company;`
  line `( c ) an order of assessment made after the 30th day of September, 1984, on the basis of the`
  line `directions issued by the Deputy Commissioner under section 144A;`
  line `( d ) an order made by the Deputy Commissioner under section 154;`
  line `6 [( da ) an order of assessment made by an Assessing Officer under clause ( c ) of section 158BC, in`
  line `respect of search initiated under section 132 or books of account, other documents or any assets`
  line `requisitioned under section 132A, on or after the 1st day of January, 1997;`
  line `( db ) an order imposing a penalty under sub-section ( 2 ) of section 158BFA;]`
  line `1. The words, figures and letters “section 271C, section 271D, section 271E,”omitted by Act 12 of 1990, s. 41 (w.e.f. 1 -4-`
  line `1990). Earlier “Section 271E, Section 272A, Section 272AA or Section 272BB” were substituted for “Section 271E or`
  line `Section 272A” by Act 3 of 1989, s. 43 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `2. The words, brackets and figures “sub -section ( 1 ) of section 271,” omitted by Act 3 of 1989, s. 43 (w.e.f. 1 -4-1989).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 10 of 2000, s. 65 (w.e.f. 1-6-2000).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 32 of 1994, s. 46, for “an order specified in sub -section ( 1 ) where such order” (w.e.f. 1 -6-1994).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 3 of 1989, s. 43 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
