  line 728
  line `( d ) an order made under section 163 treating the assessee as the agent of a non-resident;`
  line `( e ) an order made under sub-section ( 2 ) or sub-section ( 3 ) of section 170;`
  line `( f ) an order made under section 171;`
  line `( g ) an order made under clause ( b ) of sub-section ( 1 ) or under sub-section ( 2 ) or sub-section ( 3 )`
  line `or sub-section ( 5 ) of section 185 in respect of an assessment for the assessment year commencing on`
  line `or before the 1st day of April, 1992;`
  line `( h ) an order cancelling the registration of a firm under sub-section ( 1 ) or under sub-section ( 2 )`
  line `of section 186 in respect of any assessment for the assessment year commencing on or before the 1st`
  line `day of April, 1992 or any earlier assessment year;`
  line `1 [( ha ) an order made under section 201;]`
  line `2 [( hb ) an order made under sub-section ( 6A ) of section 206C;]`
  line `( i ) an order made under section 237;`
  line `( j ) an order imposing a penalty under —`
  line `( A ) section 221; or`
  line `( B ) section271, section 271A, 2 [section 271AAA,] 3 [section 271AAB,] 4 [section`
  line `271F, section 271FB,] section 272AA or section 272BB;`
  line `( C ) section 272, section 272B or section 273, as they stood immediately before the 1st day of`
  line `April, 1989, in respect of an assessment for the assessment year commencing on the 1st day of`
  line `April, 1988, or any earlier assessment years;`
  line `5 [( ja ) an order of imposing or enhancing penalty under sub-section ( 1A ) of section 275;]`
  line `( k ) an order of assessment made by an Assessing Officer under clause ( c ) of section 158BC, in`
  line `respect of search initiated under section 132 or books of account, other documents or any assets`
  line `requisitioned under section 132A on or after the 1st day of January, 1997;`
  line `( l ) an order imposing a penalty under sub-section ( 2 ) of section 158BFA;`
  line `( m ) an order imposing a penalty under section 271B or section 271BB;`
  line `( n ) an order made by a Deputy Commissioner imposing a penalty under 6 [section 271C, section`
  line `271CA,] section 271D or section 271E;`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 10 of 2000, s. 66 (w.e.f. 1-6-2000).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 22 of 2007, s. 71 (w.e.f. 1-6-2007).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 94 (w.e.f. 1-7-2012).`
  line `4. Subs. by Act 18 of 2005, s. 57, for “Section 271F” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2006).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 29 of 2006, s. 17 (w.e.f. 13-7-2006).`
  line `6. Subs. by Act 21 of 2006, s. 51, for “section 271C” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2007).`
