obj_root_law_sections_734_content:
  string
  line 734
  line `253. Appeals to the Appellate Tribunal. — ( 1 ) Any assessee aggrieved by any of the following`
  line `orders may appeal to the Appellate Tribunal against such order —`
  line `( a ) an order passed by 1 [an 2 [Deputy Commissioner (Appeals)] 3 [before the 1st day of October,`
  line `1998] or, as the case may be, a Commissioner (Appeals)] under 4 *** 5 [section 154], 6 *** section`
  line `250, 7 [ section 270A ] 8 [, section 271, section 271A 9 [, section 271J] or section 272A]; or`
  line `10 [( b ) an order passed by an Assessing Officer under clause ( c ) of section 158BC, in respect of`
  line `search initiated under section 132 or books of account, other documents or any assets requisitioned`
  line `under section 132A, after the 30th day of June, 1995, but before the 1st day of January, 1997; or]`
  line `11 [( ba ) an order passed by an Assessing Officer under sub-section ( 1 ) of section 115VZC; or]`
  line `( c ) 12 [an order passed by a 13 [Principal Commissioner or Commissioner] 14 [under section 12AA or`
  line `under clause ( vi ) of sub-section ( 5 ) of section 80G] or under section 263] 7 [ or under section`
  line `270A ] 15 [or under section 271] 16 [or under section 272A] 5 [ 17 *** or an order passed by him`
  line `under section 154 amending his order under section 263] 18 [or an order passed by a 19 [Principal Chief`
  line `Commissioner or Chief Commissioner] or a 20 [Principal Director General or Director General] or`
  line `a 21 [ 22 [Principal Director or Director] under section 272A]; or]`
  line `23 [( d ) an order passed by an Assessing Officer under sub-section ( 3 ), of section 143 or 24 [section`
  line `147 or section 153A or section 153C] in pursuance of the directions of the Dispute Resolution Panel`
  line `or an order passed under section 154 in respect of such order;]`
  line `25 [( e ) an order passed by an Assessing Officer under sub-section ( 3 ) of section 143 or`
  line `section 147 or section 153A or section 153C with the approval of the 13 [Principal Commissioner`
  line `or Commissioner] as referred to in sub-section ( 12 ) of section 144BA or an order passed`
  line `under section 154 or section 155 in respect of such order;]`
  line `26 [( f ) an order passed by the prescribed authority under 27 [sub-clause ( iv ) or sub-clause ( v ) or]`
  line `sub-clause ( vi ) or sub-clause ( via ) of clause (23C) of section 10.]`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 29 of 1977, s. 39 and the Fifth Schedule, for “an Appellate Assistant Commissioner” (w.e.f. 10 -7-1978).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 4 of 1988, s. 2, for “Appellate Assistant Commissioner” (w.e.f. 1-4-1988).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 21 of 1998, s. 52 (w.e.f. 1-10-1998).`
  line `4. The words, brackets and figures “sub -section ( 2 ) of section 131” omitted by Act 3 of 1989, s. 46 (w.e.f. 1 -4-1989).`
  line `5. Ins. by Act 31 of 1964, s. 12 (w.e.f. 6-10-1964).`
  line `6. The word, figur es and letters “section 246A,” omitted by Act 3 of 1989, s. 95 (w.e.f. 1 -4-1989). Earlier the quoted`
  line `expression portion inserted byAct 4 of 1988, s. 126 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 95 (w.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
  line `8. Subs. by Act 41 of 1975, s. 60, for “or section 271” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1976).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 13 of 2018, s. 52 (w.e.f. 1-4-2018).`
  line `10. Subs. by Act 14 of 1997, s. 9, for clause ( b ) (w.e.f. 1-1-1997). Earlier the clause ( b ) was inserted by Act 22 of 1995,`
  line `s. 45 (w.e.f. 1-7-1995).`
  line `11. Ins. by Act 23 of 2004, s. 54 (w.e.f. 1-10-2004).`
  line `12. Subs. by Act 27 of 1999, s. 85, for “an order passed by a Commissioner under section 263” (w.e.f. 1 -6-1999).`
  line `13. Subs. by Act 25 of 2014, s. 4, for “Commissioner” (w.r.e.f. 1 -6-2013).`
  line `14. Subs. by Ac t 22 of 2007, s. 74, for “under section 12AA” (w.e.f. 1 -6-2007).`
  line `15. Ins. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 98 (w.e.f. 1-6-2002).`
  line `16. Ins. by Act 41 of 1975, s. 60 (w.e.f. 1-4-1976).`
  line `17. The words “or under section 285A” omitted by Act 26 of 1988, s. 54 (w.e.f. 1-4-1988).`
  line `18. Ins. by Act 3 of 1989, s. 46 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `19. Subs. by Act 25 of 2014, s. 4, for “Chief Commissioner” (w.r.e.f. 1 -6-2013).`
  line `20. Subs. by s. 4, ibid., for “Director General” (w.r.e.f. 1 -6-2013).`
  line `21. Subs. by Act 33 of 2009, s. 73, for “Director under section 272A.” (w.e.f. 1 -10-2009).`
  line `22. Subs. by Act 25 of 2014, s. 4, for “Director” (w.r.e.f. 1 -6-2013).`
  line `23. Ins. by Act 33 of 2009, s. 73 (w.e.f. 1-10-2009).`
  line `24. Subs. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 95, for “section 147” (w.e.f. 1 -10-2009).`
  line `25. Ins. by Act 17 of 2013, s. 57 (w.e.f. 1-4-2016). Earlier clause ( e ) was omitted by Act 17 of 2013, s. 57 (w.e.f. 1-4-2016)`
  line `which was inserted by Act 23 of 2012, s. 95 (w.e.f. 1-4-2013).`
  line `26. Ins. by Act 20 of 2015, s. 65 (w.e.f. 1-6-2015).`
  line `27. Ins. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 83 (w.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
