  content obj_root_law_sections_760_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_760_footnotes
  sourcePage 760
obj_root_law_sections_760_content:
  string
  line 760
  line `1 [ CHAPTER XXB`
  line `R EQUIREMENT AS TO 2 [ MODE OF ACCEPTANCE, PAYMENT OR REPAYMENT ]`
  line `IN CERTAIN CASES TO COUNTERACT EVASION OF TAX`
  line `3 [ 269SS.Mode of taking or accepting certain loans, deposits and specified sum. — No person shall`
  line `take or accept from any other person (herein referred to as the depositor), any loan or deposit or any`
  line `specified sum, otherwise than by an account payee cheque or account payee bank draft or use of`
  line `electronic clearing system through a bank account, if, —`
  line `( a ) the amount of such loan or deposit or specified sum or the aggregate amount of such loan,`
  line `deposit and specified sum; or`
  line `( b ) on the date of taking or accepting such loan or deposit or specified sum, any loan or deposit or`
  line `specified sum taken or accepted earlier by such person from the depositor is remaining unpaid`
  line `(whether repayment has fallen due or not), the amount or the aggregate amount remaining unpaid; or`
  line `( c ) the amount or the aggregate amount referred to in clause ( a ) together with the amount or the`
  line `aggregate amount referred to in clause ( b ),`
  line `is twenty thousand rupees or more:`
  line `Provided that the provisions of this section shall not apply to any loan or deposit or specified sum`
  line `taken or accepted from, or any loan or deposit or specified sum taken or accepted by, —`
  line `( a ) the Government;`
  line `( b ) any banking company, post office savings bank or co-operative bank;`
  line `( c ) any corporation established by a Central, State or Provincial Act;`
  line `( d ) any Government company as defined in clause ( 45 ) of section 2 of the Companies Act, 2013`
  line `(18 of 2013);`
  line `( e ) such other institution, association or body or class of institutions, associations or bodies which`
  line `the Central Government may, for reasons to be recorded in writing, notify in this behalf in the`
  line `Official Gazette:`
  line `Provided further that the provisions of this section shall not apply to any loan or deposit or`
  line `specified sum, where the person from whom the loan or deposit or specified sum is taken or accepted`
  line `and the person by whom the loan or deposit or specified sum is taken or accepted, are both having`
  line `agricultural income and neither of them has any income chargeable to tax under this Act.`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this section, —`
  line `( i ) “banking company” means a company to which the provisions of the Banking Regulation Act,`
  line `1949 (10 of 1949) applies and includes any bank or banking institution referred to in section 51 of`
  line `that Act;`
  line `( ii ) “co - operative bank” shall have the same meaning as assigned to it in Part V of the Banking`
  line `Regulation Act, 1949 (10 of 1949);`
  line `( iii ) “loan or deposit” means loan or deposit of money;`
  line `( iv ) “specified sum” means any sum of money receivable, whether as a dvance or otherwise, in`
  line `relation to transfer of an immovable property, whether or not the transfer takes place.]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 38 of 1981, s. 2 (w.e.f. 11-7-1981).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 21 of 1984, s. 28, for “MODE OF REPAYMENT” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1984).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 20 of 2015, s. 68, for section 269SS (w.e.f. 1-6-2015).`
obj_root_law_sections_760_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_761:
  kind page
