obj_root_law_sections_761_content:
  string
  line 761
  line `1 [ 269ST. Mode of undertaking transactions. — No person shall receive an amount of two lakh`
  line `rupees or more —`
  line `( a ) in aggregate from a person in a day; or`
  line `( b ) in respect of a single transaction; or`
  line `( c ) in respect of transactions relating to one event or occasion from a person,`
  line `otherwise than by an account payee cheque or an account payee bank draft or use of electronic clearing`
  line `system through a bank account:`
  line `Provided that the provisions of this section shall not apply to —`
  line `( i ) any receipt by —`
  line `( a ) Government;`
  line `( b ) any banking company, post office savings bank or co-operative bank;`
  line `( ii ) transactions of the nature referred to in section 269SS;`
  line `( iii ) such other persons or class of persons or receipts, which the Central Government may, by`
  line `notification in the Official Gazette, specify.`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this section, —`
  line `( a ) “banking company” shall have the same meaning as assigned to it in clause ( i ) of the`
  line `Explanation to section 269SS;`
  line `( b ) “co - operative bank” shall have the same meaning as assigned to it in clause ( ii ) of the`
  line `Explanation to section 269SS.]`
  line `2 [ 269T.Mode of repayment of certain loans or deposits. — No branch of a banking company or a`
  line `co-operative bank and no other company or co-operative society and no firm or other person shall repay`
  line `any loan or deposit made with it 3 [or any specified advance received by it] otherwise than by an account`
  line `payee cheque or account payee bank draft drawn in the name of the person who has made the loan or`
  line `deposit 3 [or paid the specified advance,] 4 [or by use of electronic clearing system through a bank account]`
  line `if —`
  line `( a ) the amount of the loan or deposit 3 [or specified advance] together with the interest, if any,`
  line `payable thereon, or`
  line `( b ) the aggregate amount of the loans or deposits held by such person with the branch of the`
  line `banking company or co-operative bank or, as the case may be, the other company or co-operative`
  line `society or the firm, or other person either in his own name or jointly with any other person on the date`
  line `of such repayment together with the interest, if any, payable on such loans or deposits, 3 [or]`
  line `3 [( c ) the aggregate amount of the specified advances received by such person either in his own`
  line `name or jointly with any other person on the date of such repayment together with the interest, if any,`
  line `payable on such specified advances,]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 84 (w.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 99, for section 269T (w.e.f. 1-6-2002).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 20 of 2015, s. 69 (w.e.f. 1-6-2015).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 25 of 2014, s. 69 (w.e.f. 1-4-2015).`
obj_root_law_sections_761_footnotes:
