  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_777_footnotes
  sourcePage 777
obj_root_law_sections_777_content:
  string
  line 777
  line `B = amount of tax that would have been chargeable had the total income assessed as per the`
  line `general provisions been reduced by the amount of income in respect of which particulars have been`
  line `concealed or inaccurate particulars have been furnished;`
  line `C = amount of tax on the total income assessed as per the provisions contained in section`
  line `115JB or section 115JC;`
  line `D = amount of tax that would have been chargeable had the total income assessed as per the`
  line `provisions contained in section 115JB or section 115JC been reduced by the amount of income in`
  line `respect of which particulars have been concealed or inaccurate particulars have been furnished:`
  line `Provided that where the amount of income in respect of which particulars have been concealed or`
  line `inaccurate particulars have been furnished on any issue is considered both under the provisions`
  line `contained in section 115JB or section 115JC and under general provisions, such amount shall not be`
  line `reduced from total income assessed while determining the amount under item D:`
  line `Provided further that in a case where the provisions contained in section 115JB or section`
  line `115JC are not applicable, the item ( C - D ) in the formula shall be ignored;`
  line `( b ) where in any case the amount of income in respect of which particulars have been concealed`
  line `or inaccurate particulars have been furnished has the effect of reducing the loss declared in the return`
  line `or converting that loss into income, the amount of tax sought to be evaded shall be determined in`
  line `accordance with the formula specified in clause ( a ) with the modification that the amount to be`
  line `determined for item ( A - B ) in that formula shall be the amount of tax that would have been`
  line `chargeable on the income in respect of which particulars have been concealed or inaccurate`
  line `particulars have been furnished had such income been the total income;`
  line `( c ) where in any case to which Explanation 3 applies, the amount of tax sought to be evaded shall`
  line `be the tax on the total income assessed as reduced by the amount of advance tax, tax deducted at`
  line `source, tax collected at source and self-assessment tax paid before the issue of notice under section`
  line 148.]]
  line `1 [ Explanation 5. — Where in the course of a 2 [search initiated under section 132 before the 1st day of`
  line `June, 2007], the assessee is found to be the owner of any money, bullion, jewellery or other valuable`
  line `article or thing (hereafter in this Explanation referred to as assets) and the assessee claims that such assets`
  line `have been acquired by him by utilising (wholly or in part) his income, —`
  line `( a ) for any previous year which has ended before the date of the search, but the return of income`
  line `for such year has not been furnished before the said date or, where such return has been furnished`
  line `before the said date, such income has not been declared therein; or`
  line `( b ) for any previous year which is to end on or after the date of the search,`
  line `then, notwithstanding that such income is declared by him in any return of income furnished on or after`
  line `the date of the search, he shall, for the purposes of imposition of a penalty under clause ( c ) of sub-section`
  line `( 1 ) of this section, be deemed to have concealed the particulars of his income or furnished inaccurate`
  line `particulars of such income, 3 [unless, —`
  line `( 1 ) such income is, or the transactions resulting in such income are recorded, —`
  line `( i ) in a case falling under clause ( a ), before the date of the search; and`
  line `( ii ) in a case falling under clause ( b ), on or before such date,`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 67 of 1984, s. 48 (w.e.f. 1-10-1984).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 22 of 2007, s.76, for “search under section 132” (w.e.f. 1 -6-2007).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 46 of 1986, s. 19, for certain words (w.e.f. 10-9-1986).`
obj_root_law_sections_777_footnotes:
  string
  line
