obj_root_law_sections_778_content:
  string
  line 778
  line `in the books of account, if any, maintained by him for any source of income or such income is`
  line `otherwise disclosed to the 1 [ 2 [Principal Chief Commissioner or Chief Commissioner] or 3 [Principal`
  line `Commissioner or Commissioner] before the said date; or]`
  line `( 2 ) he, in the course of the search, makes a statement under sub-section ( 4 ) of section 132 that any`
  line `money, bullion, jewellery or other valuable article or thing found in his possession or under his control,`
  line `has been acquired out of his income which has not been disclosed so far in his return of income to be`
  line `furnished before the expiry of time specified in 4 *** sub-section ( 1 ) of section 139, and also specifies in`
  line `the statement the manner in which such income has been derived and pays the tax, together with interest,`
  line `if any, in respect of such income.]`
  line `5 [ Explanation 5A. — Where, in the course of a search initiated under section 132 on or after the 1st day`
  line `of June, 2007, the assessee is found to be the owner of —`
  line `( i ) any money, bullion, jewellery or other valuable article or thing (hereafter in`
  line `this Explanation referred to as assets) and the assessee claims that such assets have been acquired by`
  line `him by utilising (wholly or in part) his income for any previous year; or`
  line `( ii ) any income based on any entry in any books of account or other documents or transactions`
  line `and he claims that such entry in the books of account or other documents or transactions represents`
  line `his income (wholly or in part) for any previous year,`
  line `which has ended before the date of search and, —`
  line `( a ) where the return of income for such previous year has been furnished before the said date but`
  line `such income has not been declared therein; or`
  line `( b ) the due date for filing the return of income for such previous year has expired but the assessee`
  line `has not filed the return,`
  line `then, notwithstanding that such income is declared by him in any return of income furnished on or after`
  line `the date of search, he shall, for the purposes of imposition of a penalty under clause ( c ) of sub-section ( 1 )`
  line `of this section, be deemed to have concealed the particulars of his income or furnished inaccurate`
  line `particulars of such income.]`
  line `6 [ Explanation 6. — Where any adjustment is made in the income or loss declared in the return under`
  line `the proviso to clause ( a ) of sub-section ( 1 ) of section 143 and additional tax charged under that section,`
  line `the provisions of this sub-section shall not apply in relation to the adjustment so made.]`
  line `7 [ Explanation 7. — Where in the case of an assessee who has entered into an 8 [international transaction`
  line `or specified domestic transaction] defined in section 92B, any amount is added or disallowed in`
  line `computing the total income under sub-section ( 4 ) of section 92C, then, the amount so added or disallowed`
  line `shall, for the purposes of clause ( c ) of this sub-section, be deemed to represent the income in respect of`
  line `which particulars have been concealed or inaccurate particulars have been furnished, unless the assessee`
  line `proves to the satisfaction of the Assessing Officer or the Commissioner (Appeals) 9 [or the 3 [Principal`
  line `Commissioner or Commissioner]] that the price charged or paid in such transaction was computed in`
  line `accordance with the provisions contained in section 92C and in the manner prescribed under that section,`
  line `in good faith and with due diligence.]`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 4 of 1988, s. 2, for “Commissioner” (w.e.f. 1 -4-1988).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 25 of 2014, s. 4, for “Chief Commissioner” (w.r.e.f. 1 -6-2013).`
  line `3. Subs. by s. 4, ibid., for “Commissioner” (w.r.e.f. 1 -6-2013).`
  line `4. The words, brackets and letters “clause ( a ) or clause ( b ) of” omitted by Act 3 of 1989, s. 50 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 33 of 2009, s. 74, for “ Explanation 5A ” (w.r.e.f. 1-6-2007). Earlier it was inserted by Act 22 of 2007, s. 76`
  line `(w.e.f. 1-6-2007 ).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 3 of 1989, s. 50 (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `7. Ins. by Act 14 of 2001, s. 86 (w.e.f. 1-4-2002).`
  line `8. Subs. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 97, for the words “International transaction” (w.e.f. 1 -4-2013).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 20 of 2002, s. 101 (w.e.f. 1-6-2002).`
