obj_root_law_sections_781_content:
  string
  line 781
  line `( 2 ) Nothing contained in sub-section ( 1 ) shall apply if the assessee, —`
  line `( i ) in the course of the search, in a statement under sub-section ( 4 ) of section 132, admits the`
  line `undisclosed income and specifies the manner in which such income has been derived;`
  line `( ii ) substantiates the manner in which the undisclosed income was derived; and`
  line `( iii ) pays the tax, together with interest, if any, in respect of the undisclosed income.`
  line `( 3 ) No penalty under the provisions of clause ( c ) of sub-section ( 1 ) of section 271 shall be imposed`
  line `upon the assessee in respect of the undisclosed income referred to in sub-section ( 1 ).`
  line `( 4 ) The provisions of sections 274 and 275 shall, so far as may be, apply in relation to the penalty`
  line `referred to in this section.`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this section, —`
  line `( a ) “undisclosed income” means—`
  line `( i ) any income of the specified previous year represented, either wholly or partly, by any`
  line `money, bullion, jewellery or other valuable article or thing or any entry in the books of account or`
  line `other documents or transactions found in the course of a search under section 132, which has —`
  line `( A ) not been recorded on or before the date of search in the books of account or other`
  line `documents maintained in the normal course relating to such previous year; or`
  line `( B ) otherwise not been disclosed to the 1 [Principal Chief Commissioner or Chief`
  line `Commissioner] or 2 [Principal Commissioner or Commissioner] before the date of search; or`
  line `( ii ) any income of the specified previous year represented, either wholly or partly, by any`
  line `entry in respect of an expense recorded in the books of account or other documents maintained in`
  line `the normal course relating to the specified previous year which is found to be false and would not`
  line `have been found to be so had the search not been conducted;`
  line `( b ) “specified previous year” means the previous year—`
  line `( i ) which has ended before the date of search, but the date of filing the return of income under`
  line `sub-section ( 1 ) of section 139 for such year has not expired before the date of search and the`
  line `assessee has not furnished the return of income for the previous year before the said date; or`
  line `( ii ) in which search was conducted.]`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 25 of 2014, s. 4, for “Chief Commissioner” (w.e.f. 1 -6-2013).`
  line `2. Subs. by s. 4, ibid., for “Commissioner” (w.e.f. 1 -6-2013).`
