obj_root_law_sections_783_content:
  string
  line 783
  line `( iii ) on or before the specified date —`
  line `( A ) pays the tax, together with interest, if any, in respect of the undisclosed income; and`
  line `( B ) furnishes the return of income for the specified previous year declaring such`
  line `undisclosed income therein;`
  line `( b ) a sum computed at the rate of sixty per cent of the undisclosed income of the specified`
  line `previous year, if it is not covered under the provisions of clause ( a ).]`
  line `( 2 ) No penalty under the provisions of 1 [section 270A or] clause ( c ) of sub-section ( 1 ) of section`
  line `271 shall be imposed upon the assessee in respect of the undisclosed income referred to in sub-section`
  line `( 1 ) 2 [ or sub-section ( 1A )].`
  line `( 3 ) The provisions of sections 274 and 275 shall, as far as may be, apply in relation to the penalty`
  line `referred to in this section.`
  line `Explanation. — For the purposes of this section, —`
  line `( a ) “specified date” means the due date of furnishing of return of income under sub -section ( 1 )`
  line `of section 139 or the date on which the period specified in the notice issued under section 153A for`
  line `furnishing of return of income expires, as the case may be;`
  line `( b ) “specified previous year” means the previous year—`
  line `( i ) which has ended before the date of search, but the date of furnishing the return of income`
  line `under sub-section ( 1 ) of section 139 for such year has not expired before the date of search and`
  line `the assessee has not furnished the return of income for the previous year before the date of search;`
  line or
  line `( ii ) in which search was conducted;`
  line `( c ) “undisclosed income” means—`
  line `( i ) any income of the specified previous year represented, either wholly or partly, by any`
  line `money, bullion, jewellery or other valuable article or thing or any entry in the books of account or`
  line `other documents or transactions found in the course of a search under section 132, which has —`
  line `( A ) not been recorded on or before the date of search in the books of account or other`
  line `documents maintained in the normal course relating to such previous year; or`
  line `( B ) otherwise not been disclosed to the 3 [Principal Chief Commissioner or Chief`
  line `Commissioner] or 4 [Principal Commissioner or Commissioner] before the date of search; or`
  line `( ii ) any income of the specified previous year represented, either wholly or partly, by any`
  line `entry in respect of an expense recorded in the books of account or other documents maintained in`
  line `the normal course relating to the specified previous year which is found to be false and would not`
  line `have been found to be so had the search not been conducted.]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 103 (w.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 48 of 2016, s. 3 (w.e.f. 15-12-2016).`
  line `3. Subs. by Act 25 of 2014, s. 4, for “Chief Commissioner” (w.r.e.f. 1 -6-2013).`
  line `4. Subs. by s. 4, ibid., for “Commissioner” (w.r.e.f. 1 -6-2013).`
