obj_root_law_sections_785_content:
  string
  line 785
  line `1 [ 271C. Penalty for failure to deduct tax at source. — 2 [ 3 [( 1 )] If any person fails to —`
  line `( a ) deduct the whole or any part of the tax as required by or under the provisions of Chapter`
  line `XVII-B; or`
  line `( b ) pay the whole or any part of the tax as required by or under —`
  line `( i ) sub-section ( 2 ) of section 115-O; or`
  line `( ii ) the second proviso to section 194B,`
  line `then, such person shall be liable to pay, by way of penalty, a sum equal to the amount of tax which such`
  line `person failed to deduct or pay as aforesaid.]`
  line `4 [( 2 ) Any penalty imposable under sub-section ( 1 ) shall be imposed by the 5 [Joint Commissioner].]`
  line `6 [ 271CA. Penalty for failure to collect tax at source. — ( 1 ) If any person fails to collect the whole`
  line `or any part of the tax as required by or under the provisions of Chapter XVII-BB, then, such person shall`
  line `be liable to pay, by way of penalty, a sum equal to the amount of tax which such person failed to collect`
  line `as aforesaid.`
  line `( 2 ) Any penalty imposable under sub-section ( 1 ) shall be imposed by the Joint Commissioner.]`
  line `271D. Penalty for failure to comply with the provisions of section 269SS. — 7 [( 1 )] If a person takes`
  line `or accepts any loan or deposit 8 [or specified sum] in contravention of the provisions of section 269SS, he`
  line `shall be liable to pay, by way of penalty, a sum equal to the amount of the loan or deposit 8 [or specified`
  line `sum] so taken or accepted.`
  line `9 [( 2 ) Any penalty imposable under sub-section ( 1 ) shall be imposed by the 5 [Joint Commissioner].]`
  line `10 [271DA. Penalty for failure to comply with provisions of section 269ST. — ( 1 ) If a person`
  line `receives any sum in contravention of the provisions of section 269ST, he shall be liable to pay, by way of`
  line `penalty, a sum equal to the amount of such receipt:`
  line `Provided that no penalty shall be imposable if such person proves that there were good and sufficient`
  line `reasons for the contravention.`
  line `( 2 ) Any penalty imposable under sub-section ( 1 ) shall be imposed by the Joint Commissioner. ]`
  line `271E. Penalty for failure to comply with the provisions of section 269T. — 11 [( 1 )] If a person`
  line `repays any 12 [loan or deposit] 13 [or specified advance] referred to in section 269T otherwise than in`
  line `accordance with the provisions of that section, he shall be liable to pay, by way of penalty, a sum equal to`
  line `the amount of the 12 [loan or deposit] 13 [or specified advance] so repaid.]`
  line `14 [( 2 ) Any penalty imposable under sub-section ( 1 ) shall be imposed by the 5 [Joint Commissioner].]`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 4 of 1988, s. 108, (w.e.f. 1-4-1989).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 26 of 1997, s. 53, for sub-section ( 1 ), (w.e.f. 1-6-1997). Earlier it was amended by Act 12 of 1990, s. 44`
  line `(w.e.f. 1-4-1990).`
  line `3. Section 271C renumbered as sub-section ( 1 ) thereof by Act 12 of 1990, s. 44 (w.e.f. 1-4-1990).`
  line `4. Ins. by s. 44, ibid (w.e.f. 1-4-1990).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 21 of 1998, s. 3, for “Deputy Commissioner” (w.e.f. 1 -10-1998).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 21 of 2006, s. 52 (w.e.f. 1-4-2007).`
  line `7. Section 271D renumbered as sub-section ( 1 ) thereof by Act 12 of 1990, s. 45 (w.e.f. 1-4-1990).`
  line `8. Ins. by Act 20 of 2015, s. 71 (w.e.f. 1-6-2015).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 12 of 1990, s. 45 (w.e.f. 1-4-1990).`
  line `10. Ins. by Act 7 of 2017, s. 85 (w.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
  line `11. Section 271E renumbered as sub-section ( 1 ) thereof by Act 12 of 1990, s. 46 (w.e.f. 1-4-1990).`
  line `12. Subs. by Act 32 of 2003, s. 95, for “Deposit” (w.e.f. 1 -6-2003).`
  line `13. Ins. by Act 20 of 2015, s. 72 (w.e.f. 1-6-2015).`
  line `14. Ins. by 12 of 1990, s. 46 (w.e.f. 1-4-1990).`
