obj_root_law_sections_790_content:
  string
  line 790
  line `he shall pay, by way of penalty, a sum 1 [of one hundred rupees] for every day during which the failure`
  line `continues:`
  line `2 [Provided that the amount of penalty for failures in relation to 3 [a declaration mentioned in section`
  line `197A, a certificate as required by section 203 and] returns under sections 206 and 206C`
  line `4 [and 5 [statements under sub-section (2A) or sub-section (3) of section 200 or the proviso to sub-section`
  line `( 3 ) or under sub-section ( 3A ) of section 206C]] shall not exceed the amount of tax deductible or`
  line `collectible, as the case may be:]`
  line `6 [Provided further that no penalty shall be levied under this section for the failure referred to in clause`
  line `( k ), if such failure relates to a statement referred to in sub-section ( 3 ) of section 200 or the proviso to sub-`
  line `section ( 3 ) of section 206C which is to be delivered or caused to be delivered for tax deducted at source`
  line `or tax collected at source, as the case may be, on or after the 1st day of July, 2012.]`
  line `( 3 ) Any penalty imposable under sub-section ( 1 ) or sub-section ( 2 ) shall be imposed —`
  line `( a ) in a case where the contravention, failure or default in respect of which such penalty is`
  line `imposable occurs in the course of any proceeding before an income-tax authority not lower in rank`
  line `than a 7 [Joint Director] or a 8 [Joint Commissioner], by such income-tax authority;`
  line `9 [( aa )in a case falling under clause ( d ) of sub-section ( 1 ), by the income-tax authority who had`
  line `issued the notice or direction referred to therein;]`
  line `( b ) in a case falling under clause ( f ) of sub-section ( 2 ), by the 10 [Principal Chief Commissioner or`
  line `Chief Commissioner] or 11 [Principal Commissioner or Commissioner]; and`
  line `( c ) in any other case, by the 7 [Joint Director] or the 8 [Joint Commissioner].`
  line `( 4 ) No order under this section shall be passed by any income-tax authority referred to in sub-section`
  line `( 3 ) unless the person on whom the penalty is proposed to be imposed is given an opportunity of being`
  line `heard in the matter by such authority.`
  line `Explanation. —In this section, “income - tax authority” includes a 12 [Principal Director General or`
  line `Director General], 13 [Principal Director or Director], 7 [Joint Director] and an 14 [Assistant Director or`
  line `Deputy Director] while exercising the powers vested in a court under the Code of Civil Procedure, 1908`
  line `(5 of 1908), when trying a suit in respect of the matters specified in sub-section ( 1 ) of section 131.]`
  line `15 [272AA. Penalty for failure to comply with the provisions of section 133B. — ( 1 ) If a person`
  line `16 *** fails to comply with the provisions of section 133B, he shall, on an order passed by the 8 [Joint`
  line `Commissioner], 14 [Assistant Director or Deputy Director] or the 17 [Assessing Officer], as the case may be,`
  line `pay, by way of penalty, a sum which may extend to one thousand rupees.`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 27 of 1999, s. 88, for “which shall not be less than hundred rupees, but which may extend to two hundred`
  line `rupees,” (w.e.f. 1 -6-1999).`
  line `2. Ins. by Act 49 of 1991, s. 68 (w.e.f. 1-10-1991).`
  line `3. Ins. by Act 21 of 1998, s. 62 (w.e.f. 1-4-1999).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 21 of 2006, s. 53 (w.e.f. 1-6-2006).`
  line `5. Subs. by Act 20 of 2015, s. 76, for “statement under sub -section ( 3 ) of section 200 or the proviso to sub-section ( 3 ) of`
  line `section 206C” (w.e.f. 1 -6-2015).`
  line `6. Ins. by Act 23 of 2012, s. 104 (w.e.f. 1-7-2012).`
  line `7. Subs. by Act 21 of 1998, s. 3, for “Deputy Director” (w.e.f. 1 -10-1998).`
  line `8. Subs. by s. 3, for ibid., “Deputy Commissioner” (w.e.f. 1 -10-1998).`
  line `9. Ins. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 105 (w.e.f. 1-4-2017).`
  line `10. Subs. by Act 25 of 2014, s. 4, for “Chief Commissioner” (w.r.e.f. 1 -6-2013).`
  line `11. Subs. by s. 4, ibid., for “Commissioner” (w.r.e.f. 1 -6-2013).`
