  line `( 21 ) Seamless tubes.`
  line `( 22 ) Gears.`
  line `( 23 ) Ball, roller and tapered bearings.`
  line `( 24 ) Component parts of the articles mentioned in item Nos. (4), (5), (7) and (9), that is to say, such`
  line `parts as are essential for the working of the machinery referred to in the items aforesaid and have been`
  line `given for that purpose some special shape or quality which would not be essential for their use for any`
  line `other purpose and are in complete finished form and ready for fitment.`
  line `( 25 ) Cotton seed oil.`
  line `1 [( 26 ) Tea.`
  line `( 27 ) Printing machinery.]`
  line `2 [( 28 ) Processed seeds.`
