  line `( 30 ) Processed (including frozen) fish and fish products.`
  line `( 31 ) Vegetable oils and oil-cakes manufactured by the solvent extraction process from seeds other than`
  line `cotton seed.]`
  line `3 [( 32 ) Textiles (including those dyed, printed or otherwise processed) made wholly or mainly of cotton,`
  line `including cotton yarn, hosiery and rope.`
