  line 870
  line `1 [THE EIGHTH SCHEDULE`
  line `[ See section 80-IA(2)( iv )( b )]`
  line `L IST OF INDUSTRIALLY BACKWARD STATES AND UNION TERRITORIES`
  line `( 1 ) Arunachal Pradesh`
  line `( 2 ) Assam`
  line `( 3 ) Goa`
  line `( 4 ) Himachal Pradesh`
  line `( 5 ) Jammu and Kashmir`
  line `( 6 ) Manipur`
  line `( 7 ) Meghalaya`
  line `( 8 ) Mizoram`
  line `( 9 ) Nagaland`
  line `( 10 ) Sikkim`
  line `( 11 ) Tripura`
  line `( 12 ) Andaman and Nicobar Islands`
  line `( 13 ) Dadra and Nagar Haveli`
  line `( 14 ) Daman and Diu`
  line `( 15 ) Lakshadweep`
  line `( 16 ) Pondicherry.]`
  line ________
  line `[THE NINTH SCHEDULE]. Omitted by the Taxation Laws (Amendment & Miscellaneous`
  line `Provisions) Act, 1986 (46 of 1986), s. 31( w.e.f. 1-4-1988). Original Ninth Schedule was inserted`
  line `by the Direct Taxes (Amendment) Act, 1974 (26 of 1974), s. 16 ( w.e.f. 1-4-1975).`
  line _________
  line `[THE TENTH SCHEDULE]. Omitted by the Finance Act, 1999 (27 of 1999), s. 89 ( w.e.f. 1-4-200 0 ).`
  line `1. Ins. by Act 38 of 1993, s. 37 (w.e.f. 1-4-1994). Prior to inseted by Act 26 of 1974, s. 14 (w.e.f. 1-4-1974). Later on`
  line `amended by Act 66 of 1976, s. 24 (w.e.f. 1-4-1976). And omitted by Act 46 of 1986, s. 30 (w.e.f. 1-4-1984).`
