  line `paper or paperboard, impregnated,`
  line `coated or covered with plastics`
  line `(including thermoset resins or`
  line `mixtures thereof or chemical`
  line `formulations containing melamine,`
  line `phenol, urea formaldehyde with or`
  line `without curing agents or catalysts),`
  line `compressed together in one or more`
  line `operations; Products known`
  line `commercially as decorative`
  line laminates.
