  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_878_footnotes
  sourcePage 878
obj_root_law_sections_878_content:
  string
  line 878
  line `11. Processing of essential oils and fragrances industry.`
  line `12. Processing and raising of plantation crops — tea, rubber, coffee, coconuts, etc.`
  line `13. Gas based Intermediate Products Industry manufacturing or producing —`
  line `( i ) Gas exploration and production;`
  line `( ii ) Gas distribution and bottling;`
  line `( iii ) Power generation;`
  line `( iv ) Plastics;`
  line `( v ) Yarn raw materials;`
  line `( vi ) Fertilizers;`
  line `( vii ) Methanol;`
  line `( viii ) Formaldehyde and FR resin melamine and MF resin;`
  line `( ix ) Methylamine, Hexamethylenetetramine, Ammonium bi-carbonate;`
  line `( x ) Nitric Acid and Ammonium Nitrate;`
  line `( xi ) Carbon black;`
  line `( xii ) Polymer chips.`
  line `14. Agro forestry based industry.`
  line `15. Horticulture industry.`
  line `16. Mineral based industry.`
  line `17. Floriculture industry.`
  line `18. Agro-based industry.`
  line `PART B`
  line `F OR THE STATE OF SIKKIM`
  line `S. No. Activity or article or thing or operation`
  line `1. Eco - Tourism including Hotels, Resorts, Spa, Amusement Parks and Ropeways.`
  line `2. Handicrafts and handlooms.`
  line `3. Wool and silk reeling, weaving and processing, printing, etc.`
  line `4. Floriculture.`
  line `5. Precision Engineering including watch making.`
  line `6. Electronics including computronics hardware and software and Information Technology (IT) related`
  line industries.
  line `7. Food processing including Agro - based industries. Processing, preservation a nd packaging of fruits and`
  line `vegetables (excluding conventional grinding/extraction units).`
  line `8. Medicinal and aromatic Herbs — Plantation and Processing.`
  line `9. Raising and processing of plantation crops, i.e., tea, oranges and cardamom.`
  line `10. Mineral based industry.`
  line `11. Pharma products.`
  line `12. Honey.`
  line `13. Biotechnology.`
